Njam fene tamb\u233?n gh\u233?kfam f\u233?m n\u233?m\u233?inda yaufiyot, tutor a t\u233?ngwayang. Yau minde m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m feyot \u225?mb fifikafe s\u225?i t\u233?nfang, w\u233?nde minde m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m feyot m\u233?inyotio fifi s\u225?i yiyota f\u233?s\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
A njam fene tamb\u233?n ng\u225?ngayam n\u233?m\u233?inda yaufiot, t\u233?n\u233?f a t\u233?ngwai. Yau minde yaufi y\u233?m feyot \u225?mb fifi kafe s\u225?i t\u233?nfang, w\u233?nde minde yaufi y\u233?m feyot fene m\u233?inyotio fifi s\u225?i yiyota f\u233?s\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum korayau amaf watemb\u233?ghm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
"Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k w\u233?i noraye nden\u233?, 'Emon korong\u233? y\u225?njo amaf so taramang\u233? y\u225? watemb\u233?gh f\u233?r\u233?n.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon f\u233?fe ewaufrotan nden\u233? emon yau so m\u233? amaf tatembang\u233?, t\u225?fandro amaf njam yam yafrota \u225?mb \u225?rom, y\u233?mon njam yafrota, y\u233?mon y\u233?m\u233?inde m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? so kamndang\u233? amafanyo wan\u233?gh \u225?r. A emon njam kawerang\u233? watemb\u233?gh amaf yaufi kor t\u233?f\u233? yafrote amafanyo wan\u233?ghan.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum korayau sotaf\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar sim\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
"F\u233?m w\u233?i t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd nden\u233? korayaw\u233?t \u225?rfefaf t\u225?nd\u225?i, 'Yau t\u225?f fenjo sotaf\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar si er\u225?fna, w\u233?nde ew\u233?reta fenjo sotaf\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar si f\u233?mo \u225?rk\u233? noraye Yurafaf.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?fe, 'Yau sotaf\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar si norayati, njafarm\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? y\u233?m; {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
o yau m\u233?naye mband marate, m\u233?nam\u233?n Y\u225?ne kafkaf k\u233?t\u233? nenat, o yau Jerusalem, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Ndimbal Warsagh \u225?roene tesen. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
A yau sotaf\u233? uny\u233?ghofnar si noraya fenjo s\u233?nkoe, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mo yau so tengo \u225?mbiro s\u233?f kwayaghat o kw\u233?fitat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
\u193?fr\u225?taye m\u233? koraya, 'F\u233?t\u233?' o 'Yau,' n\u233?m\u233? si koraya y\u233?n\u233? farun y\u233?m yaufi \u225?roeta.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum korayau fai wangoghm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
"F\u233?m t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?retati nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k noraye, 'Emon njam tutorng\u233? fene gh\u233?k\u233?f, f\u233?mo w\u233?i so tutor y\u225?ne gh\u233?k\u233?fro. Emon njam t\u233?sufang\u233? fene s\u233?n, f\u233?mo w\u233?i so t\u233?suf y\u225?ne s\u233?nro.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?fe, 'Yau y\u233?kena yaufi \u225?r. \u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom njam k\u233?nsmang\u233? tamb\u233?n f\u233?tta, witm\u233? f\u233?t tawengo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Njam \u225?mb \u225?rom ng\u233?nmanang\u233? mogh\u233?t m\u233?nam\u233?n fene s\u225?l\u225?mem\u233?n a yanang, m\u233? t\u233?ngwaram fene sod\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
\u193?mb \u225?rom njam m\u225?m\u233?gh\u233?raye n\u233?mafareta rokar r\u233?sagh\u233?t \u225?mbiro kilomit\u233? \u225?ligh\u233?t, m\u233? t\u233?ngwasamngo s\u243?mbio kilomitat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Taram y\u225? emon f\u233?m k\u233?mamnendang\u233?, a yau sem tawengo y\u225?yot emon watm\u233? rokar r\u233?sagh\u233?t t\u225?fngong\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yuweta fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
"F\u233?m t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd nden\u233?, 'Euwetati f\u233?fenjo kaka \u225?r, m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat efandati m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?fe nden\u233?, euwetati f\u233?fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r, a Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati y\u233?feyot emofem ewas\u233?rmbotat f\u233?m, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m so k\u225?y\u225?tongi f\u233?fene njafarm\u233?n Afane ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, y\u233?mon y\u233?m\u233?inde efogh atremngogh\u233?t yaufi \u225?r\u233?t a mer \u225?r\u233?t, a y\u233?nmafarete nu mbark\u225?nd \u225?r\u233?t a mbark\u225?ndofnar \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
F\u233?mofem njam euwetati f\u225?ro emofem euwetat f\u233?m, n\u233?m\u233? fai f\u233?mofem so tawanangi y\u233?n\u233? yamm\u233?n? Yau. T\u233?u mani kaf\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m t\u250?m\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? ewafrotat! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
F\u233?mofem njam esnetati f\u233?fenjo fut\u225?r\u233?fro, f\u233?fene yamam ewaindat \u225?rfene yam? Yau. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nofnar \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? yam ewafrotat! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
F\u233?m aem m\u233? f\u233?w\u233?nf\u233?w\u233?nofnar nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?fene njafarm\u233?n Af\u233? nder\u233? f\u233?w\u233?nf\u233?w\u233?nofnar y\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 6
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum korayau ram\u233?gh yamm\u233?n yauyau \u225?rfeyot
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
"Kor nawarawenati yau f\u233?mofem ewafrotati meryam \u225?r s\u225?fan m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mofem so efandat. F\u233?mofem njam ewafrotati, f\u233?fene fai yau so em f\u233?fene njafarm\u233?n Afata.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
"Njam f\u233?mofem tawaramangi \u225?ronjagh \u225?r\u233?t, yau t\u225?f marataye keye nden\u233? \u225?r efe em faruta mer w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau, nufrotat \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngon a endm\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?r\u233?m so eut\u233?mndat. Y\u233?ndon efalo emndetan, y\u233?mofem t\u233? ewanangi y\u233?fenjo fai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
W\u233?nde njam f\u233?mofem tawaramangi yauyau \u225?r\u233?t, yau t\u225?f mat tiy\u225?to f\u233?fene fatra ng\u225?ng\u233? n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?fene tamb\u233?n ng\u225?ngayam yafrote, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?fene ram\u233?gh yam s\u225?i y\u233?m kwankwane. F\u233?yo F\u233?feraf\u233? emo y\u233?fande n\u233?m\u233? yam wafrogh kwankwane y\u233?m so fai y\u233?nmafrote.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum ewatamete Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?ghm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
"A njam f\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati, yau t\u225?f nden\u233? em \u225?r efe em faruta mer w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau efe n\u225?uwetat Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oraighan ewakai \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngon a ndimbal endm\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i efandat \u225?r\u233?m. Y\u233?ndon efalo emndetan, y\u233?mofem t\u233? ewanangi y\u233?fenjo fai m\u233?inyoe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
W\u233?nde njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati, k\u233?nyawangi f\u233?fenjo m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?t, t\u233?n\u233?mnangi s\u233?safne a Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati y\u225?faf F\u233?ferafafaf, efe y\u233?m fandaghofnar. F\u233?yo F\u233?ferafam emo efande kwankwane yam wafroghan so fai ewafrote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?m njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati, yau t\u225?rf\u225?r fifiofnar si norayati nden\u233? T\u233?ndo \u225?r k\u233?s em, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? nden\u233? nemnat y\u233?fene ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so ey\u225?rete t\u225?rf\u225?r sian. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Yau t\u225?f nden\u233? em f\u225? k\u233?s em, m\u233?nam\u233?n F\u233?feraf\u233? fronde mat y\u233?m f\u233?fene m\u233?nde n\u233?mat f\u233?mofem yamnendati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u233?yo, nden\u233? so Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati:
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 'T\u233?fene Af\u233? njafar tuk\u233?n,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 so m\u233? y\u233?m fene y\u233?tkw\u233?n nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
fene lim\u225?n\u233?gh so y\u233?n\u233?m,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 a fene m\u233?nde so nufrote y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? njafaran k\u233?s y\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
T\u233?nmaram t\u233?fe s\u233?nonjo efoghm\u233?n njamke.
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
K\u233?mawalindang\u233? t\u233?fene yaufi,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 nden\u233?yameyo y\u233?nd t\u233? y\u233?nmawalinda y\u233?fene yaufi t\u233?fefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Yau y\u233?nd y\u233?nlimnda ufogh yamam\u233?,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 w\u233?nde y\u233?nmanjana y\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? yaufi \u225?roe tamb\u233?n.
