"F\u233?m t\u225?f tawawalindang\u233? \u225?mb \u225?rfene yaufiyam y\u233?mofem njam ewafrotat f\u233?fefaf, F\u233?feraf\u233? njafaran w\u233?i so tawalindang\u233? f\u233?fene yaufi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?m yau njam tawawalindang\u233? \u225?rfene yaufiyam, f\u233?fene Af\u233? yau so tawalindang\u233? f\u233?fene yaufi.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum korayau awafarman\u233?ghm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
"Njam nawafarmetati, yau yuyafotati gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? s\u225?f nden\u233? \u225?r k\u233?s nufrotat efe em faruta mer w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mofem eyatotat y\u233?fenjo s\u225?f gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisaf\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?r\u233?m so efandat nden\u233? f\u225? nawafarmetat. Y\u233?ndon efalo emndetan, y\u233?mofem t\u233? ewanangi y\u233?fenjoyo fai m\u233?inyoe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
W\u233?nde njam f\u233?m nawafarmetati, efaghanati s\u233?nko a eumbnati s\u225?f. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? ewafrotati m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?r yau mat so em nden\u233? nawafarmetati, w\u233?nde m\u233? F\u233?ferafaro efe y\u233?m fandaghofnar; F\u233?feraf\u233? efe n\u233?rete y\u233?n\u233? yam wafroghan em kwankwane so fai ewafrote f\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum korayau ngonj\u233?lm\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? njafaran
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
"Yau t\u225?f eumendati f\u233?fendio ngonj\u233?l y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan, \u225?nde gh\u233?njam a nek\u233?rnek\u233?ram ewasrombotat, a \u225?nde so k\u233?nyawangi oro t\u233?fn\u225?r orot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
W\u233?nde eumendati f\u233?fendio ngonj\u233?l k\u233?t\u225?n njafarot, \u225?nde gh\u233?njam a nek\u233?rnek\u233?ram yau so ewas\u233?rmbotat, a \u225?nde yau so k\u233?nyawangi oro t\u233?fn\u225?r orot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
F\u233?yo \u225?nde f\u233?fene ngonj\u233?l y\u233?m, k\u233?t\u233? f\u233?fene tik\u233?f w\u233?ikor y\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
"Gh\u233?k\u233?f siy\u233?m lambef\u233? y\u233?m fifioene. T\u225?f f\u233?fene gh\u233?k\u233?f njam em mer, f\u233?fene m\u233?inyo fifi so y\u233?m kwayaghanro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
W\u233?nde t\u225?f f\u233?fene gh\u233?k\u233?f njam em m\u225?m\u225?fi, f\u233?fene m\u233?inyo fifi so y\u233?m kw\u233?fitayanro\u451? Njam kwayagh\u233? f\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n kamndang\u233? kw\u233?fit\u233?, f\u233?m so em minde kw\u233?fitayan\u451?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
"Yau f\u233?mofem so ey\u225?totati s\u243?mbio yur\u233?. \u193?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? s\u225?i m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat y\u233?fandati a \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? s\u225?i yuwetati, o \u225?mb s\u225?i ey\u225?totati efaloe a \u225?mb s\u225?i y\u233?karotati. F\u233?m yau so n\u225?s\u225?fotati s\u243?mbio yurat Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne a maniot.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum emndai yau m\u225?m\u233? mwigh\u233? em
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde y\u233?ndon emndetan f\u233?m, yau m\u225?m\u233? mwigh\u233? em ndern\u225?ye f\u233?m emor, n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mofem so enetati njamke a nu; o w\u233?i f\u233?fenjo fifim\u233?n, n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mofem so nawotati. Gh\u233?rs\u233? siy\u233?m minde ndimbal, w\u233?nde njamke siy\u233?m n\u233?mbnare y\u233?m, a fifi siy\u233?m minde ndimbal y\u233?m, w\u233?nde s\u225?l\u225?me siy\u233?m n\u233?mbnare y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Efandati men; f\u225? yau n\u225?s\u225?fotat y\u233?ghan, targhan, wamane umeng\u233?ghan, w\u233?nde f\u233?fene njafarm\u233?n Afam emanjne f\u225?. F\u233?m \u225?r sem minde ndimbal em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene gh\u233?kfan a ewaindati men. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Mwigh\u233? \u233?w\u243?rsoghe f\u233?mofem yau so tomb\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? ey\u225?totati.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
"N\u233?mam\u233?n w\u233?t mwighan n\u233?worsotati s\u225?l\u225?mem\u233?n? Efandati ndern\u225?ye k\u233?ghat mbumbu nanotat. Y\u233?mofem yau s\u225?l\u225?me ewafrotat y\u233?fendio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan Solomon y\u225?njo m\u233?inyotio w\u233?m\u225?ran nden\u233? umaneghkaf yau k\u233?retau f\u225? sem. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? nden\u233? y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam k\u233?s yus ewamanete k\u233?ghatan, s\u233?nonjo \u225?rk\u233? em a k\u225?ye f\u233?s\u233?n nak\u233?rnat. F\u233?m so Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewamanete ndimbal k\u233?r\u225?ye. F\u233?m n\u233?mbnar ndimbal mwighaf\u233?! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
F\u233?yo yau mwighayam ewaw\u243?rsota norayati, 'N\u233?m\u233? so y\u233?ndfem enetam?' o 'N\u233?m\u233? nu so enetam?' o 'N\u233?m\u233? so y\u233?nd y\u233?nmawo?' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n T\u233?ndo \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?nde y\u233?ngwaitotat, f\u233?yo f\u233?fene njafarm\u233?n Af\u233? mat y\u233?m f\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?nde em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
W\u233?nde fronde yafarenati Ng\u225?nj\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh a y\u225?ne mbark\u225?ndyam, a f\u233?yo m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? rokar so eramete f\u233?yotaroe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n kaitaum\u233?n yau n\u233?ngemnati, m\u233?nam\u233?n k\u225?ye efgham so y\u233?n\u233?rse y\u225?njo m\u233?ghm\u233?gh. S\u233?nonjo efoghm\u233?n k\u233?rt\u233? sem s\u233?nonjoyot.
