"Yau moghan \u225?mb \u225?r ekmetati, m\u233?n\u225?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yau so moghan k\u233?n\u233?kmang\u233?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so moghan k\u233?n\u233?kmang\u233? nden\u233?yameyo f\u233?mon ndern\u225?ye \u225?mb \u225?r moghan ekmete, a nden\u233?yameyo y\u233?mo so ewafrote f\u233?mo ndern\u225?ye \u225?mb \u225?r moghan ekmete.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
"N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mo yafande fe f\u250?tarene gh\u233?k\u233?f f\u233?m\u233?gh w\u233?nde f\u233?mo yau y\u233?fande fenjo gh\u233?kfan y\u233?m w\u233?n t\u233?nj? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Ndern\u225?ye f\u233?m so koraya f\u250?tarefaf, 'Kumyo y\u233?ndon so k\u233?mautor\u233?n fene gh\u233?k\u233?f f\u233?m\u233?gh, t\u225?f fefaf y\u233?m w\u233?n t\u233?nj fenjo gh\u233?kfan? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u233?m farun mer n\u233?rete w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau! Fronde tutor fene gh\u233?kfan w\u233?n t\u233?nj, f\u233?yo f\u233?mo so efande saf\u233?nro a f\u233?mo t\u225?f so tautor f\u250?tarene gh\u233?k\u233?f f\u233?m\u233?gh.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
"Yau ewarametati n\u233?m\u233? em nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar \u225?ghafet a yau ewawitati f\u233?fenjo ndindi kimbafet. Njam f\u233?mofem yafrotati, y\u233?mofem so es\u233?nat y\u233?n\u233? rokar y\u233?fene ng\u225?ngaye a so kawengongi a eft\u233?rnat f\u233?m kar\u233?fkarfot.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Kamota, k\u225?ronja, kautar
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
"Namotati Yurafaf, a y\u233?mo so tawaramang\u233?; n\u225?ronjati a so tinjongi; nautanati, a s\u233?safne so k\u225?s\u225?w\u233?rng\u233? f\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n m\u233?inyotio \u225?r efe n\u243?mnendat y\u233?mofem so tawanangi, efe n\u225?ronjat y\u233?mofem so tinjongi, a f\u225? efe nautanat, s\u233?safne so k\u225?s\u225?w\u233?rng\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
"Njam f\u233?fene ambum k\u243?mnendangi flawayat, f\u233?mofem so tawaramangi w\u237?m? Yau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u225? njam kamotangi wagifot, f\u233?mofem so tawaramangi rar\u233?gh kamban? Yau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?m, efe em yaufi, mat em ndern\u225?ye f\u233?mofem so ewarametati mer ram\u233?gh rokar f\u233?fene ambumat. F\u233?yo f\u233?fene Af\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam njafaran efaloe so tawaramang\u233? mer ram\u233?gh rokar y\u233?feyot emofem tamnendangi f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde m\u233?inyotio k\u233?nj\u250?n, ewawafrotati \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?t n\u233?mat f\u233?m m\u233?nde em \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m s\u225?i ewafrotat f\u233?fe. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?f\u233?n y\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? Mosesene n\u225?k a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?rfene Bukam y\u233?nd y\u233?nmatametat."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 N\u233?mbne a marat s\u233?safne
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
"K\u233?lawangi n\u233?mbne s\u233?safnem\u233?. M\u233?nam\u233?n s\u233?safne siy\u233?m marat a end \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? y\u233?k\u233?m \u225?fr\u225?taye y\u233?m f\u233?s\u233?t, a t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r n\u233?nyawetat y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
W\u233?nde s\u233?safne siy\u233?m n\u233?mbne a end \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?k\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n efalo gh\u233?rsafaf taik\u233?r y\u233?m, a m\u233? nambio \u225?r\u233?mro tinjongi y\u233?n\u233? end.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 W\u233?n a y\u225?ne mbwe
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
"Kor nawarawenati uny\u233?gh Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?rfenem\u233?n. F\u225? en\u233?m f\u233?fefaf sif s\u225?l\u225?meyaf\u233?, w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n f\u225? em t\u233?kratro munjan \u225?gh\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?mofem so f\u225? tawayamngongi y\u233?fenjo mbweyan. W\u233?t \u225?r\u233?m so ekafetat y\u233?ro w\u233?tw\u233?taf\u233? mbwe o wiwi fasalaron? Yau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
M\u233?inyotio mer w\u233?nam efune mer mbwe, w\u233?nde m\u225?m\u225?fi w\u233?nam efune m\u225?m\u225?fi mbwe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Mer w\u233?nam yau efune m\u225?m\u225?fi mbwe, a m\u225?m\u225?fi w\u233?nam yau efune mer mbwe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
M\u233?inyotio w\u233?nam yau njam mer mbwe efunat so enfetat a ewitat f\u233?s\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?mofem so tawayamngongi uny\u233?gh Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r y\u233?fenjo yam wafroghan."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Efalo waitogh \u225?r a uny\u233?gh waitogh \u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
"M\u233?inyotio \u225?r efe norayat tafaf nden\u233?, 'Tane Yur\u233?, tane Yur\u233?,' yau so k\u233?lawangi njafar lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t, w\u233?nde m\u233? f\u225?ro emofem yafrotat tane Afane m\u233?nde efe y\u233?m njafaran. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
T\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r so norayat tafaf mogh efghon, 'Tane Yur\u233?, tane Yur\u233?, fene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan y\u233?ndfem kafrotaw\u233?m Buk si a fene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r tawifnaw\u233?m a s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam tawafrotaw\u233?m?' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?nd so korayang\u233?n y\u233?fefaf, 'Y\u233?nd mafina w\u233?m f\u233?m efe em. Kit\u233?rmbongi tafafta, f\u233?m yaufiyam wafrogh \u225?r.'
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 K\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? \u225?r a onon m\u233?ngo ram\u233?gh \u225?r
