"Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, \u225?r efe n\u225?y\u225?retat y\u233?n\u233? si tanem\u233?n a ewaitotat ndenanit em k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? \u225?r emon m\u233?ngo yeitam w\u237?m tuk\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Nu afam\u233?gh nufngoi, wanje k\u233?f\u233?r armbogh nufngoi, a mbormbor t\u233?fnjau a y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ngo y\u233?smai; w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ngo yau y\u233?fury\u233?ng. M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne s\u233?ras\u233?r tayang\u233?rw\u233?n w\u237?man. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
W\u233?nde \u225?r efe n\u225?y\u225?retat y\u233?n\u233? si tanem\u233?n w\u233?nde yau ewaitotat ndenanit em onon \u225?r emon m\u233?ngo yeitam mirian. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Nu afam\u233?gh nufngoi, wanje k\u233?f\u233?r armbogh nufngoi, a mbormbor t\u233?fnjau a m\u233?ngo y\u233?smai, a y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ngo y\u233?fury\u233?ng ambino."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
