Yesu njam n\u233?newory\u233?ng k\u233?tam\u233? mband tunak\u233?f tamb\u233?n, t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r m\u233?rnam yaitoy\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Yaufi gh\u233?nganaf\u233? \u225?r s\u233?lngw\u233?le y\u233?nmorm\u233?n a budme niyai y\u225?faf a t\u233?mndang\u233?, "Yur\u233?, f\u233?m m\u233?nde njam n\u233?m, f\u233?mo so mer kwiy\u225?to Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene gh\u233?kfan."
