\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
"Y\u225?nafem so taramangi y\u225?nng\u233?nof m\u233?n\u225?t so t\u225?kmangi krot, a y\u225?refafem y\u233?fenjo ambum so ewafrotat nden\u233?yameyo, ambum w\u233?i so k\u233?nawengongi y\u225?refafefaf a krot t\u225?kmangi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
M\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m so m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat n\u233?fandat tanem\u233?n, w\u233?nde efe njam yakai taikrataye k\u233?t\u225?n kerker so kunjarng\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u233?m njam \u225?mb tesenan ewas\u233?rmbotat, kenngongi \u225?mb tesenfaf. Y\u233?ndon efalo emndetan, f\u233?mofem yau so tifongi f\u233?fenjo \u225?ligh y\u233?nam\u233? tesenam\u233? Israil k\u233?nj\u250?n njam \u193?roene Ambum n\u233?nangota.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
"Waitogh \u225?r yau y\u233?m tuk\u233?n y\u225?ne watamegh \u225?roefaf, a faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r yau y\u233?m tuk\u233?n y\u225?ne yurafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Waitogh \u225?r siy\u233?m f\u233?yotaro y\u233?m s\u225?i kamndang\u233? nden\u233? y\u225?njo watamegh \u225?r w\u233?nde yau so yainde, a nden\u233?yameyo y\u233?m faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r y\u225?ne yurafaf. T\u225?f m\u233?r\u233?n s\u233?nko t\u233?fn\u225?r njam t\u233? y\u233?mndetat Beljebul, w\u233?i nder\u233? minde y\u225?ne m\u233?r\u233?n w\u233?i so ewasalitat!
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yau f\u233?rf\u233?r em n\u233?mam\u233?n w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde yau t\u225?f f\u233?rf\u233?r em y\u233?fenem\u233?n. N\u233?m\u233? \u225?tnoghe y\u233?m so saf\u233?t kufarng\u233?, a m\u233?inyotio n\u233?m\u233? kwankwane em so mat n\u225?y\u225?totat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon norayan f\u233?fefaf kw\u233?fitayan, korayangi efogh kwayaghayan, a n\u233?m\u233? ewawanjan f\u233?fene t\u233?nganan, nafrotati m\u233?ngo s\u233?man.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
"Yau f\u233?rf\u233?r em y\u233?fefaf emofem fifi so esmetat w\u233?nde yau so y\u233?smetat mb\u233?rmb\u233?r. W\u233?nde f\u233?rf\u233?r aem Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf, emo so tawife mb\u233?rmb\u233?r a fifi k\u233?t\u233? k\u233?mboghofnar f\u233?s\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
S\u243?mbio mbinj n\u233?mbne manie so tat\u233?rnangend, w\u233?nde \u225?mb yau so kuyang\u233? mbandot F\u233?ferafane matofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n mat y\u233?m nj\u233?namb s\u237?f em f\u233?fene s\u233?nkoyan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde yau f\u233?rf\u233?r em. F\u233?mofem ewaindati y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?mbnar men.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
"F\u233?m so noraye saf\u233?nro k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb \u225?rfefaf, "Y\u233?ndo efalo yiy\u225?totan Yesu.' Njam f\u233?mo yafrota y\u233?n\u233?, y\u233?ndo so t\u233?mndan tane Af\u233? njafaran, "F\u225? siy\u233?m tane waitogh \u225?r." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
W\u233?nde njam f\u233?m noraya \u225?mb \u225?rfefaf, "Y\u233?ndo yau efalo yiy\u225?totan Yesu," y\u233?ndo so t\u225?f t\u233?mndan tane Af\u233? njafaran, 'Y\u233?nd mafina w\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r. F\u225? yau y\u233?m tane waitogh \u225?r."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 \u193?r\u233?m so yuwetat Yesu mindefifi
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
"F\u233?m yau nden\u233? nemnati nden\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?nmorm\u233?n krufr\u225?t yam y\u233?n\u233?rsam\u233?n mbandot! Y\u233?nd yau w\u233?nmorm\u233?n y\u233?n\u233?rsam\u233?n krufr\u225?t yam, w\u233?nde witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? n\u225?if\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
M\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd w\u233?nmorm\u233?n s\u225?i ewengotan,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 '\u225?r y\u225?ref\u233? tamb\u233?n,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 m\u233?r\u233?s k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? y\u225?tmafe tamb\u233?n,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 a y\u225?ki al\u233? k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? y\u225?ki amaf tamb\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
\u193?roene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r so en\u233?m k\u233?tam\u233? y\u225?njo m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?ta.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
"\u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom njam uweta y\u225?ref\u233? o y\u225?tm\u233? mindefifi, w\u233?nde y\u225?ne uw\u233?gh siy\u233?m n\u233?mbnar y\u233?m tayot, f\u225? f\u233?yotarofnar y\u233?m ta waitogh\u233?t. \u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom uweta y\u225?njo ambum o m\u233?r\u233?s mindefifi, w\u233?nde y\u225?ne uw\u233?gh siy\u233?m n\u233?mbnar y\u233?m tayot, f\u225? f\u233?yotarofnar y\u233?m ta waitogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
\u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom yau njam y\u233?rsa y\u225?njo wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?n a waitota y\u233?nd, f\u225? f\u233?yotarofnar y\u233?m ta waitogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
\u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom njam yarawena y\u225?njo gh\u233?rs\u233? so y\u233?tarne, a emo njam y\u233?tarna y\u225?njo gh\u233?rs\u233? tane t\u233?fnan so tinjong\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Emofem ew\u225?ut\u225?nat Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n so tawanangi mer fai
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
"\u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom njam k\u233?mumyong\u233? f\u233?m kwumyong\u233? y\u233?nd, a \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom kwumyong\u233? y\u233?nd tumyong\u233? f\u225? emo y\u233?nd w\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
\u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom njam tumyong\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r y\u233?m, so nden\u233?yameyo fai tawanang\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?rfene k\u233?s y\u233?m. A \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom njam tumyong\u233? mbark\u225?nd \u225?r m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? siy\u233?m mbark\u225?nd \u225?r, y\u233?mo so nden\u233?yameyo fai tawanang\u233? mbark\u225?nd \u225?roene k\u233?s y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
A njam \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom tawaramang\u233? m\u233? krufr\u225?t kafusi nu y\u233?feyot \u225?mb y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?nd \u225?r\u233?t m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? siy\u233?m tane waitogh \u225?r, y\u233?ndon efalo ewaufrotan, y\u233?mo efaloe yau so y\u233?tarne y\u225?njo fai."
