Njamandio Jonene waitogh \u225?r kuwanotaw\u233?t, Yesum siot yiy\u225?toi \u225?r m\u233?rnafefaf y\u225?nem\u233?n Jon: "N\u233?m\u233? \u225?r s\u225?f f\u233?m n\u233?ngtor fanfne yuwot fandagh\u233?t? Tomb\u233? yus \u225?rk\u233? ef\u233?nje mbormboram? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
