\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
"Efe \u225?r yau so k\u233?nyawang\u233? ndimbal muyaf\u233? \u225?roene m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n rokar r\u233?sagh\u233?t t\u225?fandro y\u233?mon njam fronde yumbeta \u225?ng\u233?ghe ndimbal muyaf\u233? \u225?r. F\u233?yo t\u225?f y\u233?mon so m\u233?inyotio rokar tawanang\u233? y\u225?ne m\u233?ngota.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
"\u193?rk\u233? \u225?r efe yau y\u233?m tafaf f\u225? siy\u233?m y\u233?ndf\u233? as\u233?n\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r; emof\u233? y\u233?ndf\u233? yau eumendam \u225?r, f\u225? siy\u233?m wiror\u233?gh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan, m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfene yaufiyam a yaufi si, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n so tawalindang\u233?, w\u233?nde emon njam noraya sotaf\u233? yaufi si Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roefaf, yau so tawalindang\u233? y\u233?n\u233? yaufi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Emon njam noraya yaufi si \u193?roene Ambumoefaf, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n f\u233?yotaro so tawalindang\u233?, w\u233?nde emo njam yaufi si noraya Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roefaf, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n yau so tawalindang\u233? s\u233?nonjo o soram\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 W\u233?n a y\u225?ne mbwe
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
"Njam w\u233?n y\u233?m mer, so efune mer mbwe, a njam w\u233?n y\u233?m yaufi, so efune yaufi mbwe. \u193?r\u233?m efande w\u233?n mbwe a mat n\u225?y\u225?tote n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?n\u233? w\u233?n mer y\u233?m o yaufi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
F\u233?m kamban, f\u233?m yaufi \u225?r. F\u233?m ndern\u225?ye so norayati mer si? Mb\u237?rmb\u237?r norayat n\u233?m\u233? tik\u233?f afoghare y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Mer \u225?rom efune mer yam mer tik\u233?fta, a yaufi \u225?rom efune yaufiyam yaufi tik\u233?fta.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
"Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?fe y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, mogh efghon m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m so nafrotat n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u225? korayaw\u233?t m\u233?inyotio fifiofnar si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so emote f\u233?fenjo sim\u233?n, tamndang\u233? mbark\u225?nd o moghan so takmang\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mofem y\u233?motay\u233?nd Yesu ufarogh yamot
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
\u193?mb n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r a \u225?mb Farasi \u225?r\u233?m norayay\u233?nd, "Watamegh \u225?r, y\u233?nd m\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233?m s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam tafrota t\u233?fe fandagh\u233?t."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
Yesu norayai, "Nder\u233? yaufi a ng\u225?nj\u225?nofnar \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?nonjo efoghm\u233?n em! F\u233?mofem w\u233?motangi ufarogh yam wafrogh\u233?t? Yau! M\u233? y\u225?ne ufarogh yamro f\u233?feyot so tawaraman Jona Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Jona nambio efogh a s\u233?mb\u225?r y\u233?kmang\u233?rm\u233?n ndimbal wagifoene f\u250?t k\u233?nj\u250?n, nden\u233? endeyo \u193?roene Ambum so w\u233?i nambio efogh a s\u233?mb\u225?r mb\u233?w\u233? m\u233?ngon y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
Mogh efghon \u225?r Nin\u233?fam\u233?n so kokayongi y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r satafaf a so emronat, m\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?r Nin\u233?fan t\u233? nawengongi yaufiyamta Jonane si waitoghan; y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?feyot nden\u233? \u225?mb \u225?r y\u233?na y\u233?m ndimbalfifi, yau kor nden\u233? Jona. F\u233?m w\u233?i so kawengongi yaufiyam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Mogh efghon Warsagh amaf Sefam\u233?n so kokayong\u233? y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r satafaf a emronat, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? t\u233?nmorw\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? nayu y\u225?njo ndimbal yuta m\u233?n\u225?t Warsagh \u225?r Solomonene k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? \u225?y\u225?rgh\u233?t; y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?feyot nden\u233? \u225?mb \u225?r y\u233?na y\u233?m ndimbalfifi, yau kor nden\u233? Solomon!
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r kor w\u233?i n\u233?nangoi
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
"Njam yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r k\u233?ntorng\u233? \u225?r tamb\u233?n, f\u225? nguwanong\u233? fanfne yuwot sifay\u233? ronjagh\u233?t enagh\u233?t. Yau njam sifay\u233? tinjong\u233?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
f\u225?yo so korayang\u233?, 'Y\u233?nd so nangotan tanjo m\u233?ngot.' F\u233?yo f\u225? n\u233?ngangote a tinjong\u233? m\u233?ngo sotro, mer a freng\u233?ghkaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
F\u233?yo yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r kuwanong\u233? tanwasrong\u233? \u225?mb 7 yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r efe em minde yaufi yaindat f\u225?, f\u233?yo k\u233?lawangi a k\u225?mnjongi k\u233?t\u233?. Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? \u225?roene gh\u233?rs\u233? siy\u233?m minde m\u225?m\u225?fi k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? fronde ndern\u225?ye t\u233?morw\u233?n. Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? so ufroghan y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? yaufi \u225?r satafaf."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesuene y\u225?tm\u233? a y\u225?nngn\u233?f
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
Yesu m\u233? korayau \u225?rfefaf njam y\u225?tm\u233? a y\u225?nngn\u233?f nufary\u233?nd. F\u225? nokayoy\u233?nd t\u233?ndota, namotay\u233?nd y\u233?maf\u233? siot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
\u193?mb \u225?rom yaufroi y\u225?, "K\u233?reta, fene am\u233? a fenngn\u233?f ewakai t\u233?ndon, a f\u225? m\u233?nde em f\u233?maf\u233? siot."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "Efe y\u233?m tane am\u233?? Efe em tane n\u233?nngn\u233?f?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 49\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mon t\u225?f euyafoi y\u225?ne waitogh \u225?r a korayang\u233?, "K\u233?retangi! F\u225? em tane am\u233? a tane n\u233?nngn\u233?f! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 50\~}
\u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom njam yafrota tane njafarm\u233?n Afane m\u233?nde, f\u225? fem tane n\u233?nngn\u233?f a tane m\u233?r\u233?s a tane am\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 13
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ndau t\u233?fn\u225?rane rengerenge si
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghonyo Yesum y\u233?frangoi m\u233?ngo a n\u233?ngaflai a n\u225?mnjoi arakaf t\u233?ndota watamegh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
T\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n n\u225?umendam\u233?nd a yarenday\u233?nd Yesu. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan Yesu naflai a nuflai boutot, a n\u225?mnjoi k\u233?t\u233? a \u225?r tawakayong\u233?rw\u233?n arakaf t\u233?ndom\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u225? korayau \u225?rfefaf t\u225?rf\u225?r yamm\u233?n rengerenge sie:
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "K\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?r efe n\u233?wanoi mbwe taran\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Njam y\u233?mon mbwe tatarnau, \u225?mb kuitaw\u233?t endm\u233? a men tanmorw\u233?n a tanetaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
\u193?mb kuitaw\u233?t w\u237?m \u233?re\u233?reghat mbandot, \u225?nde n\u233?mbne mband t\u233?morw\u233?n. Mbwe w\u233?ke afiyar\u233?gh nufngoy\u233?nd, m\u233?nam\u233?n mband yau t\u233?morw\u233?n k\u233?njkam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
W\u233?nde njam efogh waftayam ewerai, w\u233?n \u233?ruyagh nufngoy\u233?nd, a k\u233?r emorm\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?fene s\u233?r\u233?mb yau niyay\u233?nd k\u233?nj\u250?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
\u193?mb mbwe kuitaw\u233?t yus w\u233?tfaf, yus kanotaw\u233?t a w\u233?tam takuindaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
\u193?mb mbwe kuitaw\u233?t mer mbandot, nanotam\u233?nd kw\u233?ki, \u225?mb 100, \u225?mb 60 a \u225?mb 30. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Efe njam t\u233?nganaf\u233? y\u233?m \u225?y\u225?rgh\u233?t, f\u225? so k\u225?y\u225?rang\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u225?ne waitogh \u225?r enmorm\u233?n Yesuefaf a y\u233?mnday\u233?nd, "N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m noraye \u225?rfefaf rengerenge sie?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Yesum ewawangoi, "Kwankwane mat njafar lim\u225?n\u233?ghm\u233?n f\u233?fe t\u233? ewaufroy\u233?n, w\u233?nde y\u233?fe yau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Njam \u225?mb \u225?roefaf matyam y\u233?m, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so taramang\u233? t\u225?rf\u225?r matyam. W\u233?nde njam \u225?mb \u225?roefaf yau y\u233?m matyam, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so takawang\u233? y\u225?yot n\u233?m\u233? n\u233?mbnar y\u225?ne y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan y\u233?nd norayan rengerenge sie y\u233?fefaf:
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "F\u233?t\u233? n\u233?retat, w\u233?nde yau y\u233?fandat,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 f\u233?t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?retat, w\u233?nde yau n\u225?y\u225?retat o mat yau n\u225?y\u225?totat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
"Aisayane mat y\u225?togh si n\u233?m\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n efalo n\u225?y\u225?toi y\u233?fenem\u233?n,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 'F\u233?m so t\u250?m\u233?n n\u225?y\u225?retati, w\u233?nde mat yau so kamndangi,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 f\u233?m so t\u250?m\u233?n n\u233?retati, w\u233?nde yau so mat n\u225?y\u225?totati.
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rfene tik\u233?f namndai t\u225?ik\u233?r,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 a y\u233?fene t\u233?ngan yau kor n\u225?y\u225?retat,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 a y\u233?mofem t\u233? eumb\u233?rtongi gh\u233?k\u233?f.
