Njam efe n\u225?y\u225?reta njafar lim\u225?n\u233?ghm\u233?n si a yau mat kamndang\u233?, yaufi \u225?r k\u233?nuwanong\u233? a si tawanang\u233? n\u233?m\u233? taitau y\u225?ne tikfan. Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m mbwe \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? tatarnau endm\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
\u193?rk\u233? mbwe kuitaw\u233?t w\u237?m \u233?re\u233?reghat mbandot, y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r fiy\u233?m efe n\u225?y\u225?rete si a tanang\u233? \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
W\u233?nde m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?fene s\u233?r\u233?mb yau, y\u233?fene akegh yau teke. Njam k\u233?rt\u233? a was\u233?rmbogh y\u233?n\u233?m m\u233?nam\u233?n si t\u233?fnan, f\u225? w\u233?kero kuyangi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
\u193?rk\u233? mbwe kuitaw\u233?t w\u233?tw\u233?t sifayan, y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r eufane efe si k\u225?y\u225?rangi, w\u233?nde mband mwighayam ewafote, mani mwighayam ewawinde a \u225?mb rokarot. \u193?rk\u233? m\u233?n\u225?yam si njang\u233?nnjang\u233?n tiy\u225?tong\u233? mbwefnarot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
W\u233?nde \u225?rk\u233? mbwe mer mbandot nuy\u225?y\u233?nd, f\u225? fiy\u233?m efe si n\u225?y\u225?rai a sioene fifi yanay\u233?ng. Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r s\u225?fam efunat 100, \u225?mb 60, \u225?mb nden\u233? 30."
