Njam mer mbwe afiyar\u233?gh nufngoy\u233?nd a s\u233?nko ufrogh nufngoy\u233?nd, a nden\u233?yameyo yaufi mbwe anogh nufngoy\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
"Ndau yurane faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r n\u233?naflay\u233?nd y\u225?faf a t\u233?mndang\u233?, 'Ndimbal, f\u233?mon taite mer mbwe fene ndawan. \u193?rkandm\u233? y\u233?n\u233? yaufi yus tan\u233?m?'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
