Taurend m\u233?rne anogh\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?notio tar\u233?gh. Y\u233?n\u233? efghon y\u233?ndo so tamndan wauyu \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, "Fronde kaf\u233?gh yaufi yus a umb\u233?gh sute m\u233?n\u225?t wakrargh\u233?t, a f\u233?yo umb\u233?gh mer mbwe r\u233?sagh wemb\u233?gh m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?t."'"
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Rengerenge si n\u233?mbne mbwem\u233?n a fak flaw\u233? minaghm\u233?n
