Ndemam\u233?n n\u233?mbne mbwe y\u233?m, w\u233?nde njam tiang\u233?, minde ndimbal ndaum\u233?n njamke t\u233?f\u233?n k\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? a w\u233?n kamndang\u233?, kafe ewatene \u225?nde menam nj\u233?n erametat."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
