\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Y\u233?mon ewawangoi, "Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emo mer mbwe eite siy\u233?m \u193?roene Ambum. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? ndau siy\u233?m mband marat a mer mbwe sem njafar lim\u225?n\u233?ghm\u233?n \u225?r; yaufi yus sem Yaufi \u225?roene \u225?r; {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
