F\u233?yo mbark\u225?nd \u225?r so katremngongi efoghnit y\u233?fene Afane lim\u225?n\u233?gh yuwon. F\u225? efe t\u233?nganaf\u233? em, f\u225? y\u233?n\u233? si so n\u225?y\u225?retat.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Rengerenge si t\u233?nogh ngonj\u233?l a ndindi mbwe
