\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Fitam yasotai t\u233?ndot a yus\u233?rmbotam, "Yau, Yur\u233?! Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yau so tumyong\u233? y\u233?n\u233? s\u225?i nufrota fefaf!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Yesu nawengoi a t\u233?mndang\u233? Fit\u233?, "S\u225?if\u233?r, kitr\u233?mb tatamb\u233?n! N\u233?t\u233?r n\u233?m tayot, m\u233?nam\u233?n fene mwigh\u233? yau y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta. W\u233?nde f\u233?m nemne ndenanit \u225?r ndern\u225?ye nemnat."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u233?yo Yesum emndai y\u225?ne waitogh \u225?r, "Efe ta waitogh\u233?t kufngong\u233? f\u225? so tawalindang\u233? y\u225?njom\u233?n, a tanang\u233? y\u225?njo wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?n a kwaitong\u233? y\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Efe njam m\u233?nde y\u233?m y\u225?njo mbandm\u233?n gh\u233?rs\u233? wanjargh\u233?t so y\u233?tarne tuot gh\u233?rs\u233?, w\u233?nde emo y\u233?tarna y\u225?njo mbandm\u233?n gh\u233?rs\u233? tane t\u233?fnan y\u233?mo so tanang tuot gh\u233?rs\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
'\u193?r\u233?m so tanang\u233? m\u233?inyotio mband marat yandio. W\u233?nde njam y\u233?mo y\u225?njo tuot gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?tarna, y\u233?n\u233? yau so y\u233?m mer y\u225?yot. Y\u233?na yau y\u233?m \u225?mb \u225?r emo so k\u233?maramang\u233? y\u225?njo gh\u233?rs\u233? w\u233?ikor. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
\u193?roene Ambum so n\u233?nangote njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?rf\u233? Y\u225?refane ndimbal kwayaghayan, a fai y\u233?mon so ewaramete f\u233?natayero \u225?r\u233?t y\u233?fene \u225?s\u225?foghm\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Y\u233?ndon efalo emndetan f\u233?m, \u225?mb y\u233?na em efe k\u233?r yau so em k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u233?mofem tinjongi \u193?roene Ambumoene angogh a f\u225? so kamndang\u233? Warsagh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 17
