6 efogh soram\u233? Yesum engwasroi Fit\u233?, Jems a y\u225?nng\u233?n Jon, a elimay\u233?ng mband tunak\u233?f tuk\u233?t f\u225?ro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
K\u233?t\u233? Yesuene fifi nafurnai y\u233?fene s\u225?fr\u233?re. Y\u225?ne s\u225?f natremngoi ndenanit efogh, a y\u225?ne s\u225?l\u225?me t\u233?morw\u233?n minde kwayagh\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?yo k\u233?t\u233? nambio waitogh \u225?r\u233?m ewinjeyay\u233?nd Moses a Elaija korayaw\u233?t Yesuf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Fitam t\u233?mndang\u233? Yesu, "Yur\u233?, nder\u233? mer y\u233?m y\u233?nd y\u233?na siy\u233?n\u233?m! F\u233?m njam m\u233?nde n\u233?m, y\u233?ndon so nambio m\u233?ngom\u233?ngo erametan y\u233?na, \u225?mb feyot, \u225?mb Mosese a Elaijai \u225?mb."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Njam f\u225? m\u233? korayau, kwayaghaye njafar kwamkwamam ewafary\u233?ng f\u225?, a si y\u233?nmorm\u233?n njafar kwamkwamta, "Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m tane tikfaf\u233? Ambum y\u233?nd endefaf n\u225?uwetan. N\u225?y\u225?retati y\u225?faf!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Njam waitogh \u225?r\u233?m n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd si, f\u225? f\u233?rf\u233?r tamorw\u233?n a niyay\u233?nd mbandot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Yesu naflai y\u233?fefaf a eyanjai f\u225? a emndai, "Kanongi, yau f\u233?rf\u233?r em." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Njam f\u225? n\u233?ngretay\u233?nd, y\u233?mofem efe yau yinjoy\u233?nd m\u233? Yesuro.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Njamandio f\u225? k\u233?newonaw\u233?t mband tunak\u233?fta, Yesum taikrataye emndai, "Ende yau tawaufrongi n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mofem y\u233?fandati, k\u233?t\u225?notio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam tanong\u233? \u193?roene Ambum k\u233?rta."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?motay\u233?nd Yesu, "N\u233?mam\u233?n n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r\u233?m norayat nden\u233? Elaija so y\u233?n\u233?m fronde?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Yesum ewawangoi, "Elaija so y\u233?n\u233?m efrenda m\u233?inyotio yam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?fe nden\u233? Elaija t\u233? y\u233?nmorm\u233?n a yau y\u225?y\u225?mngoy\u233?nd f\u225?, w\u233?nde y\u233?mofem m\u233? tawafrotaw\u233?t y\u233?fenjo m\u233?ndef\u233? yam wafrogh. Nden\u233?yameyo \u193?roene Ambumom t\u233?kr\u225?t so y\u225?rarete y\u233?fene ng\u225?ngayan." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u233?yo waitogh \u225?r mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd nden\u233? f\u225? korayau Jon walitogh \u225?roenem\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum mer yiy\u225?toi yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?raf\u233? ambum
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Njam f\u225? n\u233?ngangoy\u233?nd \u225?r m\u233?rnafefaf, \u225?r y\u233?nmorm\u233?n Yesuefaf a budme niy\u225?i y\u225?ne s\u225?fr\u233?re, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
a y\u233?mon norayai, "Yur\u233?, gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? so n\u233?m tane ambumoenem\u233?n! F\u225? siy\u233?m gh\u233?rare enjneyam taufarng\u233? a ndimbal nd\u233?mkeyan y\u233?m. F\u225? t\u250?m\u233?n f\u233?s\u233?t kaun\u225?mngong\u233? a nuot kuyang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon y\u233?n\u233?mnjam\u233?n f\u225? fene waitogh \u225?rfefaf, w\u233?nde y\u233?mofem yau mer yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Yesum yawangoy\u233?ng, "F\u233?m efalo y\u225?toghofnar a yaufi \u225?r sat\u233?! Nder\u233? teke y\u233?nd so w\u233?m f\u233?fefaf? Nder\u233? teke f\u233?mofem so k\u233?rt\u233? warametati? T\u233?n\u233?mnjend ambum tafaf!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Yesum y\u233?mndai yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r, "K\u233?tor!" n\u233?tory\u233?ng t\u225?f f\u233?t\u233? ambum mer n\u225?y\u225?toi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u233?yo y\u225?ne waitogh \u225?r enmorm\u233?n f\u225?ro y\u225?faf a y\u233?motay\u233?nd, "N\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?ndfem f\u233?yotarofnar t\u233?nmorm\u233?n yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r wit\u233?rmbogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
