Y\u233?n\u233? efghon waitogh \u225?r naflay\u233?nd Yesuefaf y\u233?motay\u233?nd, "Efe y\u233?m ndimbalfifi njafar lim\u225?n\u233?ghan?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Yesum y\u233?motay\u233?ng ambum tos\u233? y\u225?faftio a y\u233?kmai ambum y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
