F\u233?yo, \u225?rk\u233? \u225?r njam yuwan kamndang\u233? y\u233?n\u233? ambum tosanit y\u233?m ndimbalfifi njafar lim\u225?n\u233?ghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
A emon tumyong\u233? tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan nden\u233? ambum tos\u233? nden\u233?yameyo y\u233?nd kwumyong\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Emofem em\u233?indat m\u233?nd \u225?r yaufiot
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
"Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi so y\u233?m y\u225?yot k\u233?man umb\u233?gh\u233?t ndimbal w\u237?m a yitat arakafot. W\u233?nde njam \u225?mb \u225?rom y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?nd \u225?r y\u233?m\u233?inda yaufiot emo y\u233?nd efalo wiy\u225?tote siy\u233?m minde m\u225?m\u225?fi so y\u233?m y\u225?yot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m mband maratoe m\u233?nam\u233?n mband marat gh\u233?rsayam em\u233?inde \u225?r yaufiyot! Y\u233?n\u233? yam so f\u233?t\u233? nufrotat, w\u233?nde nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? \u225?roe emo em\u233?inde y\u233?n\u233? yamot!
