"Njam fene ng\u225?ngayam o kafkafam n\u233?m\u233?inde f\u233?m yaufiot, t\u233?n\u233?f a t\u233?ngwai. Y\u233?n\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m feyot \u233?laugh\u233?t gh\u233?rsat \u225?mbiro ng\u225?ngaf\u233? o \u225?mbiro kafkafaf\u233?, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? minde m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m feyot s\u243?mbio ng\u225?ng\u233? a kafkafaf\u233? s\u225?i n\u233?m a n\u233?mwitat tuot f\u233?s\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
