"Njam fe efalo y\u225?togh f\u250?tarom yafrota yaufiyam fefaf, kuwano y\u225?faf a tauyafo y\u225?ne yaufi. W\u233?nde yafrota fembia m\u233? f\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?nro. Njam y\u233?mon k\u233?ny\u225?rang\u233? f\u233?m, f\u233?mon t\u233? yango fene efalo y\u225?togh f\u250?tar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?mon yau njam k\u233?ny\u225?rang\u233? f\u233?m, t\u233?nmasro \u225?mbiro o s\u243?mbio \u225?r f\u233?mof\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i norayat y\u225?faf. F\u225? so mat kamndangi n\u233?m\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi yam fene efalo y\u225?togh f\u250?tar\u233?m tawafrote. Nawafarotati ndern\u225?ye Buk si noraye, "K\u233?t\u233? fiya em s\u243?mbio o nambio \u225?r siot m\u233?n\u225?yan nden\u233? \u225?mb \u225?rom t\u233? tafrote \u225?mb m\u225?m\u225?fi yam. S\u243?mbio o nambio \u225?r\u233?m t\u225?f tiy\u225?tongi n\u233?m\u233? njam nufrota." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Yau njam f\u225? k\u225?y\u225?rang\u233? y\u233?fefaf, f\u233?yo taufrongi m\u233?inyotiom\u233?n tane m\u233?rnat. Yau njam k\u225?y\u225?rang\u233? tane m\u233?rnoene sian, f\u233?yo yau y\u225?ut\u225?nati t\u233?frangongi nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? T\u233?ndo \u225?r a yaufi mani kaf\u233?gh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
