F\u233?yo Yesu norayai, "Y\u233?ndo so ewaufrotan si m\u233?n\u225?t so tawauyafon ndern\u225?ye njafar lim\u225?n\u233?gh y\u233?m. Warsagh \u225?r ewanmoi y\u225?njo f\u225?iofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tanmorw\u233?n a mani fai tawangongay\u233?nd n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mofem t\u233? ewanay\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
