Y\u233?mo yau so tawafangotau, f\u233?yo warsagh \u225?rom y\u233?mndai nden\u233? f\u225? a y\u225?t\u233?n a y\u225?ne ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r a y\u225?ne m\u233?inyotio rokar s\u225?i tat\u233?rnau maniot y\u225?ne fai wangogh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
