\u193?mb \u225?r y\u233?nmorm\u233?n a namotai, "Watamegh \u225?r, n\u233?m\u233? mer y\u233?ndon so yafrotan m\u233?n\u225?t tuot gh\u233?rs\u233? r\u233?sagh\u233?t?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Yesum yawangoy\u233?ng, "N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mo namota meryamm\u233?n? Yau efe mer y\u233?m m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n f\u225?ro. F\u233?m njam m\u233?nde n\u233?m tuot gh\u233?rs\u233? r\u233?sagh\u233?t, ewafrota n\u233?m\u233? n\u225?k noraye."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
