\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum yawangoi, "Yau \u225?r esmeta; yau awan\u233?gh; oro yau; yau uny\u233?ghe nafrota \u225?mb \u225?rfenem\u233?n; {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
eutmanw\u233? af\u233? am\u233?; euweta fenjo kaka \u225?r nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?myo."
