Wem\u225?r tot\u233?r \u225?rom yawangoi, "M\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? n\u225?k y\u233?ndon tawarawenan. N\u233?m\u233? w\u233?t tafaf n\u225?l\u225?itat?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Yesum y\u233?mnday\u233?ng f\u225?, "Njam f\u233?m m\u233?nde n\u233?m f\u233?w\u233?nf\u233?w\u233?nofnarot, kuwano a et\u233?rna maniot fene m\u233?inyotio rokar fene n\u233?m\u233? em a ewarameta mani yauyau \u225?r\u233?t, a fene ngonj\u233?l so nawamndat njafaran, f\u233?yo k\u233?naf, y\u233?nd kw\u233?nmaito."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Njam tot\u233?r \u225?rom y\u233?n\u233? si n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?ng, f\u225? w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? n\u233?ngwanoy\u233?ng, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n ndimbal wem\u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Yesum t\u225?f norayai y\u225?njo waitogh \u225?rfefaf, "Y\u233?ndon efalo emndetan: nder\u233? t\u225?ik\u233?r so y\u233?m wem\u225?r \u225?r\u233?t \u233?laugh\u233?t njafar lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Y\u233?ndon kor emndetan: kameloe lil f\u233?ne \u233?laugh\u233?t t\u225?ik\u233?r y\u233?m, w\u233?nde wem\u225?r \u225?roe k\u233?t\u225?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u233?laugh\u233?t siy\u233?m minde t\u225?ik\u233?r y\u233?m a y\u225?ne k\u233?rt\u233? yamam so taindang\u233? y\u233?n\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Njam waitogh \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? si n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd, f\u225? minde s\u233?lngw\u233?l emorm\u233?n a namotay\u233?nd, "F\u233?yo efe w\u233?t so ngunjarngi?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Yesum mbark\u225?ndaye engfanday\u233?ng f\u225? a ewawangoi, "Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m f\u233?yotarofnar y\u233?m \u225?r\u233?t, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne m\u233?inyotio yam f\u233?yotaro em."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Fitam t\u233?mndang\u233?, "K\u233?reta, y\u233?ndfem rokar m\u233?inyotio t\u233? tan\u233?urotam fe waitogh\u233?t! F\u233?yo n\u233?m\u233? w\u233?t y\u233?ndfem so tawanang\u233?m?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Yesum emndai f\u225?, "Y\u233?ndon efalo emndetan, njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so tawafrotang\u233? m\u233?inyotio rokar t\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? tot\u233?r, \u193?roene Ambum so k\u225?mnjong\u233? y\u225?njo ndimbal kwayaghaf\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifayan, nden\u225?yo f\u233?m tane tuwelf waitogh \u225?r so k\u225?mnjongi lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233?, m\u233?n\u225?t Israilm\u233?n tuwelf m\u233?r\u233?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
A \u225?mb \u225?r emo t\u233?frangong\u233? y\u225?njo m\u233?ngo o yanaf o m\u233?r\u233?sof o y\u225?refaf o y\u225?tmaf o ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r o ndau tane t\u233?fnan, so tawanang\u233? fai 100 mbinotm\u233? a so taraman tuot akegh gh\u233?rs\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
W\u233?nde t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r efe s\u233?nonjo fronde em so k\u233?namndangi soram\u233?, a efe s\u233?nonjo soram\u233? em so k\u233?namndangi fronde.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 20
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 \u193?s\u225?fogh \u225?r g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndawan
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
"Njafar lim\u225?n\u233?gh siy\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?m. Mband yur\u233? t\u225?nd\u225?i akwan nuwanoi \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?t mani \u225?s\u225?fogh ramgh\u233?t y\u225?ne g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndawot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?mon yiy\u225?toi y\u233?fe fai ramgh\u233?t, \u225?mbiro efoghm\u233?n t\u250?m\u233?n fai, a ew\u225?f\u225?retai f\u225? \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t y\u225?ne w\u233?n mbwe m\u233?nj ndawot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
"F\u225? kor w\u233?i nuwanoi k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?rar\u233?gh sifayafaf t\u225?f 9 aklok a ewinjoi \u225?mb \u225?r tawakayong\u233?rw\u233?n \u225?s\u225?foghofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mon tamndang\u233?, 'F\u233?m w\u233?i nguwanongi n\u225?s\u225?fotati w\u233?n mbwe m\u233?nj ndawan, a y\u233?ndon so fai ewarametan mbark\u225?nde.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? nuwanoy\u233?nd. T\u225?f efoghm\u233?f 12 aklok a kor 3 aklokan y\u233?n\u233?yamyo y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n t\u233?rar\u233?gh sifayat a \u225?mb \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r kor ekafai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Kaka k\u225?y\u225?totau 5 aklok njam f\u225? yiotam k\u233?t\u225?n t\u233?rar\u233?gh sifayat a ewinjoi \u225?mb \u225?r m\u233? tawakayong\u233?rw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233?. Y\u233?mon emotai, 'N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m \u225?s\u225?foghofnar efogh tomb\u233? ewakai?'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
"Y\u233?mofem yawangoy\u233?nd, 'Emon \u225?mb yau mani \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t y\u233?n\u233?mnde.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Y\u233?mon emndai f\u225?, 'F\u233?yotaro f\u233?m nguwanongi \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndawot.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
"Njam f\u233?r\u233?gh n\u225?y\u225?toi, yuram y\u233?mndai y\u225?njo wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r, 'Tamota \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r a fai ewarameta, k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? efe \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t soram\u233? nufnyay\u233?nd a kefong\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n efe \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t fronde nufnyay\u233?nd.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emofem \u225?s\u225?fogh yafngoy\u233?nd t\u225?f 5 aklokan y\u233?fe fai ewaramay\u233?ng \u225?mbiro efoghm\u233?n t\u250?m\u233?n fai \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiroe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo njam y\u233?n\u233? fronde \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r enmorm\u233?n fai r\u233?sagh\u233?t nden\u233? kemnaw\u233?t y\u233?mofem kar so tuk\u233?n fai tawanangay\u233?nd. W\u233?nde y\u233?mofayo \u225?mbr\u233?rero \u225?mbiro efoghm\u233?n fairo tarsaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Njam y\u233?mofem ewanay\u233?nd y\u233?fenjo mani a mikemike nufngoy\u233?nd yurafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
'Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r k\u225?s\u225?fotat \u225?mbiro efoghf\u233?nef\u233?nero, w\u233?nde f\u233?mo fai tawafrote nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?mo k\u233?s fai y\u233?nd t\u233?nmafrote efe k\u225?s\u225?fotam \u225?mbiro m\u233?inyo efogh efoghwaftayan.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Yuram yawangoi \u225?mb \u225?roe, 'Koy\u225?r\u233?, f\u250?tar. Y\u233?nd f\u233?fefaf kw\u233?m \u225?mbr\u233?rero. F\u233?mo yiy\u225?to \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t \u225?mbiro efoghm\u233?n t\u250?m\u233?n faiot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
S\u233?nonjo tawan fene fai a nguwano m\u233?ngot. Y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? \u225?roe fai ramgh\u233?t soram\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r \u225?mbr\u233?rero y\u233?ndon fe k\u233?s n\u233?maraman. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Tane mbark\u225?nd y\u233?m y\u233?nd n\u233?m\u233? m\u233?nde w\u233?m wafrogh\u233?t tane manie! O f\u233?m m\u233?ndm\u233?nd em m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd mer \u225?r w\u233?m ram\u233?ghan?'"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
"A Yesum wifogh\u233?tro si norayai, "Efe soram\u233? em so em fronde, a efe fronde em so em soram\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum korayau nambiom\u233?n si y\u225?njo k\u233?rm\u233?n
