Njam Yesu tiyotaw\u233?ng k\u233?t\u225?n Jerusalem\u233?t, y\u233?mon ewasroi y\u225?njo 12 waitogh \u225?r ewimndai t\u233?ndot a tamndang\u233? f\u225? y\u233?fembiayan, njamandio tayotaw\u233?ng endm\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?mon tamndang\u233? f\u225?, "K\u225?y\u225?rangi, y\u233?nd y\u233?nyote k\u233?t\u225?n Jerusalem\u233?t, \u225?nde \u193?roene Ambum so t\u233?ramangi k\u233?t\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?rfefaf a n\u225?k watamegh \u225?rfefaf. F\u225? so korayangi f\u225? f\u233?t\u233? so k\u233?r y\u233?m {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
a tramangi k\u233?t\u225?n T\u233?ndo \u225?rfefaf, emofem so m\u233?ndm\u233?nd yawafrotat, y\u233?fmotat, a tamangi wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nan. W\u233?nde nambio efogh soram\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so tanong\u233? gh\u233?rsat.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Amane \u243?mneng\u233?gh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
F\u233?yo Jefediene ambum, Jems a Jon y\u233?fene am\u233? y\u233?nmorm\u233?n Yesuefaf y\u225?njo s\u243?mbio ambumof\u233?, y\u225?wefnoy\u233?nd s\u225?fr\u233?re y\u225?yot, a y\u233?motay\u233?nd Yesu y\u225?ne m\u233?nde wafrogh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Yesum y\u233?motai, "N\u233?m\u233? wafrogh\u233?t f\u233?m m\u233?nde n\u233?m?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Amafom yawangoi, "Uny\u233?ghofnar si kwaram ta so tane s\u243?mbio ambum taumuy\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t so emorare \u225?mb fatrata \u225?mb tamb\u233?nta njam f\u233?mon warsagh \u225?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n tan\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
