W\u233?nde njam y\u233?nd korayang\u233?m, 'K\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? \u225?rta,' y\u233?nd f\u233?rf\u233?r y\u233?n\u233?m \u225?r\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? m\u233?t\u233? yafrotat, m\u233?nam\u233?n m\u233?inyotio \u225?r kemnaw\u233?t nden\u233? Jon f\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem yawangoy\u233?nd Yesue, "Y\u233?nd mafina y\u233?n\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 A f\u225? norayai y\u233?fefaf, "Y\u233?ndon nden\u225?yo w\u233?i yau so tawaufron n\u233?m\u233? muyayan y\u233?ndon ewafrotan y\u233?n\u233? yam."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Rengerenge si s\u243?mbio ambumm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
"Ndern\u225?ye w\u233?t f\u233?m nemnati y\u233?n\u233? rengerenge sim\u233?n? K\u233?t\u233? \u225?mb \u225?r t\u233?morw\u233?n endene ambum t\u225?rw\u233?n s\u243?mbio. F\u225? nuwanoi fronde s\u233?nko ambumoefaf a norayai, 'Ambum, nguwano \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndawot s\u233?nonjo.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Y\u233?mon yawangoi, 'Y\u233?nd yau m\u233?nde w\u233?m.' W\u233?nde soram\u233? y\u233?mon mwigh\u233? y\u225?itoi a nuwanoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?feraf\u233? n\u233?nwanoi k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb ambumoefaf a norayai nden\u233? sio. Y\u233?mon yawangoi, 'F\u233?yotaro, af\u233?." W\u233?nde f\u225? yau n\u233?ngwanoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
\u193?rk\u233? ambumom k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? s\u243?mbiota yiy\u225?rai n\u233?mat y\u233?feraf\u233? m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mofem yawangoy\u233?nd, "Fronde s\u233?nko ambum."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 F\u233?yo Yesu norayai y\u233?fefaf, "Y\u233?ndon efalo emndetan f\u233?m, mani kaf\u233?gh \u225?r a tukal amaf so em k\u233?t\u225?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh f\u233?fe frondeta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n Jon walitogh \u225?r y\u233?nmorm\u233?n f\u233?fefaf tawauyafotau mbark\u225?nd end f\u233?feyot r\u233?sagh\u233?t, a f\u233?mofem yau efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd f\u225?, w\u233?nde mani kaf\u233?gh \u225?r a tukal amafam efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd f\u225?. T\u225?f njam f\u233?mofem yinjoy\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? yam, f\u233?m yau nawengoy\u233?nd a efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd.
