\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Yesu norayay\u233?ng, "K\u225?y\u225?rangi \u225?mb rengerenge si. K\u233?t\u233? \u225?mb mband Yur\u233? emon yeitam g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndau m\u233?n\u225?t mbwe anogh\u233?t k\u233?t\u233?, \u225?r\u225?ke yurnam, y\u233?kw y\u233?tanam m\u233?n\u225?t g\u233?reif mbwe tumang\u233?gh\u233?t a tuk gh\u233?k\u233?f fayogh m\u233?ngo kitar\u233? y\u233?rametam. F\u233?yo y\u233?mon y\u233?ramai watma g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndau k\u233?t\u225?n ndau t\u233?fn\u225?rafefaf m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mo so ewinjote \u225?mb g\u233?reif mbwe y\u233?n\u233? ndauta a f\u225? nuwanoy\u233?ng nayu yuwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Njam \u225?rnogh efogh nawerai, \u225?mb faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r engw\u225?f\u225?retam ndau t\u233?fn\u225?rafefaf m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tawinjongay\u233?nd \u225?mb g\u233?reif mbwe y\u233?n\u233? ndauta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?mofem eweray\u233?nd y\u225?ne faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, \u225?mb y\u233?fmotam\u233?nd, \u225?mb y\u233?smetam\u233?nd krotio, w\u237?me \u225?mb tafiy\u225?totaw\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
"F\u233?yo w\u233?ikor y\u233?mon \u225?mb t\u225?rf\u225?r faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r ew\u225?f\u225?retam, ndau t\u233?fn\u225?ram nden\u233?yameyo tawafrotaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Soram\u233?fifi y\u233?mon y\u225?f\u225?retam y\u225?njo ambum k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?fefaf. F\u225? norayay\u233?ng, 'Efaloe y\u233?mofem so yut\u233?mndat tane ambum.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
W\u233?nde njam ndau t\u233?fn\u225?ram yinjoy\u233?nd ambum, y\u233?mofem norayay\u233?nd y\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?nro, 'Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m Yurane ambum. K\u233?naflangi, so y\u233?smetam f\u225?, a m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?n\u233? ndau so kamndang\u233? t\u233?fene!' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem yeray\u233?nd f\u225?, yitam\u233?nd g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndau t\u233?ndota, a krotio y\u233?smetam\u233?nd."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Yesum emotai, "F\u233?yo, njam g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndau yur\u233? n\u233?nangota, n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon so yafrote ndau t\u233?fn\u225?rafefaf?
