Yesu kor m\u233? korayau, "F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon emndetan f\u233?m, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh so tawakawang\u233? f\u233?feyot a tawaramang\u233? \u225?r\u233?t emofem efunat mer mbwe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
\u193?rk\u233? \u225?r njam kuyang\u233? y\u233?n\u233? w\u237?man so natyane kar\u233?fkarfot a f\u225? endefaf njam kuyang\u233? so y\u233?farne."
