Lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r a Farasi \u225?r\u233?m njam n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd Yesuene rengerenge si a mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd nden\u233? y\u233?mon korayaw\u233?ng y\u233?fenem\u233?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
f\u233?yo y\u233?mofem wergh\u233?t Yesu t\u233?rametaw\u233?t. W\u233?nde f\u225? f\u233?rf\u233?r tamorw\u233?n \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n, emofem nemnat nden\u233? f\u225? siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r.
