"Njafar lim\u225?n\u233?gh ndenanit y\u233?m. K\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n warsagh \u225?r emon y\u233?frendam\u233?ng awer\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?nd njamke y\u225?njo ambumoenem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u225?njo faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r ew\u225?f\u225?retam y\u233?fe wasrogh\u233?t efe t\u233? eng\u233?mndai fronde, w\u233?nde f\u225? yau m\u233?nde tamorw\u233?n \u225?ligh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
