\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
"W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? wan t\u233?fn\u225?r efe t\u233? eng\u233?mndai fronde yau namnyoy\u233?nd \u225?ligh\u233?t a f\u225? nuwanoy\u233?nd y\u233?fenjo m\u233?ndef\u233? yam wafrogh\u233?t: \u225?mb nuwanoi y\u225?njo ndaufaf, \u225?mb y\u225?njo s\u233?tuwafaf, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
t\u225?f \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m eweray\u233?nd y\u225?ne faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, ngi ewafngoy\u233?nd, a esmetam\u233?nd f\u225? krotio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Warsagh \u225?r minde n\u233?kw t\u233?morw\u233?n. F\u233?yo y\u233?mon y\u225?njo fiyar\u233? ew\u225?f\u225?retam y\u233?n\u233? tesenot \u225?nde y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r tamorang\u233?rw\u233?n. Y\u233?mofem esmetam\u233?nd \u225?r emofem esmetam\u233?nd warsagh \u225?roene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r a ewas\u233?rmbotam\u233?nd y\u233?fene tesen f\u233?se.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
"F\u233?yo y\u233?mon emotai y\u225?njo faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r a tamndang\u233? f\u225?, 'Tane awer\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?nd freng\u233?ghkaf y\u233?m, w\u233?nde \u225?r efe y\u233?ndon eng\u233?mndan f\u225? f\u233?yotarofnar em s\u225?i en\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
S\u233?nonjo tang\u233?m t\u250?m\u233?n endfaf a tan\u233?mndangi t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r t\u233?m\u233?ndfaf njam tawinjongi.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r nuwanoy\u233?nd end\u233?t a engwasrotam\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio \u225?r efe t\u233? ewinjoy\u233?nd, mer a yaufi \u225?r, a awer\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?nd m\u233?ngo \u225?r\u233?m nofayoy\u233?ng.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
"Warsagh \u225?r n\u233?ngaflai wan t\u233?fn\u225?r fandagh\u233?t. Y\u233?mo yinjoi \u225?mb \u225?r efe yau tawong\u233?rw\u233?n awer\u233?gh s\u225?l\u225?me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Warsagh \u225?rom y\u233?motay\u233?ng, 'F\u250?tar, ndern\u225?ye f\u233?m y\u233?na n\u233?m awer\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?nd s\u225?l\u225?mefnar?' W\u233?nde \u225?rom yau nuwangoy\u233?ng.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
