F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem y\u233?fenjo waitogh \u225?r engw\u225?f\u225?retam\u233?nd Yesuefaf a \u225?mb \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Erodene m\u233?r\u233?nta a korayangi, "Watamegh \u225?r, y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?m sn\u233?m efalo si afrogh \u225?r. F\u233?mon ewatamete efalo si n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?nde y\u233?m \u225?r\u233?t. F\u233?m yau f\u233?rf\u233?r n\u233?m \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? nemnat fenem\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mo m\u233?inyotio \u225?r efande \u225?mbiror\u233?ran. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
F\u233?yo t\u233?nmaufro t\u233?feyot, ndern\u225?ye w\u233?t f\u233?m nemne? Y\u233?n\u233? mbark\u225?nd y\u233?m mani ram\u233?ghm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n Rom tuk warsagh \u225?r, Kaisarefaf o yau?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
W\u233?nde Yesu mat n\u225?y\u225?toi y\u233?fene yaufi mwigh\u233? a f\u225? norayai, "F\u233?m farun mer n\u233?retati w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau em. N\u233?mam\u233?n ta f\u233?mofem uny\u233?gh sie ur\u233?r wakeindati? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Kw\u233?mauyafend ta mani mbwe \u225?rk\u233? mani ram\u233?gh f\u225?yot!"
