Y\u233?mofem yawangoy\u233?nd, "Kaisarene."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 F\u233?yo Yesu norayai y\u233?fefaf, "Kaisare taramangi y\u225?ne n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m, a Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne taramangi y\u225?ne n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m."
