\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 \u193?mogh si m\u233?nam\u233?n k\u233?rta anoghm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghonyo \u225?mb Saduki \u225?r enmorm\u233?n Yesuefaf \u225?mogh\u233?t. Y\u233?mofem efalo tiy\u225?totaw\u233?t nden\u233? \u225?r k\u233?rta yau so nanotat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u225? korayangi, "Watamegh \u225?r! Moses\u233?m y\u233?farotam n\u225?k nden\u233? njam efe \u225?r ambumofnar k\u233?r y\u233?m, y\u225?nng\u233?nom f\u233?t\u233? so kwir\u233? kawerang\u233? a ambum eunjeta yanai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Y\u233?na tamorang\u233?rw\u233?n 7 ambum t\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n. Fronde s\u233?nkom nawerai a k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n ambumofnar, f\u233?yo y\u233?mon y\u233?frangoi kwir\u233? y\u225?nngnoe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Y\u233?namayom nawerai a k\u233?r y\u233?morw\u233?n, a nambiom\u233?n nawerai. N\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?notio sefenm\u233?n efe t\u233?morw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Soram\u233? amaf k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
T\u225?f y\u233?n\u233? efghon njam \u225?r k\u233?rta nanotat gh\u233?rsat, endene amaf so y\u233?m? M\u233?nam\u233?n m\u233?inyotioam t\u233? naweretam\u233?nd f\u225?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Yesum ewawangoy\u233?ng y\u233?feyot, "F\u233?fene mwigh\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m. M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m yau mat em Buk si a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene waft\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Njam k\u233?r \u225?r kanongi gh\u233?rsat, f\u225? nden\u233? so em njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r njafaran a yau so naweretat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
K\u233?rta angoghm\u233?n gh\u233?rsat, f\u233?mofem t\u233? yaftam\u233?nd n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam emndai f\u233?m? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n norayam, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
'Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Ebraamene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, Aisekene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a Jeikofene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n.' F\u225? siy\u233?m gh\u233?rs\u233? \u225?rfene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u233?m, yau k\u233?r \u225?rfene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Njam \u225?r m\u233?rnam n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?, f\u225? emorm\u233?n s\u233?lngw\u233?l y\u225?ne watameghm\u233?n.
