Njam Farasi \u225?r n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd nden\u233? Yesum t\u233? ekmboy\u233?ng Saduki \u225?r, Farasi \u225?r m\u233?rne n\u225?umenday\u233?nd, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
a \u225?mb Farasi \u225?r efe t\u233?morw\u233?n n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r, kemnau Yesue \u225?mogh sie ufogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u233?motai, "Watamegh \u225?r! \u193?rk\u233? n\u225?kam ewainde \u225?mb n\u225?k?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "'Yuweta fenjo Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n m\u233?inyotio fenjo tikfe, m\u233?inyotio fenjo mb\u233?rmb\u233?re, m\u233?inyotio fene mwighaye.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m fronde a minde ndimbal n\u225?k y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
Y\u233?namayo minde ndimbal n\u225?k siy\u233?m, 'Euweta fenjo kaka \u225?r nden\u233? f\u233?myo ndern\u225?ye n\u225?uwete.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? s\u243?mbio n\u225?k ere m\u233?inyotio Mosesene n\u225?k a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?rfene watameghene t\u233?f\u233?n ere."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 \u193?mogh si Kerisoenem\u233?n
