Njam \u225?mb Farasi \u225?r n\u225?umenday\u233?nd m\u233?rne, Yesum emotay\u233?ng, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
"Ndern\u225?ye w\u233?t f\u233?m nemnati y\u233?n\u233? Kerisoenem\u233?n? \u193?rk\u233? \u225?kim\u233?n f\u225? y\u233?m?"
