\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
'Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n noraye k\u233?t\u225?n tane Yurafaf:
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 K\u225?mnjo y\u233?nandm\u233? tane tamb\u233?nta
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u233?ndon fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r t\u225?kman fene kafkaf mbanmbanan.'
\par\pard\plain \s61\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
Deifid\u233?m njam y\u233?mndeta Keriso 'Yur\u233?,' ndern\u225?ye so y\u233?n\u233? Keriso y\u233?m y\u225?ne \u225?kiambum?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
