\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum mat t\u225?y\u225?totau n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r a Farasi \u225?rfenem\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
F\u233?yo Yesu korayau \u225?r m\u233?rnafefaf a y\u225?ne waitogh \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
"N\u225?k watamegh \u225?r a Farasi \u225?r em waftaf\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t Mosesene n\u225?koene fifi wafergh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?m t\u225?f so n\u225?y\u225?retati a ewaitotati m\u233?inyotio n\u233?mat y\u233?mofem njam emndetat wafrogh\u233?t, w\u233?nde yau t\u225?f y\u233?fene yam wafrogh nuf\u233?nmetati, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mofem yau wafrogh yaman y\u233?kmetat n\u233?m\u233? ewatametat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?mofem tafayongi k\u233?rt\u233? \u225?rfene faderan \u225?rk\u233? em k\u233?rt\u233? a r\u233?sagh\u233?t t\u225?ik\u233?r, w\u233?nde y\u233?fene w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh ng\u225?ng\u233? yau y\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? r\u233?sagh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
"Y\u233?mofem m\u233?inyotio yam ewafrotat m\u233?n\u225?t nden\u233? \u225?r\u233?m so efandat f\u225?. F\u225? ewawo n\u233?mbnar boks m\u233?nayaf\u233? faroghkaf Buk si m\u233?nj y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?n, w\u233?nde y\u233?mofem engwafrotat y\u233?n\u233? boks minde ndimbale. Y\u233?mofem eumbetat tomb\u233? say\u233?rsay\u233?r s\u225?l\u225?meyan! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?mofem t\u250?m\u233?n m\u233?ndef\u233? efandat utman\u233?gh sifay\u233? t\u233?m\u233?ndfaf a merfifi \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngom\u233?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
y\u233?fene \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? y\u233?m \u225?r\u233?m s\u225?i esmetat t\u233?rar\u233?gh sifayam\u233? a s\u225?i emndetat 'Watamegh \u225?r.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
"\u193?r\u233?m yau t\u225?f ewanmotat 'watamegh \u225?r,' m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m \u225?mbr\u233?rero em a m\u233? \u225?mbiro Watamegh \u225?r y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
A f\u233?mofem yau t\u225?f y\u233?mndetati \u225?mb \u225?r y\u233?na mband maratan 'Af\u233?,' m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fene Af\u233? njafaran siy\u233?m \u225?mbiroro y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Yau \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m t\u225?f ewanmotat 'Lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r,' m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fene m\u233? f\u225?ro a \u225?mbiro lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Minde tuk\u233?n \u225?r f\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n s\u225?i y\u233?m f\u233?fene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Efe f\u225?yo nawarmbote Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so t\u233?kmang\u233? yuwan, a efe yuw\u233?n y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so t\u233?kmang\u233? tuk\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu korayau Farasi \u225?r a n\u225?k watamegh \u225?rfene m\u225?m\u225?fim\u233?n
