"Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m f\u233?feyot, n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r a Farasi \u225?r. F\u233?m farun mer n\u233?retati w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau. F\u233?mofem njafar lim\u225?n\u233?gh s\u233?safne y\u233?mnati \u225?rfene s\u225?fr\u233?re. F\u233?m f\u233?myo yau n\u233?lawangi, yau eumyotati f\u225? efe m\u233?nde em \u233?laugh\u233?t!{\super m{\footnote \pard\plain \s212\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22  {\super m}{{\cs214\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 23.14 }
