"Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m f\u233?feyot, n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r a Farasi \u225?r. F\u233?m farun mer n\u233?retati w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau. F\u233?m boute eyota arakafam\u233? a n\u233?f\u233?rmetati m\u233?inyotio yuwom\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?mbiro waitogh \u225?r winjogh\u233?t, a f\u233?mofem njam tinjongi y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r, f\u233?mofem minde yaufiaf\u233? tiy\u225?tongi k\u233?mboghofnar f\u233?s\u233?t, y\u225?ne yaufiyam tawaindang\u233? f\u233?fene yaufiyam!
