"Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m f\u233?feyot, kw\u233?fkw\u233?f lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r. F\u233?m watameghan em, 'Njam \u225?r noraya kw\u233?rnar si w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngoe, y\u233?mon f\u233?yotaro so erafne y\u225?njo si. W\u233?nde njam f\u225? noraya kw\u233?rnar si gole w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon, y\u233?mon t\u225?f yau so erafne y\u225?njo si.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Kw\u233?fkw\u233?f onon \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n! \u193?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? minde tuk\u233?n y\u233?m, gol o w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam tiy\u225?tong\u233? gol nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar? W\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u233?mofem w\u233?i ewatametati, '\u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom njam kw\u233?rnar si noraya gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitarae, y\u233?mon f\u233?yotaro so erafne y\u225?njo si. W\u233?nde emon njam kw\u233?rnar si noraya ram\u233?gh rokar gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitarayan, y\u233?mon t\u225?f yau so erafne y\u225?njo si.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u233?m kw\u233?fkw\u233?f \u225?r! \u193?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? minde tuk\u233?n y\u233?m, ram\u233?gh rokar o gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitar\u233? \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam ram\u233?gh rokar nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar tiy\u225?tong\u233?? Gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitarayam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde, njam \u225?rom gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitarae kw\u233?rnar si noraya, f\u225? siy\u233?m y\u233?naye kw\u233?rnar si noraye a m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? ram\u233?gh rokaran. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
A njam f\u225? kw\u233?rnar si noraya w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngoe, f\u225? kw\u233?rnar si noraye y\u225?njo w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngoe a Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne, efe y\u233?mor k\u233?t\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
A njam \u225?mb \u225?r kw\u233?rnar si noraya njafare, f\u225? kw\u233?rnar si noraye Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifayae a Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne efe y\u233?mor k\u233?t\u233?.
