"Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m f\u233?feyot, n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r\u233?t a Farasi \u225?r\u233?t! F\u233?m farun mer n\u233?retati w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau em. F\u233?mofem taramangi Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne \u225?mbiro tenm\u233?n ram\u233?gh w\u233?rw\u233?ran, n\u233?mbne rokar nden\u233? ngandar\u233?, m\u233?ng\u233?r \u225?rau, w\u233?nde f\u233?mofem ekarotati efalo ndimbal watamegh n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m n\u225?kan, nden\u233? mbark\u225?ndyam a gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisayam a ndimbal mwigh\u233?. F\u233?mofem t\u225?f so n\u233?mbnar rokarm\u233?n \u225?mbiro tenm\u233?n ram\u233?gh yafrotati, w\u233?nde w\u233?i so ewafrotati y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal yam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
