\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
"Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi f\u233?feyot, n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r a Farasi \u225?r. F\u233?m farun mer n\u233?retati w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau em. F\u233?mofem ew\u225?ny\u225?nyotati farutaro f\u233?fene kafusi a merekin, t\u225?f k\u233?nj\u250? siy\u233?m yaufi mwigh\u233? afoghkaf a nit\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
