"Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi f\u233?feyot, n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r a Farasi \u225?r\u233?t. F\u233?m farun mer n\u233?retati w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau em. F\u233?m nden\u233? em kwayagh\u233? faruta w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250? k\u233?rk\u233?f mb\u233?w\u233? m\u233?ngonit, \u225?rk\u233? n\u233?retat mer faruta w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250? siy\u233?m k\u233?r \u225?rfene sot afoghare a k\u233?rk\u233?f fifi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
