"Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi f\u233?feyot, n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r a Farasi \u225?r! F\u233?m farun mer n\u233?retati w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau em. F\u233?mofem ewafrotati m\u233? mer mb\u233?w\u233? m\u233?ngo y\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?rfene a ewamanetati y\u233?fene mb\u233?w\u233? m\u233?ngo f\u225? efe tamorang\u233?rw\u233?n mbark\u225?nd gh\u233?rsaye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
F\u233?m norayati, 'Y\u233?nd njam t\u233?nmorw\u233?n t\u233?fene \u225?kiafene efghon, y\u233?ndfem yau \u225?mb yam so tafrotaw\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mofem tawafrotaw\u233?t esmetam\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
F\u233?m efalo norayati nden\u233? f\u233?m em y\u233?n\u233? \u225?kim\u233?n emofem esmetam\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
F\u233?yo nguwanongi a m\u233? engwafrotati n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?fene \u225?kifem t\u233? yaufi tawafrotaw\u233?t!
