"F\u233?m kamban a kambanene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r! Ndern\u225?ye ende w\u233?t f\u233?m so kawanjarngi k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? f\u233?m k\u233?mboghofnar f\u233?s\u233?t s\u225?i eng\u233?m f\u233?fene yaufiyamm\u233?n? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Y\u233?ndon f\u233?m emndetan nden\u233? y\u233?ndon so engw\u225?f\u225?retan f\u233?feyot Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r a k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? \u225?r a watamegh \u225?r. F\u233?mofem \u225?mb so esmetati, enamndati wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nan, a efmotati \u225?mb k\u233?t\u233? \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngon a ewifnati k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? tesenta w\u233?i \u225?mb tesenot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Mbark\u225?nd \u225?rfene ngi t\u233?fn\u225?rafene t\u233?krat so y\u233?m f\u233?feyot, k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? mbark\u225?nd \u225?r Abel k\u233?t\u225?n Jakaraya Berekiane ambum, efe f\u233?mofem esmetam\u233?nd w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon a gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitar\u233? n\u233?ndk\u233?fan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
