"Jerusalem, Jerusalem! F\u233?mon t\u225?smetau Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r a w\u237?me tawafiyatotaw\u233?t si r\u233?sagh \u225?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam engw\u225?f\u225?retam f\u233?feyot! Nj\u233?namb mbinotm\u233? y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m tane ng\u225?ng\u233? wareng\u233?gh so y\u233?m fene \u225?r\u233?t, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? amaf kowiam t\u225?umendang\u233? y\u225?ne tos\u233?tos\u233? njamb mbanmbanan, w\u233?nde f\u233?mon y\u233?nd mat yau wiy\u225?to! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
