F\u225? norayai, "F\u233?yotaro, f\u233?mofem kor efandati y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?inyotio m\u233?ngo. Y\u233?ndon fem efalo emndetan nden\u233?, yau \u225?mb w\u237?m so y\u233?fai \u225?mb w\u237?man, m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? taran\u233?ghm\u233?n em."
