Yesum ewawangoy\u233?ng, "Mwigh\u233? s\u233?nt\u233?, yau \u225?mb \u225?rom t\u225?f ewawinda f\u233?fe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
T\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r so en\u233?m tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan n\u233?norayat, 'Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Keriso,' a so ewawindat t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?m so n\u225?y\u225?retati m\u233?km\u233?n kaka a afrogh si m\u233?km\u233?n nayum\u233?n, w\u233?nde f\u233?m f\u233?rf\u233?r yau em. Y\u233?n\u233? yam f\u233?t\u233? so nufrotat, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? fifi yau y\u233?m nden\u233? yatogh efogh t\u233? nawer. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
\u193?mb ndimbal yu so n\u225?smetat \u225?mb ndimbal yuaf\u233?, warsagh \u225?r lim\u225?n\u233?gh yu so n\u225?smetat \u225?mb warsagh lim\u225?n\u233?gh yuaf\u233?. K\u233?t\u233? so y\u233?m k\u225?uk\u225?u a sokrere f\u233?nat\u233? yuwom\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? yam so em ndenanit fronde t\u233?kr\u225?t y\u233?nau y\u233?m ambum \u225?r\u225?fghan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
"F\u233?m so tawerangi a ewas\u233?rmbotat a krot takmangi. M\u233?inyotio mband marat \u225?r m\u233?ndm\u233?nd so em f\u233?fefaf m\u233?nam\u233?n tane t\u233?fnan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghon, t\u225?rf\u225?ram so etarnat ndimbal mwigh\u233?, a so s\u233?n nufrotat a m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat nafandat f\u225?rof\u225?ro.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
"T\u225?rf\u225?r uny\u233?gh mat y\u225?togh \u225?r so nufanat a ewawindat t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? yaufioene \u225?s\u225?fogh maratan so em a \u225?rfene uw\u233?gh so k\u233?kmbong\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
W\u233?nde efe njam taikre nawereta kerker efoghtio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so kawanjarng\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? mer si njafar lim\u225?n\u233?ghm\u233?n so y\u233?ngwaitotat m\u233?inyotio mband maratan matot m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t, a f\u233?yo so y\u233?n\u233?m yatogh.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Minde m\u225?m\u225?fi yam
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
"F\u233?mofem so tinjongi 'Minde m\u225?m\u225?fi yam' Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r Daniel\u233?m \u225?rk\u233? korayau. Minde m\u225?m\u225?fi \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? so yakai yiy\u225?tota w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo m\u225?m\u225?fi." F\u233?r\u233?n matot waf\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?t: mat kamnd\u233? y\u233?n\u233? sioene fifi n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
"Efe njam Judian em t\u225?f n\u233?nng\u233?rsat t\u225?rf\u225?r mband tunakfot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r efe njam m\u233?ngo tuk\u233?n y\u233?fai yau t\u225?f k\u233?neworng\u233? rokar r\u233?sagh\u233?t m\u233?ngot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r efe njam ndawan y\u233?m yau t\u225?f ngangong\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me r\u233?sagh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Nder\u233? t\u233?kr\u225?t y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon so y\u233?m y\u233?feyot amafat efe suaf\u233? njam em a amaf efe fasri ambumaf\u233? s\u225?i em! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
So Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m yau so kenngo yunj\u233?f n\u233?ndk\u233?fan o Safatan! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
K\u233?rt\u233? y\u233?n\u233? efghon so y\u233?m minde tuk\u233?n m\u225?m\u225?fi \u225?nde nden\u233? yau y\u233?nmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? mband ufrogh k\u233?t\u225?notio s\u233?nonjo. Soram\u233? efghon \u225?mb nden\u233? yam yau so kor y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yau njam efogh t\u233?njfi t\u225?y\u225?tong\u233?, efe yau so kunjarng\u233?. W\u233?nde m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne wafer\u233?gh \u225?r t\u233?fnan, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam efogh so t\u233?njfi t\u225?y\u225?tong\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
"F\u233?yo, njam emon tamndang\u233? f\u233?m, 'K\u233?retangi, Keriso siy\u233?m' o 'K\u233?t\u233? k\u233?s y\u233?m,' yau t\u225?f efalo yiy\u225?totati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Uny\u233?gh Keriso a uny\u233?gh mat y\u225?togh \u225?r so en\u233?m. Y\u233?mofem minde tuk\u233?n f\u233?nat\u233? ufarogh yam wafrogh a s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam so ewafrotat m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?naye \u225?r so ewawindat m\u233?inyotio \u225?r, a w\u233?i Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene wafer\u233?ghm\u233?n \u225?r, y\u233?n\u233? njam f\u233?yotaro y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
K\u225?y\u225?rangi! Y\u233?ndon f\u233?m frondeyo t\u233? en\u233?mndetam\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
"O, njam \u225?r\u233?m tamndang\u233? f\u233?m, 'K\u233?retangi, f\u225? k\u233?t\u233? fanfne yuwon y\u233?m,' yau eng\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n; o y\u233?mofem tamndangi, 'K\u233?retangi, f\u225? k\u233?t\u233? m\u233?ngo s\u225?tayan y\u233?m,' efalo yau t\u225?f yiy\u225?totati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n \u193?roene Ambum so y\u233?n\u233?m ndenanit toya kwayagh\u233? y\u233?nau y\u233?m njafaran k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? werta k\u233?t\u225?n mbormbor tamb\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
"\u193?nde k\u233?r fifi y\u233?kmang, ndik\u225?k\u233? k\u233?t\u233? so n\u225?umendat.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 \u193?roene Ambumoene angoghm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
"Tekofnar was\u233?rmbogh efogh soram\u233?,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 efogh so t\u233?f\u233?rtang\u233? kw\u233?fit\u233?,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 nden\u225?yo gh\u233?rare kwayagh\u233? yau so y\u233?m,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 k\u233?nd so n\u233?nuitat k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? njafarta,
\par\pard\plain \s78\ql\fi-540\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 a njafarm\u233?n waftaf\u233? rokar so n\u225?s\u225?mbnetat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233? efghon \u193?roene Ambumoene ufar\u233?gh s\u225?f so kufarng\u233? njafaran, a \u225?r m\u233?inyotio mband maratan so nendat t\u225?f \u193?roene Ambum njam tinjongi njafar kwamkwaman y\u233?n\u233?m waftaf\u233? a ndimbal kwayaghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Suf\u233?r keyaf\u233? y\u233?mon so taw\u225?f\u225?retang\u233? y\u225?ne njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r m\u233?inyotio yu a m\u233?ngotuot m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?umeng\u233?gh\u233?t y\u225?ne wafer\u233?gh \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? \u225?mb mband maratoene yatogh k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mbfaf.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Tanangi matyam fig w\u233?nta
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
"Matyam tanangi fig w\u233?nta. Njam y\u225?ne kafekafe k\u233?namndangi w\u233?n \u225?rau ngarot a \u225?fr\u225?t a tot\u233?r mb\u233?m \u225?rau afiyar\u233?gh ngufngongi, f\u233?m mat kamndangi nden\u233? efogh yu siy\u233?m kaka y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Nden\u233? endeyo, f\u233?mofem njam tinjongi m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? yam f\u233?m so mat kamndangi nden\u233? \u193?roene Ambumoene angogh kw\u233?f kaka y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Y\u233?ndo emndetan y\u233?n\u233?: y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r sat\u233? yau so m\u233?inyotio k\u233?r em k\u233?t\u225?notio m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? yam nufrotat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Njafar a mband marat so kawaindangend, w\u233?nde tane si siy\u233?m yau so kawaindang\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Efe \u225?mb yau mat y\u233?m njam \u193?roene Ambum so n\u233?nangote
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
"Efe \u225?mb yau mat y\u233?m njam y\u233?n\u233? efogh o efoghf\u233?nef\u233?ne so ufroghan y\u233?m-yau njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r nden\u225?yo a yau Ambum w\u233?nde Afaro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
\u193?roene Ambumoene angogh siy\u233?m ndenanit n\u233?m\u233? nufrotam Noane efghon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghon soram\u233? k\u233?f\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n \u225?r njamke a nu n\u233?neyan, \u225?r a amaf kaweretaw\u233?t, k\u233?t\u225?n efogh nawerai Noa n\u233?lawai bout k\u233?nj\u250?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
F\u225? yau mat namnday\u233?nd n\u233?m\u233? so kufrotau k\u233?t\u225?notio k\u233?f\u233?ram ewalitotam m\u233?inyotio ewifoi. Nden\u233? yam so fiy\u233?m njam \u193?roene Ambum n\u233?nangota. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
T\u225?f y\u233?n\u233? efghon s\u243?mbio \u225?r \u225?s\u225?foghan so ere ndawan: \u193?roene Ambumom so t\u233?ngwanang\u233? \u225?mb \u225?r, \u225?mb so t\u233?frangong\u233? yambia. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
S\u243?mbio amaf k\u233?t\u233? so ere m\u233?rne biskar soghan: \u193?roene Ambumom so t\u233?ngwanang\u233? \u225?mb, \u225?mb so t\u233?frangong\u233? yambia. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Kor aem gh\u233?k\u233?f s\u233?nt\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m mafina em \u225?rk\u233? efghon f\u233?fene Yur\u233? so kufarng\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
Njam m\u233?ngo yur\u233? mat y\u233?m oro t\u233?fn\u225?roene efogh, f\u225? t\u225?f so m\u233? n\u233?rete y\u225?ne m\u233?ngo yau so k\u233?lawang\u233? oro t\u233?fn\u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?m t\u250?m\u233?n afreng\u233?ghkaf aem. \u193?roene Ambum so y\u233?n\u233?m t\u225?f f\u233?m yau s\u225?i nemnati y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?r ro o yau ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?r ro faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
"Efe y\u233?m ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?r ro a k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r? Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efe y\u225?ne yuram t\u233?kmang\u233? wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r \u225?mb faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r\u233?t s\u225?i ewarameta njamke freng\u233?ghkaf efghon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
Nder\u233? \u225?uw\u233?gh y\u233?n\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?roe njam y\u225?ne yuram tinjong\u233? y\u233?n\u233? yam wafroghan njam f\u225? n\u233?nangota m\u233?ngot! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
Efalo, y\u233?ndon f\u233?m emndetan, yuram so t\u233?kmang\u233? y\u233?n\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r m\u233?inyotio y\u225?ne rokar wanjeng\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
W\u233?nde njam f\u225? yaufi faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r y\u233?m, a korayang\u233? f\u225?yo, 'Tane yur\u233? yau so n\u233?nangote w\u233?keye,' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 49\~}
a y\u233?mon ewafngoi ngi y\u225?njo faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh f\u250?tar\u233?f njamke a w\u233?ri nu enetam w\u233?ri \u225?rf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 50\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?roene yur\u233? so n\u233?nangote y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon \u225?nde f\u225? yau so afreng\u233?ghkaf y\u233?m a yau nawanjete y\u225?yot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 51\~}
Yuram so y\u233?nfete ndimbulndimbul a t\u233?kmang\u233? k\u233?t\u233? \u225?nde f\u225? em efe farun mer n\u233?retat w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau. K\u233?t\u233? f\u225? so ye nendat a s\u233?n ek\u233?rnat.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 25
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Rengerenge si ten tot\u233?r amafenem\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon njafar lim\u225?n\u233?gh siy\u233?m ndenanit so y\u233?m. K\u233?t\u233? tamorw\u233?n ten yuwagia m\u233?r\u233?s emofem tarsaw\u233?t y\u233?fenjo lambef\u233? a nuwanoy\u233?nd amaf awer\u233?gh \u225?roe wanf\u233?gh\u233?t a nguwanongay\u233?nd y\u225?n\u233? awer\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?ndfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
\u193?mb 5 tamorw\u233?n ong\u233?n mwighayan, a \u225?mb 5 tamorw\u233?n k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? ong\u233?n mwighaf\u233? tot\u233?r m\u233?rsam ewanay\u233?nd lambef\u233? w\u233?nde yau ewanay\u233?nd \u225?mb farun oil, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
w\u233?nde 5 tamorw\u233?n k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? ewanay\u233?nd \u225?mb farun oil s\u233?fkw\u233?nan y\u233?fenjo lambefat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Amaf awer\u233?gh \u225?r som\u233? t\u233?siyong\u233?rw\u233?n, f\u233?yo f\u225? k\u233?mgham ewifoi a nakmay\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
"Njam s\u233?mb\u225?r n\u233?ndk\u233?f namndai ke t\u225?f y\u233?morm\u233?n, 'Snufar amaf awer\u233?gh \u225?r! K\u233?naflangi a tumyongi f\u225?!' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Ten m\u233?r\u233?s nanoy\u233?nd a tafrendaw\u233?t y\u233?fenjo lambef\u233? mer s\u225?i k\u225?s\u225?fotaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
F\u233?yo ong\u233?n mwighaf\u233? m\u233?rsam norayay\u233?nd y\u233?fefaf k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? m\u233?rsafefaf, 'T\u233?nmaramangi t\u233?fe \u225?mb f\u233?fenem\u233?n oil, m\u233?nam\u233?n t\u233?fene lambef\u233? umb\u233?rtogh\u233?tro em.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
K\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? m\u233?rsam ewawangoy\u233?nd, "Yau, so f\u233?yotarofnar y\u233?m f\u233?fe a t\u233?feyot. Nguwanongi k\u233?t\u225?n s\u233?tuat a tanwanangi \u225?mb f\u233?fendio.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo ong\u233?n mwighaf\u233? m\u233?r\u233?s nuwanoy\u233?nd \u225?mb oil r\u233?sagh\u233?t. Njamandio n\u233?nguwanoy\u233?nd, amaf awer\u233?gh \u225?r nufary\u233?ng, y\u233?n\u233? 5 efe afreng\u233?ghkaf kawanjetaw\u233?t n\u233?nglaway\u233?nd k\u233?nj\u250?t y\u233?maf\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n awer\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?ndfaf, a s\u233?safne namnai.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
"Soram\u233? \u225?mb ong\u233?n m\u233?r\u233?s nufary\u233?nd a f\u225? n\u243?mnenday\u233?nd, "Yur\u233?, yur\u233?! T\u233?nmasaw\u233?r s\u233?safne!' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Amaf awer\u233?gh \u225?rom ewawangoi, "Y\u233?ndo efalo emndetan, y\u233?nd mafina w\u233?m f\u233?m.'"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Yesum soram\u233? si norayai, "Mwigh\u233? s\u233?nt\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m yau mat em y\u233?n\u233? efogh o efoghf\u233?nef\u233?ne tane angoghm\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Rengerenge si nambio faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rfenem\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233? efghon y\u233?nd so n\u233?nangotan w\u233?ikor, njafar lim\u225?n\u233?gh siy\u233?m nden\u233? so y\u233?m. K\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?r efe \u225?ligh\u233?t nufngoi, y\u233?mon eumendai y\u225?njo faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r a tawarametau y\u225?njo mani y\u233?feyot wanjeng\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u233?mon mani ewarametam y\u233?fenjo \u225?s\u225?fogh muy\u233? f\u233?yotaroan: \u225?mb \u225?roe yaramai 5,000 gol mani mbwe, \u225?mb \u225?roe y\u233?ramai 2,000 gol mani mbwe, a \u225?mb \u225?roe 1,000 gol mani mbwe. Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? f\u225? nuwanoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r emon ewanai 5,000 gol mani mbwe yiotam tekofnaye. Y\u233?mo ersam w\u233?ikor mani wafrogh\u233?t. Njam y\u233?n\u233? yafrotam, y\u233?mo ewinjoi w\u233?ikor \u225?mb 5,000 gol mani mbwe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Nden\u233?yameyo w\u233?i \u225?mb faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r emon ewanai 2,000 gol mani mbwe ewinjoi w\u233?ikor \u225?mb 2,000 gol mani mbwe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r emon ewanai 1,000 gol mani mbwe yiotam, y\u233?kw natanam ey\u225?toi mbandan, a etnoi y\u225?ne yurane mani.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
"Soram\u233? tek awafing\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?n faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rfene yur\u233? n\u233?nangotam a mat tiy\u225?totaw\u233?t manim\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r ende yaramai 5,000 gol mani mbwe n\u233?lawai yaramai \u225?mb 5,000 gol mani mbwe a norayay\u233?ng, 'F\u233?mon waramai ta 5,000 gol mani mbwe, yur\u233?. Tafanda! Sem \u225?mb 5,000 gol mani mbwe \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?ndon t\u233? tafrotan.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Y\u225?ne yuram y\u233?mndai, "Mer \u225?s\u225?fogh, f\u233?m mer a ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?r ro faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r! F\u233?m ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?r ro k\u233?n\u233?m n\u233?mbne rokar wanjeng\u233?t, f\u233?yo y\u233?ndon so k\u233?n\u233?kman t\u225?rf\u225?r rokar wanjeng\u233?gh sifayan. K\u233?naf a y\u233?ndf\u233? \u225?uw\u233?gham so y\u233?nre!'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
"\u193?s\u225?fogh \u225?r ende yaramai 2,000 gol mani mbwe n\u233?lawai a norayai, 'F\u233?mon waramai ta 2,000 gol mani mbwe, yur\u233?. Tafanda! Sem \u225?mb 2,000 gol mani mbwe \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?ndon t\u233? tafrotan.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u225?ne yuram y\u233?mndai, "Mer \u225?s\u225?fogh, f\u233?m mer a ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?r ro faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r! F\u233?m ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?r ro k\u233?n\u233?m n\u233?mbne rokar wanjeng\u233?t, f\u233?yo y\u233?ndon so k\u233?n\u233?kman t\u225?rf\u225?r rokar mani wanjeng\u233?gh sifayan. K\u233?naf a y\u233?ndf\u233? \u225?uw\u233?gham so y\u233?nre!'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
"\u193?mb faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r ende y\u233?ramai 1,000 gol mani mbwe n\u233?lawai a norayay\u233?ng, 'Yur\u233?, y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m f\u233?m n\u233?m t\u225?ik\u233?r \u225?r; f\u233?mon etane fifi k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? \u225?nde f\u233?mon yau tiang a ekafete mbwe k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? f\u233?mon \u225?nde yau etarnam mbwe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Y\u233?nd f\u233?rf\u233?r kw\u233?m, f\u233?yo y\u233?nd wiotam a etnoy\u233?n fene mani mband k\u233?nj\u250?n. Tafanda! Sem n\u233?m\u233? fene em.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
"Y\u225?ne yuram y\u233?mndai, 'F\u233?m yaufi a sak\u233?r faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r! F\u233?m t\u233? mat k\u233?nmorw\u233?n nden\u233? y\u233?ndon etnam\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? \u225?nde y\u233?ndon yau eitam\u233?n, a eumendam\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?ndon \u225?nde etarnam\u233?n mbwe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
F\u233?yotaro y\u233?m f\u233?mon miya tanyawangai tane mani k\u233?t\u233? bankot, a y\u233?ndon t\u225?f so tawanangay\u233?n minagh maniaf\u233? njam k\u233?nangotaw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?yo mani tanwan y\u225? tamb\u233?n a taram y\u233?n\u233? \u225?roe efe y\u233?m 10,000 gol mani mbweyaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
K\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?n\u233? \u225?roefaf efe y\u233?m t\u225?rf\u225?r rokaraf\u233?, y\u233?ndo so taraman minde t\u225?rf\u225?r a y\u225?ne n\u233?m\u233? em so k\u233?namndangi minde t\u225?rf\u225?r. A y\u225?yot endene y\u233?m n\u233?mbnar, y\u233?ndo so takawan n\u233?m\u233? n\u233?mbnar y\u225?faf y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?n\u233? sak\u233?r faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, yitat y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r s\u233?mta k\u233?t\u225?n kw\u233?fitafaf, \u225?nde f\u225? so nende a y\u225?njo s\u233?n so ek\u233?rne.'
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ambinom\u233?n mogh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
"Njam \u193?roene Ambum n\u233?nangota nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? warsagh \u225?r a m\u233?inyotio njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?rf\u233?, f\u225? so k\u233?n\u225?mnjong\u233? y\u225?njo ndimbal kwayaghaf\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifayayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
\u193?r m\u233?inyotio ndimbal yuta t\u225?f so n\u225?umende y\u225? s\u225?fr\u233?re. F\u233?yo y\u233?mon s\u243?mbio m\u233?r\u233?n so tafale, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? sif wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?rom nder\u233? tafalong\u233? sif k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? gout tamb\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Y\u233?mon so t\u225?kmang\u233? mbark\u225?nd \u225?r y\u225?ne tamb\u233?nta a \u225?mb \u225?r y\u225?ne fatrata.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
"F\u233?yo Warsagh \u225?rom so korayang\u233? \u225?rfefaf efe em y\u225?ne tamb\u233?nta, 'K\u233?naflangi, f\u233?m efe tane Afam efrenday\u233?ng! K\u233?naflangi a k\u233?lawangi lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t \u225?rk\u233? freng\u233?ghkaf y\u233?m f\u233?feyot k\u233?tam\u233? mband marat ufrogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd njam siogh kw\u233?morw\u233?n f\u233?mofem kw\u233?manjnaw\u233?t y\u233?nd, nu siogh a f\u233?mofem kwaramangay\u233?nd nu, y\u233?nd wan t\u233?fn\u225?r kw\u233?morw\u233?n a f\u233?mofem kwumyongay\u233?nd y\u233?nd f\u233?fene m\u233?ngot, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
njam s\u225?l\u225?meofnar kw\u233?morw\u233?n, f\u233?mofem kwawongay\u233?nd s\u225?l\u225?me, a y\u233?nd njam enjne kw\u233?morw\u233?n f\u233?mofem kwanjetaw\u233?t y\u233?nd, a njam kw\u233?morw\u233?n kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon f\u233?mofem kwiyafotaw\u233?t y\u233?nd.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
"T\u225?f mbark\u225?nd \u225?r\u233?m so tawangongi y\u225?yot, 'Yur\u233?, njam y\u233?ndfem f\u233?m k\u233?nfandaw\u233?m siogh k\u233?nmorw\u233?n a k\u233?manjnay\u233?m njamke, o nu siogh k\u233?nmorw\u233?n, nu k\u233?maramangay\u233?m feyot? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Njam y\u233?ndfem k\u233?nfandaw\u233?m f\u233?m wan t\u233?fn\u225?r, k\u233?mumyongay\u233?m f\u233?m t\u233?fene m\u233?ngon, o njam s\u225?l\u225?meofnar k\u233?nmorw\u233?n awogh\u233?t, y\u233?ndfem k\u233?mawotaw\u233?m? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
Njam y\u233?ndfem k\u233?nfandaw\u233?m f\u233?m enjneyan o k\u233?t\u233? kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon, y\u233?ndfem k\u233?nyafotaw\u233?m f\u233?m? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Warsagh \u225?rom so tawawangong\u233?, 'Y\u233?ndon efalo emndetan, n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mofem tawafrotaw\u233?t \u225?mb n\u233?mbnar \u225?roe tane efalo y\u225?togh \u225?rm\u233?n, f\u233?mofem tafrotaw\u233?t tayot!'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
"F\u233?yo y\u233?mon w\u233?i so tamndang\u233? y\u233?n\u233? fatrata efe em, 'Nguwanongi ta tamb\u233?n, f\u233?m efe em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u233?kw mbanmbanan! Tang\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n tuot akegh f\u233?s\u233?t freng\u233?ghkaf \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m S\u225?if\u233?re a y\u225?ne yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Y\u233?nd njam siogh kw\u233?morw\u233?n f\u233?mofem yau kw\u233?manjnaw\u233?t y\u233?nd, nu sioghan, f\u233?mofem yau kwaramangay\u233?nd nu, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
a njam y\u233?nd kw\u233?morw\u233?n wan t\u233?fn\u225?r, f\u233?mofem yau kwumyongay\u233?nd y\u233?nd f\u233?fene m\u233?ngot, a njam s\u225?l\u225?meofnar kw\u233?morw\u233?n, f\u233?mofem yau kwawongay\u233?nd s\u225?l\u225?me, a y\u233?nd njam enjne kw\u233?morw\u233?n, f\u233?mofem yau kwanjetaw\u233?t y\u233?nd, a njam kw\u233?morw\u233?n kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon, f\u233?mofem yau kwiyafotaw\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
"F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem so tawangongi, "Yur\u233?, njam y\u233?ndfem k\u233?nfandaw\u233?m f\u233?m siogh o nu siogh o wan t\u233?fn\u225?r o firo o enjne o k\u233?t\u233? kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon, y\u233?ndfem yau k\u233?nm\u225?ut\u225?naw\u233?m fe?' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
Warsagh \u225?rom so tawawang\u233?, 'Y\u233?ndon efalo emndetan, njam f\u233?mofem yau t\u225?ut\u225?naw\u233?t \u225?mb n\u233?mbnar \u225?roe tane efalo y\u225?togh \u225?rm\u233?n, f\u233?mofem yau k\u225?ut\u225?naw\u233?t ta!'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
"F\u233?yo f\u225? so kuwanongi k\u233?t\u225?n k\u233?mboghofnar t\u233?kratfaf, w\u233?nde mbark\u225?nd \u225?r so eng\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n tuot akegh gh\u233?rsafaf."
