F\u233?m t\u225?f mat n\u233?m y\u233?ndo so tamnendang\u233?n tane Af\u233? ta w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t, a y\u233?mon so tekofnar enw\u225?f\u225?rete 72,000 minde t\u225?rf\u225?r njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n so nasmetat tayot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 54\~}
Y\u233?mofem so kwanjarngi. W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? yamm\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233? norayai Buk si k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n yau so nufrote. F\u233?yo so nufrote y\u233?n\u233? ende.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 55\~}
