Y\u233?mon ewaufroi, "Kwankwane mat Ng\u225?nj\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?ghm\u233?n f\u233?fe t\u233? ewaramay\u233?n, w\u233?nde \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?t siy\u233?m rengerenge sie {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t,
