Yesu norayai y\u233?fefaf, "F\u233?mofem t\u233? y\u225?yamngotati y\u233?n\u233? rengerenge si? Nder\u233? m\u233?n\u225?yan f\u233?m so mat k\u225?y\u225?tongi \u225?mb rengerenge si? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Ndau t\u233?fn\u225?ram t\u233?tarnau si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r nden\u233? em end t\u233?ndon \u225?nde si kuyang\u233?. Njamandio f\u225? k\u225?y\u225?rangi, S\u225?if\u233?r y\u233?n\u233?m si oroe eng\u233?rse \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? tatarnau y\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
\u193?mb nden\u233? em w\u237?m sifayan \u225?nde si kuyang\u233?, ka\u769?ya\u769?retaw\u233?t si a w\u233?keye tanangay\u233?nd \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? tamorw\u233?n s\u233?r\u233?mbofnar, y\u233?fene efalo yiy\u225?togh siy\u233?m tekofnar. Njam k\u233?rt\u233? o ufogh y\u233?n\u233?m m\u233?nam\u233?n sim\u233?n, f\u225? w\u233?keye kuyangi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r nden\u233? em mbandot mbwe \u225?rk\u233? kuyangi yus w\u233?tfaf, na\u769?ya\u769?retat si; {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
w\u233?nde f\u225? mband mwighayam wafogh ewafngoi. Mani mwighayam tawaweindau \u225?mb rokarot. \u193?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u225?yam si njang\u233?nnjang\u233?n tiy\u225?totau mbweofnayot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r nden\u233? em mer mbandan \u225?nde mbwe kuyangi, si n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd yumyoy\u233?nd a nafoi kw\u233?ki \u225?mb 30, \u225?mb 60 a \u225?mb 100."
