Yesum nden\u233?yameyo noyarai, "\u193?r yau nden\u233? nufarotat lambef\u233? sinan s\u225?i etnotat a yame mbanmbanan. W\u233?nde \u225?r\u233?m tafayongi lambef\u233? kitar\u233?kitarayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
K\u233?t\u233? siy\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? yau warambnoghm\u233?n y\u233?m, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? so kakmang\u233? marataye. N\u233?m\u233? t\u233?noghe y\u233?m saf\u233?n so kakmang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Njam t\u233?nganaf\u233? n\u233?m, ka\u769?ya\u769?r\u451?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
"Ka\u769?ya\u769?r merk\u233?r\u225?ye n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?m na\u769?ya\u769?rete\u451? Ndern\u225?ye ende f\u233?mon efrende \u225?mb \u225?r nden\u233? endeyo f\u233?m so n\u233?frendat, a minde tuk\u233?n mer so y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
F\u225? efe tane si na\u769?ya\u769?retat y\u233?fe minde matyam so tawaramang\u233?, w\u233?nde y\u233?feyot efe yau na\u769?ya\u769?retat n\u233?m\u233? n\u233?mbnar y\u233?fene matyam y\u233?m so tawakawang\u233?."
