Yesu kor norayai, "Ng\u225?nj\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh siy\u233?m ndenanit y\u233?m. \u193?r n\u233?wanoi mbwe taran\u233?gh\u233?t mbandot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
S\u233?mb\u225?ran a efghon, f\u225? k\u233?m\u233?gh y\u233?k\u233?m o kanong\u233?, mbwe k\u225?fyarng\u233? anoghafayo, f\u225? mafina y\u233?m ndern\u225?ye nanote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
M\u233?inyotio f\u225?yo mbandam y\u233?fune mbwe, fronde siy\u233?m mb\u233?m, soram\u233? siy\u233?m t\u233?f\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n afoghfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Njamandio \u225?rnogh w\u233?rw\u233?r kawerang\u233? a mbwe wau kayongi, f\u233?yo ndau t\u233?fn\u225?ram n\u233?f\u233?gh naifaye tawafngong\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Rengerenge si n\u233?mbne mbwem\u233?n
