W\u233?ikor Yesu norayai, "Y\u233?ndon so ewaufrotan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?ghm\u233?n rengerenge si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
