W\u233?nde njam tiyangi, so nanote minde ndimbal ndaum\u233?n njamke t\u233?f\u233?n k\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? a w\u233?n n\u225?y\u225?toi. Kafe yatene f\u233?yotaro menam \u225?nde nj\u233?n so erametat y\u225?ne njaran."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
