\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Kimb wanjeng\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r n\u233?tonam a kafrotau y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n tesenan a yu tunan, \u225?r n\u233?wanoy\u233?nd fandagh\u233?t n\u233?m\u233? yam kufrotau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Njam f\u225? enmorm\u233?n Yesuefaf, y\u233?mofem yinjoy\u233?nd \u225?r efe t\u233?morw\u233?n yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r afoghare, f\u225? t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n s\u225?l\u225?me umaneghaf\u233? a mer mwighaf\u233?, a f\u225? f\u233?rf\u233?r tamorw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
\u193?r emofem yinjoy\u233?nd ewafroy\u233?nd \u225?r\u233?t n\u233?m\u233? kufrotau yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r was\u233?rmbogh \u225?roenem\u233?n a w\u233?i ewaufroy\u233?nd kimbafenem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
\u193?r\u233?m yamnenday\u233?nd Yesu y\u233?fene yu frangogh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
