\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
W\u233?nde njam fa\u769? n\u233?ngretay\u233?nd tuk\u233?t, y\u233?mofem yinjoy\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? w\u237?m, a\u769?rk\u233? ndimbal t\u233?morw\u233?n t\u233? nit\u233?rmboi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Njam amaf mb\u233?w\u233? m\u233?ngon n\u233?laway\u233?nd, y\u233?mofem yinjoy\u233?nd tot\u233?r a\u769?r kwayagh\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me tawong\u233?rw\u233?n t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n amafafene tamb\u233?n ng\u225?ngata, a amaf f\u233?rf\u233?ram ewifoi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
W\u233?nde njafar si r\u233?sagh a\u769?rom emndai, "Yau f\u233?rf\u233?r em. F\u233?mofem efe y\u233?ronjati Yesu Najaretm\u233?n efe y\u233?namndam\u233?nd. Fa\u769? y\u233?na yau y\u233?m, k\u233?rta t\u233? nano. K\u233?retangi k\u233?t\u225?n y\u225?ne fifi \u225?nde y\u233?kmay\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
W\u233?nde kuwanongi, tawaufrongi y\u233?n\u233? si y\u225?ne waitogh \u225?rfet a Fit\u233?, 'F\u233?fe frondeta f\u225? t\u233? y\u233?ng\u233?m Galili yuwot. F\u233?mofem so tinjongi k\u233?t\u233?, ndern\u225?ye y\u233?mon fronde tamndetau."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Amaf n\u233?tory\u233?nd a n\u233?ngengoy\u233?nd mb\u233?w\u233? m\u233?ngo tamb\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? tamorw\u233?n ngernger mwighayan kow\u233?rsotaw\u233?t. Fa\u769? n\u233?m\u233? si yau norayay\u233?nd m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?rf\u233?r tamorw\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 T\u225?nd\u225?w\u225?r y\u225?togh mer sifaf 16.9-20
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu nufary\u233?ng Meri Makdalinefaf
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Njam Yesu nanoi k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? k\u233?rta Sande akwan, Yesu fronde nufary\u233?ng Meri Makdalinefaf, ende tamb\u233?n Yesum ewifnai 7 yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Amaf n\u233?wanoi Yesuene waitogh \u225?rfefaf, efe gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? tamorw\u233?n a ye kendaw\u233?t, a ewaufroi y\u233?fe n\u233?m\u233? kufrotau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
W\u233?nde njam y\u233?mon ewaufroi y\u233?fe nden\u233? Yesu gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?m, t\u233? yinjon, y\u233?mofem efalo yau yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu nufary\u233?ng s\u243?mbio waitogh \u225?rfefaf
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? Yesu nufary\u233?ng f\u233?nat\u233? s\u225?fot s\u243?mbio \u225?rfefaf njamandio fa\u769? tang\u233?rw\u233?n endm\u233? a\u769?mb yuwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Fa\u769? n\u233?ngwaneyay\u233?nd a\u769?mb waitogh a\u769?r\u233?t ewafroy\u233?nd y\u233?feyot n\u233?m\u233? kufrotau, w\u233?nde y\u233?mofem yau efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu nufary\u233?ng 11 waitogh \u225?rfefaf
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Soram\u233?fifi Yesu nufary\u233?ng 11 waitogh \u225?rfefaf njam y\u233?mofem njamke t\u225?netaw\u233?t. Y\u233?mon tamndetau m\u233?nam\u233?n ndimbal mwigh\u233? yau tawamorw\u233?n. F\u225? tik\u233?f t\u225?ik\u233?r tamorw\u233?n Yesue efalo y\u225?togh\u233?t emofem t\u233?fandaw\u233?t fa\u769? soram\u233? k\u233?rta nanoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Yesum fa\u769? emndai, "Kuwanongi m\u233?inyotio yuwom\u233?, mat engy\u225?totati Mer si m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Njam emofem efalo yiy\u225?totat a fa\u769? so ewalitotat, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so tawanjarng\u233?. W\u233?nde njam yau efalo yiy\u225?totat, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so tawaramang\u233? yaufioene fai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?ndon so ewarametan waft\u233? s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam wafrogh\u233?t m\u233?inyotio efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?t. Y\u233?mofem so yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r ewifnat tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan a fa\u769? so norayat \u225?mb \u225?rfene sie \u225?rk\u233? yau kotametaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?mofem ng\u225?ngaye kamban so eweretat, a y\u233?mofem k\u233?r nu njam enetat, n\u233?m\u233? yau so nufrote. Y\u233?mofem ng\u225?ng\u233? njam efayotat enjne t\u233?fn\u225?rfefaf, fa\u769? so mer n\u225?y\u225?totat."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Njam Yur\u233? Yesum si ewifoi y\u233?fefaf, fa\u769? ta\u769?f n\u233?nguyoi njafarot a n\u225?mnjoi Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene tamb\u233?n ng\u225?ngata. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
F\u233?yo waitogh \u225?r ta\u769?f nofarnay\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio yuwom\u233?, mat tangy\u225?totaw\u233?t mer si. Yur\u233? ka\u769?sa\u769?fotau y\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? a t\u225?rf\u225?r s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam tawafrotaw\u233?t. Y\u233?n\u233? yamam tuyafotau nden\u233? y\u225?ne si efalo t\u233?morw\u233?n.
