Y\u233?ndon t\u233? merk\u233?r\u225?ye t\u233?fandawan m\u233?inyotio yam k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? ufrogh, mer k\u233?retau tayot farogh\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t merk\u233?r\u225?ye nden\u233?fifi n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? kufrotau. Y\u233?ndon yafrotan feyot minde merfifi Tiafilus, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
