\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Jon walitogh \u225?r y\u225?ne \u225?r\u225?f\u233?ghm\u233?n si afrogh
