Y\u233?n\u233? efghon Erod njam t\u233?morw\u233?n Judiam\u233?n warsagh \u225?r, k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Jakaraya efe tafnyang\u233?rw\u233?n gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r Abiane m\u233?r\u233?n, y\u225?ne amaf Elisabet Aron \u225?kim\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Jakaraya a Elisabet Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene gh\u233?kfan mer gh\u233?rsaye tamorarw\u233?n, m\u233?inyotio Yurane n\u225?k tawaitogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
W\u233?nde ambumofnar tarw\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n Elisabet\u233?f mwinu t\u225?rw\u233?n, a f\u225? bulu n\u225?y\u225?teyay\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
\u193?mb efghon Jakarayane m\u233?r\u233?nta gh\u233?ng\u233?n \u225?s\u225?fogh efogh nawerai, y\u233?mon gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?s\u225?fogh y\u233?rnyai Ng\u225?nj\u225?n s\u225?fr\u233?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?fene t\u250?m\u233?n t\u233?mndan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam taferngai m\u233?n\u225?t mer wimaf\u233? rokar w\u225?rogh\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?n w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Njam efogh n\u225?werai mer wimaf\u233? rokar w\u225?rogh\u233?t, m\u233?inyotio \u225?r n\u225?umendam\u233?nd w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo sifayan Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oraigh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?yo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r nufary\u233?ng y\u225?faf, nokayoy\u233?ng gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh s\u233?ki tamb\u233?nta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Njam Jakarayam yinjoy\u233?ng, f\u225? s\u233?lngw\u233?l y\u233?morm\u233?n a f\u233?rf\u233?ram yifoy\u233?ng. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
W\u233?nde njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?rom y\u233?mnday\u233?ng, "Yau f\u233?rf\u233?r n\u233?m, Jakaraya, fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh si t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?rang. Fene amaf Elisabet so n\u233?sle ghak\u233?r ambum, f\u233?mon t\u225?f y\u233?tkw\u233?n taram Jon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u225? so y\u233?m \u225?uw\u233?gh a remngogh feyot, a t\u225?rf\u225?r so n\u225?uwetat m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne \u233?slaghm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u225? ndimbal so y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene gh\u233?kfan, w\u233?ri n\u233?nefnar a \u225?mb t\u225?ik\u233?r nu, a f\u225? so y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r wafoghkaf k\u233?t\u225?ndmayo \u233?slagh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
T\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r Israilm\u233?n y\u233?mon so ewangote k\u233?t\u225?n Yur\u233? y\u233?fenjo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
A f\u225? so y\u233?ng\u233?m Yurane frondeta, mb\u233?rmb\u233?ran a waftayan ndenanit Elaija k\u233?s t\u233?morw\u233?n, m\u233?n\u225?t afafene tik\u233?f wangogh\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?fenjo ambumafefaf, a aya\u769?r\u233?ghofnaye gh\u233?rsata wangogh\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?n k\u225?fet\u233?; efalo gh\u233?rsat t\u225?frendau Yurai."
