Jakarayam y\u233?motai njafar si r\u233?sagh a\u769?r, "Ndern\u225?ye w\u233?t y\u233?nd mat so kamndan y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n? Y\u233?nd sw\u233?m bulu w\u233?m a tane amaf siy\u233?m nden\u233?yameyo aus\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?rom yawangoi, "Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Geibr\u233?l. Y\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne kaka wakai a y\u233?nd kw\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?rete siaf\u233? s\u225?i k\u233?maufron y\u233?n\u233? mer si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
A s\u233?nonjo f\u233?m k\u233?kmbo m\u233?tar a yau noraya k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u233?n\u233? ufroghene efogh kawerang\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mo efalo yau tane si so t\u225?y\u225?to. \u193?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? so efalo k\u233?namndangi y\u225?njo efghon."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? tekan \u225?r\u233?m Jakaraya njam tanjetaw\u233?t a mwigh\u233? uw\u233?rsoghan tamorw\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n tekfifi t\u233?lawang\u233?rw\u233?n w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Njam f\u225? n\u233?tory\u233?ng, f\u225? yau korayau y\u233?fefaf. Y\u233?mofem y\u225?y\u225?mngoy\u233?nd m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mon gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?gh Ng\u225?nj\u225?n yinjoi w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n, f\u225? siofnar namndai y\u233?feyot ng\u225?ngayero tawaweindau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Njam y\u225?ne w\u225?wefnogh efogh nefoy\u233?nd, f\u225? n\u233?ngangoi m\u233?ngot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Soram\u233? y\u225?ne amaf Elisabet namndai suaf\u233? a 5 gh\u233?rare m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?nro t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n yau k\u233?tonau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Elisabet norayai, "Yuram y\u233?n\u233? tafrote tayot, y\u233?n\u233? efghon Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yauyafoi y\u225?ne m\u233?nde a yit\u233?rmboi tane w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? yam \u225?rfe tamb\u233?n."
