\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Euwetati m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
"W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon emndetan f\u233?m emofem wiy\u225?retat y\u233?nd: F\u233?fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r euwetati, mer ewawafrotati y\u233?feyot emofem m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat efandat f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Efrendati f\u225? emofem ewaf\u225?ngotat f\u233?m, Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh y\u233?feyot emofem ekenat f\u233?fe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Njam \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m f\u233?tkaman k\u233?n\u233?smang\u233?, kawengo w\u233?i witm\u233? y\u225?faf. Njam \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m k\u233?mawanang\u233? fene s\u233?njt\u233? sod\u233?, yau t\u225?f t\u233?kmbo t\u233?ng\u233?umyo a \u225?mb sod\u233? t\u233?ngwaram. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Ewarameta m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t emofem n\u233?mamnendat f\u233?m, emo njam k\u233?mawanang\u233? fene n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m, yau t\u225?f tango. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r\u233?t ewafrotati fene m\u233?ndef\u233? n\u233?m\u233? em \u225?rfeyot w\u233?nde so n\u233?mawafrotat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Njam f\u233?mofem euwetati f\u225? emofem f\u233?m n\u233?muwetat, n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mofem freng\u233?gh so tanangi? Nden\u233?yameyo yaufiyam \u225?r\u233?m euwetat emofem f\u225? euwetat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
A njam f\u233?mofem ewawafrotati mer y\u233?feyotro efe mer em f\u233?fefaf, n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mofem freng\u233?gh so tanangi? Nden\u233? yam yaufiyam \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? ewafrotat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
A njam f\u233?m m\u233?ghm\u233?gh em y\u233?fefaf k\u233?tam\u233? emofem fai so k\u233?mawangongi, n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mofem freng\u233?gh so tanangi? Nden\u233?yameyo yaufiyam \u225?r\u233?m m\u233?ghm\u233?ghaf\u233? so n\u233?manjetat fai wangogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
W\u233?nde euwetati f\u233?fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r, mer ewawafrotati y\u233?feyot, yau nawanjetati fai wangogh\u233?tro. F\u233?yo f\u233?fene fai so y\u233?m ndimbal, a f\u233?m so em Minde tuk Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Ambum, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? siy\u233?m mer y\u233?fefaf k\u225?njo si emofem yau yawangotat a em yaufian. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
