\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
"\u193?rfene yaufi yau ewaftati m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam f\u233?fene yaufi yau so ewafte. \u193?r yau ewafalngotati emndetati nden\u233? yaufiyamaf\u233? em m\u233?nam\u233?n yau w\u233?i f\u233?m so ewafalngotat. Tawawalindang\u233? y\u233?fene yaufim\u233?n, a f\u233?fene so w\u233?i f\u225? tawawalindang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Ram\u233?gh \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam f\u233?fe w\u233?i so tawaramang\u233?. F\u233?mofem njam y\u233?n\u233? yam yafrotati so ewinjotati t\u225?rf\u225?r, so ewaramete k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?fene ng\u225?ng\u233? afoghare so ewam a nasunat. Nder\u233? t\u225?rf\u225?r f\u233?mofem njam ewarametati, nden\u233?yameyo f\u233?fe so ewaramete."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
Yesum tawaufrotau y\u233?n\u233? rengerenge si, "F\u233?yotaro kw\u233?fkw\u233?f \u225?r\u233?m so y\u233?mnje kw\u233?fkw\u233?f \u225?r? W\u233?t yau so k\u233?lawend y\u233?kw\u233?t? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Waitogh \u225?r\u233?m yau so taindangi y\u233?fene watamegh \u225?r, w\u233?nde efe njam ewatametat m\u233?inyotio yam, f\u225? so em nden\u225?yo y\u233?fene watamegh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
"N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mo y\u233?fande fe f\u250?tarene gh\u233?k\u233?f f\u233?m\u233?gh a yau nofande w\u233?n t\u233?nj f\u233?fenjo gh\u233?kfan? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Ndern\u225?ye f\u233?mo so fe f\u250?tar t\u233?mnde, 'F\u250?tar, kwumyo y\u233?nd fene gh\u233?k\u233?f f\u233?m\u233?gh utorgh\u233?t,' t\u225?f y\u233?fande w\u233?n t\u233?nj fenjo gh\u233?kfan? F\u233?m uny\u233?gh \u225?r, fronde tutor w\u233?n t\u233?nj fenjo gh\u233?kfan, f\u233?m t\u225?f so k\u233?reta kwayaghayan fe f\u250?tarene gh\u233?k\u233?f f\u233?m\u233?gh utorgh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 W\u233?n a y\u225?ne mbwe
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
