M\u233?inyotio w\u233?n so tawayamngo y\u233?fenjo mbweyan. \u193?r\u233?m yau so ekafetat wiwi k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? f\u233?fta o \u225?s k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? mbita. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
Mer a\u769?rom efune meryam mer tik\u233?fta, a w\u233?i nden\u233?yameyo yaufi \u225?rom yaufiyam efune yaufi tik\u233?fta. Tikfan n\u233?m\u233? afoghare y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? noraye.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 S\u243?mbio m\u233?ngo ram\u233?gh \u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
"N\u233?mam\u233?n w\u233?t y\u233?nd w\u233?mndetati 'Yur\u233?, Yur\u233?,' a yau ewafrotati nden\u225?ye y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? norayan? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
