Y\u233?mofem efe yinjoy\u233?nd ewafroy\u233?nd \u225?r\u233?t ndern\u225?ye yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r was\u233?rmboghkaf \u225?r mer namndai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
K\u233?tam\u233? Gerasenes m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m Yesu yamnenday\u233?nd s\u225?i tafrangongai, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? f\u233?rf\u233?ram ewifoi. F\u233?yo f\u225? boutan nuflay\u233?nd \u225?ligh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? ende tamb\u233?n yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r tawifnau, y\u233?mon yamnendai Yesu y\u233?maf\u233? \u225?ligh\u233?t, w\u233?nde Yesum y\u233?ngwatembai nden\u233? siaf\u233?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
"Ngangota m\u233?ngotuot a tawaufro nder\u233? ndimbal Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam k\u233?mawafrote feyot." F\u233?yo \u225?r nuwanoi, a kafrotau tesenam\u233? nder\u233? ndimbal Yesum yawafrotam y\u225?yot.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 K\u233?r m\u233?r\u233?s a enjnef\u233? amaf
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Yesu njam n\u233?ngangotam, \u225?r m\u233?rnam yumyoy\u233?nd, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mofem m\u233?ghm\u233?ghaf\u233? tanjetaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
A\u769?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Jairus, w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo ndimbal a\u769?r y\u233?nmorm\u233?n a n\u233?nuyai Yesuene kafkafot, yamnendai \u225?ligh\u233?t y\u225?njo m\u233?ngot {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne f\u233?f\u233?t m\u233?r\u233?s, 12 yunj\u233?f krotro t\u233?morw\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Njam Yesu n\u233?ndkfan n\u233?ngayatoi, t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r\u233?m t\u233?ngsotaw\u233?t f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
A amaf k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n efe f\u233?r\u233?k kertau 12 yunj\u233?f, w\u233?nde emon yau y\u233?frendai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
F\u225? s\u233?mta y\u233?nmorm\u233?n a yiy\u225?njai Yesuene s\u225?l\u225?me f\u233?tf\u233?tro f\u233?r\u233?k t\u225?f n\u233?kmboi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
Yesu namotai, "Emo wiy\u225?nja?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Njam f\u225? m\u233?inyotio nawanyotay\u233?nd, Fit\u233? norayai, "Yur\u233?, \u225?r m\u233?rnam n\u233?marendangi a n\u233?ngsotat f\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
W\u233?nde Yesu norayai, "A\u769?mb a\u769?rom t\u233? wiy\u225?nja. Y\u233?nd mat n\u225?y\u225?ton waft\u233? t\u233? n\u233?ngf\u233?r\u233?m ta tamb\u233?n."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
Njam amaf y\u233?nmorm\u233?n fandaghofnar a mat siofnar, f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? t\u233?nmorw\u233?n n\u233?nuyai y\u225?ne kafkafot. M\u233?inyotio \u225?rfene s\u225?fr\u233?r\u233?, y\u233?mon y\u233?mndai n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?mon yiy\u225?njai a ndern\u225?ye f\u225? t\u225?fandio freng\u233?gham yanai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
Ndenaye Yesum y\u233?mday\u233?ng, "M\u233?r\u233?s, fenjo ndimbal mwighayam mer niy\u225?to. Kuwano mer so n\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 49\~}
Njamandio Yesu m\u233? korayau, \u225?mb \u225?r y\u233?nmorm\u233?n Jairusene m\u233?ngota, efe t\u233?morm\u233?n \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngo ndimbal \u225?r. Y\u233?mon y\u233?mndai, "Fene m\u233?r\u233?s k\u233?r t\u233?m. Yau yaw\u233?rsota watamegh \u225?r nde nayu." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 50\~}
Yesu njam n\u225?y\u225?rai y\u233?n\u233?, f\u225? y\u233?mndai Jairus, "Yau f\u233?rf\u233?r n\u233?m. Efalo tiy\u225?to a so mer k\u225?y\u225?tong\u233?." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 51\~}
Njam f\u225? nufary\u233?ng Jairusene m\u233?ngot, y\u233?mon yau efe yumyoi y\u233?maf\u233? \u225?ligh\u233?t f\u225?ro Fit\u233?, Jon, Jems a ambumoe y\u225?ref\u233? a y\u225?tm\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 52\~}
Njamandio m\u233?inyotio \u225?r kendaw\u233?t a kutnaw\u233?t gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? tamorw\u233?n y\u225?faf. Yesum emndayai, "Yau nendati, yau k\u233?r t\u233?m w\u233?nde k\u233?m\u233?gh y\u233?k\u233?m." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 53\~}
Y\u233?mofem turtaw\u233?t m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? mat tamorw\u233?n nden\u233? k\u233?r t\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 54\~}
W\u233?nde yeray\u233?ng ng\u225?ngayan a y\u233?mndai, "Tane ambum, kano!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 55\~}
Y\u225?ne mb\u233?rmb\u233?r n\u233?nangoi, t\u225?fandio n\u233?nokayoi. F\u233?yo Yesum emndai njamke taram\u233?nd n\u233?net. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 56\~}
Y\u225?refaf s\u233?lngw\u233?l emorm\u233?n, w\u233?nde Yesum emnday\u233?ng yau nafrotati n\u233?m\u233? kufrote.
