A\u769?mb efghon Yesum eumendai y\u225?ne 12 waitogh a\u769?r m\u233?rne a ewarametam waft\u233? a muy\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r \u233?torgh\u233?t a enjneta mer y\u225?togh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
A f\u225? ew\u225?f\u225?retai Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?ghm\u233?n si waitogh\u233?t a enjne t\u233?fn\u225?r freng\u233?gh\u233?t {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?mon emndai, "N\u233?m\u233? yau \u225?lighan tawanangi-yau w\u233?tu, yau y\u225?f, yau njamke, yau mani, yau \u225?mb awalogh s\u225?l\u225?me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
\u193?rk\u233? m\u233?ngo njam k\u233?lawangi, k\u233?t\u233?miya emor k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u233?n\u233? tesen t\u233?frangongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
\u193?r\u233?m yau njam taumyongi, kafkaf ngw\u233?rm\u233?ng tas\u233?nangi t\u225?f t\u233?nfrangongi y\u233?fene tesen, aw\u233?farogh so y\u233?m y\u233?feyot njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u233?kw kufarng\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne si y\u233?kenay\u233?nd." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? n\u225?frendam\u233?nd a tayotau m\u233?inyotio m\u233?ngotuam\u233?, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mer si t\u225?itotaw\u233?t a a\u769?r tang\u233?frendaw\u233?t m\u233?inyotio sifayan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Erod lim\u225?n\u233?gh a\u769?r n\u225?y\u225?rai m\u233?inyotio n\u233?m\u233? kufrotaw\u233?t. A f\u225? k\u233?w\u233?rsotaw\u233?t m\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?mb korayaw\u233?t, "Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m Jon k\u233?r tamb\u233?n n\u233?nano," {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
a\u769?mb kemnaw\u233?t, "Elaija nufar," a a\u769?mb kemnaw\u233?t nde \u225?mb t\u225?nd\u225?w\u225?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh a\u769?r n\u233?nango gh\u233?rsat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde Erod norayai, "Y\u233?ndon emnday\u233?n Jonene s\u233?nko n\u233?fgh\u233?t. Efe y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m y\u233?nd t\u225?rf\u225?r si n\u225?y\u225?retan y\u225?nem\u233?n?" A f\u225? m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n s\u225?i tinjongai Yesu.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum emanjnam 5,000 a\u769?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Njam Yesuene muyaf\u233? a\u769?r n\u233?nangoy\u233?nd, y\u233?mofem nafroy\u233?nd Yesuefaf n\u233?m\u233? tawafrotaw\u233?t. Y\u233?mon engwasroi a f\u225? n\u233?ngwanoi enagh\u233?t tesen y\u233?tkw\u233?n Betsaidat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
W\u233?nde t\u225?rf\u225?r a\u769?r mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n a yaitoy\u233?nd fa\u769?. Y\u233?mon eumyoi a emndayeng Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?ghm\u233?n a efrenday\u233?ng fa\u769? efe freng\u233?gh m\u233?nde tamorw\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Seitefifi 12 waitogh a\u769?r enmorm\u233?n Yesuefaf a y\u233?mnday\u233?nd, "Tawafarna a\u769?r m\u233?r\u233?n, f\u225? so n\u233?ngangotat kaka m\u233?ngotuot a t\u233?ndo yuwot m\u233?n\u225?t njamke a k\u233?m\u233?gh sifayat \u225?ronjagh\u233?t, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m yauyau sifayan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?mon ewawangoi, "F\u233?mofem n\u233?mndafi tawaramangi n\u233?net y\u233?feyot."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mofem yawangoy\u233?nd, "T\u233?fene em 5 f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? a s\u243?mbio wagif, y\u233?nd njam m\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r manjargh\u233?t, y\u233?nd so kuwanong\u233?m y\u233?fene njamke r\u233?sagh\u233?t." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r tamorw\u233?n 5,000nit. W\u233?nde emndai y\u225?njo waitogh a\u769?r, "K\u225?mnjongi m\u233?r\u233?n tawafrotangi 50nit." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yo waitogh \u225?r\u233?m yafrotam\u233?nd, a m\u233?inyotio a\u769?r n\u225?mnjotam\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Yesum euyoi 5 f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? a s\u243?mbio wagif, a n\u233?wewoi njafar tuk\u233?t, k\u225?njo yaramai a etfotam. F\u233?yo eramai waitogh \u225?rfefaf tawarametaw\u233?t \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
