\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
\u193?mb efghon Yesum efrangoi a\u769?r m\u233?r\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oraigh\u233?t yambia a y\u225?njo waitogh \u225?rf\u233? tamorw\u233?n, y\u233?mon emotai f\u225?, "Efe m\u233?r\u233?n korayaw\u233?t y\u233?nd efe w\u233?m?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?mofem yawangoy\u233?nd, "A\u769?mb korayaw\u233?t Jon walitogh a\u769?r, a\u769?mb \u225?r\u233?m korayaw\u233?t Elaija, w\u233?nde a\u769?mb \u225?r\u233?m korayaw\u233?t nden\u233? t\u225?nd\u225?w\u225?r a\u769?mb Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r k\u233?nangote gh\u233?rsat."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
