\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fitam yawangoi, "Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Keriso."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu korayau y\u225?njo k\u233?rm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Yesum t\u225?ik\u233?r si tawaw\u233?ngsotau y\u233?fe ende yau taufrongi y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
A f\u225? norayai, "\u193?roene Ambumom so f\u233?t\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? y\u233?ngfande t\u225?rf\u225?r yaman a y\u233?karotat s\u233?nko \u225?r\u233?m, lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r\u233?m a n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r\u233?m, a f\u225? so f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?smetat a nambio efogh soram\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so tanong\u233? gh\u233?rsat."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mo emndayeng m\u233?inyotio: "Njam efe waitogh\u233?t k\u233?nufngo ta soram\u233?, f\u225? so f\u233?t\u233? kakenang\u233? f\u225?yo a tanang\u233? y\u225?njoyo wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?n m\u233?inyotio efghon a kw\u233?nmaitong\u233? y\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Efe m\u233?nde njam y\u233?m y\u225?njo gh\u233?rs\u233? wanjargh\u233?t so y\u233?tarne, w\u233?nde emo njam y\u225?ne gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?tarna tanem\u233?n so tanjarng\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
A nder\u233? mer y\u233?m \u225?roe s\u225?i tanang\u233? m\u233?inyotio mband marat, w\u233?nde y\u233?tarna o nawas\u233?rmbota f\u225?yo? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Njam w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? efe y\u233?m tanem\u233?n a tane sim\u233?n, \u193?roene Ambum so y\u233?m w\u225?iw\u225?i y\u225?nem\u233?n njam f\u225? n\u233?nangota y\u225?ne ndimbal kwayagh\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?n a Y\u225?refane ndimbal kwayagh\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?n a k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar njafar si r\u233?sagh a\u769?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Y\u233?ndon efalo ewaufrotan, a\u769?mb efe ewakai y\u233?na, y\u233?mofem so y\u233?fandati Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh soram\u233? so k\u233?r em."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Nambio waitogh \u225?r\u233?m yinjoy\u233?nd Yesuene ndimbal kwayagh\u233?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
8 efogh soram\u233? Yesum ewasroi Fit\u233?, Jon a Jems y\u233?maf\u233? n\u233?ngwanoy\u233?nd mband tunakfot Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? koraiw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Njamandio f\u225? Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? koraiw\u233?t, y\u225?ne s\u225?f natambnai, a y\u225?ne s\u225?l\u225?me n\u225?y\u225?toi m\u233? kwayagharo n\u225?l\u225?lai toyanit. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
S\u243?mbio a\u769?r, Moses a Elaija, ndimbal kwayagh\u233? nufary\u233?ng, Yesuf\u233? korayaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Y\u233?mofem korayaw\u233?t y\u225?ne \u225?lighm\u233?n, a\u769?rk\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?nde so kufrotau s\u225?i k\u233?r t\u233?morw\u233?n Jerusalem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Fit\u233? a y\u225?ne m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?m\u233?gh k\u233?r t\u225?kmang\u233?w\u233?n, w\u233?nde njam f\u225? nanoy\u233?nd, y\u233?mofem yinjoy\u233?nd y\u225?ne ndimbal kwayagh\u233? a s\u243?mbio a\u769?r tawakayarw\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Njamandio Moses a Elaijafem t\u233?frangow\u233?t Yesu, Fitam y\u233?mndai, "Yur\u233?, mer n\u233?rete f\u233?maf\u233? s\u225?i y\u233?na y\u233?n\u233?m. So erametam nambio m\u233?ngo, \u225?mbiro feyot, \u225?mbiro Mosese a \u225?mbiro Elaija." F\u225? mafina t\u233?morw\u233?n n\u233?mam\u233?n korayau.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Njamandio f\u225? korayau, njafar kwamkwam nufary\u233?ng a f\u225? engwafary\u233?ng, a f\u225? f\u233?rf\u233?r tamorw\u233?n njam ewafary\u233?ng njafar kwamkwaman. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Si k\u233?m y\u233?nmorm\u233?n njafar kwamkwamta, n\u233?norayai, "Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m tane ambum, efe y\u233?ndon yafery\u233?n, yiy\u225?retati f\u225?." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
Si njam nefoi, Yesuro yinjoy\u233?nd yambia. Endefet \u225?mb yau ewafroy\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? efghon n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mofem yinjoy\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum y\u233?frendai yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?raf\u233? ambum
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
\u193?mb efghon, njam f\u225? k\u233?nangotaw\u233?t mband tunak\u233?fta, ndimbal m\u233?rnam y\u233?f\u225?ngoy\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
A\u769?r nutnai m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?ta, "Watamegh a\u769?r, y\u233?ndon n\u233?mamnendan m\u233?n\u225?t tane ambum so tinjo, m\u233?nam\u233?n tane y\u233?naro ambum fiy\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
Yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram yarsote f\u225? a sunsune kutnang\u233?, y\u233?mo t\u233?tarmang\u233? t\u225?ikram yafrote a f\u233?fokam ew\u233?tote t\u225?f s\u233?nfneta. Yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram yau t\u233?frangong\u233? f\u225? m\u233? yas\u233?rmbote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Y\u233?ndon ewamnendan fene waitogh a\u769?r m\u233?n\u225?t yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r wit\u233?rmbogh\u233?t, w\u233?nde f\u225? f\u233?yotarofnar em."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
Yesum ewawangoi, "F\u233?m ndimbal mwighafnar a \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghofnar a\u769?r, nder\u233? teke f\u233?maf\u233? so y\u233?nmor a ewamarotan f\u233?m? T\u233?n\u233?mnjo fene ambum y\u233?nan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Njamandio ambum t\u233?nmorw\u233?n, yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram yitam mbandot kos\u233?nau. W\u233?nde Yesum yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r yifnai, y\u233?frendai ambum a yangoi y\u225?refafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
A f\u225? s\u233?lngw\u233?l emorm\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ndimbal yam wafroghan.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu korayau y\u225?njo k\u233?rm\u233?n y\u233?namayo
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Njam m\u233?inyotio \u225?r s\u233?lngw\u233?l emorm\u233?n a korayaw\u233?t Yesuene yam wafroghm\u233?n, y\u233?mon emndai y\u225?njo waitogh a\u769?r, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
"Mer k\u233?r\u225?ye k\u225?y\u225?rangi y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? waufrogh\u233?t f\u233?fe ewawafngon. A\u769?roene Ambum so s\u233?n y\u233?rametat a\u769?rfene ng\u225?ngat." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? yau mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd n\u233?m\u233? t\u233?s\u233?rmbnau. M\u233?nam\u233?n t\u233?noghe t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u233?fefaf, f\u225? yau mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd, a f\u225? f\u233?rf\u233?r tamorw\u233?n \u225?mogh\u233?t y\u225?faf y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Efe so y\u233?m ndimbal
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
Y\u225?ne waitogh a\u769?r mwighayan \u225?snan\u233?ghan tamorw\u233?n efe so y\u233?m ndimbal. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
W\u233?nde Yesu mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?ng y\u233?fene mwigh\u233?, f\u233?yo y\u233?mon yakayoi n\u233?mbnar ambum tos\u233? k\u233?t\u233? y\u225? t\u233?ndon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mon emndai f\u225?, "Emo njam tumyong\u233? y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?mbnar ambum tos\u233? tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan kumyong\u233? y\u233?nd, a emofem y\u233?nd umyotat f\u225? kumyong\u233? emo w\u233?m\u225?f\u225?retam. Efe n\u233?mbne y\u233?m f\u233?fefaf m\u233?inyotio f\u225? siy\u233?m ndimbal."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 49\~}
Jon norayai, "Yur\u233?, y\u233?ndfem a\u769?r yinjong\u233?m yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r tawifnau fene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan a y\u233?ta t\u233?kmbotaw\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?m f\u225? yau t\u233?fene y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 50\~}
Yesum emndai, "Yau y\u233?kmbotati m\u233?nam\u233?n emo njam yau n\u233?karota f\u225? siy\u233?m t\u233?feta."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Samariam\u233?n a\u769?r\u233?m y\u233?kenay\u233?nd Yesu
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 51\~}
Yesuene efogh kaka k\u233?namndetau angogh\u233?t njafarot, Yesum sotaf\u233? mwigh\u233? y\u233?kmai \u225?ligh\u233?t Jerusalem\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 52\~}
Y\u233?mon engw\u225?f\u225?retam si r\u233?sagh a\u769?r frondeyo, efe engmorm\u233?n Samaria m\u233?ngotuot rokar freng\u233?gh\u233?t y\u225?yot, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 53\~}
w\u233?nde a\u769?r\u233?m k\u233?t\u233? yau umyoy\u233?nd f\u225?, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? tiotau Jerusalem\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 54\~}
Njam waitogh a\u769?r Jems a Jon yinjeyay\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?, y\u233?mofem y\u233?motangeyay\u233?nd, "Yur\u233?, f\u233?m m\u233?nde n\u233?m y\u233?nd f\u233?sot kutnang\u233?m njafarot y\u233?fe was\u233?rmbogh\u233?t." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 55\~}
W\u233?nde Yesu nawengoi ew\u225?rnam f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 56\~}
A f\u225? n\u233?wanoy\u233?nd a\u769?mb m\u233?ngotuot.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Efalo Yesuene waitogh \u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 57\~}
F\u225? njam endm\u233? tangmorm\u233?n a\u769?rom y\u233?mndai Yesu, "Y\u233?ndon so n\u233?maitotan a\u769?rkam\u233? f\u233?m njam niota."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 58\~}
Yesum yawangoy\u233?ng, "\u193?gh\u233?\u225?ghafene f\u233?ne t\u233? em a menafene nj\u233?n t\u233? em, w\u233?nde \u193?roene Ambumoene sifay\u233? yau y\u233?m k\u233?m\u233?gh\u233?t a en\u225?gh\u233?t."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 59\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u233?mndai a\u769?mb a\u769?r, "Kw\u233?nmaito y\u233?nd."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 W\u233?nde a\u769?r\u233?m yawangoi, "Yur\u233?, y\u233?nd so fronde nangotan m\u233?ngot k\u233?t\u225?n tane af\u233? k\u233?r njam y\u233?m y\u233?ndon so yiy\u225?totan soram\u233? y\u233?ndon so k\u233?maiton."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 60\~}
Yesum y\u233?mndai fa\u769?, "K\u233?r a\u769?r y\u233?mofem so ey\u225?totat efe em mb\u233?rmb\u233?re k\u233?rw\u233?n, w\u233?nde f\u233?m nguwano Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?ghm\u233?n si waitogh\u233?t."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 61\~}
W\u233?i a\u769?mb norayai, "Y\u233?ndon so k\u233?maiton f\u233?m, Yur\u233?, w\u233?nde so fronde n\u233?ngangotan tane m\u233?r\u233?n watembgh\u233?t."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 62\~}
Yesum yawangoy\u233?ng, "Emo tar\u233?gh a\u769?sa\u769?fogh t\u233?rnyang\u233? a n\u233?reta s\u233?mta, f\u225? f\u233?yotarofnar y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh a\u769?sa\u769?fogh\u233?t."
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 10
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum ew\u225?f\u225?retam 72 waitogh a\u769?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? Yuram ewafery\u233?ng 72 a\u769?mb waitogh a\u769?r a s\u243?mbios\u243?mbioe ew\u225?f\u225?retam m\u233?inyotio tesenot a yuwot \u225?ndan fa\u769? \u225?ligh\u233?t m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?mon emndai, "Wau yu njamke t\u233?f\u233?n tar\u233?gh siy\u233?m ta\u769?rfa\u769?r, w\u233?nde a\u769?sa\u769?fogh a\u769?r em nambio. Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde t\u233?mndangi wau yuwan njamke t\u233?f\u233?n Yur\u233?, so ew\u225?f\u225?rete a\u769?sa\u769?fogh a\u769?r y\u225?ne njamke t\u233?f\u233?n ndawot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Kuwanongi\u451? Y\u233?ndon f\u233?m ew\u225?f\u225?retan nden\u233? w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?ghofnar tos\u233? sifnit y\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n munjan \u225?gh\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Yau ersati mani y\u225?f a \u225?wogh y\u225?f. \u193?mb sandol yau ersati. Yau teke a\u769?rf\u233? asnegh\u233?t end\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
"Njam f\u233?m k\u233?lawangi m\u233?ngon fronde korayangi, 'Freng\u233?gh y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ngon.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? freng\u233?gh \u225?r njam k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m, f\u233?fene freng\u233?gh so nene y\u225?faf, yau njam, f\u233?fefaf so k\u233?nangong\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
K\u233?t\u233? t\u225?f emor y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ngon, njamke nu n\u233?m\u233? njam ewarametat n\u233?net, m\u233?nam\u233?n a\u769?sa\u769?fogh a\u769?r\u233?m t\u225?f ersat y\u233?fenjo fai. Yau nusanati w\u233?laf\u233? m\u233?ngom\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
"Njam tesenot k\u233?lawangi a taumyongi, enetati f\u233?feyot n\u233?m\u233? em freng\u233?ghkaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Enjne t\u233?fn\u225?r mer ey\u225?totati efe k\u233?t\u233? em ewaufrotati nden\u233?, 'Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh siy\u233?m kaka y\u233?m f\u233?fefaf.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
W\u233?nde njam tesenot k\u233?lawangi a yau taumyongi, endm\u233? kuwanongi a korayangi, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
