M\u233?nam\u233?n m\u233?inyotio a\u769?r emofem namotat so yanangi, m\u233?inyotio a\u769?r efe y\u233?ronjat so tinjongi; f\u225? efe n\u225?ut\u225?nat, s\u233?safne so kasaw\u233?rng\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
"F\u233?m af\u233?, fenjo ambumom njam k\u233?nmamnendang\u233? wagifot, n\u233?m\u233? so taram kamban? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
O njam k\u233?nmamnendang\u233? ghak\u233?r kowi mbweyot, n\u233?m\u233? so taram nd\u233?rkam\u233? y\u225?tm\u233?? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?m ndemam\u233?n yaufi n\u233?m, f\u233?m mat n\u233?m mer rokar ram\u233?gh fenjo ambumafet. Nder\u233? mer y\u233?m minde tuk\u233?n fene Af\u233? njafaran tawaramang\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r y\u233?feyot efe n\u243?mnendat y\u225?faf\u451?"
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu a Beljebab
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
A\u769?mb efghon Yesum yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r yutory\u233?ng bab\u233? a\u769?roeta, a njam yaufi mb\u233?mb\u233?ram y\u233?frangoi, a\u769?r efe bab\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n si nufngoi. A\u769?r m\u233?r\u233?n s\u233?lngw\u233?l emorm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
W\u233?nde \u225?mb \u225?r norayay\u233?nd, "Yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?rafene s\u233?nko t\u233?fn\u225?roene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan Beljebab, Yesum yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r eutone." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
A\u769?mb a\u769?r\u233?m yufotam Yesu \u225?mogh sie y\u233?motay\u233?nd njafar tukm\u233?n yam wiyafogh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Yesu mat namndai y\u233?fene mwigh\u233?, f\u233?yo emndai fa\u769?: "A\u769?rk\u233? yu afalogh\u233?t kufngong\u233? yambiayot so kirorng\u233? a a\u769?rk\u233? m\u233?ngo m\u233?r\u233?n afalogh\u233?t kufngong\u233? yambiayot so kuyang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Njam S\u225?if\u233?r afalogh\u233?t kufngong\u233? yambiayot, ndern\u225?ye y\u225?ne yu so yakai? Y\u233?ndon norayan y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m nemnati nden\u233? Beljebabene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan y\u233?ndon kar yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r eutonan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Njam y\u233?ndo eutonan yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r Beljebabene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, w\u233?t endene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan eutonat fene waitogh a\u769?r\u233?m? Fenjo waitogh a\u769?r\u233?m efalo niy\u225?totat f\u233?m yau mbark\u225?nd n\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
W\u233?nde njam y\u233?ndon eutonan yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?n waftaye t\u225?f nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh y\u233?na y\u233?m f\u233?fefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
"Njam muyaf\u233? a\u769?r yakai umaneghkaf yambwete y\u225?njo m\u233?ngo t\u225?f y\u225?ne rokar mer so em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
W\u233?nde njam minde muyaf\u233? a\u769?rom t\u233?smang\u233? a taindang\u233? fa\u769?, y\u233?mon tangwanang\u233? m\u233?k rokar \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayan yur\u233? kamyotau a efaloi n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon ewanai oroe.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
"Efe yau y\u233?ndf\u233? y\u233?nre, fa\u769? siy\u233?m ta kenagh a\u769?r, a emon y\u233?nd yau s\u225?i w\u225?ut\u225?na umengan, fa\u769? so nironat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
"Yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r njam k\u233?ntorng\u233? a\u769?r tamb\u233?n, fa\u769? nguwanong\u233? fanfne yuwot sifay\u233? ronjagh\u233?t en\u225?gh\u233?t. W\u233?nde yau njam sifay\u233? tinjong\u233?, so korayang\u233?, 'Y\u233?nd so nangotan k\u233?t\u225?n a\u769?rk\u233? m\u233?ngota w\u233?nmorm\u233?n.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Njam k\u233?nangong\u233? tinjong\u233? m\u233?ngo s\u225?mbur\u233?ghkaf nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar a mer freng\u233?ghkaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
F\u233?yo yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r kuwanong\u233? a tanwasrong\u233? a\u769?mb 7 mb\u233?rmb\u233?r minde yaufi nden\u233? fa\u769?yo, f\u225? k\u233?lawangi a emor k\u233?t\u233?. A a\u769?roene gh\u233?rs\u233? minde m\u225?m\u225?fi kamndang\u233? k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? fronde ndern\u225?ye t\u233?morw\u233?n."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Yesum njam korayau y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, amaf nutnay\u233?ng a\u769?r m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n, "Freng\u233?ghkaf amaf y\u233?m emo n\u225?r\u225?ftam a endene nonoyan kanotau."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "Freng\u233?ghkaf fa\u769? em efe n\u225?y\u225?retat Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si a wafroghan t\u233?kmangi."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Jonane yam ufarogh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Njam a\u769?r m\u233?r\u233?n t\u225?rf\u225?r k\u233?n\u225?y\u225?totau, Yesu norayai, "Y\u233?n\u233? yaufiyaufi a\u769?r m\u233?r\u233?n em. Fa\u769? namotat Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene wafroghyamot, w\u233?nde n\u233?m\u233? yau so tawaramangan m\u233? Jonane ufarogh yamro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Nden\u233? Jona t\u233?morw\u233?n Nin\u233?fa tesenm\u233?n \u225?r\u233?t yam ufarogh, nden\u233? endeyo \u193?roene Ambum so w\u233?i y\u233?m yam ufarogh y\u233?n\u233? a\u769?r m\u233?rnat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Sifa ndimbal yuoene warsagh am\u233? so kokayong\u233? mogh\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? a\u769?r m\u233?rnafefaf a so tawafalngonga nden\u233? fa\u769? srem yaufiyamaf\u233?; m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? amaf y\u233?nmorm\u233?n yu nayu Solomonene k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? \u225?y\u225?rgh\u233?t, a a\u769?mb a\u769?r y\u233?na y\u233?m y\u225? tuk\u233?n Solomon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
A\u769?r Nin\u233?fam\u233?n so kokayongi moghan y\u233?n\u233? a\u769?r m\u233?r\u233?nfaf a so tafalngongi, m\u233?nam\u233?n fa\u769? nawengoy\u233?nd Jonane si waitoghan, a a\u769?mb a\u769?r y\u233?na y\u233?m y\u225? tuk\u233?n Jona.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fifioene Kwayagh\u233?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
"A\u769?rk\u233? \u225?rom kwayagh\u233? yau so t\u233?kmang\u233? k\u233?t\u233? \u225?nde so y\u233?tno, o mb\u225?fy\u225?f mbanmbanan. W\u233?nde y\u233?mon t\u233?fayong\u233? y\u225?njo fayogh sifayan, m\u233?n\u225?t efe njam en\u233?m y\u233?mofem kwayagh\u233? so y\u233?fandat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Fene gh\u233?k\u233?f sem kwayagh\u233? em fene fifiot. Fene gh\u233?k\u233?f njam mer ere, fene m\u233?inyotio fifi so y\u233?m kwayaghayan. W\u233?nde njam m\u225?m\u225?fi ere fene gh\u233?k\u233?f, fene fifi so y\u233?m m\u233?inyotio kw\u233?fkw\u233?fan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Kor f\u233?m an\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t kwayagh\u233? fene k\u233?nj\u250?n yau t\u225?f y\u233?m kw\u233?fkw\u233?f. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
F\u233?yo t\u225?f fene m\u233?inyotio fifi s\u225?i y\u233?m ndimbal kwayaghayan, a\u769?mb fifi kafe yau so y\u233?m kw\u233?fkw\u233?fan, so y\u233?m m\u233?inyotio kwayaghayan njam lambefane kwayagh\u233? k\u225?tremngong\u233? fefaf."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum t\u225?ik\u233?r si tamndetau Farasi a\u769?r a n\u225?k watamegh t\u233?fn\u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Yesum njam si yifoi Farasi a\u769?rom yumyoi y\u233?mafe n\u233?net. F\u233?yo Yesu naflai a n\u225?mnjoi n\u233?net. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
W\u233?nde Farasi a\u769?r s\u233?lngw\u233?l y\u233?morm\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n ng\u225?ng\u233? umbarghofnar Yesum n\u233?ne ewafngoi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
Yuram y\u233?mndai Farasi a\u769?r, "F\u233?m Farasi a\u769?r kafusi a sin faruro es\u233?nnati, w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n f\u233?m sem kw\u233?njta a yaufi k\u233?r ro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
F\u233?m afreng\u233?ghofnar a\u769?r\u451? F\u233?m mat em emo faru yafrotam, w\u233?i nden\u225?yo yafrotam k\u233?nj\u250?? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
W\u233?nde tawaram n\u233?m\u233? enyau fene k\u233?nj\u250?n yauyau a\u769?r\u233?t, m\u233?inyotio so em f\u233?feyot nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
"Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi so y\u233?m Farasi a\u769?r f\u233?feyot, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fene ram\u233?gh siy\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?neyot m\u233?inyotio ndau tamb\u233?n, w\u233?nde f\u233?mofem y\u233?kenati Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene uw\u233?gh a mbark\u225?nd yam. F\u233?mofem so otamegh\u233?t y\u233?kmetati Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene uw\u233?gh a mbark\u225?nd yam, a yau n\u233?kmbotati ndau njamke ram\u233?ghta.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
"Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi so y\u233?m Farasi a\u769?r f\u233?feyot, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem m\u233?ndef\u233? y\u233?fandati mer \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngon, a \u225?uw\u233?gh si utman\u233?gh t\u233?rar\u233?gh sifayan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
"Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi so y\u233?m Farasi \u225?r f\u233?feyot, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m ndenanit em wayamngoghofnar mb\u233?w\u233?, \u225?rkam\u233? a\u769?r eyota matofnar."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
A\u769?mb n\u225?k watamegh \u225?rom yawangoi, "Watamegh a\u769?r, njam f\u233?m noraye y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, f\u233?mon m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?nd y\u233?ny\u225?tote nden\u225?ye."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "F\u233?m, na\u769?k watamegh a\u769?r, nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi so y\u233?m f\u233?feyot, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem a\u769?r\u233?t ewafayotati k\u233?rt\u233? r\u233?sagh\u233?t, w\u233?nde f\u233?mofem yau so ew\u225?ut\u225?nati k\u233?rt\u233? r\u233?sagh\u233?t \u225?mbiro tomb\u233? min ng\u225?ngaye y\u233?fe w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
"Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi so y\u233?m f\u233?feyot, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem mb\u233?w\u233? m\u233?ngo erametati y\u233?feyot Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?rfet, efe f\u233?fene \u225?kifem t\u233? esmetam\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
F\u233?m nafrotati efalo yiy\u225?totati f\u233?fene \u225?kifem n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? yafrotam\u233?nd; y\u233?mofem esmetam\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r a f\u233?mofem y\u233?fene mb\u233?w\u233? m\u233?ngo erametati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 49\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u225?njo k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? norayam, 'Y\u233?ndon so ew\u225?f\u225?retan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r a Yesuene muyaf\u233? a\u769?r, w\u233?nde a\u769?mb so esmetat, a\u769?mb w\u233?i so ewifnat.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 50\~}
F\u233?yo a\u769?r m\u233?r\u233?n y\u233?nanotio s\u233?nonjo efogh so em t\u233?fnot m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?rfene f\u233?r\u233?k er\u233?ghm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?ndmayo r\u233?ny\u233?gh, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 51\~}
k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Abelene f\u233?r\u233?k k\u233?t\u225?n Jakarayane f\u233?r\u233?k, efe y\u233?smetam\u233?nd gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh kitar\u233? a nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar sifay\u233? y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?ndk\u233?fan. N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, y\u233?ndon n\u233?maufrotan fe, a\u769?r m\u233?r\u233?n y\u233?nanotio s\u233?nonjo efogh so em t\u233?feyot m\u233?inyotioat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 52\~}
"Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi so y\u233?m n\u225?k watamegh t\u233?fn\u225?r\u233?t, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem m\u233? t\u233? tamndaw\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? ki matyam s\u233?safne saur\u233?ghm\u233?n. F\u233?myo yau so k\u233?lawangi k\u233?nj\u250?t, a f\u233?mofem ekmbotati fa\u769? efe \u233?laugh\u233?t narametat."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 53\~}
Njam Yesu nuwanoi k\u233?t\u233?, Farasi a\u769?r a na\u769?k watamegh t\u233?fn\u225?r n\u233?kwe tasotaw\u233?t a \u225?mogh si tarametaw\u233?t t\u225?rf\u225?r yamm\u233?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 54\~}
kawanjetaw\u233?t s\u225?i terangay\u233?nd Yesu m\u233?n\u225?yan n\u233?m\u233? yaufi si s\u225?i korayangai.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 12
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Matot t\u225?waw\u233?ngsotau
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Njam a\u769?r m\u233?r\u233?n n\u225?umendam\u233?nd, f\u233?yo f\u225?rof\u225?ro kafkafe katumndaw\u233?t. Yesum si y\u233?rnyai fronde y\u225?njo waitogh \u225?rfefaf korayau, "F\u233?m so nawarawenati k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Farasi a\u769?rf\u233? uny\u233?gh gh\u233?rs\u233? tamb\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Efogh y\u233?n\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? m\u233?inyotio yafar so kanendang\u233?, a n\u233?m\u233? t\u233?noghe y\u233?m so nufanat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? noraye kw\u233?fitayan so kufarng\u233? kwayaghat, a f\u233?mon n\u233?m\u233? yawanjai t\u233?nganan k\u233?nj\u250?nro so yaitote k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? m\u233?ngo s\u233?msota.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
"Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan, tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, f\u233?rf\u233?r yau em emofem fifi esmetat a y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? y\u233?mofem yau n\u233?m\u233? so yafrotat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon ewauyafotan f\u233?feyot efe so f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? y\u233?fandati: f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? y\u233?fandati Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, f\u233?fene ngi soram\u233?, f\u225? muyaf\u233? y\u233?m emo so ewite f\u233?s\u233?t. N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, f\u225? y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m efalofifi f\u233?mofem efe so f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? y\u233?fandati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
N\u233?m\u233? 5 n\u233?mbne men tamorw\u233?n 20 toyaye? W\u233?nde n\u233?m\u233? yau wawaling\u233? y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, f\u233?ne s\u233?nko s\u233?f sem Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene waf\u233?ghkaf em. F\u233?m yau f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? em. F\u233?mofem ewaindati n\u233?mbne men t\u233?rt\u233?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
"Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan, emofem y\u233?nd wiy\u225?totat saf\u233?n nde f\u225? em tane, nden\u233?yameyo \u193?roene Ambumom so efalo tay\u225?tong\u233? nde f\u225? em tane k\u233?t\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene njafar si r\u233?sagh a\u769?rfene s\u225?fr\u233?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde emofem njam w\u233?kenat y\u233?nd a\u769?r saf\u233?n w\u233?i so ekenan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene njafar si r\u233?sagh a\u769?rfene s\u225?fr\u233?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Efe njam noraya \u193?roene Ambumoeta so tawalindang\u233?, w\u233?nde efe njam noraya yaufi si Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roefaf yau so tawalindang\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
"Njam f\u233?m n\u233?n\u233?mnjat \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngot, lim\u225?n\u233?gh a\u769?r a muyaf\u233? a\u769?rfefaf, f\u233?m yau m\u225?m\u233? mwigh\u233? em ndern\u225?ye f\u233?m so nawamarotati o f\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? so norayati, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram so ewatamete f\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? efghon n\u233?m\u233? so norayati."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Wem\u225?r m\u225?m\u225?fi a\u769?roene rengerenge si
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
A\u769?mb a\u769?r norayai m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u225?faf, "Watamegh a\u769?r, t\u233?mnde tane an\u233? falogh\u233?t n\u233?m\u233? tane afam euroi."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "F\u250?tar, emo w\u233?kafai y\u233?nd m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ndon efalotan rokarrokar f\u233?fene n\u233?ndk\u233?fan s\u243?mbio \u225?r?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Ndenaye fa\u769? norayai y\u233?fefaf, "Kor f\u233?t\u233?! M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fene m\u233?inyotio f\u233?nataf\u233?nat\u233? kw\u233?njtam\u233?n; m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fene gh\u233?rs\u233? yau so rokaram tawanjarng\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?yo Yesum emnday\u233?ng y\u233?n\u233? rengerenge si: "K\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n a\u769?mb wem\u225?r a\u769?r efe t\u233?morw\u233?n mband yur\u233? n\u233?m\u233? kanotaw\u233?t mer rokar ndawan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Fa\u769? nemnay\u233?ng, 'Y\u233?ndo n\u233?m\u233? so yafrotan? Tane yau kor sifay\u233? y\u233?m \u225?nde tane m\u233?inyotio rokar so ewamndan.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
"F\u233?yo fa\u769? norayai, 'Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? so yafrotan. Y\u233?ndon so yironan tane wam\u225?ng\u233?gh m\u233?ngo so y\u233?rametan ndimbalfifi, a k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?ndon tanjo ndau rokar a tanjo a\u769?mb rokar so ewamndan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?nd so korayang\u233?n tandio t\u225?f, "Tafaf em ta\u769?rfa\u769?r mer rokar ekmang ta\u769?rfa\u769?r yunj\u233?f. Afr\u225?t gh\u233?rsaye so n\u233?mor; njamke n\u233?ne k\u233?nj\u250?n, w\u233?ri nu n\u233?neyan a so n\u225?uw\u233?te."'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
"W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?mndai fa\u769?, 'F\u233?m m\u225?m\u225?fi a\u769?r\u451? Y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?mb\u225?ran f\u233?mon fene gh\u233?rs\u233? so t\u233?ram. F\u233?yo emon so tawanang\u233? m\u233?inyotio rokar f\u233?mon n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? t\u225?frende fendio?'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m ndern\u225?ye so y\u233?m a\u769?mb a\u769?r emon rokar ewamnde yandio w\u233?nde yau em wem\u225?r a\u769?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?n k\u233?nj\u250?n."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 M\u225?m\u233? mwigh\u233? yau
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
F\u233?yo Yesum emndai y\u225?njo waitogh a\u769?r, "Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?ndon emndetan, mwighayam yau ewaw\u233?rsota m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fene gh\u233?rsam\u233?n, n\u233?m\u233? so enetati; m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fene fifim\u233?n a n\u233?m\u233? so ewawo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Gh\u233?rs\u233? siy\u233?m minde tuk\u233?n, w\u233?nde njamke siy\u233?m yuwanyo y\u233?m, a fifi siy\u233?m minde tuk\u233?n, w\u233?nde s\u225?l\u225?me siy\u233?m yuwanyo y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
K\u233?retangi k\u233?t\u225?n kwagh k\u233?s em: y\u233?mofem yau eitat o etanat, y\u233?fene wam\u225?ng\u233?gh m\u233?ngo yau ewam; w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam emanjne f\u225?. F\u233?m em minde tuk\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene gh\u233?kfan a ewaindati y\u233?n\u233? men! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
F\u233?m so f\u233?yotaro em nden\u233? teke s\u225?i emor m\u233?n\u225?yan mwigh\u233? waw\u233?rsoghan y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
T\u225?f njam yau ewafrotati y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?mbne rokar, f\u233?m n\u233?mam\u233?n m\u225?m\u233? mwigh\u233? so nemnati \u225?mb rokarm\u233?n?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
"K\u233?retangi ndern\u225?ye k\u233?ghat mbumbu nanotat. F\u225? yau n\u225?s\u225?fotat minde y\u233?fenjo s\u225?l\u225?met. W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon emndetan, yau mer nden\u233? Solomon y\u225?ne m\u233?inyotio merfifi rokar k\u233?nj\u250?n f\u225? umaneghkaf t\u233?morw\u233?n nden\u233? mbumbu k\u233?s em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u225? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u233?m emo ewamanete k\u233?ghat yus, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? s\u233?nonjo y\u233?na em k\u225?ye kawaindangi a ewite f\u233?s\u233?t. Nder\u233? minde tuk\u233?n y\u233?mon n\u233?mamanete f\u233?m? Nder\u233? n\u233?mbne mwighaf\u233? f\u233?m em\u451? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
F\u233?m yau f\u233?fenjo tik\u233?fan nuitati njamkem\u233?n a num\u233?n, f\u233?m yau mwighayam ewaw\u233?rsota y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n t\u233?ndo a\u769?r y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan n\u233?rsat y\u233?n\u233? rokarot, a fene Af\u233? mat y\u233?m f\u233?fene n\u233?m\u233? m\u233?nde em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ronjati Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh, a y\u233?n\u233? rokar so tawaramang\u233? f\u233?feyot f\u233?yotaro.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
"F\u233?rf\u233?r yau em, n\u233?mbne m\u233?r\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fene Af\u233? \u225?uw\u233?ghan y\u233?m so tawaramang\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
F\u233?mofem t\u225?t\u233?rnangi f\u233?fene n\u233?m\u233? ewam a tawaramangi yauyau \u225?r\u233?t. N\u233?usnati mani y\u225?f f\u233?fendio \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yau so kefongi, f\u233?fene ngonj\u233?l so njafaran y\u233?m k\u233?t\u233? \u225?nde yau so kefongi, m\u233?nam\u233?n yau oro t\u233?fn\u225?ram so tawanangi a yau so gh\u233?njam ewas\u233?rmbotat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?nde f\u233?fene ngonj\u233?l y\u233?m, f\u233?fene tik\u233?f k\u233?t\u233? so em.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Kor gh\u233?k\u233?f s\u233?nt\u233? em
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
"T\u250?m\u233?n afreng\u233?ghkaf aem Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene a\u769?sa\u769?fogh\u233?t m\u233?inyotio efogh a s\u233?mb\u225?r, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
ndenanit a\u769?sa\u769?fogh \u225?r kawanjetaw\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?fene ndimbal \u225?r so n\u233?nangote awer\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?ndta, fa\u769? njam n\u233?nangota a n\u225?ut\u225?na, y\u233?mofem s\u233?safne t\u225?fandio so tasaw\u233?rngi y\u225?yot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Nder\u233? \u225?uw\u233?gh so y\u233?m y\u233?feyot y\u233?n\u233? a\u769?sa\u769?fogh a\u769?r\u233?t y\u233?fenjo yuram tawinjong\u233? fa\u769? ta\u769?f afreng\u233?ghkaf njam em fa\u769? s\u225?i n\u233?nangota. Y\u233?ndon f\u233?fe ewaufrotan efaloe, y\u233?mon so t\u233?fitrarng\u233? awer\u233?gh s\u225?l\u225?me m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i efrenda faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, so tamndang\u233? \u225?mnjogh\u233?t njamke sifayan a s\u225?i ewarameta y\u233?feyot njamke. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Nder\u233? \u225?uw\u233?gh so y\u233?m y\u233?feyot \u225?s\u225?fogh a\u769?r\u233?t y\u233?fene yuram njam tawinjong\u233? afreng\u233?ghkaf, fa\u769? njam n\u233?nangota y\u233?n\u233? efghon s\u233?mb\u225?r n\u233?ndk\u233?fan o akwan faurghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?m so mat em: M\u233?ngo yur\u233? mat njam t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n a\u769?rk\u233? efogh f\u233?nef\u233?nean oro t\u233?fn\u225?r so t\u233?nmorw\u233?n, y\u233?mo yau so tumyong\u233? oro t\u233?fn\u225?r y\u225?ne m\u233?ngo f\u233?trargh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
F\u233?m so afreng\u233?ghkaf em, m\u233?nam\u233?n \u193?roene Ambum s\u225?i y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? efoghf\u233?nef\u233?neyan f\u233?m yau njam nawanjeta afreng\u233?ghofnar."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
Fitam y\u233?motai, "Yur\u233?, F\u233?mo y\u233?n\u233? rengerenge si noraye t\u233?fendro o m\u233?inyotio a\u769?r\u233?t?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Yuram yawawangoi, "Efe nden\u233? y\u233?m ndimbal mwighaf\u233? a mer wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r? F\u225? y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m y\u225?njo yuram so t\u233?kmang\u233? m\u233?ngo wanjeng\u233?t s\u225?i ewarameta njamke efoghf\u233?nef\u233?neyan? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
Nder\u233? mer y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?rai y\u225?ne yuram tinjong\u233? y\u225?ne \u225?s\u225?foghan fa\u769? njam n\u233?nangota. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
Y\u233?ndon n\u233?maufrotan efaloe, y\u233?mo so t\u233?kmang\u233? fa\u769? wanjeng\u233?t y\u225?ne m\u233?inyotio rokaran. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
W\u233?nde t\u225?f faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r norayai yandio, 'Tane yuram y\u233?rse teke efogh angogh\u233?t,' a y\u233?mon ngi ewafngoi a\u769?sa\u769?fogh \u225?r a amaf, a njamke n\u233?net a w\u233?ri nu n\u233?net m\u233?n\u225?t w\u233?riot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?sa\u769?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?rane yur\u233? so n\u233?nangote y\u233?n\u233? efghon njam f\u225? yau y\u225?njeta f\u225? a yau y\u233?n\u233? efghon mat y\u233?m. Y\u225?ne yuram so t\u233?kr\u225?tan t\u233?kmang\u233? k\u233?ran a y\u233?mon so ewite y\u233?maf\u233? \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghofnar a\u769?rf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
"\u193?sa\u769?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r efe mat y\u233?m y\u225?ne ndimbaloene m\u233?nde w\u233?nde yau n\u225?frenda o yau yafrota y\u225?ne yurane m\u233?nde, f\u225? so efmote minde. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
W\u233?nde a\u769?sa\u769?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r efe yau mat y\u233?m a emo yaufi yafrote, f\u225? so efmote n\u233?mbnare. K\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? m\u233?inyotio a\u769?r\u233?t endefet ewaramete ndimbal y\u233?feyot, nden\u233? ndimbalyo so taramang\u233?. A k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? emon njam efalo yiy\u225?tota ndimbale, nden\u233? ndimbaleyo so taramang\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yau krufr\u225?t yam w\u233?nde falogh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 49\~}
"Y\u233?nd w\u233?nmorm\u233?n f\u233?s y\u233?n\u233?rsam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? mbandot, y\u233?nd nemnan f\u233?s t\u233? nawaro w\u233?nde yau nawaro\u451? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 50\~}
Fronde y\u233?nd t\u225?f so w\u233?m ndimbal t\u233?kr\u225?tan, a nder\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? yamam\u233? so wiota k\u233?t\u225?notio tane t\u233?kr\u225?t kefong\u233?\u451? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 51\~}
F\u233?m nemne y\u233?nd w\u233?nmorm\u233?n krufr\u225?t y\u233?n\u233?rsam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? mbandot? Yau, yau krufr\u225?t, w\u233?nde falogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 52\~}
Y\u233?nandm\u233? s\u233?nonjo \u225?mbiro m\u233?r\u233?n 5 so nafalotat m\u233? f\u225?ro, nambiota k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? s\u243?mbio a s\u243?mbiota k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? nambio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 53\~}
F\u225? so nafalotat, af\u233? k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? ambum a ambum k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? af\u233?, am\u233? k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? m\u233?r\u233?s a m\u233?r\u233?s k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? am\u233?, tanat al\u233? k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? nakum al\u233? a nakum al\u233? k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? tanat al\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Mat \u225?y\u225?togh efogh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 54\~}
Fa\u769? norayai m\u233?r\u233?nfaf, "Njam f\u233?mofem tawinjongi nu kw\u233?f n\u233?narmbotat mbormborta, efaloe f\u233?m so korayangi, 'Nuw\u233?t y\u233?m,' a so nafamnde. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 55\~}
A njam n\u225?ik\u225?i mbormbor y\u233?n\u233?fnje, f\u233?m so korayangi, 'So y\u233?m waft\u233?,' a so nufrote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 56\~}
Efe farun mer n\u233?retati w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau\u451? F\u233?m mat em ndern\u225?ye so tayamngongi yam mbandan a njafaran. F\u233?m yau mat em ndern\u225?ye so tayamngongi s\u233?nonjo efoghm\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 57\~}
"F\u233?m f\u233?myo mat em n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m mbark\u225?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 58\~}
Emon njam tawinjong\u233? f\u233?m k\u233?rt\u233? wafroghan mato k\u233?rt\u233? efrendati soram\u233? so eng\u233?m mogh sifayat. Yau njam, so tawerangi mogh sifayat. F\u233?yo na\u769?k wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m taramangi k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?lismanefaf a f\u233?lisman\u233?m t\u225?kmangi kw\u233?fkw\u233?f sifayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 59\~}
Y\u233?ndon emndetan, fem yau so k\u233?ntorngi k\u233?t\u225?notio f\u233?m njam m\u233?inyotio fai nufrotati."
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 13
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Kawengo o k\u233?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
T\u225?f y\u233?n\u233? efghon a\u769?mb a\u769?r tamorw\u233?n emofem Yesue yaufroy\u233?nd m\u233?nam\u233?n Galili yu a\u769?rfene f\u233?r\u233?k Failet\u233?m t\u233?r\u233?mnau y\u233?fene gh\u233?ng\u233?naf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "F\u233?m nder\u233? nemnati y\u233?n\u233? Galili yu a\u769?rfene yaufiyam \u225?rk\u233? ewafrotat y\u233?mofem ewaindat yaufiyam y\u233?fene \u225?mb \u225?r k\u233?s em Galili yum\u233?n, y\u233?n\u233? ende y\u233?mofem t\u233?kr\u225?t t\u233?fandaw\u233?t? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?ndon emndetan, yau\u451? W\u233?nde f\u233?m yau njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf kawengongi, f\u233?m m\u233?inyotio w\u233?i k\u233?r so em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
O efe 18 k\u233?r emorm\u233?n njam tuk m\u233?ngo Siloam k\u233?nj\u250?n nuyai y\u233?fefaf, f\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? nemnati y\u233?fene yaufiyamam ewainday\u233?nd y\u233?fene yaufiyam a\u769?mb k\u233?s tamorang\u233?rw\u233?n Jerusalem\u233?n? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u233?ndon emndetan, yau\u451? W\u233?nde f\u233?m yau njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf kawengongi, f\u233?m m\u233?inyotio w\u233?i k\u233?r so em." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mo tamndetau y\u233?n\u233? rengerenge si, "A\u769?r t\u233?morw\u233?n w\u233?n mbwe tiyang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u225?ne g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndau k\u233?nj\u250?n, a f\u225? t\u233?ng\u233?morw\u233?n w\u233?n mbwe eregh\u233?t, w\u233?nde y\u233?mon yau ewinjoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? norayai a\u769?roefaf emo tanjetau g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndau, 'Y\u233?nanotio nambio yunj\u233?f s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd t\u233? kw\u233?nmorw\u233?n w\u233?n mbwe eregh\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? w\u233?n mbweyot, w\u233?nde y\u233?ndo yau yinjon. T\u233?nfend! N\u233?mam\u233?n m\u233? anogh so nanote y\u233?n\u233? mbandan?'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
"\u193?rom yawangoi, 'Yur\u233?, m\u233? koro \u225?mbiro yunjfot, a y\u233?ndon so y\u233?tanan t\u233?ndom\u233? d\u233?gwrot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Njam kafong\u233? k\u233?tam\u233? yunjfan, mer\u451? Yau njam, t\u233?ngn\u233?f.'"
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Akny\u233?gh amafom freng\u233?gh yanai Safatan
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
A\u769?mb Safatan Yesum tawatametau a\u769?mb \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngon, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
a amaf t\u233?morw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram y\u233?keindam 18 yunj\u233?f. F\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n kan\u233?maf\u233? a yau tawalinjotau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Njam Yesum yinjoi f\u225?, y\u233?mo y\u233?motai fa\u769? a y\u233?mndai, "Amaf, f\u233?m n\u233?m mer." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u233?yo Yesum ng\u225?ng\u233? efayoi y\u225?faf, a t\u225?fandio nolinjoy\u233?nd a Ng\u225?nj\u225?n tuwetau.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
\u193?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngo lim\u225?ng\u233?gh a\u769?r n\u233?kw t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n Yesum mer t\u225?y\u225?totau Safatan, f\u225? korayau \u225?rfefaf, "K\u233?t\u233? sem 6 efogh a\u769?sa\u769?fogh\u233?t. F\u233?yo en\u233?m freng\u233?gh\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? efghon, yau Safatan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Yuram yawangoi y\u225?, "F\u233?m efe farun mer n\u233?retati w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau\u451? F\u233?mofem t\u250?m\u233?n taf\u233?rngi kau o ndonki k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? kw\u233?lalta a talim\u225?ngi nuot Safatan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? amaf, Ebraamene m\u233?r\u233?s, efe S\u225?ifram yumbai y\u233?keindam 18 yunj\u233?f. F\u225? f\u233?t\u233? nawanjar Safatan k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? n\u233?m\u233? yam y\u233?keinda."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Yesum njam korayau y\u233?n\u233?, y\u225?ne m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r w\u225?iw\u225?i yam ewifoi, w\u233?nde a\u769?r k\u225?uwetaw\u233?t n\u233?m\u233? mer Yesum tawafrotau.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Rengerenge si n\u233?mbne mbwe a yist
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u233?yo Yesum namotai, "Ndern\u225?ye n\u233?rete Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh? N\u233?mayaf\u233? so y\u233?t\u233?mndan? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Ndenanit n\u233?mbne mbwe, a\u769?rom y\u233?ngwanai yiyai y\u225?njo ndawan a nanotam w\u233?n n\u225?y\u225?toi, a menam nj\u233?n tarametaw\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? kafeyam\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
W\u233?ikor Yesu namotai, "Y\u233?ndon n\u233?mayaf\u233? so y\u233?t\u233?mndan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? yist amafom yanai a y\u233?r\u233?mnam nambio flaw\u233? baik. F\u233?yo m\u233?inyotio flaw\u233? n\u233?minam ndimbal kof\u233?kof\u233? namndai."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 N\u233?mbne s\u233?safne
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Yesu njam tiotau Jerusalem\u233?t, y\u233?mo tangwatametau tesenam\u233? a m\u233?ngotuam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
A\u769?mb a\u769?rom y\u233?motai Yesu, "Yur\u233?, f\u233?yotaro nambio \u225?rro so tawanjar?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mon emndai f\u225?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
"Minde na\u769?sa\u769?fotati m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m so k\u233?lawangi n\u233?mbne s\u233?safnem\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndon emndetan, t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r y\u233?ta so nufotati \u233?laugh\u233?t a yau so nufrote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
T\u225?f m\u233?ngo yur\u233? njam so k\u233?nangong\u233? a so t\u233?mnang\u233? s\u233?safne, f\u233?m so ewakai s\u233?safne t\u233?ndota n\u225?ut\u225?nati a norayati, 'Yur\u233?, s\u233?safne t\u233?saw\u233?r t\u233?fe.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "W\u233?nde y\u233?mon so tawawangong\u233?, 'Y\u233?nd mafina w\u233?m f\u233?m, o f\u233?m \u225?rkam\u233? en\u233?m.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
"F\u233?yo f\u233?m so korayangi, 'Y\u233?ndfem njamke a nu t\u225?netaw\u233?m f\u233?maf\u233?, a f\u233?mon t\u233?nmatametau endm\u233?.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
"W\u233?nde y\u233?mon so tawawangong\u233?, 'Y\u233?nd mafina w\u233?m f\u233?m o f\u233?m a\u769?rkam\u233? en\u233?m. Kitrongi ta tamb\u233?n, f\u233?m m\u233?inyotio yaufiyam wafrogh t\u233?fn\u225?r\u451?'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
"K\u233?t\u233? siy\u233?m yengam a s\u233?n krar\u233?gh, njam f\u233?mon tawinjo Ebraam, Aisek a Jeikof a m\u233?inyotio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r efe em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?ghan, w\u233?nde f\u233?m t\u233? k\u233?m\u233?witat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
A\u769?r so en\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? w\u233?rw\u233?rta a mbormborta a n\u225?ik\u225?ita a yamb\u233?rm\u233?ta, a so tawanangi y\u233?fenjo sifay\u233? k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?m\u233?nd k\u233?nj\u250?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?ghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Efe soram\u233? em f\u225? so k\u233?n\u225?y\u225?tongi frondeyot, efe fronde em fa\u769? so k\u233?n\u225?y\u225?tongi soramat."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesuene gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? Jerusalem\u233?t
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
A\u769?mb efghon a\u769?mb Farasi a\u769?r enmorm\u233?n Yesuefaf a y\u233?mnday\u233?nd, "Koro y\u233?n\u233? yu a kuano a\u769?mb sifayat. Erod\u233?m ngiot n\u233?mafngo f\u233?m." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "Nguwano taufro y\u233?n\u233? \u225?gh\u233?\u225?ghai, 'Y\u233?ndon so ewitrotan yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r, a eng\u233?frendan \u225?r s\u233?nonjo a k\u225?ye, a nambio efogh soram\u233? y\u233?ndon so tifon tanjo \u225?s\u225?fogh.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?nd m\u233? so w\u233?ng\u233?m s\u233?nonjo a k\u225?ye a \u225?mb efghon, \u225?mb Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r yau so k\u233?r em Jerusalem s\u233?mta.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
"O Jerusalem, Jerusalem, f\u233?m emofem esmetat Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r a ewafiy\u225?totat w\u237?me efe enw\u225?f\u225?retam f\u233?fefaf, y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m fene a\u769?r so eumendan, nden\u233?yame am\u233? ghak\u233?r kowiam y\u225?ne tos\u233?tos\u233? y\u233?nau tawamong\u233? njambe, w\u233?nde f\u233?m yau m\u233?nde k\u233?n\u233?m\u451? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
K\u233?reta, fene tesen so kafrangong\u233?. Y\u233?ndon n\u233?maufrotan feyot, f\u233?mon yau so kwinjo w\u233?i k\u233?t\u225?notio f\u233?m njam koraya, 'Nder\u233? freng\u233?gh y\u233?m efe y\u233?n\u233?m Yurane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan!'"
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 14
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu Farasi a\u769?roene m\u233?ngon
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
A\u769?mb Safatan, njam Yesu t\u233?ngmorw\u233?n Farasi a\u769?rfene utman\u233?gh \u225?roene m\u233?ngot n\u233?net, a\u769?r\u233?m kor t\u233?fandaw\u233?t Yesu kakafifi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
A\u769?mb a\u769?r efe t\u233?morw\u233?n kafkaf a ng\u225?ng\u233? mbwef\u233? y\u233?nmorm\u233?ng Yesuefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Yesum emotai Farasi a\u769?r a na\u769?k watamegh t\u233?fn\u225?r, "N\u233?m\u233? na\u769?k y\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t a\u769?r freng\u233?gh\u233?t Safatan o yau?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? m\u233?tar nufrotam\u233?nd. Yesum y\u233?ngwasroi a\u769?r y\u233?frendai a y\u233?ngwatembai.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Yesum emotai, "Njam endene \u225?mbiro ambum o kau kuyang\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?kw\u233?t Safatan, f\u233?mo w\u233?keye yau so turto?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
A y\u233?feyot \u225?mb yau si.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Njam f\u225? mat n\u225?y\u225?toi wan t\u233?fn\u225?ram yafery\u233?ng mer sifay\u233? njamke s\u233?kian, y\u233?mon tawaufrotau y\u233?n\u233? rengerenge si: {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
"Njam a\u769?mb a\u769?rom k\u233?mumyong\u233? f\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n awer\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?ndfaf, yau tan\u233? y\u233?n\u233? tuk sifay\u233?. Yau aem nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? sifay\u233? k\u233?s y\u233?m nawamnde \u225?roe y\u233?mo t\u233? yumyo endene em tuk\u233?n yam a k\u233?maindang\u233? f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Njam nufrota, emon njam taumiye f\u233?m so k\u233?naflend a tamndend f\u233?m, 'Fene sifay\u233? taram y\u233?n\u233? a\u769?roe.' Nder\u233? w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? y\u233?m, f\u233?mon so tan\u233? yuwon sifay\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?m njam k\u233?mumyongi, yuwon sifay\u233? tan\u233?, fene t\u233?m\u233?nd yur\u233? njam y\u233?n\u233?m, y\u233?mon so k\u233?n\u233?mndang\u233?, 'F\u250?tar, kimnda tuk sifayat.' F\u233?m so n\u233?mut\u233?mndat wan t\u233?fn\u225?rafene s\u225?fan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Efe nawarmbotat f\u225?yo so newonat yuwot, efe njam n\u233?wonat f\u225? so kay\u225?tongi ndimbal."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u233?yo Yesu norayai y\u225?njo t\u233?m\u233?nd yurafaf, "F\u233?mon njam ewarameta efoghm\u233?f n\u233?ne o s\u233?ite n\u233?ne, f\u233?mo yau taumyo fe f\u250?tar\u233?f a fene an\u233?f a fene m\u233?r\u233?n o fene wem\u225?r f\u250?tar\u233?f, f\u233?mon njam yafrota, f\u233?m so k\u233?mumyongi a so n\u233?mawaf\u225?ngotat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?mon njam tawaram njamke, taumyo yauyau a\u769?r, akny\u233?gh a\u769?r, waw\u233?r, gh\u233?k\u233?f kw\u233?fkw\u233?f a\u769?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?mofem yau so fai n\u233?mawaf\u225?ngotat. W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so n\u233?frende a fai k\u233?mawangog\u233? njam y\u225?ne a\u769?r n\u233?nanotat k\u233?rta."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Rengerenge ndimbal t\u233?m\u233?ndm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Soram\u233? Yesum si waitogh yifoi, \u225?mb wan \u225?r norayai, "Freng\u233?gh y\u233?m y\u225?yot emo so enete t\u233?m\u233?nd k\u233?nj\u250?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?ghan!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "A\u769?mb a\u769?rom t\u233?frendau ndimbal t\u233?m\u233?nd a eumyoi t\u225?rf\u225?r wan t\u233?fn\u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
T\u233?m\u233?nd efghon, y\u233?mo ew\u225?f\u225?retam y\u225?njo a\u769?sa\u769?fogh a\u769?r tanwaufrongi efe t\u233? eumyon, 'Tan\u233?m, s\u233?nonjo m\u233?inyotio rokar siy\u233?m freng\u233?ghkaf y\u233?m.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
"W\u233?nde y\u233?mofem si waufrogh ewafngoy\u233?nd. Fronde a\u769?r norayai, 'Y\u233?ndon mband t\u233? yanan, a y\u233?nd so w\u233?ng\u233?m fandagh\u233?t. Gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? kwawalo tayot.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
"A\u769?mb norayai, 'Y\u233?ndo t\u233? ewanan 5 kau, a y\u233?nd \u225?lighan w\u233?m so eufotan. Gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? kwawalo tayot.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
"W\u233?i a\u769?mb norayai, 'Y\u233?nd som\u233? naweran. F\u233?yo y\u233?nd yau so w\u233?n\u233?m.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
"A\u769?sa\u769?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r nangotam a kafrotau y\u233?n\u233? y\u225?njo yurafaf. F\u233?yo m\u233?ngo yur\u233? n\u233?kwaf\u233? naf\u233?ghetam a y\u225?f\u225?retam y\u225?njo a\u769?sa\u769?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r, 'Nguwano k\u233?tor w\u233?keye n\u233?mbne endm\u233? a k\u233?ghat endm\u233? y\u233?n\u233? tesenan a tanwasro yauyau a\u769?r, akny\u233?gh a\u769?r, gh\u233?k\u233?f kw\u233?fkw\u233?f a\u769?r a waw\u233?r.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
"A\u769?sa\u769?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?rom y\u233?mndai 'Yur\u233?, f\u233?mon n\u233?m\u233? w\u233?mndai t\u233? kufrote, w\u233?nde k\u233?t\u233? m\u233? em sifay\u233?.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
"F\u233?yo yuram y\u233?mndai y\u225?njo a\u769?sa\u769?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r, 'Nguwano k\u233?tor n\u233?mbne endm\u233? a k\u233?ghat end\u233?t a tanwaur\u233?mnau, 'K\u233?naflangi k\u233?nj\u250?t,' m\u233?n\u225?t tane m\u233?ngo so y\u233?m afoghare. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Y\u233?ndon n\u233?mndetan, efe fronde eumyong\u233?n y\u233?mofem yau so tufongi tane njamke\u451?'"
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Waitogh a\u769?roene yam
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Ndimbal m\u233?r\u233?n tayotau Yesuf\u233?, a nawengoi y\u233?fefaf y\u233?mon emndai: {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
"Efe njam y\u233?n\u233?m tafaf s\u225?i kamndang\u233? tane waitogh \u225?r, y\u233?nd so uwete mindefifi, y\u233?namayo so euwete y\u225?njo af\u233? a am\u233?, y\u225?njo amaf a ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, y\u225?ne ghak\u233?r a m\u233?r\u233?sm\u233?r\u233?s, n\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, nden\u225?yo y\u225?njo gh\u233?rs\u233?. Yau njam, f\u225? yau so y\u233?m tane waitogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
A emo yau njam y\u233?rsa y\u225?njo wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?n a kw\u233?nmaitong\u233? y\u233?nd f\u225? yau so y\u233?m tane waitogh a\u769?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
"Njam efe a\u769?r m\u233?nde y\u233?m ndimbal m\u233?ngo ramgh\u233?t, f\u225? fronde so k\u225?mnjong\u233? a nuf\u233?nmeta y\u233?fanda nj\u233?namb mani y\u233?m wifogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Y\u233?mon so tafngong\u233? m\u233?ngo ram\u233?gh, w\u233?nde yau so tifong\u233?. F\u233?yo m\u233?inyotio a\u769?r\u233?m y\u233?fandat n\u233?m\u233? nufrote so yurtat fa\u769?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
F\u225? korayaw\u233?t, 'Y\u233?n\u233? a\u769?rom y\u233?rnyai ram\u233?gh w\u233?nde yau yifoi.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
"N\u233?m\u233? so yafrote warsagh a\u769?rom t\u225?f y\u225?ne njam em 10,000 fiyar\u233? yandio awamarogh\u233?t k\u233?tam\u233? a\u769?mb warsagh \u225?r emaf\u233? so n\u225?sm\u233?t 20,000 fiyaraf\u233?? Fronde njam kuwanong\u233? m\u233?kot, f\u233?yo f\u225? so k\u225?mnjong\u233? mwigh\u233? so y\u233?farone waing\u233?gh\u233?t? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
F\u225? yau njam y\u233?m f\u233?yotarofnar, y\u233?mon so y\u225?f\u225?rete si r\u233?sagh a\u769?r t\u225?fandio a\u769?mb m\u233? esio a f\u225? so kw\u243?mnendang\u233? krufr\u225?tot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? endeyo, f\u233?mon tafrango m\u233?inyotio rokar, f\u233?m so n\u233?m tane waitogh a\u769?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
"Sol siy\u233?m mer y\u233?m, w\u233?nde y\u225?ne m\u233?nde njam kefong\u233?, ndern\u225?ye so sol nawafarnj\u233? w\u233?ikor? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Yau mer y\u233?m mbandot o \u225?mb rokarot, \u225?r\u233?m t\u225?f y\u233?ngwitat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Efe njam t\u233?nganaf\u233? y\u233?m, so ka\u769?ya\u769?rang\u233? y\u233?n\u233? si."
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 15
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Oling\u233?gh Sif
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Mani kaf\u233?gh \u225?r a yaufiyam t\u233?fn\u225?r m\u233?inyotio k\u225?umendaw\u233?t \u225?y\u225?rgh\u233?t y\u225?faf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
W\u233?nde Farasi \u225?r a n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r mike nufngoy\u233?nd, "Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rom eumyote yaufiyam \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mafe n\u233?net."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?yo Yesum tawaufrotau y\u233?n\u233? rengerenge si, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
"Njam \u225?mbiro \u225?roene em 100 sif a kolindang\u233? \u225?mbiro, n\u233?m\u233? so yafrote? Y\u233?mon efaloe so tafrangong\u233? 99 marat sifayan a nguwanong\u233? oling\u233?gh sif ronjagh\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u233?mo tinjong\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
T\u225?f y\u233?mon njam tinjong\u233?, y\u233?mo \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? tambnang\u233? sif t\u233?fayong\u233? y\u225?ne fader tuk\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u225? so nguwanong\u233? m\u233?ngot. F\u233?yo y\u233?mon emotai y\u225?ne f\u250?tar\u233?f a \u225?mb kaka \u225?r a norayai y\u233?fefaf, '\u193?uw\u233?gh yangotam y\u233?ndf\u233?. Y\u233?ndon t\u233? yinjon tane oling\u233?gh sif.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Y\u233?ndon emndetan f\u233?m k\u233?t\u233? njafaran nden\u233?yameyo k\u233?t\u233? so y\u233?m ndimbal \u225?uw\u233?gh. Efaloe \u225?uw\u233?gh 99 mbark\u225?nd \u225?rfenem\u233?n efe em yaufiyamofnar, y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m n\u233?mbnarfifi, w\u233?nde minde \u225?uw\u233?gh y\u233?m \u225?mbiro yaufiyam \u225?r efe njam kawengong\u233? y\u225?njo yaufita.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Oling\u233?gh mani mbwe
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
"N\u233?m\u233? so yafrote amafom t\u225?f y\u225?ne 10 silf\u233? mani mbwe em a kolindang\u233? \u225?mbiro? Y\u233?mon t\u225?f lambef\u233? tuwarong\u233? a s\u225?mbur\u233?gh m\u233?ngo tafngong\u233? ronjagh merk\u233?r\u225?ye k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u233?mon tinjong\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mon njam yinjoi, y\u233?mon emotai f\u250?tar\u233?f a \u225?mb kaka \u225?r a norayai y\u233?fefaf, '\u193?uw\u233?gh yangotam y\u233?ndf\u233?, y\u233?ndon t\u233? yinjon tane oling\u233?gh mani mbwe.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?ndon emndetan f\u233?m, nden\u233? endeyo, k\u233?t\u233? so y\u233?m \u225?uw\u233?gh Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r s\u225?fr\u233?re \u225?mbiro yaufiyam \u225?r efe njam kawengong\u233? yaufita."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Oling\u233?gh ambum
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Yesum w\u233?ikor si y\u233?ngwafngoi, "K\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?r s\u243?mbio ambumaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Kertrom y\u233?mndai y\u225?ref\u233?, 'Af\u233?, y\u233?nd yau so nawanjetan k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?m k\u233?r n\u233?m. S\u233?nonjo kwaram fene rokarta tane n\u233?m\u233? so em.' F\u233?yo y\u233?mon ewafaleyai rokar n\u233?ndk\u233?fan y\u225?njo s\u243?mbio ambumat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
"F\u233?yo tekofnaye, kertrom ewanai y\u225?ne n\u233?m\u233? tamorw\u233?n, n\u225?frendam nuwanoi nayu yuwot a mani taran\u233?gh y\u233?ngwafngoi yaufi gh\u233?rsayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? y\u233?mon njam ewifoi m\u233?inyotio rokar, k\u233?t\u233? nuyai k\u225?uk\u225?u y\u233?n\u233? yuwon, f\u233?yo f\u225? \u225?ronjagh nufngoi sioghm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? nuwanoi \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t n\u243?mnendai \u225?mb \u225?rfefaf y\u233?n\u233? yuwon, a \u225?rom y\u233?ngw\u225?f\u225?retam f\u225? kimb wanjeng\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u225? minde siogh t\u233?morw\u233?n, f\u225? m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n kimbafene njamke mbarmbar n\u233?net. W\u233?nde emo yau taramangai y\u225?yot n\u233?mndafi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
"F\u225? njam n\u233?nangoi mwighat, f\u225? norayai, 'M\u233?inyotio tane afane faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r f\u233?yotaro njamkeyan em, a y\u233?na y\u233?nd sw\u233?m krotro w\u233?m\u451? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?nd so nangotan tane afafaf a t\u233?mndan, "Af\u233?, y\u233?ndon yaufiyam t\u233? tafrotan njafarot a fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?nd yau f\u233?yotaro w\u233?m s\u225?i w\u233?mndeta fene ambum. Y\u233?nd kuy\u225?to ndenanit fene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r."' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? nokayoi a nuwanoi y\u225?refafaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Njam k\u233?t\u233? m\u233? t\u233?nmorw\u233?n nayu, y\u225?refam y\u233?ngwinjoi f\u225? a gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? yam yafoi y\u225?nem\u233?n. F\u225? n\u233?ngengoi y\u225?njo ambumoefaf a yambnai a t\u233?snetau.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
"Ambumom y\u233?mndai y\u225?ref\u233?, 'Af\u233?, y\u233?ndon yaufiyam t\u233? tafrotan njafarot a fefaf. Y\u233?nd yau w\u233?mndeta fene ambum y\u233?nd w\u233?m.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
"W\u233?nde y\u225?refam y\u233?mndai y\u225?ne faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, 'W\u233?keye\u451? Mer tot\u233?r s\u225?l\u225?me t\u233?nmawanangi a tawongi. Talawend ghil y\u225?ne ng\u225?ngayan tawend sandol kafkafan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
T\u233?nmanengi yarsaf\u233? kau t\u233?smangi. So t\u233?m\u233?nd yafrotam a \u225?uw\u233?gh yangotam, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? tane ambum efe k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n s\u233?nonjo gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?m. F\u225? t\u233? nolindai a s\u233?nonjo t\u233? yinjong\u233?m.' F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem \u225?uw\u233?gh tangotaw\u233?t. {\cs259\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 |GR-gn33n_noLabel.tif|col||\u169? Global Recordings Network, globalrecordings.net.|Oling\u233?gh ambum: y\u225?ref\u233? n\u233?rse kert\u233?r ambumoefaf (Luk 15.20)|15.20}

\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
"T\u225?fandio, fronde s\u233?nko ambum t\u233?morw\u233?n ndawan. F\u225? njam n\u233?n\u225?y\u225?toi m\u233?ngo kaka, f\u225? n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?ng wagh ke a erm\u225?ng\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mon yanmoi \u225?mb faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r a y\u233?motai n\u233?m\u233? yam nufrote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Y\u233?mon yawangoi, 'Fene n\u233?ng\u233?n t\u233? nufar, a fene afam yarsaf\u233? kau t\u233? y\u233?s\u233?m m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? y\u233?na y\u233?m a merro y\u233?m.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
"F\u233?yo fronde s\u233?nko ambum n\u233?kw n\u225?werai a yau n\u233?lawai m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?t. Y\u225?ref\u233? n\u233?ntory\u233?ng a yamnendai \u233?laugh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?mo yawangoi y\u225?refai, 'K\u233?reta\u451? M\u233?inyotio yunj\u233?f y\u233?ndon \u225?s\u225?fogh tafrotan feyot a yau kwawalinde fene si. W\u233?nde f\u233?mon n\u233?m\u233? \u225?mb yau waramai ta tos\u233? gout m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ndfem t\u233?m\u233?nd s\u225?i tafrotaw\u233?m tane f\u250?taraf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
W\u233?nde njam y\u233?n\u233? fene ambum emo fene mani t\u225?t\u233?rnaw\u233?ng yaufi gh\u233?rayan k\u233?nangote m\u233?ngot, f\u233?mon yesmang yar\u233?saf\u233? kau y\u225?yot\u451?'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
"Y\u225?ref\u233? norayai, 'Tane ambum, f\u233?m t\u250?m\u233?n y\u233?ndf\u233? t\u233?nre. M\u233?inyotio rokar tane sem fene em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndfem \u225?sneghaf\u233? a \u225?uw\u233?gh tafrotam m\u233?nam\u233?n feng\u233?n k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n a s\u233?nonjo gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?m. F\u225? nolindai a s\u233?nonjo y\u233?na y\u233?m.'"
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 16
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Mwigh\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Yesum emndai y\u225?ne waitogh \u225?r, "\u193?mb wem\u225?r \u225?rom y\u233?kafai \u225?r y\u225?ne rokar wanjeng\u233?t. W\u233?nde wem\u225?r \u225?roe yaufroy\u233?nd nden\u233? rokar wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?rom fene mani t\u233? ewalinda. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mo yanmoi f\u225? a y\u233?motai, 'N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m y\u233?nd n\u225?y\u225?ran fenem\u233?n? Kwaram fene \u225?s\u225?foghm\u233?n mat ndernaye tanjete, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m yau so n\u233?m wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233?.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
"Wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r norayai y\u225?faf\u233?tio, 'Y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? so yafrotan s\u233?nonjo? Tane yuram tane \u225?s\u225?foghta wut\u233?r. Y\u233?nd muyafnar w\u233?m targh\u233?t, a y\u233?nd w\u225?iw\u225?i w\u233?m \u243?mneng\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon so yafrotan m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?r\u233?m m\u233? so umyotat y\u233?nd y\u233?fene m\u233?ngom\u233? njam y\u233?ndon tanjo \u225?s\u225?fogh koron.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
"F\u233?yo y\u233?mon tamotau \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiroe y\u225?ne yurane fai wangogh\u233?t. Y\u233?mo y\u233?motai fronde \u225?r, 'Nj\u233?namb fai ekmang tane yurane?' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?mo yawangoi, '20 dram olif w\u233?kw\u233?r.' Wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?rom y\u233?mndai f\u225?, 'T\u233?ngwan fenjo fef\u233?, k\u225?mnjo w\u233?keye, a tafarota 10 dram.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
"W\u233?i y\u233?mo y\u233?motai y\u233?namayo \u225?r, 'Fefaf nj\u233?namb em?' Y\u233?mon yawangoi y\u225?, '1,000 flaw\u233? baik.' Y\u233?mon y\u233?mndai f\u225?, 'T\u233?ngwan fenjo fef\u233?. Tafarota k\u233?t\u225?n 800 flaw\u233? baikot.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
"Yuram tuwetau y\u225?ne uny\u233?gh rokar wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? kawarawenau merk\u233?r\u225?ye. \u193?r y\u233?n\u233? mbandan nawarawenat merk\u233?r\u225?ye w\u233?nde kwayaghane \u225?r yau nden\u233? em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?fe, f\u250?tar n\u225?y\u225?totati f\u233?myo mband rokere, njam tafrango, f\u233?m so k\u233?mumyong\u233? tuot m\u233?ngotuot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
"Efe njam ndimbal mwighaf\u233? y\u233?m n\u233?mbne yaman, nden\u225?yo w\u233?i so y\u233?m ndimbal yaman. Efe njam uny\u233?gh \u225?r n\u233?mbne yaman y\u233?m, nden\u225?yo w\u233?i ndimbal yaman so y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?m yau njam efalo n\u233?m mbandoene rokar wanjeng\u233?t, ndern\u225?ye f\u233?m so niy\u225?totat efalo wem\u225?ran? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
A f\u233?m yau njam efalo k\u233?n\u233?m \u225?mb \u225?roene rokar wanjeng\u233?t, emon so k\u233?maramang\u233? fenjo rokar?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
"\u193?s\u225?fogh \u225?r yau so y\u233?m s\u243?mbio yurafene lim\u225?n\u233?gh mbanmbanan. F\u233?mon so y\u233?kene \u225?mb a so yuwete \u225?mb, o f\u233?m so kamnyong \u225?mbfaf a t\u233?kena \u225?mb. Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m yau so s\u243?mbio lim\u225?n\u233?gh mbanmbanan n\u233?m, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a mani."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Farasi \u225?r sem mani m\u233?ndero \u225?r em. Y\u233?mofem njam n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? si a f\u233?n yafngoy\u233?nd Yesu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Yesum emndai f\u225?, "F\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m efe mer nitaro k\u233?namndangi \u225?rfene gh\u233?kfan, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n mat y\u233?m f\u233?fene tik\u233?f. N\u233?m\u233? minde tuk\u233?n \u225?rfene mwighayan fifiofnar y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene gh\u233?kfan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
"Mosesene n\u225?k a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?roene watamegh si t\u225?itotaw\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?notio Jonene efogh. K\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? y\u233?n\u233? efghon, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?ghm\u233?n mer si waitogh y\u233?rnyai, m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m end t\u225?ronjaw\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?ghfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
\u193?fr\u225?te y\u233?m njafar a mband so kawaindangend, w\u233?nde n\u233?mbne si Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene sian yau so titr\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
