\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Wem\u225?r \u225?r a Lajarus
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
"K\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n wem\u225?r \u225?r efe kumanetau minde tuk\u233?n s\u225?l\u225?me a t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u225?njo meran m\u233?inyotio efghon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u225?ne m\u233?ngo s\u233?safnefaf k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n \u243?mneng\u233?gh \u225?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Lajarus efe t\u233?morw\u233?n f\u233?nend k\u233?r ro {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
a m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n n\u233?net n\u233?m\u233? kuitaw\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? wem\u225?r \u225?roene njamke kitarata. T\u225?fandio \u225?gh\u233? tanmorw\u233?n tasambnaw\u233?t y\u225?ne f\u233?nend. {\cs259\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 |IB-048gr.tif|col||by Farid Faadil. \u169? Biblica, Inc. Used with permission. All rights reserved worldwide.|Lajarus w\u233?m\u225?roene s\u233?sfnefaf \u225?ghaf\u233? (Luk 16.20-21)|16.20-21}

\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
"\u211?mneng\u233?gh \u225?r k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n a njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r y\u233?nmorm\u233?n a y\u233?ngwasroy\u233?nd f\u225? k\u233?t\u225?n Ebraamefaf. F\u233?yo wem\u225?r \u225?r k\u233?r y\u233?morm\u233?n a yiy\u225?totam\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Efoghofnar y\u233?kw sifayan, wem\u225?r \u225?r t\u233?kr\u225?tan t\u233?morw\u233?n, njam f\u225? n\u233?retai tuk\u233?t yinjoi Ebraam nayuta, y\u233?maf\u233? Lajarus y\u225?ne t\u233?ndota. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? nutnai, 'Af\u233? Ebraam, tayot gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? a t\u233?mnde Lajarus ng\u225?ng\u233? tauwarng\u233? nuan a tane k\u225?nk\u233? krufr\u225?t tiy\u225?to m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd f\u233?s k\u233?nj\u250?n t\u233?kr\u225?tan w\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
"W\u233?nde Ebraam\u233?m yawangoi, 'Ambum, kawafarota k\u233?t\u233? fene gh\u233?rs\u233? \u225?mnjogh efghon, f\u233?m meran k\u233?nmorw\u233?n, t\u225?f Lajarus yauyauan, w\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo f\u225? enaghan y\u233?m y\u233?na a f\u233?m t\u233?kr\u225?tan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
\u193?mb t\u233?f\u233?n siy\u233?m, f\u233?yotarofnar y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?kw ndimbalam y\u233?nfalow\u233?, m\u233?n\u225?t efe m\u233?nde \u233?f\u233?rman\u233?gh\u233?t y\u233?nandm\u233? fefaf siy\u233?m t\u225?ik\u233?r y\u233?m.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
"Y\u233?mo yawangoi, 'F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon n\u233?mamnendan f\u233?m, af\u233?, t\u233?ngw\u225?f\u225?reta Lajarus k\u233?t\u225?n tane afane m\u233?ngot, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
m\u233?nam\u233?n tane em 5 n\u233?ngn\u233?f. Mat so t\u225?y\u225?tong\u233? f\u225? yau so en\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?kr\u225?t sifayat.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
"Ebraam\u233?m yawangoi, 'Buk k\u233?t\u233? em Moses a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r efarotam\u233?nd, f\u225? s\u225?i n\u225?y\u225?retat y\u233?fendio.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
"F\u225? norayai, 'Yau, af\u233? Ebraam, \u225?mb k\u233?r \u225?r njam n\u233?ngangota k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?fefaf, f\u225? so kawengongi.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
"F\u225? norayai y\u225?faf, 'Yau njam n\u225?y\u225?retat Moses a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?roefaf, f\u225? yau so nawengotat w\u233?i nden\u233?yameyo k\u233?r tamb\u233?n njam k\u233?nangong\u233? gh\u233?rsat.'"
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 17
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Watamegh w\u225?ny\u225?ny\u233?ghm\u233?n a ndimbal mwigh\u233?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Yesu norayai y\u225?njo waitogh \u225?rfefaf, "\u193?rk\u233? yaman em\u233?inde \u225?r t\u250?m\u233?n yaufiot, w\u233?nde t\u233?kr\u225?t y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? \u225?roe emo em\u233?inde. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?roefaf ndimbal w\u237?m so yumbetat k\u233?man a yitat arakafot, y\u233?n\u233? m\u233? t\u233? y\u233?m n\u233?mbne k\u233?rt\u233?. W\u233?nde emo tam\u233?inde n\u233?mbne ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r yaufiot, fene k\u233?rt\u233? so y\u233?m ndimbal. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?yo kor kafandangi f\u233?myo.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Njam fenam yaufi yafrota, y\u225?rna, a f\u225? njam kawengong\u233?, tawalinda. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Njam y\u233?mo yaufi yafrota fefaf 7 mbinotm\u233? \u225?mbiro efogh k\u233?nj\u250?n, a 7 mbinotm\u233? n\u233?nangota w\u233?ikor fefaf a korayang\u233?, 'Y\u233?nd t\u233? nawengon,' f\u233?mon tawalinda."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r norayay\u233?nd Yurafaf, "Yur\u233?, t\u233?nmamina t\u233?fene ndimbal mwigh\u233?\u451?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "Njam fene ndimbal mwigh\u233? y\u233?m ndenanit n\u233?mbne mbwe, f\u233?m f\u233?yotaro so koraya y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal w\u233?nfaf, 'Karufang a kayang arakafan,' a so k\u233?ny\u225?r\u225?ng\u233? f\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
"Njam fene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r n\u233?nangota tar\u233?gh tamb\u233?n o sif wanjeng\u233?gh tamb\u233?n, ndimbal \u225?r so korayang\u233?, 'K\u233?naf k\u225?mnjo njamke n\u233?net'? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? so korayang\u233?, 'Tane njamke kwanegh, kw\u225?frenda a kwanjeta njam enetan. Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? f\u233?mo so enete.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
K\u225?njo yaramai faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?roe m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne \u225?y\u225?r\u233?ghm\u233?n n\u233?mat y\u233?mon y\u233?mndai wafrogh\u233?t? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Nden\u233?yameyo f\u233?mofem njam ewafrotati m\u233?inyotio n\u233?mat t\u233? emndai wafrogh\u233?t, norayay\u233?nd, 'Y\u233?nd si\u233?n\u233?m faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rro y\u233?n\u233?m. Y\u233?ndfem tanwafrotam t\u233?fenjo \u225?s\u225?foghro.'"
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 10 \u225?r yaufi gh\u233?ngan enjnef\u233?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Yesu \u225?lighan t\u233?morw\u233?n Jerusalem\u233?t, tiotau Samaria a Galili yu n\u233?ndk\u233?fan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u225? njam kufanau m\u233?ngotuot, 10 \u225?r yaufi gh\u233?ngan enjnef\u233? tamorw\u233?n y\u233?f\u225?ngoy\u233?nd f\u225?. F\u225? n\u233?nokayoy\u233?nd nayu {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
a nutnay\u233?nd minde tuk\u233?n, "Yesu, Yur\u233?, gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? t\u233?feyot\u451?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Yesum ewinjoi f\u225? a norayai, "Nguanongi, ngauyafongi f\u233?myo gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?rfefaf." A njamandio n\u233?ngwanoy\u233?nd, f\u225? mer n\u233?ngamnday\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
\u193?mbiroam, njam yinjoi freng\u233?gham yanai, n\u233?nangoi, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n tuwetaw\u233?t minde tuk\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u225? budme niyai Yesuene kafkaffaf, k\u225?njo yaramai y\u225?yot. F\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n Samariam\u233?n \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Yesum y\u233?motai, "N\u233?m\u233? 10 \u225?r m\u233?inyotio freng\u233?ghkaf em? \u193?nde \u225?mb 9 \u225?r em? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
N\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? T\u233?ndo \u225?rro n\u233?nangoi Ng\u225?nj\u225?n freng\u233?gh\u233?t?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u233?yo Yesum y\u233?mndai f\u225?, "Kokai a nguwano. Fenjo ndimbal mwighayam mer t\u233? niy\u225?to."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
\u193?mb efghon Farasi \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?motai Yesu, "Njam so Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh y\u233?n\u233?m?" Yesum ewawangoi, "Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh yau y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? ende f\u233?mon so tinjo fenjo gh\u233?kfe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
F\u233?m yau so norayati, 'Siy\u233?m' o 'K\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m' m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh siy\u233?m f\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
F\u233?yo Yesu norayai y\u225?njo waitogh \u225?rfefaf, "Efogh y\u233?na y\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?m njam so m\u233?nde em winjogh\u233?t \u225?mb efghon \u193?roene Ambumoenem\u233?n, w\u233?nde f\u233?mofem yau so tinjongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
\u193?r\u233?m so tawaufrongi f\u233?fe, 'K\u233?t\u233? f\u225? y\u233?m,' o 'Y\u233?na f\u225? y\u233?m.' Yau n\u233?waitotati y\u233?fe soram\u233? y\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n \u193?roene Ambum njam n\u233?nangota, m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m so y\u233?fandat ndenanit toy\u233? kwayaghanit so t\u233?l\u225?l\u225?ng\u233? witm\u233? njafar kw\u233?ndkw\u233?ndta k\u233?t\u225?n witm\u233? njafar kw\u233?ndkw\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
W\u233?nde fronde y\u233?mon so t\u225?rf\u225?r t\u233?kr\u225?t efande a so y\u233?kenat y\u233?n\u233? sat\u233? \u225?r m\u233?rnam.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
"Ndenaye f\u233?t\u233? Noane efghon k\u233?s tamorw\u233?n, nden\u233?yameyo so y\u233?m \u193?roene Ambumoene efghon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
\u193?r\u233?m njamke a nu t\u225?netaw\u233?t, amaf \u225?r kaweretaw\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?n efogh nawerai Noa n\u233?lawai minde ndimbal ng\u225?rndot. F\u233?yo t\u225?f k\u233?f\u233?r nakmai a y\u233?rambary\u233?ng m\u233?inyotio \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
"Nden\u233?yameyo tamorw\u233?n Lotene efghon. \u193?r\u233?m njamke a nu t\u225?netaw\u233?t, k\u233?ufnamotaw\u233?t rokar, njamke y\u233?ghan a m\u233?ngo ram\u233?ghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? efghon Lot\u233?m y\u233?frangoi Sodom, f\u233?s a f\u233?saf\u233? w\u237?m k\u233?nuitaw\u233?t njafarta nunit kafamndau, a y\u233?rambary\u233?ng m\u233?inyotio \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
"Nden\u233?yameyo \u193?roene Ambumoene efghon so nufrote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghon efe m\u233?ngo t\u233?ndon em yau so k\u233?nyawangi m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?t rokar r\u233?sagh\u233?t. Nden\u233?yameyo, efe ndawan em yau so n\u233?ngangotat rokar r\u233?sagh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Yafarotati Lotene amaf\u451? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Emo njam y\u233?ta y\u225?njo gh\u233?rs\u233? yambeta so y\u233?tarne, emo njam y\u233?tarna y\u225?njo gh\u233?rs\u233? so kawanjarng\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Y\u233?ndon n\u233?maufrotan fe, y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?mb\u225?ran s\u243?mbio \u225?r so ekmare \u225?mbiro k\u233?m\u233?gh sifayan, \u225?mb Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so t\u233?ngwanang\u233? \u225?mb so t\u233?frangong\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
S\u243?mbio amaf so n\u233?us\u233?nan\u233?t njamke m\u233?rne, \u225?mb so y\u233?mon t\u233?ngwanang\u233?, \u225?mb so t\u233?frangong\u233?." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
