 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?motay\u233?nd, "\u193?ndan, Yur\u233??"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum ewawangoi, "\u193?nde k\u233?r f\u250? y\u233?m, ndik\u225?k\u233? k\u233?t\u233? so n\u225?umendat."
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 18
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Rengerenge si kwiranem\u233?n a mwigh\u233? faror\u233?gh \u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Yesum tawaufrotau y\u225?njo waitogh \u225?r\u233?t a rengerenge si ewauyafoi y\u233?fe f\u225? so t\u250?m\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayat a yau so k\u233?kmbongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Yesu norayai, "\u193?mb tesenan k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n mwigh\u233? faror\u233?gh \u225?r efe Ng\u225?nj\u225?n f\u233?rf\u233?rofnar t\u233?morw\u233?n utman\u233?ghofnar \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
K\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?mb kwir\u233? y\u233?n\u233? tesen k\u233?nj\u250?n efe kat\u233?rnau t\u250?m\u233?n y\u225?faf siaf\u233?, 'Ta kwaram mbark\u225?nd y\u233?n\u233? si \u233?wighm\u233?n m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?raf\u233? siy\u233?nmare.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
"N\u225?k s\u233?nko \u225?rom y\u233?kenai \u225?mb efghot, w\u233?nde ambinom\u233?n norayai y\u225?njom\u233?n, 'Y\u233?nd f\u233?rf\u233?rofnar w\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf a utman\u233?ghofnar \u225?rfefaf, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? kwiram t\u250?m\u233?n waw\u233?rsote y\u233?nd, y\u233?ndon so tinjon y\u225?faf mbark\u225?nd, m\u233?n\u225?t yau so n\u233?nat\u233?rne tafaf t\u250?m\u233?n\u451?'"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? norayai, "K\u225?y\u225?rangi k\u233?t\u225?n n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?n\u233? mbark\u225?ndofnar mwigh\u233? faror\u233?gh \u225?r norayai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so f\u233?t\u233? enwarse mbark\u225?nd y\u225?njo wafer\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?t, efe nendat y\u225?faf efogh a s\u233?mb\u225?r. Y\u233?mon yau so t\u250?m\u233?n ekarote f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?ndon n\u233?maufrotan fe, y\u233?mon so tinjong\u233? nde y\u233?maf\u233?m mbark\u225?nd yanangi w\u233?keye. W\u233?nde njam \u193?roene Ambum n\u233?nangota, y\u233?mon so tawinjong\u233? efe em ndimbal mwighaf\u233? y\u233?n\u233? mbandan?"
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Farasi \u225?r a mani kaf\u233?gh \u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Yesum tawaufrotau y\u233?n\u233? rengerenge si \u225?mb \u225?roefaf efe tawewonaw\u233?t nden\u233? kemnaw\u233?t nden\u233? y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m mbark\u225?nd \u225?r a f\u225? yau: {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
"S\u243?mbio \u225?r nuwaneyay\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngot Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oraigh\u233?t, \u225?mb t\u233?morw\u233?n Farasi \u225?r a \u225?mb t\u233?morw\u233?n mani kaf\u233?gh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Farasi \u225?r nokayoi Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? koraiw\u233?t, 'Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, k\u225?njo fe nden\u233? y\u233?nd yau w\u233?m nden\u233? \u225?mb \u225?r k\u233?s em, oro t\u233?fn\u225?r, yaufi wafrogh \u225?r, amaf wan\u233?gh \u225?r, o ndenanit y\u233?n\u233? mani kaf\u233?gh \u225?r k\u233?s em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?nd nawafarmetan s\u243?mbio efogh \u225?mbiro Safatan a y\u233?ndon t\u250?m\u233?n ram\u233?gh yam so yafrotam Mosesene n\u225?kam noraye Ng\u225?nj\u225?neyot.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
"W\u233?nde mani kaf\u233?gh \u225?r takayong\u233?rw\u233?n nayu. F\u225? yau n\u233?wewoi nden\u225?yo njafarot, w\u233?nde y\u225?njo kafan nasmai a norayai, 'Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? tayot, y\u233?nd yaufi \u225?r w\u233?m.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
"Y\u233?ndon n\u233?mndetan f\u233?m, y\u233?n\u233? yaufi \u225?r, yau nden\u233? Farasi \u225?r, f\u225? kangotau m\u233?ngot \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene s\u225?fr\u233?re. F\u233?m njam nawarmbota \u225?mb \u225?rfefaf, f\u233?m so k\u233?meworngi, a f\u233?m njam yuwan n\u233?m, f\u233?m so n\u233?m tuk\u233?n."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r a Yesu
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
\u193?r\u233?m tan\u233?rsaw\u233?t ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r Yesuefaf m\u233?n\u225?t freng\u233?gh\u233?t. Njam waitogh \u225?r\u233?m yinjoy\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?, y\u233?mofem ekmboy\u233?nd y\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
W\u233?nde Yesum emotai ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r y\u225?faftio norayai, "Tanumyongi ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r k\u233?naflangi tafaf, yau ekmbotati ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh siy\u233?m nden\u233? \u225?r\u233?t ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r k\u233?s em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?ndon efalo si ewaufrotan, \u225?mb \u225?rom emo yau tanang\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh ndenanit ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r sem yau so k\u233?nyawangi."
