\u193?mb Ju s\u233?nko \u225?rom y\u233?motai f\u225?, "Mer watamegh \u225?r, n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon so yafrotan tuot gh\u233?rs\u233? r\u233?sagh\u233?t?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "N\u233?mam\u233?n w\u233?mndete y\u233?nd mer? Efe yau mer y\u233?m f\u225? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
F\u233?m mat n\u233?m n\u225?kn\u225?k, 'Amafanyo wan\u233?gh yau, \u225?r ngi yau, oro yau, uny\u233?gh yau, eutmanw\u233? af\u233? a am\u233?.'"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Y\u233?mo y\u233?mndai, "K\u233?t\u225?ndmayo y\u233?nd tos\u233? kw\u233?morw\u233?n, y\u233?ndon y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?inyotio n\u225?k tawaraw\u233?naw\u233?n." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Yesum njam n\u225?y\u225?rai y\u233?n\u233?, f\u225? norayai y\u225?faf, "Fefaf m\u233? n\u225?l\u225?ite \u225?mb yam wafrogh\u233?t. Et\u233?rna maniot fene n\u233?m\u233? em m\u233?inyotio, ewarameta y\u233?feyot yauyau \u225?r\u233?t, a f\u233?m so n\u233?m wem\u225?r njafaran. F\u233?yo k\u233?naf, kw\u233?nmaito y\u233?nd."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u233?mon njam n\u225?r\u225?yai y\u233?n\u233? si, f\u225? nawinjoi gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisaf\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n minde wem\u225?r \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Yesum y\u233?fandai a y\u233?mndai, "Nder\u233? t\u225?ik\u233?r y\u233?m nden\u233? wem\u225?r \u225?r\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u233?laugh\u233?t\u451? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Taikre kemole \u233?law\u233?gh nidul f\u233?nem\u233? siy\u233?m ndimbal, w\u233?nde taikre wem\u225?r \u225?roe \u233?laugh\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? yam y\u225?inde."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
