Yesum ewawangoi, "N\u233?m\u233? t\u225?ik\u233?r y\u233?m \u225?r\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?neyot siy\u233?m \u225?frat."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Fit\u233? norayai y\u225?faf, "Y\u233?ndfem enfrangong\u233?m m\u233?inyotio t\u233?fene n\u233?m\u233? tam f\u233?m n\u233?maitong\u233?m\u451?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
