so kor ewinjotati t\u225?rf\u225?r mbinotm\u233? s\u233?nonjo y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?rayan, a so akegh gh\u233?rs\u233? tinjongi Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta soram\u233? yuwon."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu w\u233?ikor korayau y\u225?njo k\u233?rm\u233?n
