Yesum ewasroi 12 waitogh \u225?r t\u233?ndot a emndai f\u225?, "Y\u233?nd kuwanong\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n Jerusalem\u233?t, a m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?farotam\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?m \u193?roene Ambumoenem\u233?n so nufrote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
