"N\u233?m\u233? wafrogh\u233?t m\u233?nde n\u233?m tafaf?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mon yawangoi, "Yur\u233?, y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m \u233?regh\u233?t."
