Yesu t\u233?ngmorw\u233?n Jerikom\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
\u193?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n Jekies, f\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n mani kaf\u233?gh s\u233?nko \u225?r efe t\u233?morw\u233?n wem\u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u225? m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n Yesue fandagh\u233?t, w\u233?nde nd\u233?mbnd\u233?mb \u225?rm\u233?n yau yinyoy\u233?ng m\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n takayong\u233?rw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? frondeyo nengoi a narmboi ndimbal w\u233?nan ndenanit wanj w\u233?n Yesue winjogh\u233?t, t\u225?f Yesu m\u233? t\u233?ngmorw\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? endm\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Njam Yesu nufary\u233?ng y\u233?n\u233? sifayan, Yesu n\u233?wewoi tuk\u233?t a y\u233?mndai f\u225?, "Jekies, k\u233?newor w\u233?keye yuwot. Fene m\u233?ngon s\u233?nonjo so w\u233?mor." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? n\u233?newory\u233?ng w\u233?keye a Yesu \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? yumyoi y\u225?njo m\u233?ngot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
M\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m yinjoy\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? yam a mikemike nufngoy\u233?nd, "F\u225? n\u233?ngwanoi wan t\u233?fn\u225?r n\u225?y\u225?toi yaufi \u225?roefaf."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
W\u233?nde Jekies nokayoi a norayai Yurafaf, "K\u233?reta, Yur\u233?\u451? S\u233?nonjo y\u233?nandm\u233? y\u233?ndon efalotan n\u233?ndk\u233?fan tane rokar yauyau \u225?r\u233?t, a y\u233?nd njam t\u233? kuindan \u225?rfefaf rokarm\u233?n, so ewangotan y\u233?fene fai fo mbinotma."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Yesu norayai y\u225?faf, "S\u233?nonjo wanjar\u233?gh y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ngot, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r siy\u233?m Ebraamene \u225?kim\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n \u193?roene Ambum y\u233?nmorm\u233?n ronjagh\u233?t oling\u233?gh \u225?r wanjargh\u233?t."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Rengerenge si ten faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rfenem\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Njam f\u225? k\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?t y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, y\u233?mon tawawaitotau rengerenge si m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n Jerusalem kaka a \u225?r kemnaw\u233?t nden\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh kar s\u233?lngw\u233?le so kufarngai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u225? norayai, "\u193?mb s\u233?nko \u225?r nuwanoi nayu yuwot m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225?yo n\u225?y\u225?toi warsagh \u225?r a so w\u233?i n\u233?nangote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mon emotai ten faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r a y\u233?feyot ewarametam \u225?mb r\u233?rero ndimbal mani. F\u225? norayai, 'Takmangi y\u233?n\u233? mani \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u233?nd n\u233?nangotan.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
"W\u233?nde y\u225?njo \u225?r\u233?m m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat tafandaw\u233?t a ew\u225?f\u225?retam f\u233?nat\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh m\u233?r\u233?n soram\u233? f\u225? norayay\u233?nd, 'Y\u233?nd m\u233?ndefnar y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r s\u225?i kamndang\u233? t\u233?fene warsagh \u225?r.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
"F\u225? n\u225?y\u225?toi warsagh \u225?r f\u233?yo f\u225? n\u233?nangotam m\u233?ngotuot. F\u233?yo y\u233?mon ew\u225?f\u225?retam faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?n endefet mani ewarametam m\u233?n\u225?t matot nj\u233?namb mani ewafrotam\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
"Fronde \u225?mbiro \u225?r y\u233?nmorm\u233?n a norayai, 'Yur\u233?, fene maniam t\u233? efuna \u225?mb ten.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
"Y\u225?ne yuram yawangoi, 'Mer y\u233?m. Tane mer faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r\u451? M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m t\u233? efalo n\u225?y\u225?to n\u233?mbne mani funaghan, f\u233?mon so ewanjete ten ndimbal tesen.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
"S\u243?mbiom\u233?n y\u233?nmorm\u233?n a norayai, 'Yur\u233?, fene maniam t\u233? efuna \u225?mb 5.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
"Y\u225?ne yuram yawangoi, 'F\u233?mon so ewanjete 5 ndimbal tesen.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
"Nambiom\u233?n faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r y\u233?nmorm\u233?n a norayai, 'Yur\u233?, fene mani siy\u233?m. Y\u233?ndon fene mani tamndan a etnoy\u233?n s\u225?l\u225?me sutaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Y\u233?nd fenem\u233?n f\u233?rf\u233?r kw\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m n\u233?m t\u225?ik\u233?r \u225?r. F\u233?mon tot\u233?r n\u233?m\u233? yau y\u233?lawai a y\u233?tane n\u233?m\u233? yau yiy\u225?y\u233?ng.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
"Y\u225?njo yuram yawangoi, 'Y\u233?ndon so k\u233?mawit\u233?rmbon fe fenjo sieyo, f\u233?m yaufi faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r\u451? F\u233?m mat n\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?m t\u225?ik\u233?r \u225?r a y\u233?ndon ewangotan \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yau em tane a etanan y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? y\u233?ndon yau eitam\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
N\u233?mam\u233?n w\u233?t tane mani yau y\u233?lawai mani funagh sifayan m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?nd njam n\u233?nangotan, y\u233?ndon so tinjong\u233?n minaghkaf?'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
"F\u233?yo y\u233?mon f\u225? emndai efe tawakayong\u233?rw\u233?n kaka, 'Takawangi y\u225?ne mani y\u225? tamb\u233?n a taramangi y\u225? efe ten maniaf\u233? y\u233?m.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
"F\u225? norayay\u233?nd, 'Yur\u233?, t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?tongi ten mani y\u225?ne\u451?'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
"Y\u233?mon tawangong\u233?, 'Y\u233?ndon n\u233?mndetan nden\u225?ye m\u233?inyotio endene t\u225?rf\u225?r em, y\u225? so taramangi t\u225?rf\u225?r, w\u233?nde endene yau em, so takawangi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
W\u233?nde tane m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r efe em m\u233?ndefnar f\u225? em y\u233?nd s\u225?i w\u233?m y\u233?fene warsagh \u225?r, tanwasrongi a t\u225?smetangi tane s\u225?fr\u233?re.'"
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu warsagh \u225?r n\u233?lawete Jerusalem\u233?t
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? si soram\u233? Yesu t\u233?ngmorw\u233?n frondeyo Jerusalem\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Njam kaka n\u225?y\u225?toi Betefes a Betani mband tunak\u233?f yu y\u233?tkw\u233?n olif\u233?n, y\u233?mon ew\u225?f\u225?retangeyai y\u225?njo s\u243?mbio waitogh \u225?r, emndeyai f\u225?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
"Kuwanend m\u233?ngotuot fronde, njam k\u233?lawend, so tinjend ndonki r\u233?ny\u233?ghkaf, efe yau y\u233?fayong\u233?rm\u233?n. T\u233?nferend a y\u233?n\u233?mnj\u233?t y\u233?nan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
\u193?mb \u225?rom njam tamotang\u233?, 'N\u233?mat f\u233?mofem y\u233?fer\u233?t?' taufrend y\u225?, 'Yur\u233? m\u233?nde y\u233?m.'"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efe ewafarem\u233?ng nuwaneyay\u233?nd a yinjeyay\u233?nd ndern\u225?ye t\u233? eng\u233?mndeyai f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Njamandio y\u233?mofem t\u233?ferw\u233?t ndonki, y\u233?n\u233? yuram emotangeyai f\u225?, "N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mofem y\u233?fer\u233?t ndonki?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Y\u233?mofem yawangeyay\u233?nd, "Yurane m\u233?nde y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?n\u233?mnjem\u233?nd Yesuefaf, y\u233?fenjo s\u225?l\u225?me efayeyay\u233?nd ndonkiyan a Yesu nafayoi y\u233?n\u233? tuk\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
Njamandio Yesu t\u233?ngmorw\u233?n, \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?fenjo s\u225?l\u225?me tang\u233?fyangotaw\u233?t endm\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
F\u225? njam t\u233?ngmorw\u233?n kaka n\u233?ngamndai y\u233?n\u233? sifayan \u225?nde end ngewonau Olif Mband tunakfot, m\u233?inyotio Yesuene waitogh \u225?r nufngoy\u233?nd wagh \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf marat k\u233?me, t\u233?f\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fandaw\u233?t Yesuefaf:
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
"Freng\u233?gh n\u233?m warsagh \u225?r efe n\u233?n\u233?m Yurane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan\u451?
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Krufrat njafar tuk\u233?n a ndimbal kwayagh\u233? minde tuk\u233?n!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
\u193?mb Farasi \u225?r k\u233?nj\u250?n norayay\u233?nd Yesuefaf, "Watamegh \u225?r, t\u225?w\u225?rna fene waitogh \u225?r\u451?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Y\u233?mon ewawangoi, "Y\u233?ndon emndetan f\u233?m, njam f\u225? m\u233?tar ekmbo, w\u237?m so nutnat\u451?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
Njam Yesu kaka ufargh\u233?tro t\u233?morw\u233?n Jerusalem\u233?t, y\u233?ngwinjoi y\u233?n\u233? tesen, Yesu t\u225?f ye nufngoi y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
a norayai, "Jerusalem\u233?n \u225?r, y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m f\u233?m mat kamndangi s\u233?nonjo n\u233?m\u233? yam krufr\u225?t y\u233?n\u233?rse f\u233?fefaf, w\u233?nde yau mat em. M\u233?nam\u233?n t\u233?noghe y\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? f\u233?fene gh\u233?k\u233?fta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
Efogh y\u233?na en\u233?m f\u233?feyot njam f\u233?fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?ram so tawarendangi f\u233?m a tawanawangi f\u233?fe m\u233?inyotio t\u233?ndom\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
Y\u233?mofem so tawalindangi f\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n mbandot, f\u233?m a ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r fene sifayan. Y\u233?mofem \u225?mb yau so taurongi w\u237?m kw\u233?ndkw\u233?ndan yaufifi, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem yau y\u225?yamngongi Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene wanjar\u233?gh f\u233?feyot."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
F\u233?yo Yesu n\u233?lawai w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo sifayan a wifar\u233?gh ewafngoi emofem rokar t\u233?w\u225?fnamotaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
F\u225? norayai y\u233?fefaf, "Buk sian y\u233?kai, 'Tane m\u233?ngo so y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh m\u233?ngo,' w\u233?nde f\u233?mofem yiy\u225?tongi oro t\u233?fn\u225?rafene \u225?tnogh y\u233?kw."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
M\u233?inyotio efghon f\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n watameghan w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon. W\u233?nde lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r, n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r a lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r m\u233?nde tamorw\u233?n Yesue ngiot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?mofem yau end ewinjoy\u233?nd y\u225? ngiot, m\u233?nam\u233?n m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfene mwigh\u233? tarnyang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u225?ne sifaf.
