Y\u233?mon ewawangoi, "Y\u233?ndon so nden\u233?yameyo f\u233?m t\u233?motang\u233?n \u225?mogh si. Ta kwaufrongi, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
