F\u225? t\u233?ngmorw\u233?n tawawaitotau \u225?r\u233?t rengerenge si, "\u193?r\u233?m yeitam g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndawan, noroi faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rfefaf a nuwanoi teke. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Wau yuwon y\u233?mon y\u225?faretam faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?n ndau wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?rfefaf m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mofem so t\u233?ramangi y\u225?yot \u225?mb g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj mbwe y\u233?n\u233? ndaum\u233?n, w\u233?nde wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m t\u233?smetaw\u233?t f\u225? a y\u225?tembay\u233?nd firo rokarofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u225?f\u225?retam y\u233?namayo faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r\u233?m nden\u233?yameyo t\u233?smetaw\u233?t, m\u225?m\u233? w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? y\u225?tembay\u233?nd firo rokarofnar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u225?f\u225?retam nambiom\u233?n a t\u233?smetaw\u233?t f\u233?rkaf\u233? yitam\u233?nd f\u225?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
"G\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndau yur\u233? norayai, 'Y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? so yafrotan? Y\u233?ndon so y\u233?ngw\u225?f\u225?retan tane ambum efe y\u233?ndon yuwetan. Efalo yiy\u225?toi y\u233?mofem so yut\u233?mndat.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
"W\u233?nde njam ndau wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m yinjoy\u233?nd f\u225?, y\u233?mofem korayaw\u233?t y\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?nro, 'Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m ndau yurane ambum y\u233?m. W\u233?t y\u233?smetam krotio f\u225?, a ndau rokar so k\u233?namndangi t\u233?fene.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem yitam\u233?nd g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndau k\u233?nj\u250?ta a yesmay\u233?nd krotio f\u225?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "N\u233?m\u233? so yafrote g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndau yuram y\u233?fefaf? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u225? so y\u233?n\u233?m a eng\u233?smete krotio y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n a tawaramang\u233? g\u233?reif mbwe m\u233?nj ndau \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?t."
