Yesu n\u233?ngretai y\u233?fefaf mbark\u225?ndaye a emotai, "F\u233?yo n\u233?m\u233? fifi y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? y\u233?farotam\u233?nd,
\par\pard\plain \s77\ql\fi-720\lin1080\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 'S\u233?ras\u233?r \u225?rk\u233? m\u233?ngo ram\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?ram y\u233?kenay\u233?nd a namnday\u233?ng n\u233?ndk\u233?f s\u233?ras\u233?r.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
