\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
N\u225?k watamegh \u225?r a lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r end t\u225?ronjaw\u233?t wergh\u233?t w\u233?keye, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd nde f\u225? korayau y\u233?n\u233? rengerenge si y\u233?fenem\u233?n. W\u233?nde f\u225? f\u233?rf\u233?r tamorw\u233?n \u225?rfenem\u233?n.
