W\u233?nde Moses\u233?m njam yufarotam\u233?ng k\u233?ghat f\u233?s aw\u225?roghan, y\u233?mon yuyafoi nden\u233? k\u233?r so nanotat gh\u233?rsat. Y\u233?mon t\u233?motau Yur\u233? 'Ebraamene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, Aisekene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a Jeikofene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
