"Kor nawarawenati n\u225?k watamegh \u225?rfenem\u233?n. F\u225? m\u233?nde em tomb\u233? s\u225?l\u225?mef\u233? areng\u233?t a s\u225?i eut\u233?mndat t\u233?rar\u233?gh sifayan, a y\u233?fene mwigh\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n minde mer sifayan \u225?mnjogh\u233?t \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n a y\u233?mofem m\u233?ndef\u233? tafandaw\u233?t lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? t\u233?mndan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
Y\u233?mofem uny\u233?ghe kwirafene rokar tawarsaw\u233?t a f\u225? mermer kuindaw\u233?t tomb\u233? sie Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh \u225?r s\u225?fan. Nden\u233? \u225?r\u233?m t\u233?kr\u225?t so y\u233?rsat minde tuk\u233?n."
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 21
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Kwirane ram\u233?gh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Njamandio Yesu n\u233?ngretai, y\u233?mon ewinjoi wem\u225?r \u225?r\u233?m takmetaw\u233?t ram\u233?gh rokar w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?mon yinjoi yauyau kwir\u233? s\u243?mbio n\u233?mbne mani mbwe k\u233?mghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?mon emndai, "Y\u233?ndon efalo ewaufrotan, y\u233?n\u233? yauyau kwiram ewaindai f\u225? emofem mani takmetaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
M\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r\u233?m takmetaw\u233?t n\u233?mbnare t\u225?rf\u225?r rokarta, w\u233?nde kwiram ekmeyai m\u233?inyotio y\u225?njo gh\u233?rs\u233? \u225?mnjoghm\u233?n."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Kerker efoghene ufarogh yam
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
\u193?mb y\u225?ne waitogh \u225?r tamorw\u233?n sian m\u233?nam\u233?n ndern\u225?ye w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo yamanetam\u233?nd mer w\u237?me a ram\u233?gh yam wateghkaf Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne. W\u233?nde Yesu norayai, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
"M\u233?inyotio f\u233?mo n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?fande y\u233?na, efogh y\u233?na y\u233?n\u233?m \u225?nde \u225?mbiro w\u237?m yau so kafrangong\u233? k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? \u225?mbta, m\u233?inyotio so ewite yuwot."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u225? namotay\u233?nd, "Watamegh \u225?r, njam so y\u233?n\u233? yam nufrotat? A n\u233?m\u233? yamam so tufarotang\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?n\u233? yam ufrogh\u233?tro em?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?mon ewawangoi, "Kor f\u233?t\u233? aem f\u233?m warsoghm\u233?n. Mwigh\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r so en\u233?m tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, nden\u233? siaf\u233?, 'Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Yesu,' a 'Efogh siy\u233?m kaka y\u233?m.' Yau ewaitotati f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Njam f\u233?m n\u225?y\u225?retati m\u233?km\u233?n a s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yamm\u233?n, yau t\u225?f f\u233?rf\u233?r em. Y\u233?n\u233? yam f\u233?t\u233? so nufrotat frondeyo, w\u233?nde mbandoene y\u225?togh yau m\u233? so y\u233?n\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? norayai y\u233?fefaf, "\u193?mb yu a \u225?mb yu, f\u225? so n\u225?sm\u233?t, \u225?mb ndimbal yu a \u225?mb ndimbal yu, f\u225? so n\u225?sm\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
K\u233?t\u233? so y\u233?m ndimbal sokrere, k\u225?uk\u225?u, ndimbal enjne t\u225?rf\u225?r yuwom\u233? a f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? yam a ndimbal s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam njafaran.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
"W\u233?nde y\u233?mofem so k\u233?merangi a k\u233?rtayan k\u233?n\u233?kmangi f\u233?m soram\u233? y\u233?n\u233? yam so nufrotat. F\u233?m so n\u233?mumbetat \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngon a k\u233?marmbnangi kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngot, a n\u233?ngemnjat warsagh \u225?r a gafanafene s\u225?fr\u233?re tane y\u233?tkw\u233?n t\u233?fnan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? so fiy\u233?m efoghf\u233?nef\u233?ne si waitogh\u233?t fene ndimbal mwigham\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?m mwighayam yau n\u233?maworsota frondeyo ndern\u225?ye f\u233?m so nawamarote f\u233?myo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u233?ndo so k\u233?maramang\u233?n si a k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?ram yau so k\u233?mitrombong\u233? o k\u233?n\u233?mndang\u233? f\u233?m n\u233?m uny\u233?gh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?m so s\u233?n erametat afafemyo, amafemyo, anafemyo, m\u233?rnamyo, f\u250?taramyo a y\u233?mofem f\u233?m so \u225?mb krot ekmetat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
M\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m f\u233?m so m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat efandat m\u233?nam\u233?n tanem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
W\u233?nde fene \u225?mbiro s\u233?nko s\u233?f yau so kolindang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u233?m so taikrataye ewakai m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?mo so tinjo efalo gh\u233?rs\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
"F\u233?mofem njam Jerusalem tinjongi fiyar\u233? wareng\u233?ghkaf em t\u225?f f\u233?m so mat k\u225?y\u225?tongi nde y\u225?ne was\u233?rmbogh siy\u233?m kaka y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Mat t\u225?y\u225?tongi efe Judiam\u233?n \u225?r em t\u225?f kangongi k\u233?t\u225?n mband tunakfot, efe tesenan em t\u225?f k\u233?torngi, efe em tesen s\u233?mta yau k\u233?lawangi tesenot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efogh fifiyaf\u233? n\u225?y\u225?toi \u225?rk\u233? t\u233?kr\u225?tm\u233?n y\u233?farotam\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi so y\u233?m suaf\u233? amafafet y\u233?n\u233? efogh a mbrake amafafet\u451? K\u233?t\u233? so y\u233?m ndimbal t\u233?kr\u225?t y\u233?n\u233? mbandan a n\u233?kw y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u225? so enfetat naifaye krotio a \u225?mb so eweretat kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngo \u225?rot m\u233?inyotio ndimbal yuwot. Jerusalem so y\u233?s\u233?nat T\u233?ndo \u225?r\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?notio T\u233?ndo \u225?rfene efogh ufroghfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
K\u233?t\u233? s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam so em efghan, gh\u233?rareyan a k\u233?ndafefaf. Mband tuk\u233?n, m\u233?inyotio ndimbal yuwom\u233? so y\u233?m mwigh\u233? nd\u233?mke a uw\u233?rsoghan m\u233?nam\u233?n arakaf s\u243?f su kem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
\u193?r f\u233?rf\u233?re so nuitat, m\u233?nam\u233?n k\u233?rt\u233? n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? mbandot, njafarm\u233?n fifi so n\u225?s\u225?mbnetat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghon y\u233?mofem so tinjongi \u193?roene Ambum angoghan njafar kwamkwaman m\u233?n\u225?yaf\u233? waftaf\u233? a ndimbal kwayaghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Njam y\u233?n\u233? yam ufrogh kufngongi, kokayongi a tauyongi f\u233?fene s\u233?nko, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fene wanjar\u233?gh siy\u233?m kaka y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Y\u233?mon tawaufrotau y\u233?n\u233? rengerenge si, "T\u233?fandangi fig w\u233?n a m\u233?inyotio w\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Njam w\u233?n mbambam \u233?wiwogh kufngongi, f\u233?mofem so tinjongi f\u233?fendio a mat kamndangi nde efogh yu siy\u233?m kaka y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? endeyo, njam yefandati y\u233?n\u233? yam ufroghan, f\u233?m mat so kamndangi nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh siy\u233?m kaka y\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
"Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?fe efalo si, \u225?mb \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? satam\u233?n so m\u233? em gh\u233?rs\u233? njam m\u233?inyotio yam nufrotat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Njafar a mband so kawaindangend, w\u233?nde tane si yaufifi so kawaindang\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
"Kor nawarawenati, f\u233?fenjo tik\u233?f yau ewaghnati w\u233?ri nuye, wagh t\u233?mnde a mbandoene m\u233?ghm\u233?ghe m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? efgham so t\u225?f k\u233?merang\u233? sunsune ndenanit ur\u233?rnit. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? efogh so y\u233?n\u233?m m\u233?inyotio y\u233?fefaf efe emor y\u233?n\u233? mbandan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
Aya t\u250?m\u233?n gh\u233?k\u233?f s\u233?nt\u233? aem n\u233?retati a Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m so kawanjarngi k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? n\u233?m\u233? ufrogh\u233?t em, a f\u233?m so taikrataye ewakai \u193?roene Ambum s\u225?fr\u233?re."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
M\u233?inyotio efghon Yesu t\u233?morw\u233?n watameghan w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon, a f\u225? tangmorw\u233?n m\u233?inyotio s\u233?mb\u225?ran Olif Mband tunakfan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
M\u233?inyotio \u225?r tanmorw\u233?n t\u250?m\u233?n t\u225?nd\u225?i akwan \u225?y\u225?rgh\u233?t y\u225?faf w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngot.
