\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Minaghofnar flawam\u233?n t\u233?m\u233?nd, y\u233?tkw\u233?n Waing\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?nd kaka k\u233?namndetau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r a n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r\u233?m \u225?mb end t\u225?ronjaw\u233?t Yesue wergh\u233?t, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? f\u233?rf\u233?r tamorw\u233?n \u225?rfenem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?yo S\u225?if\u233?r n\u233?lawai Judas Iskariotefaf, efe \u225?mbiro nafaloi 12 \u225?rm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
A Judas t\u233?ngmorw\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?rfefaf a w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?rfefaf a taruindaw\u233?t y\u233?maf\u233? ndern\u225?ye y\u233?mon so s\u233?n t\u233?ramangai Yesu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u225? k\u225?uw\u233?taw\u233?t a nuwangoy\u233?nd mani ramgh\u233?t y\u225?yot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Judas nuwangoi a k\u233?retau end t\u225?ronjau Yesue wergh\u233?t \u225?rofnar sifayan.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Soram\u233? njamke
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Efogh nawerai Minaghofnaye flawam\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m Waing\u233?gh sif tosane gh\u233?ng\u233?nm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Yesum ewafarem\u233?ng Fit\u233? a Jon a norayai, "Kuwanend y\u233?freng\u233?gh\u233?t Waing\u233?gh njamke t\u233?fe n\u233?net."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?motangeyay\u233?nd, "\u193?ndan fene m\u233?nde y\u233?m t\u233?feyot freng\u233?gh\u233?t?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Yesum ewawangeyai, "Njam ng\u233?lawend tesenot, \u225?r so tinjend nu s\u233?fkw\u233?naf\u233? y\u233?mon so tafange. F\u233?mofem t\u233?ngwaitend \u225?rk\u233? m\u233?ngot njam ng\u233?lawang\u233?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
a t\u233?mndend m\u233?ngo yur\u233?, 'Watamegh \u225?r\u233?m namote, "\u193?nde y\u233?m wan t\u233?fn\u225?roene m\u233?ngo sat\u233?, \u225?nde y\u233?ndon so enetan Waing\u233?gh njamke tane waitogh \u225?rf\u233??"' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?mon so tawauyaf\u233? f\u233?fe ndimbal m\u233?ngo sat\u233? tuk\u233?n, m\u233?inyotio teghkaf y\u233?m. Afreng\u233?gh k\u233?t\u233? ay\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u225? n\u233?waneyay\u233?nd rokar ewinjeyay\u233?nd nden\u225?ye f\u233?t\u233? Yesum ndern\u225?ye tamnd\u233?w\u233?ng. F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem y\u233?freng\u233?m\u233?nd Waing\u233?gh njamke.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Njam efoghf\u233?nef\u233?ne nawerai, Yesu a y\u225?njo muyaf\u233? \u225?r n\u233?n\u225?mnjoy\u233?nd njamke sifayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
A Yesum emndai f\u225?, "Y\u233?nd minde m\u233?nde kw\u233?m njamke n\u233?net f\u233?maf\u233? soram\u233? t\u233?kr\u225?t so y\u233?fandan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?fe, y\u233?ndon yau so enetan w\u233?ikor k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u233?n\u233? nufrota Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?ghan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Soram\u233? kafusi yerai, y\u233?mon k\u225?njo yaramai a norayai, "Tawanangi y\u233?n\u233? a tafalotangi f\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?nro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?fe y\u233?ndon yau so y\u233?f\u233?rtan w\u233?ri nu kor k\u233?t\u225?notio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh k\u233?nufarng\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?mon f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? yerai, k\u225?njo yaramai a etfoi, a ewaramai, y\u233?n\u233? siaf\u233?, "Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m tane fifi, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? so t\u233?raman f\u233?feyot. Y\u233?n\u233? yafrotati awafarogh\u233?t tanem\u233?n."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Nden\u233? endeyo, njamke soram\u233? y\u233?mon yerai kafusi, nden\u233? siaf\u233?, "Y\u233?n\u233? kafusi siy\u233?m tot\u233?r r\u233?ny\u233?gh tane f\u233?r\u233?k k\u233?nj\u250?n \u225?rk\u233? so nasune f\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emo y\u233?nd so s\u233?n w\u233?ramuete siy\u233?m y\u233?na y\u233?ndf\u233? y\u233?nmorare. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
\u193?roene Ambum so k\u233?r y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?ndeyan, w\u233?nde nder\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? \u225?roe emo s\u233?n y\u233?ramete." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u225? \u225?mogh nufngoy\u233?nd y\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?nro efe y\u233?na yafnyang t\u233?fefaf emon so s\u233?n y\u233?ramete.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u233?yo \u233?wigh nufngoy\u233?nd y\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?nro efe so y\u233?m ndimbal. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Yesu norayai y\u233?fefaf, "T\u233?ndo \u225?rfene warsagh \u225?r yur\u233? kamndangi waftaf\u233? y\u233?fenjo \u225?r lim\u225?ngh\u233?t, w\u233?nde f\u225? emndetat, 'F\u250?tar em \u225?rfene.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?m yau so nden\u233? em. W\u233?nde efe ndimbal y\u233?m so y\u233?m ndenanit ambumtos\u233?, a efe lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r y\u233?m f\u225? so y\u233?m ndenanit faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Efe y\u233?m ndimbal, y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efe y\u233?mor kitarayan o y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efe faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r y\u233?m? Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efe y\u233?mor kitarayan. W\u233?nde y\u233?nd w\u225?f\u233?in f\u233?fefaf faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?m f\u225? em efe tanwakai tafaf tane ufoghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
A Y\u233?ndon ewaraman f\u233?fe waft\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?ngh\u233?t nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? tane Afam waft\u233? waramai ta, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?mofem so enetati njamke a nu tane kitarayan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?ghan, a so emorang lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifayan, Israilm\u233?n 12 \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n moghan so ewakai.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu norayai Fitane kenaghm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u233?mndai, "Saimon, Saimon, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam muy\u233? yaramai S\u225?if\u233?re fe ufogh\u233?t ndenanit ndau t\u233?fn\u225?ram yafrote witr\u233?mbogh\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? mer mbweta yaufiot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? koraiwam feyot, Saimon, nde fene ndimbal mwigh\u233? yau so kuyang\u233?. F\u233?m njam k\u233?nawengo tafaf, f\u233?mon so muyaf\u233? ey\u225?tote feng\u233?n\u233?f."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?mon yawangoi, "Yur\u233?, y\u233?nd afreng\u233?ghkaf w\u233?m f\u233?maf\u233? \u225?ligh\u233?t kw\u233?fkw\u233?f sifayat a k\u233?t\u225?n krot."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "Y\u233?ndon n\u233?mndetan f\u233?m, Fit\u233?, f\u233?mon so kw\u233?kena nambinotm\u233? nde f\u233?m mafina n\u233?m tanem\u233?n soram\u233? ghak\u233?r kowi kutnang\u233? s\u233?nonjo."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
F\u233?yo Yesum emotai f\u225?, "Y\u233?ndon njam ew\u225?f\u225?retan f\u233?m mani y\u225?fofnaye, awogh y\u225?fofnaye o sandolofnaye, n\u233?m\u233? rokar \u225?mb n\u225?l\u225?ite?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mofem yawangoy\u233?nd, "Yau."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
Y\u233?mon emndai f\u225?, "W\u233?nde t\u225?f s\u233?nonjo mani y\u225?f tanangi a awogh y\u225?f tawanangi, a njam yau ewam f\u233?fene n\u225?if\u233?, s\u225?l\u225?meyaf\u233? t\u233?t\u233?rnangi \u225?mbiro n\u225?ifat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Buk si y\u233?kai, 'A f\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n waf\u233?ghkaf yaufi \u225?rfe k\u233?nj\u250?n.' Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?feyot nde y\u233?n\u233? yam efalo so nufrote tafaf. N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?farotam\u233?nd tanem\u233?n so efalo nufrote."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Waitogh \u225?r norayay\u233?nd, "T\u233?fanda, Yur\u233?, s\u243?mbio n\u225?if\u233? sere."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mon ewawangoi, "F\u233?yotaro ere."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesuf Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? koraiw\u233?t Olif Mband tunakfan
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
Yesu tiotau t\u250?m\u233?n mband tunak\u233?f y\u233?tkw\u233?n Olif, a y\u225?njo waitogh \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?namayo t\u225?itotaw\u233?t f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Njam nufary\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? sifayan, y\u233?mon emndai f\u225?, "Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayatati m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m yau so kuyangi ufoghan." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
F\u225? nitroi nayuofnaye y\u233?fetamb\u233?n a budme niyai Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oraigh\u233?t, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
"Af\u233?, fene m\u233?nde t\u233?u y\u233?m, y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?kr\u225?t titro ta tamb\u233?n, tane m\u233?nde yau, w\u233?nde fene m\u233?ndero so nufrote."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
Njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r nufary\u233?ng y\u225?faf a y\u225?ut\u225?nam f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
Yesum ndimbal t\u233?kr\u225?t y\u225?y\u225?rai, f\u225? minde tikfe Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? koraiw\u233?t a y\u225?ne m\u233?lm\u233?l t\u233?morw\u233?n ndenanit f\u233?r\u233?k nj\u233?lk\u233?fnit kasunau mbandot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
Njam f\u225? nokayoi Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?ghta f\u225? n\u233?ngangoi y\u225?njo waitogh \u225?rfefaf, y\u233?mon ewinjoi k\u233?mghan, yongnai gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisam\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
Yesum emotai f\u225?, "N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m k\u233?m\u233?gh ek\u233?m? Kanongi a Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? norayati m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m yau so ufogham tawutfong\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu yeray\u233?nd
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
Njamandio Yesu m\u233? sian t\u233?morw\u233?n, \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n enmorm\u233?n a \u225?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Judas efe t\u233?morw\u233?n 12 waitogh \u225?rm\u233?n, y\u233?mon tanlimndau f\u225?. Y\u233?mon y\u225?netai Yesu a y\u233?snetai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
W\u233?nde Yesum y\u233?motay\u233?ng f\u225?, "Judas, f\u233?mon s\u233?not yafngo \u193?roene Ambum m\u233?naye s\u233?negh\u233??"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 49\~}
Njam Yesuene waitogh \u225?r\u233?m yinjoy\u233?nd n\u233?m\u233? ufrogh\u233?tro t\u233?morw\u233?n, f\u225? norayay\u233?nd, "Yur\u233?, w\u233?t y\u233?ndfem so enfetam t\u233?fenjo naifaye?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 50\~}
A \u225?mb \u225?rom yanfai lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?roene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?roene tamb\u233?n t\u233?ngan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 51\~}
W\u233?nde Yesu norayai, "Y\u233?n\u233? yau yafrotati\u451?" A Yesum y\u233?n\u233? \u225?roene t\u233?ngan yayanjai a mer yiy\u225?toi f\u225?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 52\~}
F\u233?yo Yesu norayai lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?rfefaf, w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r a s\u233?nko \u225?r, efe t\u233? enmorm\u233?n y\u225?yot, "N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?nd \u225?y\u225?rghofnar \u225?rfene s\u233?nko \u225?r w\u233?m? \u193?rk\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m tan\u233?m naifayaf\u233? a timayaf\u233?? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 53\~}
M\u233?inyotio efghon y\u233?nd f\u233?maf\u233? t\u233?nmorw\u233?n w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon, f\u233?mofem y\u233?nd yau kw\u233?fandaw\u233?t n\u233?kwaf\u233?. W\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo f\u233?fene efogh t\u233? nawer, njamandio kw\u233?fkw\u233?foene waft\u233? f\u233?fefaf y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fitam y\u233?kenay\u233?ng Yesu
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 54\~}
Y\u233?mofem yeray\u233?nd Yesu, y\u233?ng\u233?mnjoy\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?roene m\u233?ngot. Fitam tangwaitotau nayu k\u233?r\u225?ye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 55\~}
A njam y\u233?mofem f\u233?s yuwaroy\u233?nd mogh sifay\u233? n\u233?ndk\u233?fan a f\u225? n\u225?mnjoy\u233?nd m\u233?rne, Fit\u233? w\u233?i n\u225?mnjoi y\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 56\~}
\u193?s\u225?fogh m\u233?rsom yinjoi f\u225? f\u233?s kwayaghayan t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n. M\u233?rsom y\u225?yamngoi f\u225? a y\u233?mndai, "Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r \u225?mb fiy\u233?m Yesue waitogh \u225?r."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 57\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?mon yanyotay\u233?ng a y\u233?mndai, "M\u233?r\u233?s, y\u233?nd mafina w\u233?m f\u225?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 58\~}
Tekofnaye \u225?mb \u225?rom w\u233?i yinjoi f\u225?yo a y\u233?mndai, "F\u233?m \u225?mb y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?k\u233?n\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?mon yawangoi, "\u193?r, y\u233?nd yau\u451?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 59\~}
\u193?mbiro efoghf\u233?nef\u233?ne soram\u233? \u225?mb \u225?rom m\u233?njtaye korayaw\u233?t nden\u233?, "F\u225? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m Yesue kaka \u225?r, efe y\u233?m Galili yum\u233?n."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 60\~}
Fitam yawangoi, "\u193?r, y\u233?nd mafina w\u233?m f\u233?m n\u233?mam\u233?n noraye\u451?" Njamandio korayau, ghak\u233?r kowi t\u225?f nutnay\u233?ng. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 61\~}
Yur\u233? nawengoi t\u233?fandang\u233? Fit\u233?. Fit\u233? nawafarotay\u233?ng Yurane si ndern\u225?ye y\u233?n\u233?mndai f\u225?, "F\u233?mon so kw\u233?kenang y\u233?nd nambinotm\u233? soram\u233? ghak\u233?r kowi so kutnang\u233? s\u233?nonjo." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 62\~}
A f\u225? n\u233?tory\u233?ng s\u225?f\u233?t ndimbal ye nendam.
