F\u225? norayai y\u233?fefaf, "N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m n\u233?worsotati, n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?fene mwigh\u233? d\u233?ud\u233?u nanote? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
Tafandangi tane s\u243?mbio ng\u225?ng\u233? a s\u243?mbio kafkaf. Y\u233?nd y\u233?ndio efalo f\u233?t\u233? w\u233?m\u451? Kwiy\u225?nja y\u233?nd a kw\u233?fandangi. B\u233?rseb\u233?rse yau y\u233?m fifiyaf\u233? a sotaf\u233?, f\u233?mofem k\u233?s w\u233?fandati y\u233?nd f\u233?t\u233? w\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Njam f\u225? korayau y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, y\u233?mon tawauyafotau y\u225?ne ng\u225?ng\u233? kabu a kafkaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
Y\u233?mofem m\u233? t\u233?tambnaw\u233?t efalo yau tiy\u225?totaw\u233?t m\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?uw\u233?gh a s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yamm\u233?n, y\u233?mon emotay\u233?ng f\u225?, "F\u233?fene \u225?mb n\u233?mndafi t\u233? ewam y\u233?na n\u233?net?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Y\u233?mofem yaramay\u233?nd Yesue b\u233?lam\u233?n wagif mbarmbar, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
a y\u233?mon y\u233?kafai a yerai t\u233?netau y\u233?fene gh\u233?kfan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
F\u225? norayai y\u233?fefaf, "Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?nd korayaw\u233?n t\u225?f y\u233?nd njam m\u233? t\u233?nmorw\u233?n f\u233?maf\u233?. M\u233?inyotio si efalo so n\u225?y\u225?tote n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?farotam\u233?nd tanem\u233?n Mosesene n\u225?k k\u233?nj\u250?n, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?rfene Buk a Sams."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mon ewasaw\u233?ry\u233?ng y\u233?fene mwigh\u233? mat \u225?y\u225?togh\u233?t Buk si n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?farotam\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
Y\u233?mon ewaufroi y\u233?feyot, "Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?farotam\u233?nd tanem\u233?n. Keriso so t\u233?kr\u225?tan y\u233?m a k\u233?nanong\u233? k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? k\u233?rta nambiom\u233?n efghon, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
a yaufi awengoghm\u233?n a w\u225?ny\u225?ny\u233?ghm\u233?n so yaitotat y\u225?ne y\u233?tkw\u233?nan m\u233?inyotio yuwom\u233? so t\u233?rnyangi k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Jerusalemta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
F\u233?m em fandagh \u225?r y\u233?n\u233? yamm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 49\~}
Y\u233?ndon ew\u225?f\u225?retan f\u233?m n\u233?mat tane Afam uny\u233?ghofnar si norayai. W\u233?nde tesenan so nawanjetati k\u233?t\u225?notio njafar tukta waftaye k\u233?neworng\u233? f\u233?fefaf."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesuene uyoghm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 50\~}
Y\u233?mon njam elimai Betani tesenta, Yesum ng\u225?ng\u233? euyoi a efrendai f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 51\~}
Njamandio f\u225? t\u225?frendaw\u233?ng, y\u233?mon engfrangoi f\u225? t\u225?f n\u233?nguyoi njafarot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 52\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem y\u225?wefnoy\u233?nd Yesue a kangotaw\u233?t Jerusalem\u233?t ndimbal \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 53\~}
A f\u225? t\u250?m\u233?n kawanjetaw\u233?t w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon m\u233?inyotio efghon, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n tuw\u233?taw\u233?t. {\cs259\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 |IB04179gr.tif|col||by Farid Faadil. \u169? Biblica, Inc. Used with permission. All rights reserved worldwide.|Yesu narmboi njafarot (Luk 24.50-51)|24.50-51}

