K\u233?t\u233? t\u233?fnan Si t\u233? kaketau; Si Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? t\u225?rw\u233?n, a Si t\u233?morw\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
K\u233?tam\u233?fifi t\u233?f\u233?n Si Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? t\u225?rw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u225?ne k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewafrotam m\u233?inyotio rokar; yau \u225?mbiro rokar n\u225?l\u225?ite m\u233?inyotio ufrogh k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u225?yofnaye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Si t\u233?morw\u233?n gh\u233?rs\u233? t\u233?f\u233?n, a y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? yam y\u233?n\u233?rsam kwayagh\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Kwayagh\u233? n\u225?l\u225?le kw\u233?fkw\u233?fan, a kw\u233?fkw\u233?fam yau so taindang\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam y\u225?njo si r\u233?sagh \u225?r, \u225?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Jon, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
efe y\u233?nmorm\u233?n kafrotau \u225?rfefaf kwayagham\u233?n, m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?inyotio so n\u225?y\u225?retat si a efalo tiy\u225?tongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
F\u225? f\u225?yo yau kwayagh\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n; f\u225? y\u233?nmorm\u233?n kafrotau kwayagham\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?f t\u233?morw\u233?n efalofifi kwayagh\u233? \u225?rk\u233? kwayagh\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m mband maratot a n\u225?l\u225?le m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Si t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n mband marat k\u233?nj\u250?n, a ndemam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yafrotam mband marat y\u225?ne k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, w\u233?nde mband maratam yau y\u225?yamngoy\u233?ng f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u225? y\u233?nmorm\u233?n y\u225? yuwot, w\u233?nde y\u225?njo \u225?r\u233?m yau yumyoy\u233?nd f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
W\u233?nde \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m f\u233?t\u233? t\u233? yumyoy\u233?nd f\u225? a efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd; y\u233?mon ewaramai muy\u233? n\u233?namnday\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u225? yau n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r fifie \u225?r\u225?fghe o \u225?rfene m\u233?ndeye o m\u233?naye s\u225?i n\u225?r\u225?ftat fifie afafe k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?; w\u233?nde \u225?r\u225?f\u233?gh \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Si n\u225?y\u225?toi \u225?r a t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n t\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n, ng\u225?r\u225?m a efalo afoghkaf. Y\u233?ndfem yinjoy\u233?m y\u225?ne ndimbal kwayagh\u233?, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?mon yanai nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Afane f\u233?f\u233?t Ambum.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Jon korayau y\u225?nem\u233?n. F\u225? nutnai, "Y\u233?n\u233? f\u225? fiy\u233?m y\u233?nd endenem\u233?n k\u233?norayan t\u225?f njam korayan, 'F\u225? y\u233?n\u233?m ta soram\u233?, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd wainde y\u233?mo, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? fronde kaketau y\u233?nd soram\u233? n\u225?r\u225?ftam\u233?n.'"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u225?ne afoghkaf ng\u225?r\u225?me y\u233?mo t\u233? y\u233?nfrendai y\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio, a y\u233?nmaramete t\u233?fe \u225?mb freng\u233?gh y\u233?namayo w\u233?i \u225?mb. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?ramai n\u225?k Mosese k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, w\u233?nde ng\u225?r\u225?m a efalo y\u233?nmorm\u233?n y\u225? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? Yesu Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Emo \u225?mb yau yinjoi Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. F\u233?f\u233?t Ambumomro, efe y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nyo a efe y\u233?m kaka Afafaf, y\u233?mo t\u233? saf\u233?n y\u233?kmai f\u225?.
