K\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?mb Ju s\u233?nko \u225?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Nikodimas, efe t\u233?morw\u233?n Farasi m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
\u193?mb s\u233?mb\u225?r f\u225? y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n Yesuefaf a norayai y\u225?faf, "Watamegh \u225?r, y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?m n\u233?m watamegh \u225?r efe n\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam. Yau emo so \u225?mb ufarogh yam ewafrote y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?mon sewafrote t\u225?fandro Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? njam f\u233?m ere."
