Yesu nuwangoi, "Y\u233?ndon efalo n\u233?maufrotan fe: emo yau so tinjong\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh t\u225?fandro njam w\u233?ikor n\u225?r\u225?fta."
