Nikodimas namotai, "Ndern\u225?ye so anoghkaf \u225?r n\u225?r\u225?fte w\u233?ikor? F\u225? yau so k\u233?lawang\u233? y\u225?tmane kafkalot a s\u225?i n\u225?r\u225?fta s\u243?mbinotma!"
