Yesum yawangoi, "Y\u233?ndon n\u233?maufrotan efalofifi, efe \u225?mb yau so k\u233?lawang\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t t\u225?fandro njam n\u225?r\u225?fta nue a Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
\u193?r siy\u233?m n\u225?r\u225?fte fifiyan afafeta, w\u233?nde n\u225?r\u225?fte mb\u233?rmb\u233?ran Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
