Mbormbor y\u233?fnje k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?ndan t\u233? m\u233?nde y\u233?m; f\u233?mon y\u233?n\u233? r\u233?r ke n\u225?y\u225?rete \u225?rk\u233? yafrote, w\u233?nde f\u233?m yau mat n\u233?m \u225?rk\u233? tamb\u233?n y\u233?n\u233?m o \u225?ndan w\u233?i y\u233?ng\u233?m. Y\u233?n\u233? nden\u233? fiy\u233?m y\u233?fe m\u233?inyotio efe n\u225?r\u225?ftat Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?re.
