Nikodimas namotai, "Ndern\u225?ye y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "F\u233?m sn\u233?m ndimbal watamegh \u225?r Israil k\u233?nj\u250?n, a f\u233?m yau mat n\u233?m y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?ndon n\u233?maufrotan fe efalo: y\u233?ndfem norayam n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m a yufanam n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndfem t\u233? t\u233?fandam, w\u233?nde som\u233? \u225?mb yau f\u233?m m\u233?nde em t\u233?fene si umyogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Fene efalo y\u225?togh yau y\u233?m tafaf njam y\u233?ndon n\u233?maufrotan fe m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? mbandm\u233?n rokarm\u233?n; ndern\u225?ye so f\u233?mon efalo wiy\u225?tote y\u233?nd njam y\u233?ndon n\u233?maufrotan njafar rokarm\u233?n? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
A yaufifi efe \u225?mb y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n tuk\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?n njafarot m\u233? \u193?roene Ambumro, efe y\u233?nmorm\u233?n yuwot njafarta."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
