Y\u233?n\u233? fifiyan, m\u233?inyotio emofem f\u225? efalo yiy\u225?totat so em tuot gh\u233?rsaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
