M\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yau y\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam y\u225?njo Ambum y\u233?nan mband maratot m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u233?m mogh \u225?r, w\u233?nde m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i f\u225? y\u233?m y\u225? wanjar\u233?gh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
