Nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m \u225?s\u225?fogh moghan: kwayagh\u233? t\u233? t\u233?n\u233?m mband maratot, w\u233?nde \u225?r\u233?m m\u233?ndef\u233? y\u233?fandat kw\u233?fkw\u233?f a yau kwayagh\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?fene yam sem yaufi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
