W\u233?nde emofem ewafrotat n\u233?m\u233? em efalo en\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n kwayaghafaf m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m so efandat nden\u233? y\u233?mofem y\u233?n\u233? yafrotat n\u233?mat Ng\u225?nj\u225?n m\u233?nde y\u233?m.
