Amafom yawangoi, "F\u233?m sn\u233?m Ju \u225?r, a y\u233?nd sw\u233?m Samariam\u233?n \u225?maf-y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n nde ndern\u225?ye so f\u233?mon wamnende y\u233?nd nuot?" M\u233?nam\u233?n Ju \u225?r yau so nafghetat Samaria \u225?rf\u233? kafusi a merekinam\u233? n\u233?neyan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "Njam t\u233? f\u233?m mat k\u233?nmorw\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ram\u233?gh y\u233?m a efe f\u225? y\u233?m emon n\u233?mamnende nuot, f\u233?mon so t\u225?mnenda f\u225?, a y\u233?mon so k\u233?maramang\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? akegh nu."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Amaf norayai, "Ndimbal, f\u233?m sn\u233?m ukw\u233?gh rokarofnar, a y\u233?kw siy\u233?m k\u233?njkam. \u193?nde so f\u233?mon t\u233?nman y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? akegh nu? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
T\u233?fene \u225?kim Jeikof\u233?m y\u233?nmaramai t\u233?fe y\u233?n\u233? nu y\u233?kw; f\u225? a y\u225?njo ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r a y\u225?njo m\u225?njar\u233?gh w\u233?r\u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n m\u233?inyotio nu y\u233?naf t\u225?netaw\u233?t. F\u233?mo y\u225?inde af\u233? Jeikof?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "M\u233?inyotio emofem y\u233?n\u233? nu y\u233?netat m\u233? so em nu m\u233?nde, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
w\u233?nde emon njam y\u233?neta y\u233?n\u233? nu y\u233?ndon sewarametan yaufifi so efinde nuam. N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, nu y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?ndon sewarametan y\u233?fe so kamndang\u233? \u233?fnogh nu y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n so efrone akegh gh\u233?rs\u233? nue a so tawaramang\u233? tuot gh\u233?rs\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Amaf norayai y\u225?faf, "Ndimbal, kwaram ta y\u233?n\u233? nu m\u233?n\u225?t yau y\u233?nd so nuam w\u233?finde a yau so w\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?nan nu uk\u233?gh\u233?t."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Yesum y\u233?mndai amaf, "Kuwano, fenjar t\u233?nmasro a k\u233?nango."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Amaf nuwangoi, "Tanjar yau w\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu norayai amafoefaf, "F\u233?mon efalo f\u233?t\u233? noraye nden\u233? fenjar yau n\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
W\u233?nde efalo siy\u233?m, f\u233?m t\u233? n\u233?masroy\u233?nd 5 \u225?r\u233?m, a \u225?r s\u233?nonjo emaf\u233? emorare yau fenjarfifi y\u233?m. F\u233?mo efalo t\u233? waufro."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Amaf norayai, "Ndimbal, y\u233?nd mat namndan nden\u233? f\u233?m sn\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
T\u233?fene \u225?kifem y\u233?n\u233? mband tunakfan t\u225?wefnotaw\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne, w\u233?nde f\u233?m Ju \u225?r norayati nden\u233? Jerusalem y\u233?n\u233? yu fiy\u233?m \u225?nde y\u233?ndfem so y\u225?wefnotam Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Yesu norayai y\u225?faf, "Amaf, Efalo kwiy\u225?to y\u233?nd, efogh y\u233?na y\u233?n\u233?m \u225?nde f\u233?mofem yau so y\u225?wefnotati Afai y\u233?n\u233? mband tunakfan o k\u233?t\u233? Jerusalem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
F\u233?m Samariam\u233?n \u225?r yau mat em f\u233?mofem endefifi y\u225?wefnotati, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd Ju \u225?r mat y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?ndfem ende y\u225?wefnotam, m\u233?nam\u233?n wanjar\u233?gh si\u233?n\u233?m Ju \u225?rfeta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
W\u233?nde efogh y\u233?na y\u233?n\u233?m a t\u233? efogh nufar, \u225?nde efalo w\u225?wefnogh \u225?r\u233?m so y\u225?wefnotat Afai m\u233?naye Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?re a efaloe, m\u233?nam\u233?n nden\u233? w\u225?wefnogh \u225?rfaf Af\u233? m\u233?nde fiy\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n siy\u233?m Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r, y\u225?ne w\u225?wefnogh \u225?r\u233?m so y\u225?wefnotat Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?re a efaloe."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Amaf norayai, "Y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m nden\u233? Keriso so y\u233?n\u233?m. Njam f\u225? y\u233?n\u233?m so y\u233?nmawafene m\u233?inyotio yam t\u233?feyot."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Yesu nuwangoi, "Y\u233?nd faf w\u233?m, efe y\u233?nd norayan fefaf."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghonyo, n\u233?nangoy\u233?nd Yesuene waitogh \u225?r, a s\u233?lngw\u233?l emorm\u233?n syinjoy\u233?nd amafof\u233? skoraiw\u233?t. W\u233?nde yau efe \u225?mb namotai, "N\u233?m\u233? m\u233?nde n\u233?m f\u233?m?" o "N\u233?mat f\u233?m norayet amafof\u233??"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?yo amafom noroi y\u225?njo nu s\u233?fkw\u233?n, n\u233?ngangoi k\u233?t\u225?n tesenot a ewaufroi \u225?r\u233?t, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
"Awe, t\u233?fandangi y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emon waufrote m\u233?inyotio yam y\u233?ndon \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? tawafrotan. M\u233? t\u233? f\u225? y\u233?m Keriso?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
F\u233?yo f\u225? n\u233?wanoy\u233?nd tesenta a tayotau k\u233?t\u225?n Yesuefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efoghf\u233?nef\u233?neyan waitogh \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?mnday\u233?nd Yesu, "Watamegh \u225?r, njamke \u225?mb koneta!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? norayai y\u233?fefaf, "Tane t\u233? njamke y\u233?m n\u233?net y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rk\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m mat yau em."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
F\u233?yo waitogh \u225?r kamotangi y\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n, "M\u233?t\u233? emon t\u225?f y\u233?nmarsa y\u225? njamke?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Yesu norayai, "Tane njamke y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m s\u225?i y\u225?ne m\u233?nde yafrotan emon kw\u233?m\u225?f\u225?rete y\u233?nd a s\u225?i tifon y\u233?n\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? waramai ta wafrogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
F\u233?m t\u250?m\u233?n norayati, '4 gh\u233?rarero em k\u233?t\u225?n wau yu.' Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?fe, tasaw\u233?rngi f\u233?fenjo gh\u233?k\u233?f t\u233?fandangi ndau sifay\u233?! F\u225? sem wau em m\u233?n\u225?t targh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
A f\u225? emon etane wau yuwon fai tawanang\u233? a eum\u233?nde njamke rokar nden\u233? eumendat \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?n tuot gh\u233?rsat, f\u233?yo m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r a tar\u233?gh \u225?r so \u225?uw\u233?ghan ere m\u233?rne. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n si nden\u225?ye y\u233?m efaloe, '\u193?mb \u225?rom eite a \u225?mb \u225?rom w\u233?i etane.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Y\u233?ndon tanw\u225?f\u225?retan f\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t frar\u233?gh\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m yau k\u225?s\u225?fotati; \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m t\u233? tafrotat t\u225?ik\u233?r \u225?s\u225?fogh, a f\u233?mofem y\u233?fandati freng\u233?gh y\u233?fene \u225?s\u225?foghta."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
T\u225?rf\u225?r Samariam\u233?n \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? tesenan efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd Yesu m\u233?nam\u233?n amafoene efalo sim\u233?n, "Y\u233?mon kaufrote ta m\u233?inyotio yam n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon t\u233? tawafrotan." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
F\u233?yo njam Samariam\u233?n \u225?r enmorm\u233?n y\u225?faf, y\u233?mofem yamnenday\u233?nd \u225?mnjogh\u233?t y\u233?maf\u233?, a Yesu y\u233?morang\u233?rm\u233?n s\u243?mbio efogh k\u233?t\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
T\u225?rf\u225?ram m\u233? y\u233?m efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?njo sim\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Y\u233?mofem norayay\u233?nd amafofefaf, "Y\u233?ndfem yau efalo yiy\u225?tong\u233?m m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mon n\u233?m\u233? noraya; s\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndio t\u233?f\u233? n\u225?y\u225?retam, a y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efalo f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m mband maratoene Wanjar\u233?gh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum mer yiy\u225?toi gafaman \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?roene ambum
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
S\u243?mbio efogh soram\u233? Yesu nuwanoi a y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n Galili yuwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
T\u233? Yesu f\u225?yo norayai, "Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r sem yau eut\u233?mndat y\u233?fenjo yuwon." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
Njam f\u225? nufary\u233?ng Galili yuwot, \u225?r\u233?m k\u233?t\u233? yumyoy\u233?nd f\u225?, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? t\u233? engmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n Waing\u233?gh t\u233?m\u233?ndfaf Jerusalem\u233?t a t\u233? t\u233?fandaw\u233?t m\u233?inyotio yam n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon tafrotau t\u233?m\u233?ndfaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
F\u233?yo Yesu n\u233?ngangoi k\u233?t\u225?n Kana Galili yu k\u233?nj\u250?t, \u225?nde y\u233?mon t\u233? yengoi nu w\u233?ri nuot. Warsagh \u225?roene \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n endene ambum enjne t\u233?morw\u233?n K\u225?fenam\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
Njam y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rom n\u225?y\u225?rai nde Yesu t\u233? nufar Galili yuwot k\u233?tam\u233? Judiata, f\u225? y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n y\u225?faf a yamnendai Yesu m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i t\u233?ngmorw\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n a mer tiy\u225?tongai y\u225?ne ambum, efe t\u233?morw\u233?n kaka krotro.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
Yesu norayai y\u225?faf, "Emon \u225?mb yau efalo so tiy\u225?to t\u225?fandro f\u233?mon s\u225?i y\u233?fanda ufarogh yam a s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 49\~}
Gafaman \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r nuwangoi, "Ndimbal, awe y\u233?ndf\u233? m\u233?t\u233? t\u225?f tane ambum k\u233?r y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 50\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "Nguwano; fene ambum so gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rom efalo yiy\u225?toi Yesuene si f\u233?yo nuwanoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 51\~}
Njam m\u233? t\u233?ngmorw\u233?n endm\u233?, y\u225?njo faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?f\u225?ngoy\u233?nd f\u225? y\u233?n\u233? ghanyaf\u233? nden\u233? y\u225?ne ghak\u233?r ambum gh\u233?rs\u233? m\u233? y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 52\~}
Y\u233?mon emotai f\u225? \u225?rk\u233? efghe namndai mer, y\u233?mofem yawangoy\u233?nd, "Wawenagh enjneyam y\u233?frong\u233? f\u225? k\u225?ye s\u233?ite t\u225?f wan aklok."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 53\~}
F\u233?yo y\u225?ref\u233? nawafarotai nde y\u233?n\u233? efghe fifi Yesum y\u233?mndai, "Fene ambum so gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?m." F\u233?yo f\u225? a y\u225?njo m\u233?inyotio m\u233?r\u233?n efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd Yesu.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 54\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n s\u243?mbiom\u233?n ufarogh yam Yesum \u225?rk\u233? yafrotam soram\u233? t\u225?f sinmorm\u233?n Judiata k\u233?t\u225?n Galili yuwot.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 5
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Mer y\u225?togh k\u233?t\u233? n\u233?mbne saw\u233?n
