Soram\u233? Yesum yinjoi f\u225? k\u233?t\u233? w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo sifayan a norayai y\u225?faf, "T\u233?fanda, f\u233?m sn\u233?m merot t\u233? nango. K\u233?kmbo yaufiyam wafrogh o minde m\u225?m\u225?fi m\u233?t\u233? nufrota fefaf." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r n\u233?ngwanoi a ewaufroi Ju s\u233?nko \u225?r\u233?t nden\u233? Yesum mer yiy\u225?toi f\u225?.
