Yesum ewaramai y\u233?fe y\u233?n\u233? uwangogh, "Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan efaloe nden\u233? Ambumom yau so n\u233?m\u233? yafrote yambiyaye, y\u233?mon so y\u233?naro ewafrote n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon efande Afam \u225?rk\u233? ewafrote, m\u233?nam\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? njam Afam yafrota w\u233?i Ambumom f\u233?t\u233? so yafrote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n Afam yuwete Ambum a yauyafote y\u225? m\u233?inyotio y\u233?mon n\u233?m\u233? ewafrote. A Afam so yauyafote ndimbal yam y\u233?mo s\u225?i ewafrota, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam so y\u225?inde \u225?s\u225?fogh y\u233?mo \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? ewafrote, a f\u233?m so s\u233?lngw\u233?l em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Afam k\u233?s ewanote k\u233?r \u225?r a tawaramang\u233? y\u233?fe gh\u233?rs\u233?, nden\u233?yameyo Ambumom tawaramang\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?feyot y\u225?ne m\u233?nde endefaf em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n Afam yau mogh yam yafrote endefaf, w\u233?nde t\u233? y\u233?ramai m\u233?inyotio mogh yam k\u233?t\u225?n Ambumoefaf, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m so yut\u233?mndat Ambum nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?mofem k\u233?s yut\u233?mndat Af\u233?. Emon njam yau yut\u233?mnda Ambum yau yut\u233?mnde Af\u233?, emon y\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam f\u225?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?fe efalo, emon njam k\u225?y\u225?rang\u233? tane si a efalo tiy\u225?tong\u233? f\u225? emon kw\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?rete y\u233?nd y\u233?fe so y\u233?m tuot gh\u233?rs\u233? a yau so em moghan w\u233?nde t\u233? n\u233?f\u233?rmangi k\u233?rta k\u233?t\u225?n gh\u233?rsat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Y\u233?ndon ewaufrotan f\u233?fe efalo, efogh y\u233?na y\u233?n\u233?m a t\u233? efogh nufar \u225?nde so k\u233?r \u225?r k\u225?y\u225?rangi Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Ambumoene k\u233?m a emofem njam k\u225?y\u225?rangi, f\u225? so gh\u233?rsaf\u233? k\u233?n\u225?y\u225?tongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Afafaf k\u233?s y\u233?m gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u225?njo k\u233?nj\u250?n, nden\u233?yameyo y\u233?mon t\u233? yaramai Ambumoe m\u233?n\u225?t Ambumoefaf so y\u233?m gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u225?njo k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
