Y\u233?ndon f\u233?yotarofnar w\u233?m wafrogh\u233?t tanjo muyay\u233? y\u233?ndon mogh yafrotan y\u233?naro Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ndern\u225?ye kw\u233?mndang\u233? y\u233?nd, y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n tane mogh siy\u233?m mbark\u225?nd, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndon yau yafrotan tanjo m\u233?nde w\u233?nde y\u225?ne emon w\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam y\u233?nd.
