Y\u233?nd t\u233? kw\u233?n\u233?m tane Afane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, a f\u233?mofem y\u233?nd yau wumyongi; w\u233?nde njam efe y\u233?n\u233?m f\u225? y\u225?njo y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, f\u233?mofem so tumyongi f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
F\u233?m m\u233?nde em f\u233?mro-f\u233?mro s\u225?i n\u225?uwetati. \u193?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u225?yam em\u233?inde \u225?uw\u233?gh\u233?t. W\u233?nde f\u233?mofem yau ewafrotati meryam m\u233?n\u225?t efe f\u225?ro y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?namro s\u225?i euwete f\u233?m. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan f\u233?mofem yau so efalo wiy\u225?totati.
