Njam ghak\u233?r ambum gh\u233?ngan tanfangi Safatan m\u233?n\u225?t Mosesene n\u225?k yau so erafnat, n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m n\u233?kw em tafaf m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndon \u225?roene fifi mer yiy\u225?ton Safatan? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Yau waf\u233?nman\u233?gh farun yaman, w\u233?nde waf\u233?nman\u233?gh merk\u233?r\u225?ye.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 N\u233?m\u233? f\u225? Keriso y\u233?m?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r Jerusalemm\u233?n korayaw\u233?t, "Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r fiy\u233?m efe ngiot y\u233?rametat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
K\u233?retangi! F\u225? noraye marataye, a n\u233?mndafi si lim\u225?ng\u233?gh \u225?r yau norayat y\u225? tamb\u233?n! O m\u233?t\u233? nemnat f\u225? y\u233?m efalo Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
W\u233?nde Keriso njam y\u233?n\u233?m, efe \u225?mb yau mat y\u233?m f\u225? naim\u233?n y\u233?m. W\u233?nde y\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio mat y\u233?n\u233?m \u225?rkam\u233? y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r y\u233?n\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Yesum njamandio tawatametau w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo sifayan, f\u225? norayai marat k\u233?me, "F\u233?m matfifi t\u233? em y\u233?nd efe w\u233?m a \u225?rkam\u233? w\u233?nmorm\u233?n? Y\u233?nd yau w\u233?nmorm\u233?n tanjo mwigh\u233? faror\u233?ghan. W\u233?nde f\u225? emo w\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam siy\u233?m efalo. F\u233?m mat yau em f\u225?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
w\u233?nde y\u233?nd mat f\u225? w\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd w\u233?nmorm\u233?n y\u225? tamb\u233?n a y\u233?mon y\u233?nd w\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem y\u233?ta wergh\u233?t t\u233?rametaw\u233?t, w\u233?nde emo \u225?mb yau ng\u225?ng\u233? efayoi y\u225?faf, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne efogh som\u233? yau nawer. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
W\u233?nde t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n efalo f\u225? yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd. F\u225? norayay\u233?nd, "Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r\u233?m ewafrote minde t\u225?rf\u225?r s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam. Efaloe f\u225? y\u233?m Keriso. S\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam y\u233?mo n\u233?m\u233? ewafrote ewainde \u225?mb \u225?rfene.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m engw\u225?f\u225?retam\u233?nd Yesue wergh\u233?t
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Farasi \u225?r\u233?m ey\u225?ray\u233?nd \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n Yesuenem\u233?n k\u225?w\u225?wanjaw\u233?t y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, f\u233?yo f\u225? a lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r\u233?m engw\u225?f\u225?retam\u233?nd \u225?mb wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t y\u225? wergh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Yesu norayai, "Y\u233?nd f\u233?mof\u233? so y\u233?n\u233?m n\u233?mbne efoghf\u233?nef\u233?netro, a y\u233?nd so w\u233?i ngangon k\u233?t\u225?n emon y\u233?nd w\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
F\u233?mofem y\u233?nd so kw\u233?ronjangi, w\u233?nde f\u233?mofem yau so kwinjongi y\u233?nd, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m yau k\u233?t\u225?n so eng\u233?m y\u233?nd \u225?nde so w\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Ju s\u233?nko \u225?r namotay\u233?nd y\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?nro, "F\u225? \u225?ndan nufngo y\u233?ndfem f\u225? yau s\u225?i tinjong\u233?m? F\u225? so nguwanong\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n Grik tesenot k\u233?t\u225?n t\u233?fene \u225?r k\u233?s emor, a so ewatamete Grikm\u233?n \u225?r? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
F\u225? nden\u233? noraye y\u233?ndfem so y\u233?ronjam w\u233?nde yau so tinjong\u233?m f\u225?, a y\u233?nd yau so k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?n\u233?ng\u233?m f\u225? \u225?nde so y\u233?m. N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mo y\u233?s\u233?rmbne?"
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Gh\u233?rs\u233? ram\u233?gh w\u233?r\u233?r nu
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
K\u233?t\u233? soramam\u233?n efghon ndimbalfifi t\u233?mndan Yesu nokayoi a norayai marataye k\u233?me, "Efe njam nuam n\u233?finda, k\u233?naf tafaf, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
a emon njam efalo y\u233?nd kwiy\u225?tong\u233? y\u233?mon so nu y\u233?nete. Nden\u233? Buk si k\u233?s noraye, 'Gh\u233?rs\u233? ram\u233?gh w\u233?r\u233?r nu so nasune y\u233?fefaf k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? efalo \u225?rfene k\u233?nj\u250?ta.'" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
Njam Yesu korayau y\u233?n\u233? si, f\u225? korayau nden\u233? emofem efalo tiy\u225?tongi y\u233?mofem so tanangi Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r. Y\u233?n\u233? efghon Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r yau y\u233?ramai y\u233?fefaf, m\u233?nam\u233?n Yesu yau n\u233?nguyoi ndimbal kwayaghafaf.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Afalogh \u225?r k\u233?nj\u250?n
