\u193?mb \u225?r\u233?m m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n yiy\u225?ray\u233?nd f\u225? korayau y\u233?n\u233? a norayay\u233?nd, "Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r siy\u233?m efalo y\u233?n\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
\u193?mb korayaw\u233?t, "F\u225? siy\u233?m Keriso!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 W\u233?nde \u225?mb korayaw\u233?t, "Yau Keriso so y\u233?n\u233?m Galili yuta! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Buk si noraye nden\u233? Keriso so y\u233?m Deifidene \u225?kim\u233?n a so n\u225?r\u225?fte Betliem\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? Deifid \u225?nde t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
K\u233?t\u233? mwighayan afalogh tamorw\u233?n \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n Yesuenem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r m\u233?nde tamorw\u233?n wergh\u233?t, w\u233?nde emon yau ng\u225?ng\u233? efayoi y\u225?faf.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Efalo y\u225?toghofnar Ju s\u233?nko \u225?r
