Njam wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r n\u233?nangoy\u233?nd, lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r a Farasi \u225?r\u233?m emotay\u233?nd, "N\u233?mam\u233?n yau f\u233?mofem fy\u233?n\u233?mnjati f\u225??"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
Wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m ewawangoy\u233?nd, "Efe \u225?mb yau korayau nden\u233? ende f\u225? k\u233?s korayau!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
Farasi \u225?r\u233?m emotay\u233?nd, "Y\u233?mo w\u233?i t\u233? tawaweinde. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
Yau \u225?mb s\u233?nko \u225?r o Farasi \u225?r\u233?m efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd f\u225?? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 49\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n yau mat em Mosesene n\u225?km\u233?n. F\u225? sem Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mogh mbanmbanan!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 50\~}
\u193?mbiro Farasi \u225?r k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n f\u225? Nikodimas, y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efe y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n a Yesu yinjoi fronde. F\u225? norayai k\u233?t\u233? \u225?mb \u225?rfefaf, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 51\~}
"T\u233?fene n\u225?kam yau y\u233?nmumyote nde \u225?r k\u233?rtat s\u225?i t\u233?kmang\u233?m, fronde so tiy\u225?rang\u233?m sian. Yau so yawaftam \u225?mbro k\u233?t\u225?n mat kor kamndang\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? yam tawafrote."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 52\~}
