W\u233?nde Yesu n\u233?ngwanoi Olif Mband tunakfot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
T\u225?nd\u225?i \u225?mb akwan f\u225? y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo sifayat. T\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r y\u225?faf enmorm\u233?n a Yesu n\u225?mnjoi a watamegh ewafngoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
N\u225?k watamegh \u225?r a Farasi \u225?r y\u233?n\u233?mnjam\u233?nd amaf efe ewinjeyay\u233?nd \u225?mb \u225?rof\u233? efe yau y\u225?ne \u225?r t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?r s\u225?fan yakayoy\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?mnday\u233?nd, "Watamegh \u225?r, y\u233?n\u233? amafom yafrote yaufi walot a y\u233?mofem yinjongi f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Mosesene n\u225?kam nden\u233? y\u233?nmatamete, nden\u233? s\u225?fot amaf fiya w\u237?me tafiy\u225?totangi krot. Ndern\u225?ye so koraya?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?mofem \u225?mogh si tarametaw\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t Yesu so terangay\u233?nd. W\u233?nde Yesu n\u225?wefnoi a ng\u225?ngaye farogh ewafngoi mbandan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Njam y\u233?mofem m\u233? t\u233?motaw\u233?t f\u225?, Yesu nokayoi a norayai y\u233?fefaf, "Efe f\u233?m yaufiyam wafroghofnar n\u233?m tita fronde w\u237?m y\u225?faf." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
W\u233?ikor k\u225?wefnong\u233? a mbandan afarogh kufnong\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Njam f\u225? n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? si, f\u225? m\u233?inyotio nofarnay\u233?nd, \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiroero, \u225?r ndimbal fronde a tot\u233?r \u225?r, k\u233?t\u225?notio Yesufro efrangeyay\u233?nd amafof\u233? m\u233? tawakayarw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Yesu nokayoi a y\u233?mndai, "Amaf, \u225?nde f\u225? em? Efe \u225?mb nafrango fe waghangh\u233?t?"
