\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum y\u233?mndai, "Y\u233?ndon w\u233?i yau so n\u233?maghnan f\u233?m. Nguwano, w\u233?nde yaufi yau ewafrota w\u233?ikor"
