Njam w\u233?ikor Yesu korayau \u225?rfefaf, f\u225? nden\u233? norayai, "Y\u233?nd w\u233?m kwayagh\u233? mband maratoe. Emon kw\u233?nmaitong\u233? y\u233?nd yau so yiote kw\u233?fitayan a y\u225?faf so y\u233?m kwayagh\u233? \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m gh\u233?rsat."
