Farasi \u225?r norayay\u233?nd y\u225?faf, "S\u233?nonjo f\u233?m t\u233? norayang fenjo yamm\u233?n. N\u233?m\u233? f\u233?m noraye muyafnar y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Yesum ewawangoi, "Yau, ndemam\u233?n y\u233?nd norayan tanjom\u233?n, y\u233?nd n\u233?m\u233? norayan efalo y\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m \u225?rkam\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?nmorm\u233?n a \u225?ndan y\u233?nd wiota. F\u233?m mafina em y\u233?nd \u225?rkam\u233? w\u233?nmorm\u233?n a \u225?ndan y\u233?nd wiota. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?mofem mogh tafrotati mbandoene ende y\u233?ndon yau yafnamotan mogh \u225?mb \u225?roefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndo njam yafrotan mogh, tane mwigh\u233? wafrogh em efalo, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd yau tambia w\u233?m; Afam emo y\u233?nd w\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam y\u233?ndf\u233? y\u233?nre. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
K\u233?t\u233? y\u233?farotam\u233?nd f\u233?fene n\u225?kan nden\u233? s\u243?mbio fandagh \u225?r\u233?m njam efalo tiatend, n\u233?m\u233? f\u225? norayang\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m efalo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?nd nafrotan tanjom\u233?n, a Afam emon y\u233?nd w\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam f\u225? nden\u225?yo nafrote tanem\u233?n."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?motay\u233?nd, "\u193?nde y\u233?m feraf\u233??"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum ewawangoi, "F\u233?m mafina em tanem\u233?n o tane Afanem\u233?n. F\u233?m njam mat em tanem\u233?n, f\u233?m mat so em Afanem\u233?n nden\u225?yo."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Yesum norayai m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? si njam y\u233?mon tawatametau k\u233?t\u233? w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo sifayan, k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?n\u233? satayan \u225?nde ram\u233?gh boks t\u233?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n. A emo yau y\u233?rai f\u225?, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne efogh yau som\u233? nawerai.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 F\u233?m yau k\u233?t\u225?n so eng\u233?m y\u233?nd \u225?ndan w\u233?ng\u233?m
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
W\u233?i Yesu norayai y\u233?fefaf, "Y\u233?nd so kuwanong\u233?n; f\u233?mofem so w\u233?ronjati y\u233?nd, w\u233?nde f\u233?m so k\u233?r em f\u233?fenjo yaufiyan. F\u233?m yau so eng\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?nd \u225?ndan w\u233?ng\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Ndenaye Ju s\u233?nko \u225?r norayay\u233?nd, "F\u225? norayai y\u233?nd yau so w\u233?ng\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n f\u225? \u225?ndan y\u233?ng\u233?m. N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?n\u233? sioene fifi y\u233?m, f\u225?yo so n\u225?smete?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Yesum ewawangoi, "F\u233?m sem y\u233?n\u233? mband maratm\u233?n em y\u233?n\u233? yuwan, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd sw\u233?m tukm\u233?n w\u233?m. F\u233?m sem y\u233?n\u233? mband maratm\u233?n em, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd yau y\u233?n\u233? mband maratm\u233?n w\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?ndon f\u233?m t\u233? tamndetaw\u233?n f\u233?m so k\u233?r em f\u233?fenjo yaufi k\u233?nj\u250?n. A f\u233?m so k\u233?r em f\u233?fenjo yaufi k\u233?nj\u250?n yau njam efalo yiy\u225?totati nden\u233? Y\u233?nd W\u233?m Efe Y\u233?nd W\u233?m."{\super t{\footnote \pard\plain \s212\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22  {\super t}{{\cs214\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 8.24 }
{\cs215\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Eksod\u233?s 3:14}
}}}

\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?motay\u233?nd f\u225?, "Efe f\u233?m n\u233?m?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum ewawangoi, "N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon tan\u233?mndetan f\u233?m k\u233?tamayo t\u233?f\u233?nta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Tane em t\u225?rf\u225?r mogh f\u233?fefaf, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam so t\u225?kmang\u233? k\u233?rtat. W\u233?nde emo y\u233?nd w\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam f\u225? siy\u233?m efalo, a y\u233?ndon yaufrotan mband maratoe y\u233?naro n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?n y\u225? tamb\u233?n."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
F\u225? yau mat tamorw\u233?n nden\u233? Yesu korayau Y\u225?refanem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?yo nden\u233? norayai y\u233?fefaf, "Njam f\u233?mofem tuyongi \u193?roene Ambum, f\u233?m so mat em nden\u233? Y\u233?nd W\u233?m Efe Y\u233?nd W\u233?m; f\u233?yo f\u233?m so mat em nden\u233? y\u233?ndon yau ewaufrotan tanjo muyaye, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd norayan m\u233? y\u233?naro Afam ndern\u225?ye w\u233?n\u233?mndetam siot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Emon y\u233?nd w\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam f\u225? siy\u233?m y\u233?ndf\u233? y\u233?nr\u233? y\u233?mon y\u233?nd yau w\u233?frango tambia, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndo t\u250?m\u233?n y\u225?ne m\u233?nde yawafrotan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
T\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r efe n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd Yesu korayau y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd f\u225?.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Efaloyam so yuwek k\u233?ny\u225?tong\u233?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Yesum \u225?r emndai efe ndimbal mwighaf\u233? em y\u225?faf, "F\u233?m njam n\u225?myotati tane watamegh sifaf, f\u233?m efalo tane waitogh \u225?r so em; {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
f\u233?m mat so em efalo, a efaloyam so yuwek t\u225?y\u225?tong\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
F\u225? n\u233?wangoy\u233?nd y\u225?faf, "Y\u233?nd si\u233?n\u233?m Ebraamene \u225?kiambum, a y\u233?nd yau t\u233?nmorw\u233?n \u225?mb \u225?roene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r. Ndern\u225?ye w\u233?t y\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?m k\u233?s noraye, 'F\u233?m so k\u225?y\u225?tongi yuwek'?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Yesu norayai y\u233?fefaf, "Y\u233?ndon emndetan efaloe: m\u233?inyotio \u225?r emon yaufiyam s\u225?i yafrota f\u225? siy\u233?m yaufiyamoene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?roene ambino sifay\u233? yau y\u233?m m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?n, w\u233?nde ambum y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n fifi y\u233?m tuot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
F\u233?yo Ambumom njam yuwek k\u233?ny\u225?tong\u233?, f\u233?m f\u233?t\u233? so yuwek kamnd\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?m sem Ebraamene \u225?ki m\u233?r\u233?n. W\u233?nde f\u233?mofem ngiot w\u233?rametati y\u233?nd, m\u233?nam\u233?n tane si yau f\u233?fene tikfan em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Y\u233?ndon norayan tane Afam n\u233?m\u233? kwaufrong\u233? ta, w\u233?nde f\u233?mofem yafrotati f\u233?ferafam n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? fe n\u233?maufrotam."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
F\u225? nowangoy\u233?nd y\u225?faf, "T\u233?fene af\u233? siy\u233?m Ebraam!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum ewawangoi, "Njam em efalo Ebraamene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, f\u233?mofem so ewafrotati y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh Ebraam\u233?m k\u233?s tawafrotau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? m\u233?inyotio tawafrotan y\u233?ndon efalo ewaufrotan f\u233?fe n\u233?m\u233? k\u233?n\u225?y\u225?retan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nta, w\u233?nde ngiot w\u233?rametati y\u233?nd. Ebraam\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? yau nden\u233? tawafrotau! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?mofem ewafrotati n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?ferafam tawafrotau.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 F\u225? nowangoy\u233?nd, "Ng\u225?nj\u225?nro siy\u233?m t\u233?fene Af\u233?, a y\u233?nd si\u233?n\u233?m y\u225?ne efalo ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Yesu norayai y\u233?fefaf, "Ng\u225?nj\u225?n njam f\u233?fene Af\u233? y\u233?m, f\u233?mofem so y\u233?nd wuwetati, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd w\u233?nmorm\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne tamb\u233?n a s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd y\u233?na w\u233?m. Y\u233?nd yau kw\u233?n\u233?m tane mwigh\u233? faror\u233?ghan, w\u233?nde y\u233?mon kw\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?rete. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
F\u233?mofem n\u233?mam\u233?n yau kor ersati tane si n\u233?m\u233? norayan? M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem yau so kor tane si ersati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
F\u233?m srem f\u233?fenjo afane ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r, efe y\u233?m S\u225?if\u233?r, a f\u233?m m\u233?nde em f\u233?fenjo afane mwigh\u233? s\u225?i yaitotati. K\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? r\u233?ny\u233?ghta f\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n ngi t\u233?fn\u225?r, f\u225? yau efalo t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne k\u233?nj\u250? efalo yau y\u233?m. Njam uny\u233?ghe noraye, f\u225? nauyafote efe f\u225? y\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? uny\u233?gh \u225?r y\u233?m a uny\u233?ghoe af\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndo efalo si emndetan, a n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mofem efalo yau wiy\u225?totati! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
Emo \u225?mb so kafrong\u233? tane yaufim\u233?n? Efe \u225?mb yau. Y\u233?ndon njam efalo si ewaufrotan, n\u233?mam\u233?n yau efalo kwiy\u225?tongi? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
Efe Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene em f\u225? so n\u225?y\u225?retat Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si. W\u233?nde f\u233?m efe yau Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene em, y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m yau n\u225?y\u225?retati."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu a Ebraam
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
Yesu y\u233?motay\u233?nd, "N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?nd mbark\u225?nd y\u233?n\u233?m nden\u233? snorayang\u233?m nde f\u233?m sn\u233?m Samariam\u233?n \u225?r a nden\u233?nde fefaf yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r y\u233?lau!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 49\~}
Yesu norayai, "Tane k\u233?nj\u250?n \u225?mb yau yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r y\u233?m. Y\u233?ndo yut\u233?mndan tane Af\u233?, w\u233?nde f\u233?fene wutman\u233?gh yau y\u233?m tafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 50\~}
Y\u233?ndo yau y\u233?ronjan tandio wutman\u233?gh, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so wut\u233?mnde y\u233?nd. F\u225? fiy\u233?m efalofifi mogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 51\~}
Y\u233?ndo emndetan efalo si: emon n\u225?y\u225?rete tane si f\u225? yaufifi k\u233?r so y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 52\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?mnday\u233?nd f\u225?, "S\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd mat y\u233?n\u233?m efalo f\u233?m sn\u233?m yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?raf\u233? n\u233?m! Ebraam k\u233?r t\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n, a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r w\u233?i k\u233?r t\u233? emorm\u233?n, w\u233?nde f\u233?m noraye emo fene watamegh n\u225?y\u225?reta f\u225? yau so k\u233?r y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 53\~}
F\u233?mo y\u225?inde t\u233?fene af\u233? Ebraam, efe k\u233?r t\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r k\u233?r t\u233? emorm\u233?n. F\u233?mo ndern\u225?ye nemne efe f\u233?m n\u233?m?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 54\~}
Yesum ewawangoi, "T\u225?f y\u233?ndo njam wutman\u233?gh yangotan tandio, y\u233?n\u233? wutman\u233?gh siy\u233?m fifiofnar. W\u233?nde emo y\u233?nd wut\u233?mnde siy\u233?m tane Af\u233?, y\u233?n\u233? efalo fifi y\u233?m f\u233?mon efe y\u233?mndete fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 55\~}
F\u233?m yau mat em f\u225?, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m f\u225?. Y\u233?nd njam t\u233? korayan nden\u233? y\u233?nd yau mat w\u233?m y\u225?nem\u233?n, y\u233?nd t\u225?f uny\u233?gh \u225?r sof w\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?m k\u233?s em. W\u233?nde y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m f\u225? a y\u233?nd n\u225?myotan y\u225?ne sian. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 56\~}
Fene af\u233? Ebraam f\u225? \u225?uw\u233?ghan t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mo efogh t\u233? yinjoi tane \u225?lighm\u233?n; y\u233?mo yinjoi a f\u225? \u225?uw\u233?ghan t\u233?morw\u233?n."
