Tot\u233?r n\u225?k ewaraman f\u233?fe, euwetati \u225?mb \u225?r, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?ndon euwetam\u233?n f\u233?m, y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m n\u225?uwetati f\u233?mro f\u233?mro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Y\u233?nayan m\u233?inyotio \u225?r mat so kamndangi nden\u233? f\u233?m sem tane waitogh \u225?r, f\u233?m njam n\u225?uwetati f\u233?mro f\u233?mro.
