\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum yawangoi, "\u193?ndan y\u233?nd wiote, f\u233?mo yau so kw\u233?nmaito s\u233?nonjo, w\u233?nde soram\u233? so n\u233?ngwaitote."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
