\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesum ewamarotai y\u225?njo waitogh \u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Yau t\u225?f f\u233?fene tik\u233?f n\u233?w\u233?rsotat. Efalo yiy\u225?totati Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a efalo wiy\u225?totati nden\u225?yo y\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Tane Afane m\u233?ngo siy\u233?m t\u225?rf\u225?r sataf\u233?; yau njam efalo t\u233?morw\u233?n, y\u233?nd yau so kafrotaw\u233?n nden\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?ng\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n m\u233?n\u225?t sifay\u233? freng\u233?gh\u233?t f\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?nd njam w\u233?ng\u233?m f\u233?fene sifay\u233? freng\u233?gh\u233?t, y\u233?nd so n\u233?nangotan a tangwasron tafaftio m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m so em k\u233?t\u233? \u225?nde y\u233?nd w\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?m mat em end y\u233?n\u233? sifayat \u225?ndan y\u233?nd wiota."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu end y\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n Afafaf
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Tomas\u233?m y\u233?mndai f\u225?, "Yur\u233?, y\u233?nd mafina y\u233?n\u233?m \u225?ndan f\u233?m nuwanote, ndern\u225?ye y\u233?nd mat so y\u233?n\u233?m end?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "Y\u233?nd w\u233?m end a efalo a gh\u233?rs\u233?. Yau tayofnaye \u225?mb \u225?r so y\u233?ng\u233?m Afafaf, m\u233? ta k\u233?nj\u250?maro. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Njam f\u233?mofem y\u233?nd t\u233? wayamngoy\u233?nd, f\u233?mofem nden\u233?yameyo so tayamngongi tane Af\u233?. Y\u233?nam\u233? s\u233?nonjo f\u233?m mat em f\u225? a t\u233? yinjongi."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Filif norayai, "Yur\u233?, t\u233?feyot t\u233?nmauyafo Af\u233? a y\u233?nd y\u233?nanotro m\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Yesum yawangoi, "F\u233?m t\u225?f mat n\u233?m y\u233?nd, Filif, y\u233?nd f\u233?maf\u233? t\u233?nmorw\u233?n tekefifi. \u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom y\u233?nd t\u233? winjoi y\u233?mon t\u233? yinjo Af\u233?. F\u233?m n\u233?mam\u233?n noraye, 'T\u233?fe Af\u233? t\u233?nmauyafo'? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Yau f\u233?mon efalo yiy\u225?tote nde y\u233?nd w\u233?m Afane k\u233?nj\u250?n, a Af\u233? siy\u233?m tane k\u233?nj\u250?n? Si y\u233?nd k\u233?s norayan f\u233?fefaf yau tanjoyo em. W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m Af\u233? tane k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u233?mor, emo ewafrote y\u225?njo \u225?s\u225?fogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?nd efalo wiy\u225?totati njam nden\u233? norayan y\u233?nd w\u233?m Afane k\u233?nj\u250?n a Af\u233? siy\u233?m tane k\u233?nj\u250?n. Njam yau, efalo wiy\u225?totati m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndon tanwafrotan yam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?ndon f\u233?fe ewaufrotan efalo, \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom y\u233?nd efalo wiy\u225?tota so ewafrote y\u233?n\u233? yam y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? tanwafrotan. A wafroghyam y\u233?mo so ewafrote so engwainde minde ndimbal yam nden\u233? y\u233?ndon k\u233?s tawafrotan, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd nuwanotan Afafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
A y\u233?ndon so ewaufrotan n\u233?mat f\u233?m njam n\u243?mnendati tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, m\u233?n\u225?t Afane ndimbal kwayagh\u233? so nauyafote Ambumoene k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u233?m so n\u243?mnendati tafaf n\u233?mat t\u233?u tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, a y\u233?ndon so yafrotan.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Uny\u233?ghofnar si Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roenem\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?mofem njam wuwetati y\u233?nd, f\u233?m so n\u225?myotati tane n\u225?kfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
A y\u233?ndon so tamnendang\u233?n Af\u233?, a y\u233?mon so tawaramang\u233? \u225?mb W\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh \u225?r. Y\u233?n\u233? W\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh \u225?r so y\u233?mor f\u233?mofaf\u233? tuot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
F\u225? siy\u233?m Efaloene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r. Mband maratam yau so tumyong\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mon yau so y\u233?fande o yau so tayamngong\u233? f\u225?. W\u233?nde f\u233?m mat em f\u225? m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?maf\u233? emor a so y\u233?m f\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u233?ndon yau so tauron s\u233?far\u233?kw ambumnit, y\u233?nd so m\u233? w\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
M\u233? tekofnaye, mband maratam yau so w\u233?fande, w\u233?nde f\u233?mofem so w\u233?fandati. M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd naketan, f\u233?m nden\u233?yameyo so naketati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghon f\u233?m mat so em nden\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?m tane Afane k\u233?nj\u250?n, a f\u233?m em tane k\u233?nj\u250?n a y\u233?nd w\u233?m f\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Endefaf em tane n\u225?k a ewaitotat, f\u225? y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?y\u233?m emofem y\u233?nd wuwetat, m\u233?inyotio \u225?r emofem y\u233?nd wuwetat so w\u233?i euwete tane Afam, a y\u233?ndon so euwetan f\u225? a y\u233?nd nauyafotan y\u233?fefaf."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Judas (yau Judas Iskariot) norayai, "Yur\u233?, f\u233?m f\u233?myo n\u233?mam\u233?n so nauyafote t\u233?fefafro w\u233?nde yau mband maratfaf?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Yesum y\u233?wawangoi, "T\u225?f emo njam wuweta y\u233?nd, y\u233?mo so ewaitote tane watamegh. Tane Afam f\u225? so yuwete, a tane Af\u233? a y\u233?nd so y\u233?nre y\u225?faf a y\u233?nmor y\u233?maf\u233? tuot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u225? emo yau njam wuweta y\u233?nd yau so ewaitote tane watamegh. Y\u233?n\u233? si f\u233?mofem k\u233?s n\u225?y\u225?retati yau em tanjoyo, y\u225?ne em Afane emo y\u233?nd kw\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?rete. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? yamm\u233?n y\u233?ndon t\u233? k\u233?norayan f\u233?fefaf njam f\u233?maf\u233? m\u233? t\u233?n\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
W\u233?nde W\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh \u225?r, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r, efe Afam so y\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?rete tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, so ewatamete m\u233?inyotio yaman. Y\u233?mon so eut\u225?ne f\u233?m s\u225?i ewafarotati m\u233?inyotio y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? k\u233?norayaw\u233?n f\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Krufrat gh\u233?rs\u233? norotan f\u233?fefaf; tane krufr\u225?t gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?ndon ewarametan f\u233?f\u233? yau nden\u233? mband maratam k\u233?s ewaramete y\u233?ndon ewarametan. Yau eumyotati f\u233?fenjo tik\u233?f uw\u233?rsoghan a yau f\u233?rf\u233?r em.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?mofem t\u233? kwiy\u225?retati y\u233?nd korayan, y\u233?nd so kuwanon a so n\u233?nangotan f\u233?fefaf w\u233?ikor. F\u233?mofem njam y\u233?nd wuwetati, f\u233?m so \u225?uw\u233?ghan em tane \u225?lighm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n Afafaf; m\u233?nam\u233?n Afam wainde y\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Y\u233?ndon t\u233? tawaufrotan soram\u233? so nufrote, m\u233?n\u225?t njam nufrota f\u233?mofem so efalo tiy\u225?tongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Y\u233?nd yau so norayan ndenayu, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? mband maratoene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r y\u233?n\u233?m. W\u233?nde f\u225? siy\u233?m waftafnar y\u233?m tafaf, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
w\u233?nde mband marat mat so y\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?ndon yuwetan tane Af\u233? a ewaufrotan nden\u233?fifi ndern\u225?ye tane Afam w\u233?n\u233?mndetam y\u233?nd.
