\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 W\u233?nm\u233?nj a kafekafe
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Y\u233?nd w\u233?m efalo w\u233?nm\u233?nj, a tane Af\u233? siy\u233?m ndau t\u233?fn\u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?mo enfete m\u233?inyotio kafekafe tane k\u233?nj\u250?n \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam yau efunat mbwe, a y\u233?mon m\u233?inyotio kafe ewaine \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam efunat mbwe, m\u233?n\u225?t so minde mbweyaf\u233? em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?m em wafroghkaf m\u233?nam\u233?n sim\u233?n y\u233?ndon \u225?rk\u233? tan\u233?mndetaw\u233?n f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Mia em tane k\u233?nj\u250?n, a y\u233?nd w\u233?i m\u233? so w\u233?m f\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n. Yau \u225?mb kafeyam m\u233? so y\u233?fune mbwe y\u233?monyo t\u225?fandro w\u233?nm\u233?njan njam yurau. Nden\u233?yameyo f\u233?mofemyo yau so y\u233?funati mbwe t\u225?fandro ta k\u233?nj\u250?n njam m\u233? em.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u233?nd w\u233?m w\u233?nm\u233?nj, a f\u233?m em kafekafe. \u193?r njam m\u233? y\u233?m ta k\u233?nj\u250?n a y\u233?nd w\u233?m y\u225? k\u233?nj\u250?n, y\u233?mon so y\u233?fune t\u225?rf\u225?r mbwe tayofnaye f\u233?mon yau n\u233?m\u233? so yafrote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
F\u233?m yau njam m\u233? n\u233?m ta k\u233?nj\u250?n, f\u233?m ndenanit n\u233?m kafekafe y\u233?nau engtarnat a s\u233?r\u233?t nufrotat. \u193?r\u233?m ekafetat, ewitat k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?s\u233?t a nakernat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?m njam m\u233? em ta k\u233?nj\u250?n, a tane si m\u233? em f\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n, namotati n\u233?mat f\u233?m m\u233?nde em, a so yafrote f\u233?fe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m tane Afane ndimbal kwayagh\u233? m\u233?naye f\u233?mofem efunati t\u225?rf\u225?r mbwe, a nauyafotati f\u233?myo em tane waitogh \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? Afam y\u233?nd uwetam, a y\u233?ndon euwetam\u233?n f\u233?m, s\u233?nonjo m\u233? aem tane uw\u233?ghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Njam f\u233?m n\u225?myotati tane sifaf, f\u233?m m\u233? so em tane uw\u233?ghan, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?nd t\u233? kamyotaw\u233?n Afane sifaf a m\u233? w\u233?n\u233?m y\u225?ne uw\u233?ghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?ndon t\u233? ewaufron y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t tane \u225?uw\u233?gh so y\u233?m f\u233?fefaf a m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?fene \u225?uw\u233?gh so w\u233?i y\u233?m afoghare.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m tane n\u225?k: Nauwetati f\u233?mro f\u233?mro nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?ndon k\u233?s euwetam\u233?n f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Minde tuk\u233?n uw\u233?gh fene f\u250?tar\u233?t siy\u233?m s\u225?i t\u233?ram fenjo gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u233?m em tane f\u250?tar\u233?f njam f\u233?mofem ewafrotati n\u233?mat y\u233?ndon emndetan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u233?ndon yau nden\u233? emndetan faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, m\u233?nam\u233?n faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r yau so mat y\u233?m y\u225?ne yurane \u225?s\u225?foghm\u233?n, w\u233?nde y\u233?ndo emnday\u233?n f\u250?tar\u233?f, m\u233?nam\u233?n m\u233?inyotio n\u233?m\u233? mat n\u233?n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?n Afata y\u233?ndon mat t\u233? tany\u225?totan f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?mofem yau y\u233?nd w\u233?kafay\u233?nd, w\u233?nde y\u233?ndon ekafay\u233?n f\u233?m a ewafery\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m so eng\u233?m mbwe funagh\u233?t, mbwe \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? so naketat. A n\u233?mat f\u233?m njam n\u243?mnendati tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, Afam so tawaramang\u233? f\u233?fe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m tane n\u225?k: Nauwetati f\u233?mro f\u233?mro.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Mbandam t\u233?kr\u225?t efande Yesuene waitogh \u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Njam mband maratam m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat efanda, t\u225?f nawafarotati nden\u233? y\u233?nd t\u233? m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat kw\u233?fandau fronde. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Njam f\u233?m mband maratoene n\u233?m, so n\u233?muete m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m y\u225?ne n\u233?m. W\u233?nde f\u233?m yau mband maratoene em, a y\u233?ndon t\u233? ewafery\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? mband maratta. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan mband maratam m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat efande f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Nawafarotati si y\u233?ndon k\u233?s tamndetaw\u233?n f\u233?m: 'Faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r y\u225?inde y\u225?njo yuram.' Njam y\u233?mofem was\u233?rmbotat y\u233?nd, w\u233?i so ewas\u233?rmbotat f\u233?m nden\u233?yameyo. Njam tane watameghfaf n\u225?y\u225?retat f\u225?, w\u233?i so n\u225?y\u225?retat f\u233?fene watameghfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Y\u233?mofem so ewas\u233?rmbotat nden\u225?ye tane y\u233?tkw\u233?n t\u233?fnan m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? mafina em emo y\u233?nd w\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Y\u233?nd yau njam kw\u233?nmorw\u233?n a korayaw\u233?n y\u233?fefaf, f\u225? yau so yaufiyam k\u233?rtaf\u233? tamorw\u233?n; w\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo f\u225? yau so norayat nden\u233? y\u233?ndfem yau tawafrotam yaufi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Emo y\u233?nd m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat w\u233?fande w\u233?i m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat y\u233?fande tane Af\u233? nden\u233?yameyo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Y\u233?ndon yau njam tawafrotan ufarogh yam y\u233?fefaf \u225?rk\u233? \u225?mb \u225?rom yau ewafrotam, f\u225? yau so tamorw\u233?n yaufiyam k\u233?rtaf\u233?. W\u233?nde nden\u225?ye y\u233?m y\u233?mofem t\u233? yinjoy\u233?nd a y\u233?mafem m\u233? m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat t\u233?nfandat y\u233?nd a tane Af\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m s\u225?i efalo tiy\u225?tongi n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?farotam\u233?nd y\u233?fene n\u225?kan, "Y\u233?mofem m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat w\u233?fandat m\u233? fifiofnar."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Njam W\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh \u225?r y\u233?n\u233?m, efe y\u233?ndon so y\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retan k\u233?tam\u233? Afata, Efaloene Nj\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r efe so y\u233?n\u233?m Afata, f\u225? so n\u233?ngafrote tanem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
F\u233?m w\u233?i nden\u233?yameyo so n\u233?ngafrotati tanem\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndf\u233? f\u233?m t\u233? t\u233?n\u233?m r\u233?ny\u233?ghta.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 16
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
M\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?ndon t\u233? tawaufrotan f\u233?fe m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m yau so k\u233?kmbongi ndimbal mwighata. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?mofem so eutonat \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngota, efogh y\u233?na y\u233?n\u233?m njam f\u225? emo esmetat krot f\u233?m so nemne kar y\u233?n\u233? yame \u225?s\u225?fogh yafrote Ng\u225?nj\u225?neyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?mofem so ewafrotat y\u233?n\u233? yam m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? mafina em Af\u233? o y\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?ndon t\u233? tawaufrotaw\u233?n y\u233?n\u233?, m\u233?n\u225?t njam y\u233?n\u233? efogh kufarng\u233? y\u233?feyot y\u233?n\u233? yam wafrogh\u233?t, f\u233?m so kawafarotangi n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon tan\u233?mndetan.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 \u193?s\u225?fogh Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roene
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Y\u233?ndon yau f\u233?fe ewaufrotam\u233?n r\u233?ny\u233?ghan m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd f\u233?maf\u233? t\u233?nmorw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
W\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd nuwanotan y\u225?faf emo w\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam y\u233?nd, w\u233?nde \u225?mb \u225?rom yau w\u233?mota, '\u193?ndan f\u233?m niota?' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
A s\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndon t\u233? ewaufron y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n, f\u233?fene tik\u233?f t\u233? ewafo ndimbal gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon f\u233?fe ewaufrotan efalo, y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m f\u233?fene merot y\u233?nd k\u233?s nuwanotan. M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd njam yau kuwanon, W\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh \u225?r m\u233? yau so y\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?fefaf, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd njam kuwanon, y\u233?ndon so y\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retan f\u225? f\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
A f\u225? njam y\u233?n\u233?m, y\u233?mon so tawauyafong\u233? y\u233?n\u233? mband marat \u225?r\u233?t nden\u233? f\u225? ndern\u225?ye em. Y\u233?mon tawauyafong\u233? nden\u233? f\u225? m\u225?m\u225?fi em. F\u225? yau mat em n\u233?m\u233? yaufi y\u233?m, f\u225? yau mat em efe mbark\u225?nd em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf, a f\u225? yau mat em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene moghm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u225? yau mat em mbark\u225?nde n\u233?m\u233? yaufiyam y\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mofem yau efalo wiy\u225?totat y\u233?nd; {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
f\u225? yau mat em mbark\u225?ndm\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd nuwanotan Afafaf. A f\u233?mofem yau kor so w\u233?fandati w\u233?i. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
A f\u225? yau mat em moghm\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n s\u233?nonjo y\u233?n\u233? mbandm\u233?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r t\u233? moghan y\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Tafaf t\u225?rf\u225?r yamaf\u233? em s\u225?i norayan f\u233?fefaf, w\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo so em t\u225?rf\u225?rfifi f\u233?feyot y\u225?togh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
W\u233?nde njam f\u225?, efaloene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r y\u233?n\u233?m, y\u233?mon so ewatamete m\u233?inyotio efalo fifiyam\u233?. F\u225? yau so noraye y\u225?njom\u233?n. F\u225? so y\u233?naro noraye n\u233?m\u233? f\u225? n\u233?n\u225?y\u225?rete, a y\u233?mon so ewaufrote n\u233?m\u233? so n\u233?ngufrotat soram\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?mon so y\u233?n\u233?rse ndimbal kwayagh\u233? tafaf, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mon so eng\u233?rse n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon norayan a so ewaufrote f\u233?fe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
M\u233?inyotio n\u233?m\u233? em Afane sem tane em. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan y\u233?nd norayan nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram so eng\u233?rse n\u233?m\u233? em tane a engwaufrota f\u233?feyot.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? so kawengong\u233? \u225?uw\u233?gh\u233?t
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Tekofnaye y\u233?nd yau so w\u233?fandati, w\u233?ikor tekofnaye, a f\u233?mofem w\u233?i so w\u233?fandati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
\u193?mb y\u225?ne waitogh \u225?r norayay\u233?nd f\u225?ro, "N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon y\u233?s\u233?rmbne nden\u225?ye k\u233?s noraye nden\u233?, 'm\u233? tekofnaye, f\u233?mofem yau so w\u233?fandati w\u233?ikor a tekofnaye soram\u233? so kwinjongi,' a 'm\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd wiota Afafaf'?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u225? m\u233? kamotaw\u233?t, "N\u233?m\u233? y\u233?mon y\u233?s\u233?rmbne nden\u233? m\u233? tekofnaye? Y\u233?ndfem kor yau y\u233?rsam n\u233?m\u233? f\u225? noraye!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Yesu mat t\u233?morw\u233?n n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u225? m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n mogh\u233?t t\u233?rametaw\u233?t f\u225?, y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u225? norayai y\u233?fefaf, "N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m namotati f\u233?mro y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?s\u233?rmbnan t\u225?f y\u233?nd njam norayang\u233?n nden\u233?, 'm\u233? tekofnaye, f\u233?mofem yau so w\u233?fandati w\u233?ikor a tekofnaye soram\u233? so kwinjongi w\u233?ikor'? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u233?ndon f\u233?fe ewaufrotan efalo, f\u233?m so nendati a gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? em w\u233?nde mband marat f\u225? m\u233? y\u233?m \u225?uw\u233?ghan. F\u233?m so gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? em w\u233?nde soram\u233? f\u233?fene gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? so kawengong\u233? \u225?uw\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Amaf njam n\u225?r\u225?fte ambum k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m t\u233?kr\u225?t m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne efogh t\u233? nawer; w\u233?nde t\u225?f amafom njam ambum t\u233?r\u225?ftang\u233?, f\u225? tawalindang\u233? nd\u233?mke y\u225?ne \u225?uw\u233?gh t\u233?fnan m\u233?nam\u233?n ambum t\u233? nufar y\u233?n\u233? mband maratot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?fefaf: S\u233?nonjo siy\u233?m f\u233?fene gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? efogh, w\u233?nde y\u233?ndon so tawinjon f\u233?m w\u233?ikor a f\u233?m so n\u225?uw\u233?tati, a \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom yau tangwanang\u233? f\u233?fene uw\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghon f\u233?mofem yau so w\u233?motati n\u233?m\u233? rokarot. Y\u233?ndon f\u233?fe ewaufrotan efalo: tane Afam so ewaramete n\u233?mat njam namotati tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
K\u233?tamayo s\u233?nonjo f\u233?m \u225?mb yau kamotati tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan; kamotangi a f\u233?mofem so tanangi a f\u233?fene \u225?uw\u233?gh so afoghkaf y\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Y\u233?ndon t\u233? korayan waufarogh si, m\u233?n\u225?t wafergh\u233?t f\u233?fefaf y\u233?nd n\u233?mam\u233?n t\u233? korayaw\u233?n, efogh y\u233?na y\u233?n\u233?m \u225?nde y\u233?ndon yau so n\u233?ngorayan y\u233?n\u233? waufarogh si, w\u233?nde so ewaufrotan m\u233? saf\u233?nro tane Afanem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghon f\u233?m so namotati tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, y\u233?nd yau nden\u233? norayan y\u233?ndo s\u225?i y\u233?motan Af\u233? f\u233?fenem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Yau, Afam y\u233?monyo euwete f\u233?m m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem y\u233?nd t\u233? wuwetam\u233?nd a t\u233? efalo wiy\u225?toy\u233?nd nden\u233? y\u233?nd w\u233?nmorm\u233?n Ng\u225?j\u225?neta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Y\u233?nd w\u233?nmorm\u233?n Afata a nufary\u233?n mband maratot, s\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndon y\u233?frangotan mband marat a nangotan k\u233?t\u225?n Afafaf."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
