S\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndfem t\u233? yinjong\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?m mat n\u233?m m\u233?inyotio rokar, f\u233?m yau m\u233?nde n\u233?m efe y\u233?ramai amogh si fefaf. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan, y\u233?ndfem efalo niy\u225?totam f\u233?m efaloe t\u233? n\u233?nmorm\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta."
