Soram\u233? Yesu norayai y\u233?n\u233?, f\u225? n\u233?retai njafarot a norayai:
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Af\u233?, efogh t\u233? nawer. Minde kwayagh\u233? taram fenjo Ambumoe m\u233?n\u225?t Ambumom so ndimbal kwayagh\u233? k\u233?marang\u233? fe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
F\u233?mon waft\u233? yaramai y\u225? m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t, m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mon so tawaramang\u233? tuot gh\u233?rs\u233? m\u233?inyotio y\u233?fe f\u233?mon efe yaramai y\u225?yot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Tuot gh\u233?rsane fifi siy\u233?m f\u233?m mat s\u225?i k\u233?ny\u225?tongi, m\u233? efalo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, a mat s\u225?i k\u225?y\u225?tongi Yesu Keriso, efe f\u233?mon y\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?ndon t\u233? y\u233?n\u233?rsam\u233?n feyot ndimbal kwayagh\u233? mband maratot m\u233?n\u225?yan k\u233?s yifoy\u233?n \u225?s\u225?fogh f\u233?mon n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? waramai wafrogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Af\u233?, kwaram ta ndimbal kwayagh\u233? fene s\u225?fr\u233?re s\u233?nonjo, nden\u233? s\u225?f\u233?tio ndimbal kwayagh\u233? kwaram y\u233?ndf\u233? k\u233?s y\u233?nmare f\u233?maf\u233? soram\u233? mband marat yafrotam.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesuf koraiw\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf y\u225?njo waitogh \u225?rfenem\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
"Y\u233?ndon t\u233? k\u233?muyafotan f\u233?m y\u233?fefaf f\u233?mon efe t\u233? waramai y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan. F\u225? tamorw\u233?n fen\u233? f\u233?mon eramai f\u225? tafaf. Y\u233?mofem t\u233? tarawenat fene si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
S\u233?nonjo f\u225? mat em nden\u233? m\u233?inyotio f\u233?mon kwaramete en\u233?m fe tamb\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?ndon ewaramay\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? si f\u233?mon waramai, a y\u233?mofem umyoy\u233?nd. F\u225? mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m efalo y\u233?nd w\u233?nmorm\u233?n fe tamb\u233?n, a y\u233?mofem efalo wiy\u225?toy\u233?nd nden\u233? f\u233?mon y\u233?nd kw\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?rete. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?nd norayan Fefaf Ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u233?fenem\u233?n. Y\u233?nd norayan Fefaf yau y\u233?n\u233? mband maratm\u233?n, w\u233?nde y\u233?fenem\u233?n f\u233?mon efe t\u233? waramai, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? sem fene. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
M\u233?inyotio tane n\u233?m\u233? em fene em, a fene m\u233?inyotio n\u233?m\u233? em tane em; a tane ndimbal kwayagh\u233? n\u225?l\u225?le y\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?nd yau so y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan ndenayu w\u233?mor, w\u233?nde f\u225? m\u233? so emor y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan, a y\u233?nd angogh\u233?t n\u233?nufngon fefaf. Nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar Af\u233?, ewarawena f\u225? fene waftaf\u233? y\u233?tkw\u233?ne, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?tkw\u233?n ta waramai, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? so em \u225?mbiro nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?nd \u225?mbiro k\u233?s y\u233?nre. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Njam y\u233?nd t\u233?nmorw\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233?, y\u233?ndon tawarawenaw\u233?n f\u225? m\u233?naye fene waft\u233? y\u233?tkw\u233?ne, f\u233?mon \u225?rk\u233? waramai. Y\u233?ndon tawarawenaw\u233?n a \u225?mb yau nolindai m\u233? \u225?mbiroro w\u233?nde efe t\u233? y\u233?kmay\u233?nd, m\u233?n\u225?t Buk siam s\u225?i efalo tiy\u225?tong\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
"Y\u233?nd angogh n\u233?nufngon fefaf s\u233?nonjo, w\u233?nde y\u233?ndon n\u233?ngorayan y\u233?n\u233? yamm\u233?n njamandio m\u233? w\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?inyotio tane \u225?uw\u233?gh so y\u233?m y\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?ndon ewaramay\u233?n fene si, w\u233?nde mband maratam m\u233?ndm\u233?ndat tafandaw\u233?ng f\u225?, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? yau y\u233?n\u233? mband maratm\u233?n em nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?nd yau w\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? mband maratm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Tane oray\u233?gh yau y\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?mon s\u225?i tawitr\u233?mb y\u233?n\u233? mband maratta, w\u233?nde m\u233?n\u225?t so ewarawene yaufi \u225?roe tamb\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u225? yau em y\u233?n\u233? mbandm\u233?n, y\u233?nd w\u233?i nden\u225?yo yau w\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? mband maratm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar f\u225? t\u225?y\u225?to m\u233?naye fene efalo si\u233? fene si siy\u233?m efalo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u233?mon k\u233?s kw\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?rete y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? mband maratot, y\u233?ndon w\u233?i engw\u225?f\u225?retan y\u233?n\u233? mband maratot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?feyot y\u233?nd narametan y\u233?ndio fefaf, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? w\u233?i so efaloe taramang\u233? fefaf.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yesu Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? koraiw\u233?t m\u233?inyotio efalo y\u225?togh \u225?rfenem\u233?n
