"Tane oray\u233?gh yau y\u233?feyotro y\u233?m. Y\u233?nd w\u233?i norayan y\u233?feyot emofem so efalo wiy\u225?totat y\u233?fene si waitogh k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? m\u233?inyotio so em \u225?mbiro, Af\u233?, nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? f\u233?m n\u233?m tane k\u233?nj\u250?n a y\u233?nd w\u233?m fene k\u233?nj\u250?n. F\u225? w\u233?i so em t\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n m\u233?n\u225?t mband maratam so efalo yiy\u225?tote nden\u233? f\u233?mon t\u233? w\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam y\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
