Y\u233?nd y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n a f\u233?m tane k\u233?nj\u250?n, m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? so kamndangi m\u233? \u225?mbirofifi, m\u233?n\u225?t mband marat s\u225?i mat yiy\u225?totat nden\u233? f\u233?mon y\u233?nd kw\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?rete a euwetam f\u225? nden\u233?yameyo y\u233?nd k\u233?s uwetam.
