A f\u233?m srem Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?rfene ambum a f\u233?m ewafnyang Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf n\u233?m\u233? mwigh\u233? y\u233?r\u233?indam f\u233?fekif\u233?. Y\u233?mon norayai Ebraamefaf, 'Fene \u225?ki ambum k\u233?nj\u250?n m\u233?inyotio \u225?r y\u233?n\u233? mbandan freng\u233?ghan so em.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
