Stifen, y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ng\u225?r\u225?m afoghkaf a waftaf\u233?, y\u233?mon tawafrotau ndimbal s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam a ufarogh yam \u225?rfene k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde \u225?mb Ju \u225?r k\u233?tamam\u233?n tamorw\u233?n Sairene a Aleksandriam\u233?n a Silisia a Esia yum\u233?n efe korayaw\u233?t nden\u233? y\u233?nd siy\u233?n\u233?m Yuwek \u225?r. Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r \u233?wigh nufngoy\u233?nd Stifenf\u233?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
w\u233?nde f\u225? f\u233?yotarofnar tamorw\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233? \u233?wigh\u233?t m\u233?nam\u233?n Stifen t\u233?morw\u233?n k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? a Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roene muyayan korayau.
