Y\u233?mofem kwankwane ewafery\u233?nd \u225?mb \u225?r nden\u233? siot, "Y\u233?ndfem t\u233? yiy\u225?ray\u233?m Stifen yaufi si korayau Mosesefaf a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? ende y\u233?mofem ewasemnay\u233?nd \u225?r, s\u233?nko \u225?r, a n\u225?k watamegh \u225?r. Y\u233?mofem y\u233?nmeray\u233?nd Stifen y\u233?n\u233?mnjoy\u233?nd Ju \u225?rfene s\u233?nko \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh s\u225?fr\u233?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?funay\u233?nd uny\u233?gh si, efe norayay\u233?nd, "Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r yau k\u233?kmbong\u233? wanyogh si oray\u233?gh y\u233?n\u233? w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo sifayam\u233?n a n\u225?km\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?ndfem f\u233?t\u233? tiy\u225?retaw\u233?m f\u225? korayau nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? Najaretm\u233?n Yesum so yirone y\u233?n\u233? sifay\u233? a so ewengote \u225?kiafene n\u225?k Moses\u233?m \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? t\u233? ewafnamoi t\u233?fefaf."
