M\u233?inyotio efe tamorang\u233?rw\u233?n Ju \u225?rfene s\u233?nko \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?ghan Stifen y\u233?mofem t\u233?fandaw\u233?t y\u225?ne s\u225?f n\u225?y\u225?toi ndenanit njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?rnit.
