F\u233?yo lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?rom y\u233?motai Stifen, "Y\u233?n\u233? w\u225?taran\u233?gh efalo em?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?moghm\u233?n y\u233?mo yawangoi, "F\u250?tar\u233?f a afaf, k\u233?n\u225?y\u225?rangi tafaf\u451? Minde kwayaghaf\u233? t\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n nufary\u233?ng k\u233?t\u225?n t\u233?fene \u225?ki Ebraamefaf njam f\u225? m\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n Mesofotamiyan, t\u225?f fronde njam f\u225? t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n Aranan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?mndai, 'T\u233?frango fenjo yu a fenjo \u225?r, a kuwano k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?rk\u233? mband y\u233?ndon so k\u233?mauyafon.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
"F\u233?yo y\u233?mon y\u233?frangoi Kaldia \u225?rfene mband a n\u225?mnjoi Aranan. Y\u225?refane k\u233?r soram\u233?, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?ngw\u225?f\u225?retam f\u225? y\u233?n\u233? mbandot \u225?nde f\u233?m s\u233?nonjo emor. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yau yaramai \u225?mb mband y\u233?na. W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam uny\u233?ghofnar si y\u233?mndai f\u225?, 'F\u233?m a fene \u225?kif fe soram\u233? mband so tawaramang\u233?.' Y\u233?n\u233? efghon Ebraam ambumofnar t\u233?morw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n korayau y\u225?faf y\u233?n\u233? ende, 'F\u233?fene \u225?kif so em dabi \u225?r \u225?mb \u225?rfene ndimbal yuwon yau y\u233?fenjo ndimbal yuwon, f\u225? so em \u225?rfene faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r a so taftaw\u233?t 400 yunj\u233?f. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon so t\u233?kr\u225?tan t\u233?kman y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal yu faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?tro \u225?r ey\u225?totat, a soram\u233? yuwon f\u225? so k\u233?ntorngi y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal yuta a so w\u225?wefnotat ta y\u233?n\u233? sifayan.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n a Ebraam si y\u233?reiny\u233?m\u233?nd gh\u233?ngan n\u233?f\u233?ghm\u233?n. Ebraam n\u233?namndai Aiseke y\u225?ref\u233? a gh\u233?ngan yanfai 8 efogh y\u225?ne \u225?r\u225?f\u233?gh soram\u233?. Soram\u233? Aisek n\u233?namndai Jeikofe y\u225?ref\u233?, a Jeikof n\u233?namndai 12 ambumafene y\u233?feraf\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
"Jeikofene ambumam waramnjagh yafngoy\u233?nd y\u233?fenng\u233?n Josef, y\u233?mofem f\u225? y\u233?ramay\u233?nd Ijif\u233?t faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r. W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? f\u225? t\u225?rw\u233?n {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam tambetau f\u225? k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? m\u233?inyotio y\u225?njo k\u233?rtata. Farawa Ijifm\u233?n warsagh \u225?rom m\u233?ndef\u233? t\u233?fandau Josef m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yaramai k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233?, y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan Farawam y\u233?mndai Ijif yu lim\u225?n\u233?gh\u233?t a m\u233?inyotio y\u225?ne m\u233?ngo.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
"F\u233?yo k\u225?uk\u225?u nuyai Ijif a Kanan yuwon, k\u225?uk\u225?uam y\u233?n\u233?rsam ndimbal yauyau njamke t\u233?fnan a t\u233?fene \u225?kif njamkefnar n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Njam Jeikof n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?ng nden\u233? rais k\u233?t\u233? tamorw\u233?n Ijif\u233?n, y\u233?mo ew\u225?f\u225?retam y\u225?ne ambum efe t\u233?fene n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd \u225?kif fronde yafoghan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?fene y\u233?namayo yafoghan, Josef\u233?m ewaufroi y\u225?nafet efe f\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n, a Farawa mat n\u225?y\u225?toi Josefene m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233?, Josefem ew\u225?f\u225?retam y\u225?ref\u233? Jeikofeyot a y\u225?ne m\u233?inyotio m\u233?r\u233?n, 75 m\u233?inyotio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yo Jeikof n\u233?wanoi Ijif\u233?t, \u225?nde Jeikof a t\u233?fene \u225?kif k\u233?r emorm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?fene fifi enwangotam\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n Sekem\u233?t a ekmay\u233?nd mb\u233?w\u233? m\u233?ngon Ebraam\u233?m \u225?rk\u233? yanay\u233?ng Amorene ambumta Sekemm\u233?n manie.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
"Efogh kaka k\u233?n\u225?y\u225?totau Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u225?njo si efalo s\u225?i tiy\u225?tongai Ebraamefaf, t\u233?fene \u225?r marat t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?to Ijif\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u233?yo tot\u233?r warsagh \u225?r efe mat yau t\u233?morw\u233?n Josefenem\u233?n n\u233?namndai warsagh \u225?r Ijif\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?mon yaufiyam tawafrotau t\u233?fene \u225?r a tawas\u233?rmbotau t\u233?fene \u225?kif w\u225?fareghe taw\u225?f\u225?retau m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?fene tot\u233?r r\u225?f\u233?gh ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r wigh\u233?t krot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233? efghon Moses n\u225?r\u225?ftam a Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene gh\u233?kfan f\u225? k\u233?retau mer ambum. Nambio gh\u233?rare k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u233?mon tarawenau y\u225?refane m\u233?ngon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Njam y\u233?mon y\u233?nmutory\u233?ng, Farawane m\u233?rsom y\u233?rnyai yandio ambumot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Moses m\u233?inyotio k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? yatametam\u233?nd Ijif \u225?r\u233?m a t\u233?morw\u233?n waft\u233? k\u233?r ro sian a wafroghan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
"Njam Moses t\u233?morw\u233?n 40 yunj\u233?f, y\u233?mon mwigh\u233? yaitotam yafogh\u233?t y\u225?njo Israil \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Moses\u233?m yinjoi \u225?mb \u225?r Israilm\u233?n Ijifm\u233?n \u225?rom tus\u233?rmbotau, f\u233?yo f\u225? nuwanoi y\u225? w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t a fai wangogh\u233?t Ijifm\u233?n \u225?r y\u233?smetam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Moses k\u233?ma kemnau nden\u233? y\u225?njo \u225?r\u233?m kar so tayamngongay\u233?nd nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam f\u225? t\u233?limndau y\u233?fe wanjargh\u233?t, w\u233?nde y\u233?mofem yau y\u225?y\u225?mngoy\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
\u193?mb kw\u233?fon Moses y\u233?nmorm\u233?n s\u243?mbio Israilm\u233?n \u225?r ewinjeyai \u225?sm\u233?ghan. Y\u233?mon y\u233?ta krufr\u225?t taramw\u233?ng y\u233?n\u233? sie, '\u193?r s\u243?mb\u225?r, f\u233?mro ere f\u250?tarf\u233?, f\u233?m n\u233?mam\u233?n nawaghan\u233?t?'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
"W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rom efe tus\u233?rmbotau y\u225? f\u250?tar, y\u233?mon y\u233?f\u233?rngotai Moses t\u233?ndot a norayai, 'Emo f\u233?m niy\u225?toi lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?rot a t\u233?fe gh\u233?k\u233?f fayogh\u233?t? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?mo y\u233?nd krot wafngo nden\u233?yame Ijifm\u233?n \u225?r k\u225?ye f\u233?mon y\u233?nau t\u233?smete?' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Njam Moses\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? si n\u225?y\u225?rai, f\u225? nuwanoi Midian mbandot d\u225?bi n\u225?y\u225?toi nawerai amaf s\u243?mbio ambumaf\u233? n\u225?y\u225?toi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
"40 yunj\u233?f soram\u233?, njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r nufary\u233?ng Mosesefaf k\u233?ghat f\u233?s k\u225?nk\u233?k\u225?nk\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? fanfne yuwon mband tunak\u233?f y\u233?tkw\u233?n Sainai kaka. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Njam Moses\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?s yinjoy\u233?ng, f\u225? s\u233?lngw\u233?l y\u233?morm\u233?n. Njamandio f\u225? y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n kaka fandagh\u233?t, y\u233?mon n\u225?y\u225?rai Yurane k\u233?m: {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
'Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n endeyot t\u225?wefnotaw\u233?t f\u233?fene \u225?kiam, Ebraam, Aisek, a Jeikof.' Moses ngernger t\u233?morw\u233?n f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? fandagh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
"F\u233?yo Yuram y\u233?mndai, 'Tafitrar fenjo sandol, y\u233?n\u233? sifay\u233? \u225?nde f\u233?m n\u233?makai siy\u233?m nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar mband. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
