Njam Fit\u233? m\u233? kemnau y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?ghm\u233?n, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram y\u233?mndai, "Saimon, nambio \u225?r\u233?m f\u233?m n\u233?ronjat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
F\u233?yo kokai a kewor. Yau naut\u233?mnda y\u233?maf\u233? \u225?ligh\u233?t, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndon tanw\u225?f\u225?retan f\u225?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Fit\u233? n\u233?newory\u233?ng a y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emndai, "Y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? fw\u233?m f\u233?mofem efe y\u233?ronjati. N\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?m tan\u233?m?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r\u233?m yawangoy\u233?nd, "Y\u233?nd t\u233?n\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Konelias Rom fiyar\u233? s\u233?nko \u225?roe tamb\u233?n. F\u225? siy\u233?m mbark\u225?nd a Ng\u225?nj\u225?n f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? \u225?r, efe yut\u233?mndat m\u233?inyotio Ju \u225?r\u233?m. Nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?rom y\u233?mndai \u225?r tangw\u225?f\u225?reta y\u225?ne m\u233?ngot m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mon so niy\u225?rete n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?m so noraye." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u233?yo Fitam eumyoi y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r y\u225?ne m\u233?ngot. F\u233?yo y\u225?ne wan t\u233?fn\u225?r n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fit\u233? k\u233?t\u233? Koneliasene m\u233?ngon
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 \u193?mb efghon Fit\u233? k\u225?frendau y\u233?maf\u233? \u225?ligh\u233?t, a \u225?mb efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r k\u233?tamam\u233?n Jofa tesenm\u233?n n\u233?ngwanoy\u233?nd y\u233?maf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
\u193?mb efghon Fit\u233? nufary\u233?ng Kaisaria tesenot. Konelias kawanjetau y\u225?yot a eumendai m\u233?inyotio y\u225?ne m\u233?r\u233?n a kaka f\u250?tar\u233?f. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Njam Fit\u233? n\u233?nglawai m\u233?ngot, Konelias\u233?m y\u233?f\u225?ngoi a y\u225?wefnoi y\u225?ne kafkafot utman\u233?ghaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
W\u233?nde Fitam y\u233?m\u233?indai f\u225? anogh\u233?t a y\u233?mndai, "Kokai, yau w\u225?wefnota tayot. Y\u233?nd nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? w\u233?m f\u233?m y\u233?f n\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Fit\u233? a Konelias koraiw\u233?t, y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? Fit\u233? n\u233?nglawai m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?t ewinjoi \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Fit\u233? norayai y\u233?fefaf, "F\u233?m T\u233?ndo \u225?r mer mat em t\u233?fene Ju \u225?rfene n\u225?k, Ju \u225?r yau so T\u233?ndo \u225?rfene m\u233?ngot n\u233?lawetat a nawar\u233?indat T\u233?ndo \u225?rf\u233?. W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ta t\u233? wauyafoi y\u233?ndon efe yau so k\u233?nkarotang\u233?n nden\u233? f\u233?m n\u233?m yaufi o nj\u250?nnj\u250?naf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n njam f\u233?mofem tangw\u225?f\u225?retati tafaf, y\u233?nd kw\u233?n\u233?m \u225?moghofnar. Y\u233?nd namotan f\u233?fefaf, 'N\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?nd f\u233?mofem kwarawetati?'"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Konelias\u233?m yawangoi, "Fo efogh soram\u233? y\u233?nd kw\u233?morw\u233?n tanjo m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oraighan y\u233?n\u233? efoghf\u233?nef\u233?neyan, 3 aklok s\u233?ite kar\u233?f. Sunsune \u225?r nufary\u233?ng \u225?l\u225?l\u233?gh s\u225?l\u225?meyaf\u233? tane s\u225?fr\u233?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
A njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r norayai, 'Konelias, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233? n\u225?y\u225?r\u233? fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?ghm\u233?n a n\u233?mawafarote fene rokar ram\u233?ghm\u233?n yauyau \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
\u193?r taw\u225?f\u225?reta Jofa tesenot Saimonefaf efe yanmotat Fit\u233?. F\u225? siy\u233?m wan t\u233?fn\u225?r Saimon, w\u233?r\u225?r gh\u233?ngan wator\u233?gh \u225?r, endene m\u233?ngo y\u233?m arakaf t\u233?ndon.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon tangw\u225?f\u225?retan feyot t\u225?f f\u233?t\u233?, a nder\u233? mer y\u233?m f\u233?m k\u233?s k\u233?n\u233?m. S\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio y\u233?na y\u233?n\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene s\u225?fr\u233?re m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?inyotio si \u225?y\u225?rgh\u233?t Yuram f\u233?m k\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?rete t\u233?fe waufrogh\u233?t."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
F\u233?yo Fitam si y\u233?rnyai: "Y\u233?ndon s\u233?nonjo y\u225?yamngon efalo y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yau yuyafote witmaro m\u233?nde yam {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
w\u233?nde eumyote \u225?r m\u233?inyotio yum\u233?n emofem f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? y\u233?fandat f\u225? a ewafrotat n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m mbark\u225?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
F\u233?m si mat em Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?retam Israil \u225?rfefaf, t\u225?itotau mer si krufr\u225?tm\u233?n Yesu Keriso k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, efe Yur\u233? y\u233?m m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
F\u233?m mat em n\u233?m\u233? kufrotaw\u233?t Judia k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, n\u233?narnyai k\u233?t\u233? Galili yuwon walitogh soram\u233? Jon\u233?m si t\u225?itotau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Ndern\u225?ye Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yafery\u233?ng Yesu Najaretm\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?re a waftaye, a ndern\u225?ye f\u225? tiyotaw\u233?ng mer tawafrotau a mer t\u225?y\u225?totau m\u233?inyotio f\u225? efe tamorw\u233?n S\u225?ifroene waft\u233? mbanmbanan, m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? f\u225? t\u225?rw\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
"Y\u233?nd fandagh \u225?r y\u233?n\u233?m m\u233?inyotio yamm\u233?n y\u233?mon stawafrotau Ju yuwon a Jerusalem\u233?n. Y\u233?mofem y\u233?smetam\u233?nd f\u225? y\u233?namayo yamay\u233?nd wafatar\u233?gh w\u233?nan, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yanoi f\u225? k\u233?rta nambio efogh soram\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t fandagh\u233?t, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m yau yinjoy\u233?nd, w\u233?nde fandagh \u225?r\u233?mro efe Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u225?nd\u225?i ewafery\u233?ng, nden\u233? y\u233?nd emaf\u233? t\u225?netaw\u233?m njamke a nu y\u233?maf\u233? soram\u233? f\u225? nanoi k\u233?rta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u233?n\u233?mnday\u233?ng y\u233?nd si waitogh\u233?t \u225?r\u233?t a afrogh\u233?t nden\u233? f\u225? siy\u233?m \u225?mbiro efe Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yafery\u233?ng nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? mogh \u225?r gh\u233?rs\u233? a k\u233?r \u225?r\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
M\u233?inyotio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?m nafrotat y\u225?nem\u233?n nden\u233? m\u233?inyotio \u225?r\u233?m emofem efalo yiy\u225?totat f\u225? tawalindang\u233? y\u233?fene yaufim\u233?n y\u225?ne y\u233?tkw\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
Njamandio Fit\u233? m\u233? korayau y\u233?n\u233? si, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r n\u233?newory\u233?ng y\u233?fefaf efe m\u233?inyotio k\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
Ju efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r efe t\u233? n\u233?nuwanoy\u233?nd Fitaf\u233? s\u233?lngw\u233?l emorm\u233?n nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roene tamb\u233?n t\u233? nasury\u233?ng nden\u233?yameyo T\u233?ndo \u225?r\u233?t, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mofem t\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?t f\u225? \u225?mb yum\u233?n sie korayaw\u233?t a tuwetaw\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 F\u233?yo Fit\u233? norayai, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
"Y\u233?mofem t\u233? yanangi Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?ndfem. \u193?rk\u233? \u225?rom yau so takmbong\u233? nu walitogh\u233?t." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde y\u233?mon emndai f\u225? f\u233?t\u233? so ewalitote Yesu Kerisoene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan. F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem yamnenday\u233?nd Fit\u233? \u225?mnjogh\u233?t y\u233?maf\u233? nambio efghotro.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 11
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fitam ewafene y\u225?njo wafroghyam
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Yesuene muyaf\u233? \u225?r a efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?m Judia yuwom\u233? n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd nden\u233? T\u233?ndo \u225?r\u233?m nden\u233?yameyo yanangi Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Njam Fit\u233? n\u233?ngwanoy\u233?ng Jerusalem\u233?t, Ju efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?m tanangotaw\u233?t f\u225? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
a norayai, "F\u233?m tang\u233?m T\u233?ndo \u225?rfene m\u233?ngot a y\u233?maf\u233? t\u225?netati njamke."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Fitam tawaufrotau m\u233?inyotio si y\u233?fefaf n\u233?m\u233? k\u233?t\u233? kufrotau k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? ufrogh, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
"Y\u233?nd kw\u233?morw\u233?n ndimbal tesenan Jofan Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oraighan, a y\u233?ndo yinjoy\u233?n gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?gh yam. Y\u233?ndon yinjoy\u233?n \u225?mb rokar ndenanit marat s\u225?l\u225?me k\u233?newonau k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? njafarta fo kw\u233?ndkw\u233?ndaf\u233?, a k\u233?newonau k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?nd \u225?nde kw\u233?morw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?nd n\u233?ngretay\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?t ewinjoy\u233?n fo ghamb\u233?raf\u233? w\u233?r\u225?r, munjan w\u233?r\u225?r, fute aroghagh w\u233?r\u225?r a men. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Y\u233?nd n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?n si kw\u233?mndetau nden\u233?, 'Kokai, Fit\u233?. T\u225?smeta a t\u225?neta.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
"Y\u233?nd nuwangoy\u233?n, 'Yau, Yur\u233?. Nj\u250?nnj\u250?naf\u233? a fenjfenjaf\u233? w\u233?r\u225?r yau n\u233?lawai tane s\u233?nfnet.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
"Ng\u225?nj\u225?n norayai k\u233?tam\u233? njafarta w\u233?ikor, 'Yau. F\u233?mo so enete. Yau noraya nden\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi em n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewafrota mer.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? yam kufrotau nambinotma, a y\u233?n\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me y\u233?namayo nangoi njafarot w\u233?ikor.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
"T\u225?f f\u233?t\u233? nambio \u225?r efe enw\u225?f\u225?retam\u233?ng tafaf k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Kaisaria tesenta n\u233?kmboy\u233?nd m\u233?ngon \u225?nde y\u233?nd kw\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram w\u233?mnday\u233?ng yau naut\u233?mnda \u225?ligh\u233?t y\u233?maf\u233?. Y\u233?n\u233? siks f\u250?tarf\u233? nden\u225?yo n\u233?nuwanoy\u233?m y\u233?ndf\u233?, a y\u233?nd n\u233?nglaway\u233?m Rom fiyar\u233? s\u233?nko \u225?r Koneliasoene m\u233?ngot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Konelias\u233?m y\u233?nmaufroi t\u233?fe ndern\u225?ye y\u233?mon yinjoi njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r yane m\u233?ngon a y\u233?n\u233? njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r norayai, '\u193?r ew\u225?f\u225?reta k\u233?t\u225?n Jofa tesenot Saimonefaf efe yanmotat Fit\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Fitam so f\u233?fe enwarse si \u225?rk\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? f\u233?m a m\u233?inyotio m\u233?r\u233?n so kawanjarngi.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
"Njamandio y\u233?ndon y\u233?rnyay\u233?n si, Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?r y\u233?nmorm\u233?n y\u233?fefaf nden\u233?yameyo ndern\u225?ye y\u233?morm\u233?n t\u233?fefaf frondeyan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
