Y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?mb\u225?ranyo, \u225?mb efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?m engwatembeyay\u233?nd Fol a Sailes Bereya tesenot. Ufarghan Fol a Sailes, f\u225? n\u233?ngwaneyay\u233?nd Ju \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n Bereyam\u233?n Ju \u225?r tamorw\u233?n minde mer \u225?r, y\u233?fene wafroghyamam ewainday\u233?ng Tesalonika yum\u233?n \u225?r, y\u233?mofem yumyoy\u233?nd si \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? a taf\u233?nmetaw\u233?t Buk si t\u250?m\u233?n efghon t\u233?fandaw\u233?t n\u233?m\u233? Fol efalo korayau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
T\u225?rf\u225?r Ju \u225?r\u233?m efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd si a \u225?mb ndimbal y\u233?tkw\u233?n amafam a \u225?mb Grikm\u233?n \u225?r\u233?m.
