Njam Ju \u225?r mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd Tesalonika k\u233?nj\u250?n nden\u233? Fol\u233?m t\u225?itotau Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si Bereyan, \u225?mb \u225?r w\u233?i k\u233?t\u225?n n\u233?ngwanoy\u233?nd a amror\u233?gh y\u233?rnyay\u233?nd \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n tawanjmetaw\u233?t.
