T\u225?f f\u233?t\u233? efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?m Fol y\u225?f\u225?retam\u233?nd arakaf tamb\u233?n, w\u233?nde Sailes\u233?f Timotif\u233? tamorarw\u233?n Bereyan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Njam y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?n\u233?mnjam\u233?nd Fol Aten\u233?t, Fol norayai y\u233?fefaf nden\u233?, "Sailes a Timoti tafaf t\u225?f enre w\u233?keye." F\u233?yo t\u225?f n\u233?ngwanoy\u233?nd.
