Njam Fol kawanjetau y\u233?feyot Sailes a Timoti Aten tesenan, f\u225? \u225?uw\u233?ghofnar t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n yinjoi y\u233?n\u233? tesen mewang afoghare. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?mon \u233?wigh y\u233?rnyai y\u233?maf\u233? Ju \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngon Ju \u225?r a Ng\u225?nj\u225?n f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? T\u233?ndo \u225?r. F\u225? w\u233?i t\u225?f t\u233?ngmorw\u233?n marat sifayat m\u233?inyotio efghon a \u225?r k\u233?t\u233? tamndetau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
M\u233?r\u233?n t\u225?rw\u233?n s\u243?mbio, \u225?mb Efikuria m\u233?r\u233?n a \u225?mb Stoik m\u233?r\u233?n ndimbal matyamaf\u233? \u225?r \u233?wigh y\u233?rnyay\u233?nd Folf\u233?. \u193?mb kamotangi, "N\u233?m\u233? siot y\u233?n\u233? war\u233?war\u233? nufngo?" \u193?mb korayangi, "F\u225? m\u233?t\u233? noraya \u225?mb ng\u225?nj\u225?nm\u233?n." F\u225? korayaw\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? si m\u233?nam\u233?n Fol\u233?m t\u225?itotau mer si Yesuenem\u233?n a y\u225?ne anoghm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?ngwasroy\u233?nd f\u225? s\u233?nko \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh sifay\u233? y\u233?tkw\u233?n Areyofagus, \u225?nde y\u233?mofem f\u225? t\u233?mndetaw\u233?t, "F\u233?yotaro f\u233?mo so t\u233?nmaufro matot n\u233?m\u233? tot\u233?r watamegh f\u233?mo yaitote? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
F\u233?mon t\u233?fe y\u233?n\u233?rse f\u233?nataye watamegh n\u225?y\u225?retam, a y\u233?nd m\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233?m mat s\u225?i k\u225?y\u225?tong\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? y\u225?ne fifi y\u233?m." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
(M\u233?inyotio Atenm\u233?n \u225?r a \u225?mb yuta \u225?r efe tamorang\u233?rw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? efogh tifotaw\u233?t \u225?mnjoghanro w\u233?nde korayaw\u233?t a k\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?t soramam\u233?n siot)
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
F\u233?yo Fol nokayoi s\u233?nko \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh sifay\u233? y\u233?tkw\u233?n Areyofagus a tamndang\u233?, "Atenm\u233?n \u225?r\u451? Y\u233?ndon tawafandan f\u233?mofem ew\u225?wefnotati t\u225?rf\u225?r ng\u225?nj\u225?nafet mindefifi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd njam karendan t\u225?f kor ewawinjon f\u233?fene w\u225?wefnogh rokar. Y\u233?ndon tawafandan kitar\u233?kitar\u233? y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?tkw\u233?naf\u233?: K\u233?t\u225?n Mat Y\u225?toghofnar Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. F\u233?m mat yau em n\u233?mayoe f\u233?mofem y\u225?wefnotati, s\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndon so ewaufrotan f\u233?feyot y\u225?nem\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
"Ng\u225?nj\u225?n emo yafrotam mband marat a m\u233?inyotio rokar y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?n. M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mo elimnde m\u233?inyotio rokar njafaran a mbandan, f\u225? yau y\u233?mor \u225?r ng\u225?ng\u233? ram\u233?ghm\u233?n w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
A f\u225? yau n\u225?ronje y\u233?n\u233? rokarot \u225?r\u233?m \u225?rk\u233? ewafrotat y\u225?yot, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? f\u225?yo m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfene gh\u233?rs\u233? ram\u233?gh \u225?r y\u233?m a m\u233?inyotio rokar k\u233?s. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
R\u233?ny\u233?ghan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yafrotam \u225?mbiro \u225?r, Y\u225? tamb\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewafrotam m\u233?inyotio \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n efe s\u233?nonjo emorang m\u233?inyotio mband maratan. A y\u233?mon w\u233?i mwigh\u233? y\u233?faronam \u225?nde f\u233?natayero \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n so emor a nder\u233? teke f\u225? so emor. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?n m\u233?nde y\u233?m \u225?r\u233?m s\u225?i y\u233?ronjat. M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? yau nayu y\u233?m t\u233?feta, f\u233?yo y\u233?mofem m\u233?t\u233? t\u225?f y\u233?ronjat f\u225? a tinjongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
'M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?ne waftayan y\u233?nd gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?nmor a nimndam a naketam.' Ndenanit f\u233?fenjo \u225?r efe mat em f\u233?r\u233?nafene fifi, f\u225? norayat ndenanit, 'Y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?m y\u225?ne ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
"M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ambumt\u233?rt\u233?r k\u233?s y\u233?n\u233?m, y\u233?nd yau so nemnam nden\u233? \u225?r\u233?m so ewafrotat Ng\u225?nj\u225?n k\u233?tam\u233? gol o silf\u233? o w\u237?m y\u233?fenjo matyame. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
T\u225?nd\u225?i \u225?r njam yau mat tamorw\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u233?fefaf wafrogh\u233?t, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yau k\u233?rtayan t\u225?kmangai m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?fene matyam yau, w\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam emndete m\u233?inyotio \u225?r m\u233?inyotio yuwom\u233? yaufita awengogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Efogh t\u233? yafery\u233?ng njam mband so moghan t\u233?kmang\u233?. Y\u233?mo t\u233? y\u233?kafai \u225?r emo so moghan t\u233?n\u233?kmang\u233? mbark\u225?nde. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? yuyafoi y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r, efe Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? y\u233?kafai m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i emota mband marat, y\u233?mo so moghan t\u233?kmang\u233? mband marat m\u233?nam\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yanoi k\u233?rta."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Njam f\u225? n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd \u225?roene k\u233?r anoghm\u233?n si, \u225?mb \u225?r\u233?m turtaw\u233?t, w\u233?nde \u225?mb korayaw\u233?t, "Y\u233?nd m\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233?m f\u233?m s\u225?i kor koraya t\u233?fefaf y\u233?n\u233? si t\u233?f\u233?n." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?umeng\u233?gh soram\u233? Fol\u233?m efrangoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r namnday\u233?nd Folene waitogh \u225?r a efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd. Y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n tafnyang\u233?rw\u233?n Dionisus, efe t\u233?morw\u233?n Areyofagus m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n, nden\u225?yo amaf y\u233?tkw\u233?n Damaris, a \u225?mb \u225?r k\u233?s.
