Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233?, Fol\u233?m y\u233?frangoi Aten tesen a n\u233?ngwanoi Korint tesenot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
K\u233?t\u233? y\u233?mon y\u233?f\u225?ngoi Ju \u225?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Akwila Fontusm\u233?n. F\u225? y\u233?nmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Italia y\u225?njo amafaf\u233? y\u233?tkw\u233?n Frisila, m\u233?nam\u233?n Rom tuk warsagh \u225?r Kaisar Klaudias\u233?m emndai "F\u233?m Ju \u225?r, f\u233?mofem so t\u233?frangongi Rom." Fol n\u233?ngaflai Akwila a Frisila fandagh\u233?t, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
a m\u233?nam\u233?n Fol t\u233?morw\u233?n farai m\u233?ngo ram\u233?gh \u225?r nden\u233? f\u225? k\u233?s tamorw\u233?n, Fol n\u225?mnjoy\u233?ng a k\u225?s\u225?fotaw\u233?t y\u233?maf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
M\u233?inyotio Safatan Folfem taruindaw\u233?t Ju \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngon, m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tik\u233?f \u225?frat t\u225?y\u225?tongay\u233?nd Ju \u225?r a T\u233?ndo \u225?r.
