Njam Sailes a Timoti nufareyay\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Makedoniata, y\u233?na Fol\u233?m y\u233?ta Ju \u225?r matot tarametau nden\u233? Yesu siy\u233?m Keriso. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
W\u233?nde Ju \u225?r\u233?m t\u233?karotaw\u233?t Fol a yaufi si t\u233?mndetaw\u233?t. F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?mon ngw\u233?rm\u233?ng y\u233?tnendai y\u225?njo s\u225?l\u225?meta a tamndang\u233? f\u225?, "Njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233?kratan t\u225?kmang\u233?, so y\u233?m f\u233?fenjo t\u233?fnan, yau so y\u233?m tane t\u233?f\u233?n. Y\u233?nd nawafenan f\u233?fefaf y\u233?nd yau k\u233?rt\u233? so w\u233?m. Y\u233?nandm\u233? y\u233?nd so kuwanon s\u233?nonjo T\u233?ndo \u225?rfefaf."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo Fol\u233?m y\u233?ng\u233?frangoi Ju \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngo a n\u233?ngaflai kaka m\u233?ngot, Taitus J\u233?stusene m\u233?ngot efe t\u233?morw\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n w\u225?wefnogh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Krisfus, Ju \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngo lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r, a y\u225?njo m\u233?rnam Yur\u233? efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd a t\u225?rf\u225?r Korintm\u233?n \u225?r efe k\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?t, efalo yiy\u225?toy\u233?nd a nuwan ewalitotam.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
\u193?mb s\u233?mb\u225?ran Yur\u233? norayai Folefaf gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?n, "Yau f\u233?rf\u233?r n\u233?m, sian miya n\u233?ng\u233?m, yau m\u233?tar n\u233?m a n\u233?kmbo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd f\u233?maf\u233? y\u233?nre, a emo yau so n\u233?kmbote a n\u233?mas\u233?rmbote f\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?n tane t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r em y\u233?n\u233? tesenan." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan Fol y\u233?morang\u233?rm\u233?n Korint\u233?n \u225?mbiro yunj\u233?f \u225?mb yunj\u233?f r\u233?r y\u233?ramai f\u225? tawatametau Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene si.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Njam Galio t\u233?morw\u233?n gafana Akaya ndimbal yum\u233?n, \u225?mb Ju \u225?r nafghay\u233?nd Fole k\u233?kmbogh\u233?t a y\u233?nmasroy\u233?nd mogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?mofem y\u233?mnday\u233?nd, "Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rom elimnde \u225?r Ng\u225?nj\u225?n w\u225?wefnogh\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? ende t\u233?fene n\u225?k er\u225?fne."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Fol siotro t\u233?morw\u233?n, Galio norayai Ju \u225?rfefaf, "F\u233?m Ju \u225?r njam nawatarnati y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?rtam\u233?n tayot mer n\u233?rete, f\u233?m so ey\u225?retan sian. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?na ewafnyang \u225?mogh m\u233?nam\u233?n orayaghm\u233?n a y\u233?tkw\u233?nm\u233?n a f\u233?fenjo n\u225?km\u233?n, t\u225?frendangi y\u233?n\u233? yam f\u233?mofemyo. Y\u233?nd yau so y\u233?na w\u233?m f\u233?fene moghan y\u233?n\u233? yamm\u233?n." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mon eng\u233?utory\u233?ng moghta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
F\u233?yo m\u233?inyotioyam yeray\u233?nd Sostenes Ju \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngo lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?roefaf ngi yafngoi mogh m\u233?ngo saf\u233?n. W\u233?nde Galiom yau kemnau y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n.
