Fol y\u233?morang\u233?rm\u233?n Korint\u233?n t\u225?rf\u225?r efogh. F\u233?yo y\u233?mon eng\u233?frangoi f\u250?tar\u233?f k\u233?t\u233?, a nuwanoy\u233?nd y\u233?maf\u233? Frisila a y\u225?njar Akwila. F\u225? n\u233?ngwanoy\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n Sens\u233?ri. K\u233?t\u233? Fol s\u233?f nat\u233?rtam m\u233?nam\u233?n yane uny\u233?ghofnar sim\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf. F\u225? ndimbal boute n\u233?nguwanoy\u233?nd Siria yuwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
F\u225? n\u233?kmboy\u233?nd Efesos tesenan, Fol\u233?m efrangeyai Frisila a Akwila. F\u225? yambia n\u233?ngwanoi Ju \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngot a tarundaw\u233?t Ju \u225?rf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Njam y\u233?mofem yaunenday\u233?nd \u225?mb efogh \u225?mnjogh\u233?t y\u233?maf\u233?, y\u233?mon y\u233?kenai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
W\u233?nde njam Fol\u233?m eng\u233?frangoi, y\u233?mon uny\u233?ghofnar si emndai, "Y\u233?nd so k\u233?nangon Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?ndeyan." F\u233?yo y\u233?mon y\u233?frangoi Efesos a m\u233? tanmorw\u233?n Kaisariat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Njam f\u225? nufary\u233?ng Kaisaria yuwot, f\u225? n\u233?ngwanoi Jerusalem\u233?t a \u225?uw\u233?gh si ewaramai Yesuene m\u233?rnat, a n\u233?ngangoi k\u233?t\u225?n Antiok yuwot.
