Y\u233?mon si yafngoi f\u233?rf\u233?rofnaye Ju \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n. Njam Frisila a Akwilafem yiy\u225?reyay\u233?nd f\u225?, y\u233?mofem yumyeyay\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?fenjo m\u233?ngot a tawaferw\u233?t Afolose mbark\u225?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene end.
