\u193?mb Ju \u225?r nuwanoy\u233?nd y\u233?ta yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?r tawifnaw\u233?t Yur\u233? Yesuene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan f\u225? efe yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram tawas\u233?rmbotau. \u193?mb \u225?r\u233?m norayai, "Yesuene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, endenem\u233?n Fol\u233?m yaitote, y\u233?ndo n\u233?mndetan, 'K\u233?ntor.'" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Jum\u233?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r Skefane sefen ambumam y\u233?n\u233? \u225?s\u225?fogh tafrotaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
\u193?mb efghon yaufi mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram ewawangoi y\u233?fe, "Y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m Yesu a y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m Folenem\u233?n, w\u233?nde f\u233?m efe em?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
