F\u233?yo y\u233?mon ew\u225?f\u225?rem\u233?ng y\u225?ne s\u243?mbio w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh \u225?r, Timoti a Erastus, k\u233?t\u225?n Makedoniat, w\u233?nde f\u225? m\u233? t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n Esian.
