K\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Demetrios, emo tawafrotau silf\u233? w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo Artemis mewangoe. F\u225? efe k\u225?s\u225?fotaw\u233?t y\u233?mofem tawinjotaw\u233?t t\u225?rf\u225?r mani. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
