F\u233?mofem t\u233? yinjongi a y\u225?yamngongi ndern\u225?ye Fol\u233?m \u225?frat y\u233?ny\u225?tote a \u225?mb watameghe t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r elimnde Efesos tesenan a m\u233?inyotio Esia yuwom\u233?. Y\u233?mon noraye nden\u233? \u225?r wafroghm\u233?n ng\u225?nj\u225?n yau em ng\u225?nj\u225?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? yam siy\u233?m \u225?uw\u233?ghofnar y\u233?m m\u233?nam\u233?n t\u233?fene mani winjogh end so kefong\u233?. Nden\u233?yameyo ndimbal amaf ng\u225?nj\u225?n Atemisene w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo so kamndang\u233? fifiofnar, endeyot t\u225?wefnotat Esia a mband maratan. \u193?r\u233?m yau so nemnat nden\u233? amaf ng\u225?nj\u225?n Atemis siy\u233?m ng\u225?nj\u225?n."
