\u193?r m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?w\u233?rsotaw\u233?t m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?natayero ke kutnaw\u233?t. T\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r yau mat tamorw\u233?n n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u225? k\u233?t\u233? tamorw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Ju \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?ngw\u225?f\u225?retay\u233?nd Aleksenda y\u233?fefaf siot. Y\u233?mon \u225?r\u233?t ng\u225?ngaye ewaunyai m\u233?tar ekmbogh\u233?t. F\u225? m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tamndangai f\u225? nden\u233? Ju \u225?r yau k\u233?rt\u233? y\u233?funay\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
W\u233?nde njam y\u233?mofem y\u225?y\u225?mngoy\u233?nd nde f\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n Ju \u225?r, f\u225? kutnaw\u233?t s\u243?mbio efoghf\u233?nef\u233?ne nden\u233? keyaf\u233?, "Ndimbal y\u233?m Atemis Efesosm\u233?n\u451?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Tesenm\u233?n gafanane \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rom ekmboi a norayai, "Efesosm\u233?n \u225?r, f\u233?m mat em nden\u233? Efesos tesen siy\u233?m wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r ndimbal amaf ng\u225?nj\u225?n Artamisene w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo a y\u233?n\u233? amafoene s\u225?f mbanmban \u225?rk\u233? n\u233?newory\u233?ng njafarta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
Efe yau so korayang\u233? f\u225? yau n\u233?nui njafarta. F\u233?m m\u233?tar. N\u233?m\u233? yau yafrotati namname. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
F\u233?mofem y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r t\u225?n\u233?mnjati y\u233?nan, y\u233?mofem yau yaufi si korayat t\u233?fene ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf a yau n\u233?mndafi oroe tarsat t\u233?fene ng\u225?nj\u225?nene w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngota. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
F\u233?yo njam Demetrios a y\u225?ne \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rf\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? ewam, mogh siy\u233?m saur\u233?ghkaf y\u233?m a y\u233?na em mogh \u225?r. F\u233?yotaro f\u225? so norayat y\u233?n\u233? yamm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
Njam k\u233?rt\u233? m\u233? em, so tanwanangi k\u233?t\u225?n moghfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
A f\u233?yo mat ay\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?n\u233?, nden\u233? njam s\u233?nko \u225?r k\u225?y\u225?rangi n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndfem tafrotam s\u233?nonjo, y\u233?mofem m\u233?t\u233? y\u233?n\u233?mndetat ndimbal k\u233?rt\u233? funaghm\u233?n. Y\u233?ndfem y\u233?n\u233? tafrotam fifiofnar, f\u233?yo n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?nd so norayam njam y\u233?nd y\u233?nmotat y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? si soram\u233?, y\u233?mon \u225?r ew\u225?f\u225?rnay\u233?ng.
