Njam tesenan sarake nefoi, Fol n\u233?ngwanoi k\u233?t\u225?n waitogh \u225?rfefaf, a tawaw\u233?ngsotau y\u233?fe. F\u233?yo f\u225? emnday\u233?ng "Yao" a t\u225?f n\u233?wanoi Makedonia yuwot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
F\u225? ngrendau y\u233?n\u233? yuwom\u233?, ngorayau t\u225?rf\u225?r waw\u233?ngsogh si \u225?rfefaf soram\u233? Fol n\u233?ngufary\u233?ng Grik yuwot, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
k\u233?t\u233? f\u225? y\u233?morang\u233?rm\u233?n nambio gh\u233?rare. F\u233?yo mwigh\u233? yaitotam Siria yuwot angogh\u233?t ndimbal boute, w\u233?nde f\u225? n\u225?y\u225?rai nden\u233? \u225?mb Ju \u225?r\u233?m y\u225? ngiot mwigh\u233? t\u225?itotaw\u233?t. F\u233?yo y\u233?mon mwigh\u233? yaitotam tunam\u233? angogh\u233?t Makedoniam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Sofata Firusene ambum k\u233?t\u225?ndmam\u233?n Bereya yum\u233?n, Aristakus a Sekundus k\u233?t\u225?ndmam\u233?n Tesalonika yum\u233?n, Gaius k\u233?t\u225?ndmam\u233?n Derbe yum\u233?n, Timoti nden\u233?yameyo, Tukikus a Trofimus k\u233?t\u225?ndmam\u233?n Esia marat yum\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233? Folf\u233? tayotau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r engmorm\u233?n frondeyo t\u233?nmanjetaw\u233?t y\u233?nd Troas tesenan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?nd ndimbal boute t\u233?nngmorw\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? Filifi tesenta Minaghofnar flaw\u233? t\u233?m\u233?nd soram\u233?. \u193?mb 5 efogh soram\u233? y\u233?nd nufnyay\u233?m k\u233?t\u233? Troas tesenan, \u225?nde y\u233?nd y\u233?morang\u233?rm\u233?n sefen efogh.
