Sande efghon y\u233?nd y\u233?nngmorm\u233?n m\u233?rne m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? n\u233?net. Fol\u233?m korayau \u225?rfefaf a sian m\u233? t\u233?ngmorw\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?notio s\u233?mb\u225?r n\u233?ndk\u233?f, m\u233?nam\u233?n \u225?mb efghon \u225?ligh\u233?t karametaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n k\u233?t\u233? k\u225?netaw\u233?t t\u225?rf\u225?r kwayagh\u233? \u225?nde y\u233?nd k\u225?umendaw\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
K\u233?t\u233? \u225?mb tot\u233?r \u225?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Yutikus t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n mbormbor s\u233?safneyan, njamandio Fol m\u233? korayau teke, Yutikus k\u233?m\u233?gham t\u233?rametau. Kerkeran, f\u225? k\u233?m\u233?gh nakmai nambio kitar\u233? satayan k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? n\u233?nuyai mbandot. Y\u233?mofem y\u233?kafay\u233?nd k\u233?rw\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Fol n\u233?ngewory\u233?ng yuwot, n\u233?ng\u225?wefnoi ng\u225?ng\u233? efayoi y\u225?faf. F\u233?yo Fol\u233?m tamndang\u233?, "Yau m\u225?m\u233? mwigh\u233? em, f\u225? m\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? y\u233?m\u451?" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
F\u233?yo Fol w\u233?ikor n\u233?ngarmboi tuk\u233?t, a t\u233?netau f\u233?skaf flaw\u233?. Fol m\u233? korayau k\u233?t\u225?notio akw y\u233?faw\u233?ry\u233?ng soram\u233? y\u233?mo efrangoi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
\u193?r\u233?m tot\u233?r \u225?r y\u233?ngwanay\u233?nd m\u233?ngot a y\u233?feyot ndimbal \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n k\u233?rta nanoi.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Folf\u233? naf\u225?ngoy\u233?nd Efesos s\u233?nko \u225?rf\u233?
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Fol t\u233? norayai nden\u233? y\u233?mo so t\u233?nf\u225?ngongai k\u233?t\u233? Asos\u233?n, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? tiyotau \u225?lighe. F\u233?yo fronde y\u233?nd n\u233?nguwanoy\u233?m Boutfaf a ng\u233?rsaw\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n Asos tesenot. K\u233?t\u233? y\u233?nd m\u233?nde t\u233?nmorm\u233?n s\u225?i t\u233?f\u225?ngongay\u233?m f\u225? a t\u233?ngwanangay\u233?m bout. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Njam y\u233?mon y\u233?nf\u225?ngoy\u233?ng Asos\u233?n, y\u233?ndfem f\u225? y\u233?ngwaflay\u233?m a n\u233?ngwanoy\u233?m Mitilan tesenot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
\u193?mb efghon y\u233?ndfem y\u233?frangoy\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? a n\u233?ngwanoy\u233?m ndimbal boute k\u233?t\u225?n Kios tesenot. Y\u233?n\u233? efogh soram\u233? w\u233?i n\u233?ngurtoy\u233?m Samos tesenot, s\u243?mbio efogh soram\u233? n\u233?ngufary\u233?m Miletus tesenot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Fol yau m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i t\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n Esia marat yuwon, f\u233?yo mwigh\u233? y\u233?faronam yau so k\u233?kmbongai Efesos\u233?n. M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n w\u233?keye ufargh\u233?t Jerusalem\u233?t wafarogh t\u233?m\u233?nd y\u233?tkw\u233?n Fentikost
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
K\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Miletus tesenta, Fol\u233?m si yatembai k\u233?t\u225?n Efesos yum\u233?n Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n s\u233?nko \u225?r\u233?t \u225?ligh\u233?t y\u233?maf\u233? siot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Njam s\u233?nko \u225?r nufary\u233?nd, Fol norayai y\u233?fefaf, "F\u233?m mat em ndern\u225?ye y\u233?nd k\u225?s\u225?fotan f\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?n k\u233?t\u225?ndmayo frondefifi efghon y\u233?nd njam nufary\u233?n Esia marat yuwon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?nd k\u225?s\u225?fotan ndimbal yuwan mwighaye a yengamaf\u233?. Y\u233?nd t\u233?kr\u225?tan kawamarotan m\u233?nam\u233?n Ju \u225?r\u233?m ngiot kw\u233?rametaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
F\u233?m mat em nden\u233? y\u233?nd yau f\u233?rf\u233?r kw\u233?m si waitogh\u233?t \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? f\u233?fe w\u225?ut\u225?rghaf\u233? t\u233?m w\u233?nde tawatametaw\u233?n f\u233?m marataye m\u233?inyotio m\u233?ngom\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Y\u233?ndon t\u225?itotaw\u233?n si y\u233?fe Ju \u225?r a Grikm\u233?n \u225?r\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? so nawengotat yaufita Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf a efalo so yiy\u225?totat t\u233?fene Yur\u233? Yesu.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
"S\u233?nonjo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?roene sian, y\u233?nd so kuwanon Jerusalem\u233?t, mat yau w\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? yam so nufrote k\u233?t\u233? tafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?nd y\u233?naro mat w\u233?m m\u233?inyotio tesenan Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram waufrote nden\u233? Jerusalem\u233?n \u225?r\u233?m so kw\u233?nyawangi y\u233?nd kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngon a y\u233?nd so t\u233?kratan kw\u233?kmangi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
W\u233?nde tane fifie gh\u233?rs\u233? siy\u233?m fifiofnar y\u233?m, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? fifiyaf\u233? tafaf y\u233?m: nden\u233? y\u233?ndo so tifon w\u233?rse Yur\u233? Yesum \u225?rk\u233? waramai, mer si waitogh \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene ng\u225?r\u225?mm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
"Y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m f\u233?fefafm\u233? t\u233? karendan Ng\u225?nj\u225?n lim\u225?n\u233?ghm\u233?n si t\u225?itotan. W\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m nden\u233? f\u233?mofem yau so w\u233?ikor kwinjongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd sotaf\u233? si norayan. Njam f\u233?m \u225?mb k\u233?r n\u233?m Yesu efalo y\u225?toghofnar, f\u233?mofem yau so kw\u233?fayongi y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Y\u233?nd yau f\u233?rf\u233?r kw\u233?m m\u233?inyotio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene m\u233?nde waitogh\u233?t f\u233?fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?m kor nawarawenati f\u233?myo a m\u233?inyotio Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n \u225?rk\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n Mb\u233?rmb\u233?ram t\u233? ewafery\u233?ng \u225?r wanjeng\u233?t. Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene Yesuene m\u233?r\u233?n wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r aem, y\u233?mon y\u225?njo f\u233?rke t\u233? y\u233?nmanai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Y\u233?nd nden\u233? mat w\u233?m, y\u233?nd njam kuwanon munjan \u225?gh\u233? so kufarngi f\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?nyo a yau so ewarawenat w\u233?nde so esmetat krot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?fenjo m\u233?r\u233?n k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?n \u225?r so k\u233?nokayongi a elimndat efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t so ewaitotat y\u233?fene uny\u233?gh watamegh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Aya kor f\u233?m nawarawenati\u451? T\u233? nawafarotati nden\u233? nambio yunj\u233?f y\u233?ndon tawaw\u233?ngsotaw\u233?n ekmboghofnar f\u233?m \u225?mbiro\u225?mbiroe yengamaf\u233? m\u233?inyotio efogh a s\u233?mb\u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n s\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndon ewatetan f\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf a k\u233?t\u225?n ng\u225?r\u225?m sifaf, \u225?rk\u233? siam f\u233?m so ewanote a efrende m\u233?inyotio efe t\u233? efaloi yandio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Y\u233?ndon yau f\u233?fene s\u225?l\u225?me o mani mwighaye takwnan tayot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
F\u233?m m\u233?inyo mat em nden\u233? y\u233?nd tanjo ng\u225?ngaye k\u225?s\u225?fotaw\u233?n tanjo s\u225?l\u225?met a maniot a nden\u233?yameyo tane f\u250?tarat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? ende y\u233?ndo t\u233? tawauyafotan ndern\u225?ye f\u233?m so emor. F\u233?m so n\u225?s\u225?fotati t\u225?ikrataye m\u233?n\u225?t yauyau \u225?r so ew\u225?ut\u225?nati, so nawafarotam Yur\u233? Yesuene si f\u225? \u225?rk\u233? korayau: 'Ram\u233?gh \u225?roene \u225?uw\u233?gham y\u225?inde y\u225?ne \u225?uw\u233?gh emo rokar tanang\u233?.'"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
