Fol\u233?m yawangoi, "Yau, y\u233?nd yau! y\u233?nd sw\u233?m Ju \u225?r, k\u233?t\u233? n\u225?r\u225?ftam\u233?n Tarsus tesenan, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m mer marataye matkaf tesen Silisia k\u233?nj\u250?n. F\u233?yotaro y\u233?nd so kwumyo y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rfefaf siot."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Fiyar\u233? ndimbal s\u233?nko \u225?rom yumyoi siyot, Fol nokayoi ratayan a ekmboi \u225?r. F\u225? njam m\u233?tar n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd, f\u225? korayang\u233? y\u233?fefaf Ibru sie.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 22
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
"F\u250?tar\u233?f a afaf, k\u233?n\u225?y\u225?rangi tane awamarogh sifaf."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Njam y\u233?mofem yiy\u225?ray\u233?nd Fol korayau Ibru sie, f\u225? m\u233?tar namnday\u233?nd.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 F\u233?yo Fol\u233?m korayang\u233?, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
"Y\u233?nd sw\u233?m Ju \u225?r, n\u225?r\u225?ftam\u233?n Tarsus tesenan Silisia yuwon, w\u233?nde nanotam\u233?n Jerusalem\u233?n. W\u233?morm\u233?n watametam\u233?nd afafene n\u225?ke a Gamaliel siy\u233?m tane watamegh \u225?r. Y\u233?nd m\u233?nde kw\u233?morw\u233?n s\u225?i tiy\u225?retaw\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n merk\u233?r\u225?ye nden\u233? m\u233?inyotio f\u233?mofem sewafrotati s\u233?nonjo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?ndon t\u225?smetaw\u233?n \u225?r k\u233?rotio efe kuwaitotaw\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? End\u233?n, taweretaw\u233?n \u225?r a amaf a tangwitaw\u233?n kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh s\u233?nko t\u233?fn\u225?r a m\u233?inyotio Ju s\u233?nko \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?ram so nafrotat y\u233?n\u233? sim\u233?n efalo y\u233?m. Y\u233?mofem kwaramangay\u233?nd f\u233?r\u233?n Ju \u225?rfefaf Damaskos k\u233?nj\u250?n. F\u233?yo y\u233?nd kw\u233?ngmorw\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r t\u225?n\u233?mnjaw\u233?n nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngo \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?n Jerusalem\u233?t k\u233?rtayan k\u233?mgh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
"\u193?mb efogh sotan, njam kaka y\u233?ngy\u225?toy\u233?n Damaskos, s\u233?lngw\u233?le njafarm\u233?n ndimbal kwayaghayam w\u233?l\u225?l\u225?i y\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Y\u233?nd nuy\u225?y\u233?n mbandot a n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?n k\u233?m a norayai tafaf nden\u233?, 'Sol\u451? Sol\u451? F\u233?mo n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?nd w\u233?smete?'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
"Y\u233?nd namotay\u233?n, 'F\u233?m efe n\u233?m, Yur\u233??'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Y\u233?mon ta wawangoi, 'Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Yesu Najaretm\u233?n. F\u233?mo w\u233?smete.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Tane m\u233?rnam yinjoy\u233?nd kwayagh\u233?, w\u233?nde y\u233?mofem yau y\u225?y\u225?mngoy\u233?nd y\u225?ne k\u233?m efe korayau tafaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
"Y\u233?ndon y\u233?motay\u233?n, 'N\u233?m\u233? so y\u233?ndon yafrotan, Yur\u233??'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Yuram kw\u233?mndetau, 'Kokai, kuwano k\u233?t\u225?n Damaskos\u233?t. K\u233?t\u233? \u225?r\u233?m so k\u233?maufrong\u233? m\u233?inyotio fene \u225?s\u225?fogh n\u233?m\u233? so y\u233?m.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Tane m\u233?rnam kw\u233?mnjaw\u233?t Damaskos k\u233?nj\u250?t, m\u233?nam\u233?n ndimbal kwayaghayam gh\u233?k\u233?f kw\u233?fkw\u233?f wiy\u225?toi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
"\u193?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Ananias y\u233?nmorm\u233?n ta fandagh\u233?t. F\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n w\u225?wefnogh \u225?r a ndimbal k\u233?r\u225?ye tut\u233?mndaw\u233?t Ju \u225?r\u233?m efe m\u233?inyotio k\u233?t\u233? tamorang\u233?rw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u225? nokayoi ta kaka korayang\u233?, 'F\u250?tar Sol, k\u233?reta\u451?' T\u225?f f\u233?t\u233? n\u233?retay\u233?n yinjoy\u233?n Ananias.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
"F\u233?yo Ananias norayai, 'T\u233?fene \u225?kifene Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam n\u233?mafer f\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t y\u225?ne mwigh\u233? mat f\u233?m so n\u233?m a m\u233?n\u225?t so tinjo mbark\u225?nd \u225?r a n\u225?y\u225?reta si y\u225?ne mb\u237?rmb\u237?rta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?m so n\u233?m y\u225?ne fandagh \u225?r m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfefaf n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? t\u233?fandau a k\u225?y\u225?retau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
S\u233?nonjo n\u233?mat f\u233?m nawanjete? Kokai, so n\u233?m\u225?litotat a Ng\u225?nj\u225?n so tawalindang\u233? fene yaufi t\u225?f njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oraighan n\u233?m Kerisoene y\u233?tkw\u233?nan.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? y\u233?nd n\u233?ngangoy\u233?n Jerusalem\u233?t a Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? koraiw\u233?m w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon. Y\u233?ndon yinjoy\u233?n gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?gh yam {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
a Yuram kw\u233?mndetau, 'W\u233?keye kuwano Jerusalem t\u233?frango m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mofem yau so tumyongi fene afrogh si tanem\u233?n.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
"Y\u233?ndon yawangoy\u233?n, 'Yur\u233?, y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r mat em tanem\u233?n nden\u233? y\u233?nd kwiotau t\u225?rf\u225?r Ju \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngom\u233?. Y\u233?ndon taweretaw\u233?n kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngot \u233?laugh\u233?t a t\u225?smetaw\u233?n \u225?r emofem efalo k\u233?ny\u225?totaw\u233?t f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Njam \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?smetam\u233?nd Stifen m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? korayau \u225?rfefaf fenem\u233?n, y\u233?nd k\u233?t\u233? kwakayong\u233?rw\u233?n a \u225?mbiro tik\u233?fan t\u233?nmorw\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233?. Y\u233?ndo tawanjetaw\u233?n y\u233?fene s\u225?l\u225?me emofem t\u233?smetaw\u233?t k\u233?rot Stifen.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
"F\u233?yo Yur\u233? norayai tafaf, 'Kuwano, y\u233?ndon so n\u233?m\u225?f\u225?retan f\u233?m nayu yuwot k\u233?t\u225?n T\u233?ndo \u225?rfefaf.'"
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fol naufary\u233?ng y\u233?nd sw\u233?m Romm\u233?n \u225?r
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
\u193?r m\u233?rnam kor merk\u233?r\u225?ye k\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?t Folefaf k\u233?t\u225?notio njam f\u225? norayai t\u233?ndo \u225?rfenem\u233?n. Y\u233?mofem k\u233?m euyoy\u233?nd n\u233?kwan a kutnaw\u233?t, "Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r tit\u233?rmbongi y\u233?n\u233? yuta\u451? F\u225? yau f\u233?yotaro y\u233?m m\u233? gh\u233?rs\u233? s\u225?i y\u233?m\u451?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u225? ke kutnaw\u233?t a tafnendaw\u233?t y\u233?fenjo s\u225?l\u225?me a ngw\u233?rm\u233?ng t\u233?tnendaw\u233?t tuk\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Fiyar\u233? ndimbal s\u233?nko \u225?r\u233?m y\u225?njo \u225?r ew\u225?f\u225?retai Fole wasrogh\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?n fiyarafene sifayat. Y\u233?mon emndai y\u225?njo \u225?r Fole ngiot. Y\u233?n\u233? ende f\u225? m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u225?ne \u225?r\u233?m so tinjongay\u233?nd n\u233?mam\u233?n \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n kutnaw\u233?t Folefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Njam fiyaram ngiot yafngoy\u233?nd, y\u233?mon y\u233?mndai fiyar\u233? s\u233?nko \u225?r, "Yufi y\u233?m Romm\u233?n \u225?r ngiot endene yaufi yau yinjongi!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Njam fiyar\u233? s\u233?nko \u225?r n\u225?y\u225?rai y\u233?n\u233? si, f\u225? naflai k\u233?t\u225?n fiyar\u233? ndimbal s\u233?nko \u225?roefaf a y\u233?mndai, "Yau yafrota y\u233?n\u233? yam y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rofefaf. Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r siy\u233?m Romm\u233?n \u225?r."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Fiyar\u233? ndimbal s\u233?nko \u225?r n\u233?ngaflai Folefaf a y\u233?motai, "Kwaufro ta, f\u233?m f\u233?t\u233? n\u233?m Romm\u233?n \u225?r?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fol\u233?m yawangoi, "A, y\u233?nd f\u233?t\u233? w\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?yo fiyar\u233? ndimbal s\u233?nko \u225?r norayai, "Y\u233?ndo ndimbal mani t\u233? ekman so kamndang\u233? Romm\u233?n \u225?r."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fol\u233?m yawangoi, "W\u233?nde y\u233?nd n\u225?r\u225?ftam\u233?n Romm\u233?n \u225?rot."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Fiyar\u233? efe ngiot a \u225?mogh\u233?tro femorm\u233?n Folefaf, t\u225?f f\u233?t\u233? yau yafrotam\u233?nd. Fiyar\u233? ndimbal s\u233?nko \u225?r f\u233?rf\u233?ram yifoi, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?mon emndai y\u225?njo \u225?r Fole umbgh\u233?t, w\u233?nde Fol t\u233?morw\u233?n Romm\u233?n \u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fol yakai Ju s\u233?nko \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh s\u225?fr\u233?re
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
\u193?mb efghon, fiyar\u233? ndimbal s\u233?nko \u225?rom t\u233?ronjau t\u233?f\u233?n n\u233?mam\u233?n Fol t\u233?karotaw\u233?t Ju \u225?r\u233?m. F\u233?yo \u225?mb efghon fiyar\u233? ndimbal s\u233?nko \u225?rom Folene sein yafery\u233?ng. F\u225? w\u233?i emndai lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r a m\u233?inyotio Ju s\u233?nko \u225?r \u225?umeng\u233?gh\u233?t. Y\u233?mon y\u233?ng\u233?mnjoi Fol a Ju s\u233?nko \u225?rfene s\u225?fr\u233?re nokayoi. {\cs259\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 |CN02020B.tif|col||\u169? 1996 David C Cook. Used by permission.|Fol\u233?f korayaw\u233?t Ju \u225?rfene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?rf\u233? (Acts 22.30)|23.30}

\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 23
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Fol n\u233?ngretai mbark\u225?nde k\u233?t\u225?n Ju s\u233?nko \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?ghfaf a norayai, "Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, y\u233?ndon tafrotan tanjo \u225?s\u225?fogh Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne s\u233?nonjo m\u233?inyotio mer mwighaye." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
F\u233?yo Ananias lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?rom ew\u225?f\u225?retai \u225?r efe kaka tawakayong\u233?rw\u233?n Folefaf mb\u237?rmb\u237?ran ngiot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?yo Fol norayai y\u225?faf, "Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so k\u233?ntarmang\u233?, f\u233?m farun n\u233?rete mer w\u233?nde k\u233?nj\u250?n yau! F\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?n\u225?mnjo ta mogh\u233?t Mosesene n\u225?kaf\u233?, w\u233?nde f\u233?mon y\u233?r\u225?fne n\u225?k y\u233?naye y\u233?nd sw\u233?smetati."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Efe tawakayong\u233?rw\u233?n Fole kaka norayay\u233?nd, "F\u233?mon yasalite Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Fol\u233?m ewawangoi, "F\u250?tar\u233?f, y\u233?nd yau mat kw\u233?morw\u233?n nden\u233? f\u225? siy\u233?m lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r. M\u233?nam\u233?n si nden\u233? y\u233?kai, 'Yaufi si yau norayati f\u233?fenjo lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?roefaf.'"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Fol mat n\u225?y\u225?toi nden\u233? \u225?mb \u225?r tamorw\u233?n Saduki \u225?r a \u225?mb Farasi \u225?r, f\u225? n\u233?ngutnay\u233?ng \u225?r m\u233?rnafefaf, "Tane f\u250?tar\u233?f, y\u233?nd sw\u233?m Farasi \u225?r, Farasi \u225?rfene ambum. Y\u233?nd wakayong ufogham\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n tane m\u233?ghm\u233?gh k\u233?rta anoghm\u233?n."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
