"W\u233?nde \u225?mb si kafe n\u233?m\u233? f\u225? norayat siy\u233?m efalo, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?ndon y\u225?wefnotan tane \u225?kifene Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? End waitogh \u225?r. F\u225? norayat y\u233?mofem w\u225?wefnogh yafrotat efalo Ju \u225?rfene ende, w\u233?nde f\u225? norayat y\u233?ndo w\u225?wefnogh yafrotan f\u233?nat\u233? efalo y\u225?toghe. W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon efalo ey\u225?totan m\u233?inyotio n\u233?m\u233? ekai n\u225?kan a n\u233?m\u233? efarotam\u233?nd Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Tafaf y\u233?m nden\u233? m\u233?ghm\u233?ghyo Ng\u225?nj\u225?n k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rfefaf k\u233?s em, k\u233?t\u233? so anogh y\u233?m mbark\u225?nd \u225?rfefaf a yaufi \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?nd so nufotan t\u250?m\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t tane emar\u233?gh kwayagh\u233? so y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nr\u233?re a \u225?rfefaf.
