"T\u225?rf\u225?r yunj\u233?f yuk\u233?r soram\u233?, y\u233?nd w\u233?nmorm\u233?n Jerusalem\u233?t eng\u233?rsam\u233?n tane \u225?rfene mani yauyau \u225?r\u233?t a gh\u233?ng\u233?n ramgh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Tane w\u225?taran\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m winjoy\u233?nd y\u233?nd w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon njamandio y\u233?nd kw\u233?morw\u233?n w\u225?ny\u225?ny\u233?gh wifogh t\u225?rf\u225?ran. K\u233?t\u233? yau \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n tamorw\u233?n y\u233?ndf\u233?, yau \u225?mb us\u233?rmbogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
W\u233?nde k\u233?t\u233? \u225?mb Ju \u225?r tamorw\u233?n k\u233?tamam\u233?n Esia yum\u233?n. T\u225?f y\u233?fene njam ewam \u225?w\u225?taran\u233?gh tafaf, f\u225? fiya tanmorw\u233?n y\u233?na fene s\u225?fr\u233?re a tan\u233?rsaw\u233?t w\u225?taran\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Tamotangi y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r y\u233?na, y\u233?mofem so tawaufrongi nden\u233? m\u225?m\u225?fi yau yinjoy\u233?nd njam y\u233?mofem w\u233?ngwanay\u233?nd moghfaf Ju s\u233?nko \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
\u193?mbiro yaman y\u233?nd nutnay\u233?n njam y\u233?nd kwakayong\u233?rw\u233?n y\u233?fene s\u225?fan: 'Y\u233?nd ufoghan w\u233?m f\u233?fene s\u225?fan s\u233?nonjo m\u233?nam\u233?n tane efalo y\u225?togh y\u233?m \u225?rfene anoghm\u233?n k\u233?rta!'"
