Feliks mer mat n\u225?y\u225?toi Yesuene Endm\u233?n, f\u233?yo njam n\u225?y\u225?rai y\u233?n\u233? sioene fifi, y\u233?kmboi mogh a y\u233?mndai, "Njam fiyar\u233? ndimbal s\u233?nko \u225?r Lisias k\u233?naflang\u233?, y\u233?ndon so mwigh\u233? y\u233?faronan fene awataran\u233?ghm\u233?n." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u233?mon y\u225?f\u225?retam fiyar\u233? s\u233?nko \u225?r Fole wanjeng\u233?t w\u233?nde yaramai \u225?mb enagh a yumyoi y\u225?ne f\u250?taram so tawarametaw\u233?t y\u225?ne m\u233?ndef\u233? rokar.
