T\u225?rf\u225?r efogh soram\u233? Feliks\u233?f en\u233?rm\u233?n y\u225?njo amaf Drusila, efe t\u233?morw\u233?n Jum\u233?n amaf. Y\u233?mo y\u225?f\u225?retam y\u225?njo \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r Fole wasrogh\u233?t. F\u225? m\u233?nde tamorw\u233?n s\u225?i k\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?t Folefaf \u225?rfene ndimbal mwigham\u233?n Keriso Yesuene k\u233?nj\u250?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Fol korayaw\u233?ng mbark\u225?nd gh\u233?rsam\u233?n, f\u233?myo awarawer\u233?ghm\u233?n a mogh efoghtaum\u233?n \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m, Feliks f\u233?rf\u233?r t\u233?morw\u233?n a norayai, "F\u233?yo t\u233?m s\u233?nonjoyot. F\u233?m t\u233?u kuwano. Efogh njam wam y\u233?ndon so k\u233?ngmotang\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i n\u233?n\u233?m tafaf w\u233?ikor." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghonyo f\u225? t\u233?morw\u233?n emarghan nden\u233? Fol\u233?m so mani taramangai, f\u233?yo f\u225? t\u250?m\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233? kaf\u225?ngow\u233?t a koraiw\u233?t y\u233?maf\u233?.
