Festus namndai gafana, nambio efogh soram\u233? f\u225? nuwanoi Kaisariata k\u233?t\u225?n Jerusalem. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Jerusalem k\u233?nj\u250?n, lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?r a Ju \u225?rfene s\u233?nko \u225?r nufary\u233?nd y\u225?ne s\u225?fr\u233?re a y\u233?ramay\u233?nd w\u225?taran\u233?gh si Folenem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
