Festus\u233?m ewawangoi, "Fol siy\u233?m t\u233? yangongi kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngo \u225?r y\u233?m Kaisarian, a y\u233?ndio so w\u233?ng\u233?m tekofnaye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
So \u225?mb f\u233?fene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?rf\u233? y\u233?nng\u233?m y\u233?ndf\u233?, a njam y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rom n\u233?mndafi m\u225?m\u225?fi yafrota, y\u233?mofem so w\u225?taran\u233?ghan t\u233?kmangi f\u225?."
