Njam Fol n\u233?lawai k\u233?nj\u250?t, Ju \u225?r efe enmorm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Jerusalemta yarenday\u233?nd f\u225?. Y\u233?mofem en\u233?rsam\u233?nd y\u225?faf t\u225?rf\u225?r kw\u233?rnaraf\u233? w\u225?taran\u233?gh si, w\u233?nde f\u225? f\u233?yotarofnar emorm\u233?n y\u225?togh\u233?t y\u233?fene w\u225?taran\u233?ghan.
