F\u233?yo Fol f\u225?yo nawamarotai, "Y\u233?ndon yau \u225?mb m\u225?m\u225?fi tafrotan k\u233?t\u225?n Ju \u225?rfene n\u225?kfaf o w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngofaf o Rom tuk warsagh \u225?r Kaisarefaf."
