\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Fol\u233?m yawangoi, "Y\u233?nd s\u233?nonjo wakai Rom tuk warsagh \u225?r Kaisarene mogh s\u225?fr\u233?re, \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?m mbark\u225?nd sifay\u233? tayot mogh\u233?t. F\u233?m f\u233?myo mer mat em nden\u233? y\u233?ndo \u225?mb yau m\u225?m\u225?fi tafrotan Ju \u225?rfefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
