Nambio efogh soram\u233? warsagh \u225?r Agrifa a Bernisa nufareyay\u233?nd Kaisariat. F\u225? en\u233?rm\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tumyeyay\u233?nd Festus. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
