"Y\u233?ndon ewawangoy\u233?n, 'F\u233?m nden\u233? norayati y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rom t\u233? tafrote m\u225?m\u225?fi yam. F\u225? fronde so kokayong\u233? f\u233?fene s\u225?fr\u233?re efe nawatarnat y\u225?faf. F\u233?yo y\u233?mon so tawawangong\u233? f\u233?fe, f\u233?yo y\u233?ndo so t\u225?f moghan t\u225?kman efe y\u233?m mbark\u225?nd. Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m t\u233?fene Rom n\u225?k.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Njam y\u225?ne w\u225?nangogh \u225?r y\u233?nmorm\u233?n y\u233?nan, y\u233?ndon yau yalay\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?rt\u233?. W\u233?nde y\u233?nd n\u225?umenday\u233?m mogh\u233?t \u225?mb efghon a emnday\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r y\u233?nmasroy\u233?nd k\u233?nj\u250?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Y\u225?ne w\u225?nangogh \u225?r nokayoy\u233?nd a norayay\u233?nd. Y\u233?nd kemnan nden\u233? f\u225? so norayat nden\u233? Fol\u233?m t\u233? \u225?mb minde m\u225?m\u225?fi yam tafrote. W\u233?nde f\u225? yau y\u233?n\u233? si norayay\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
W\u233?ndende, f\u225? y\u233?maf\u233? k\u233?witaw\u233?t Folf\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? Ju \u225?r\u233?m tawatametaw\u233?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?nenem\u233?n. F\u225? k\u233?witaw\u233?t y\u225?nem\u233?n efe k\u233?r t\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n Yesu. W\u233?nde Fol nden\u233? korayau f\u225? gh\u233?rs\u233? m\u233? y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Y\u233?nd yau mat w\u233?m ndern\u225?ye so tawaf\u233?nmetaw\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? \u225?w\u225?taran\u233?gh. F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon y\u233?motay\u233?n f\u225?, 'F\u233?m t\u233? m\u233?nde n\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?ligh\u233?t Jerusalem\u233?t a n\u233?makai k\u233?t\u233? ufoghan y\u233?n\u233? w\u225?taran\u233?ghan.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
W\u233?nde Fol\u233?m wawangoi ta, 'Yau, y\u233?nd m\u233?nde w\u233?m Kaisar\u233?m s\u225?i n\u225?y\u225?reta tane si.' Y\u233?nayan y\u233?nd norayay\u233?n tane fiyarafaf, 'M\u233?n\u225?t Fol s\u225?i tumbetau y\u233?na k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u233?ndon t\u233?ngwatemban Kaisarefaf.'"
