\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
\u193?mb efghon Agrifa a Bernisam numanem\u233?nd mer s\u225?l\u225?me. F\u225? n\u233?laweyay\u233?nd Gafaman m\u233?ngot y\u233?maf\u233? fiyar\u233? s\u233?nko \u225?rf\u233? a utman\u233?gh \u225?r tesenm\u233?n. Festus\u233?m emndai y\u225?njo \u225?r, "T\u233?nmasrongi Fol y\u233?nan." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Festus norayai, "Warsagh \u225?r Agrifa a m\u233?inyotio efe y\u233?na em y\u233?ndf\u233?, f\u233?mofem t\u233?fandangi y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r! M\u233?inyotio Ju \u225?r\u233?m wamnendangi y\u233?nd Jerusalem\u233?n a y\u233?na Kaisarian, kutnaw\u233?t nden\u233? f\u225? yau so nakete. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?ndon yau yinjoy\u233?n y\u225?ne yaufi wafroghyam \u225?rk\u233?mam\u233?n f\u225? krot y\u233?kmetat. W\u233?nde m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? w\u233?ikor norayai f\u225? m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n Kaisar s\u225?i k\u225?y\u225?retau y\u225?ne \u225?w\u225?taran\u233?gh. F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon mwigh\u233? yafrotam\u233?n y\u225? watembgh\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?n Rom.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
"Y\u233?nd yau mat w\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?ndon so y\u233?farotan Rom tuk warsagh \u225?rfefaf y\u225?nem\u233?n. Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde y\u233?ndon t\u233? t\u233?n\u233?mnjan f\u225? m\u233?inyotio f\u233?fefaf. Warsagh \u225?r Agrifafaf, y\u233?ndon n\u233?mamnendan f\u233?m kor merk\u233?r\u225?ye n\u225?y\u225?reta n\u233?m\u233? Fol noraye. F\u233?yo y\u233?nd so t\u225?f norayam y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?rtam\u233?n m\u233?rne. Soram\u233? y\u233?ndon so mbark\u225?nde f\u233?r\u233?n y\u233?farotan k\u233?t\u225?n Kaisarefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Y\u233?nd norayan y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?nam\u233?n njam y\u233?ndfem tatembang\u233?m kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngo \u225?r k\u233?t\u225?n Rom tuk warsagh \u225?roefaf t\u233?fnofnar yuwon, f\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? yau so mer y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 26
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
F\u233?yo Agrifa norayai Folefaf, "Koraya s\u233?nonjo."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 F\u233?yo Fol\u233?m ng\u225?ng\u233? euyoi a norayai awamarogh si, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
"Warsagh \u225?r Agrifa, y\u233?nd \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? w\u233?m fe s\u225?fr\u233?re s\u233?nonjo t\u225?f y\u233?ndon norayan awamarogh si m\u233?inyotio Ju \u225?rfene w\u225?nangoghm\u233?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m mer mat n\u233?m ndern\u225?ye Ju \u225?r emor a y\u233?fene f\u233?natayam. F\u233?yo f\u233?m n\u225?y\u225?reta tafaf m\u233?tare!
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
"M\u233?inyotio Ju \u225?r mat em tanem\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?ndmayo y\u233?nd tos\u233?. F\u225? mat em n\u233?m\u233? s\u225?fot gh\u233?rsaf\u233? y\u233?nd kw\u233?morang\u233?rw\u233?n tanjo yuwon a nden\u225?yo Jerusalem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u225? mat t\u233? tamorw\u233?n tanem\u233?n tekefifi. F\u225? so nafrotat nden\u233? y\u233?nd kw\u233?morw\u233?n Farasi \u225?r. Y\u233?ndo mbark\u225?nde ewaitotan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene n\u225?k ndenanit m\u233?inyotio Farasi \u225?r\u233?m k\u233?s ewafrotat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Tane m\u233?ghm\u233?gh siy\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?yan n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? n\u233?norayai t\u233?fene \u225?kiafefaf, y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan y\u233?nd ufoghan w\u233?m s\u233?nonjo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam uny\u233?ghofnar si norayam ndimbal yamm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n t\u233?fene 12 Israil \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?nfaf. Y\u233?ndfem m\u233?inyotio y\u225?njetam m\u233?n\u225?t so tanang\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam uny\u233?ghofnar si n\u233?ngorayai t\u233?fefaf. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan y\u233?ndfem Ju \u225?r\u233?m t\u250?m\u233?n y\u225?wefnotam Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne s\u233?mb\u225?r a efogh. Nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? Ju \u225?r sem y\u233?na, y\u233?ndo efalo yiy\u225?totan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene uny\u233?ghofnar si. W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m t\u233?f\u233?n nden\u233? f\u225? nawatarnat tafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so tam\u233?indang\u233? k\u233?r \u225?r s\u225?i kanongi gh\u233?rsat w\u233?ikor. F\u233?mofem so efalo wiy\u225?totati y\u233?nd njam norayan y\u233?n\u233? si.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
"Y\u233?nd y\u233?ndio m\u233?nde kw\u233?morw\u233?n s\u225?i k\u225?s\u225?fotaw\u233?n t\u233?karotaw\u233?n Yesu Najaretm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u233? tafrotaw\u233?n Jerusalem\u233?n. Lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?rfene si muyayan, y\u233?ndon efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r t\u225?rf\u225?r takmetaw\u233?n kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngot. Njam t\u233?fene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r\u233?m korayangay\u233?nd, 'Y\u233?n\u233? efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r t\u225?f k\u233?r em,' Y\u233?ndon y\u233?fene mwigh\u233? \u225?mbiro tiy\u225?tongay\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
T\u225?rf\u225?r mbinotma y\u233?nd kwiyotau Ju \u225?rfene \u225?umeng\u233?gh m\u233?ngom\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?fe t\u233?kr\u225?tan k\u233?mgh\u233?t. Y\u233?ndon taw\u225?f\u225?retaw\u233?n f\u225? yaufi siot Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf. Y\u233?ndon tawakeindaw\u233?n n\u233?kw kw\u233?morw\u233?n y\u233?fefaf a tawifnaw\u233?n d\u225?bi \u225?rfene tesenam\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
"\u193?mb efghon y\u233?nd \u225?lighan kw\u233?morw\u233?n Damaskos\u233?t lim\u225?n\u233?gh gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh \u225?rfene si muyaf\u233? a w\u225?f\u225?retay\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Warsagh \u225?r Agrifa, s\u233?ite kar\u233?fta, njam y\u233?nd kw\u233?ngmorw\u233?n endm\u233?, y\u233?ndo yinjoy\u233?n kwayagh\u233? njafarta, yau nden\u233? efogh kwayagh\u233?, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? y\u225?indai, a warendai y\u233?nd a y\u233?ndf\u233? \u225?ligh \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio nuy\u225?y\u233?m mbandot, a y\u233?nd n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?n k\u233?m korayau Ibru sie, 'Sol, Sol, n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u233?mo y\u233?nd wesmete? F\u233?mo njam kafkaf tautar w\u237?m minan, f\u233?mon nd\u233?mke so y\u233?fande.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
"F\u233?yo y\u233?ndon y\u233?motay\u233?n, 'Efe f\u233?m n\u233?m, Yur\u233??'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Yuram wawangoi, 'Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Yesu, efe f\u233?mon y\u233?smete. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Kano a kokai fenjo kafkafe. Y\u233?nd t\u233? nufar\u233?n fefaf f\u233?m n\u233?muyafon tane \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t a fandagh \u225?r. F\u233?mon so ewaufrote tanem\u233?n n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?mon t\u233?fande a so m\u233? y\u233?ngfande. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?ndon so k\u233?manjar\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? Ju \u225?r a T\u233?ndo \u225?r. Y\u233?ndon n\u233?m\u225?f\u225?retan t\u233?ndo \u225?rfefaf {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?fene gh\u233?k\u233?f saur\u233?gh\u233?t a so ewangote kw\u233?fkw\u233?fta kwayaghat, k\u233?tam\u233? S\u225?if\u233?roene waftata k\u233?t\u225?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf. F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem so tanangi yaufiyam wigh\u233?t yaufita a sifay\u233? tawaramangi Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?rfefaf emofem y\u233?nd efalo wiy\u225?totat.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
"F\u233?yo warsagh \u225?r Agrifa, y\u233?nd \u225?y\u225?r\u233?gh kw\u233?morw\u233?n gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?gh yaman njafarm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
Fronde ewaufrotan k\u233?t\u225?n efe tamorw\u233?n Damaskos\u233?n, nden\u225?yo y\u233?fefaf Jerusalem\u233?t a m\u233?inyotio Judiat a m\u233?inyotio T\u233?ndo \u225?rfefaf. Y\u233?ndon t\u225?itotaw\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? so nawengotat yaufita Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf a so yufarotat y\u233?fenjo awengogh yam wafroghe {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan \u225?mb Ju \u225?r\u233?m w\u233?ray\u233?nd w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo sifayan a kw\u233?rametaw\u233?t ngiot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
W\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam kw\u225?ut\u225?ne ta m\u233?inyotio efogh k\u233?t\u225?notio s\u233?nonjo. F\u233?yo y\u233?nd wakai y\u233?na a nafrotan efalo si y\u233?tkw\u233?nofnar \u225?r a y\u233?tkw\u233?naf\u233? \u225?rfefaf. Y\u233?ndo y\u233?n\u233? norayan n\u233?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r a Moses korayau so nufrotat: {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Kerisom so t\u233?kr\u225?t y\u225?y\u225?rete, a fronde so y\u233?m anogh\u233?t k\u233?tam\u233? k\u233?rta, so y\u233?n\u233?rse si kwayagh\u233? y\u225?njo \u225?rfefaf a T\u233?ndo \u225?rfefaf."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Njam Fol\u233?m m\u233? korayau, Festus\u233?m nutnai, "Fol, f\u233?m onon n\u233?m! Fenjo ndimbal otamegham n\u233?m\u233?inde ononot!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Fol\u233?m yawangoi, "Minde utman\u233?ghaf\u233? Festus. Y\u233?nd yau onon w\u233?m. Y\u233?nd n\u233?m\u233? norayan siy\u233?m efalo a fifiyaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Warsagh \u225?r mat y\u233?n\u233? yamm\u233?n y\u233?m. Y\u233?nd so norayan f\u233?rf\u233?rofnaye fefaf. Y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m nden\u233? warsagh \u225?r mat y\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?nd norayan, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? yam yau nufrotam \u225?tnoghe kw\u233?ndkw\u233?ndan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Warsagh \u225?r Agrifa, f\u233?mon efalo t\u233? ey\u225?tote Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r? Y\u233?nd mat f\u233?mo f\u233?t\u233?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
F\u233?yo Agrifa norayai Folefaf, "F\u233?m nden\u233? nemne y\u233?n\u233? tekofnare f\u233?mon so kwiy\u225?to w\u233?keye y\u233?nd nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Fol\u233?m yawangoi, "T\u233?njfi o tomb\u233? k\u233?r\u225?ye, tane oray\u233?gh Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf feyot a m\u233?inyotio emofem wiy\u225?retat y\u233?nd s\u233?nonjo so k\u233?namndangi efalo y\u225?togh \u225?r nden\u233? y\u233?nd sw\u233?m, w\u233?nde y\u233?nd yau m\u233?nde w\u233?m f\u233?m s\u225?i kamndangi kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngo \u225?r nden\u233? y\u233?nd."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Warsagh \u225?r, gafana, Bernis a m\u233?inyotio efe tamorang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233? f\u225? nokayoy\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Soram\u233? y\u233?mofem y\u233?frangoy\u233?nd a f\u225? nufngoy\u233?nd si y\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?nro, "Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rom n\u233?m\u233? yau tafrote n\u233?mndafi \u225?rk\u233?mam\u233?n krot so t\u233?kmangi o kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngot t\u233?nyawangi."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Agrifa norayai Festusefaf, "Njam y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r yau t\u233? norayai Kaisarefaf m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i k\u225?y\u225?retau yane si, f\u233?yo y\u233?ndfem so t\u233?ngwurtong\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 27
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fol tiyotau ndimbal boute k\u233?t\u225?n Rom
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Njam mwigh\u233? nufary\u233?ng nde y\u233?nd so kuwanongay\u233?m ndimbal boute k\u233?t\u225?n Italia, y\u233?mofem eramay\u233?nd Fol a \u225?mb kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngo \u225?r y\u225?faf Rom fiyar\u233? s\u233?nko \u225?r Juli\u233?s. F\u225? tafnyang\u233?rw\u233?n tuk\u233?n warsagh \u225?roene fiyar\u233? m\u233?rnan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?nd nuwanoy\u233?m ndimbal boutfaf \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? y\u233?nmorm\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? Adramitum. Y\u233?n\u233? bout t\u233?morw\u233?n kafrendau. Y\u233?n\u233? so kuwanongai y\u233?nam\u233? tesenam\u233? arakaf t\u233?ndom\u233? Esia ndimbal yuwon. Y\u233?nd nuflay\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? boutan. \u193?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Aristakus efe t\u233?morw\u233?n Tesalonika tesenm\u233?n Makedonia yuwon nuwanoy\u233?m y\u233?maf\u233?. {\cs259\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 |nmx_225wbt_Paul to Rome [bwf-light] @en_v3.tif|col||\u169? 2025 Wycliffe Bible Translators, Inc.|Folene \u225?ligh Rom\u233?t (Acts 27.1\u8212?28.14)|27.1\u8212?28.14}

