\u193?mb kw\u233?fon nufary\u233?m Sidon\u233?t. Juli\u233?s\u233?m mere Fol yumyoi fandagh\u233?t y\u225? f\u250?tarfefaf m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?mofem so taramangay\u233?nd y\u225?ne m\u233?ndef\u233? rokar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Njam y\u233?ndfem y\u233?frangoy\u233?m Sidon tesen, m\u233?nam\u233?n ndimbal mbormboram wangogh y\u233?nmafngoi, f\u233?yo y\u233?nd k\u233?rsaw\u233?m Saifr\u233?s f\u233?r t\u233?ndom\u233? \u225?rkam\u233? mbormbor yau t\u233?fnjaw\u233?ng muyaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? n\u233?f\u233?rmay\u233?m marat arakaffaf kaka k\u233?t\u225?n arakaf t\u233?ndot Silisia a Famfilia yuwon, n\u233?nufary\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n Mirat tesen Lisia yuwon. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Mira tesenan, fiyar\u233? s\u233?nko \u225?rom yinjoi Aleksandria \u225?rfene ndimbal bout \u225?rk\u233? kafrendaw\u233?t \u225?ligh\u233?t Italiat, f\u233?yo y\u233?mo y\u233?nmaflai boutan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Y\u233?nd \u225?fr\u225?e k\u233?rsaw\u233?m t\u225?rf\u225?r efogh, a t\u225?ik\u233?r m\u233? t\u233?fandaw\u233?m ufargh\u233?t S\u233?nidus yuwot. Yau mbormboram t\u233?nmumyotau y\u233?nd \u225?ligh\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? sifayam\u233?, f\u233?yo y\u233?nd t\u233?ndom\u233? nuwanoy\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n n\u225?ik\u225?i tamb\u233?n Krit f\u233?r, y\u233?ngwainday\u233?m Salmone gh\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?nd \u225?fr\u225?e k\u233?rsaw\u233?m arakaf t\u233?ndom\u233? a nufary\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? sifay\u233? y\u233?tkw\u233?n Wanjar\u233?gh Sur, yau nayu t\u233?morw\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? Lasia tesenot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?nandm\u233? y\u233?ndfem t\u233? t\u225?rf\u225?r efogh tan\u233?rsam, f\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? so y\u233?m m\u225?m\u225?fi njam m\u233? n\u233?rsam boute m\u233?nam\u233?n Ju \u225?rfene ndimbal awafarman\u233?gh efogh soram\u233? arakaf namndai minde mbormboraf\u233?. F\u233?yo Fol\u233?m emndai \u225?r boutan, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
"F\u250?tar\u233?f, k\u225?y\u225?rangi tafaf y\u233?nd njam kuwanong\u233?m s\u233?nonjo t\u233?fene ndimbal bout rokaraf\u233? so k\u233?rtayan y\u233?m, a t\u225?rf\u225?r gh\u233?rs\u233? so etarnam." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
W\u233?nde fiyar\u233? s\u233?nko \u225?r yau n\u225?y\u225?rai Folefaf n\u233?m\u233? f\u225? norayai, w\u233?nde ewaiteyai ndimbal bout wawer\u233?gh \u225?r a ndimbal bout yurane si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n sur yau mer t\u233?morw\u233?n yunjfan y\u233?fe k\u233?mgh\u233?t, t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r m\u233?nde tamorw\u233?n awaing\u233?gh\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?n sur y\u233?tkw\u233?n Finiks yunj\u233?f \u225?mnjogh\u233?t k\u233?t\u233?. Finiks sur t\u233?morw\u233?n saur\u233?ghkaf k\u233?t\u225?n arakafot s\u243?mbio ende a muyaf\u233? mbormbor yau kor t\u233?n\u233?fnjau k\u233?t\u233?. {\cs259\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 |CN02042B.tif|col||\u169? 1996 David C Cook. Used by permission.|Fol korayau Boutan mbormboran (Acts 27.9-10)|27.9-10}

\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ndimbal Mbormbor
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Njam m\u233?tar n\u225?ik\u225?i mbormbor wauf\u233?gh y\u233?nmafngoi, y\u233?mofem yinjoy\u233?nd mer t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?ligh\u233?t. F\u233?yo t\u225?f yurtoy\u233?nd wer\u233?gh t\u233?f\u233?n ndimbal boutoene a nuwanoy\u233?nd Krit arakaf t\u233?ndom\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
W\u233?nde ndimbal mbormbor y\u233?tkw\u233?n Yamb\u233?rmaw\u233?r Mbormboram eutfoi f\u225? a y\u233?nmaufetai k\u233?tam\u233? f\u233?rta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Mbormbor t\u233?maufetau minde muyaf\u233? ndimbal boutfaf. F\u233?yotarofnar tamorw\u233?n wawer\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?ram s\u225?i taweretaw\u233?t ndimbal bout mbark\u225?nde k\u233?t\u225?n mbormborfaf. F\u233?yo yumyoy\u233?nd ndimbal bout mbormboram y\u233?ngwanai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?nd y\u233?nam\u233? y\u233?ngmorm\u233?n Kauda f\u233?r n\u233?ndk\u233?fam\u233?. Bout wawer\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?ram w\u233?nmauyoy\u233?nd Boutoene ndingi nutamb\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t wanjargh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem yarmboy\u233?nd ndingi ndimbal bout tuk\u233?t. Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? y\u233?mofem wumb\u233?gh yafngoy\u233?nd \u225?ng\u233?ghe ndimbal bout m\u233?n\u225?t taikrot. M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? f\u233?rf\u233?r tamorw\u233?n nde m\u233?t\u233? t\u225?f k\u225?smetaw\u233?t w\u237?man Siritis\u233?n, y\u233?mofem yewory\u233?nd boutoene w\u233?r\u233?gh tot t\u233?f\u233?n yumyoy\u233?nd ndimbal bout y\u233?ngwanay\u233?ng mbormboram. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Ndimbal mbormbor mindefifi taufetau, f\u233?yo \u225?mb efghon \u225?mb rokar taran\u233?gh ewafngoy\u233?nd ndimbal boutta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Nambiom\u233?n efghon y\u233?mofem taran\u233?gh ewafngoy\u233?nd \u225?mb bout \u225?s\u225?foghm\u233?n rokar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
T\u225?rf\u225?r efghon y\u233?ndfem yau tafandaw\u233?m efogh a k\u233?nd. Ndimbal mbormbor m\u233? t\u233?nmaufetau muyaf\u233? a y\u233?nd f\u233?yo y\u233?nmorm\u233?n a t\u233?fene kamnang nefoy\u233?nd awanjargh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan y\u233?ndfem yau njamke t\u225?netaw\u233?m nden\u233? teke. Fol nokayoi emndai \u225?r: "F\u233?m fai k\u225?y\u225?retaw\u233?t tafaf njam tamorw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? Krit f\u233?ran, f\u233?mofem yau y\u233?n\u233? was\u233?rmbogh so tinjongay\u233?nd a t\u233? kawaghnat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
W\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndon ewamnendan f\u233?m, yau f\u233?rf\u233?r em m\u233?nam\u233?n emo \u225?mb yau gh\u233?rs\u233? so y\u233?tarne, m\u233? ndimbal boutro so nawas\u233?rmbote. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene, a y\u233?ndon y\u225?wefnotan y\u225?yot. S\u233?mb\u225?ran y\u233?mon t\u233?nm\u225?f\u225?rete njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
ta waufroi, 'Fol, yau f\u233?rf\u233?r n\u233?m! F\u233?m so n\u233?makai ufoghan Rom tuk warsagh \u225?roene r\u233?re. M\u233?nam\u233?n fenem\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so tawanjarng\u233? efe m\u233?inyotio em ndimbal boutan.' {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?rf\u233?r yau em! Y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m nden\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so yafrote mbark\u225?nd n\u233?m\u233? f\u225? norayai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
W\u233?ndende, ndimbal bout so nirone \u225?mb f\u233?ran."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Ndimbal bout niroy\u233?ng
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
14 s\u233?mb\u225?ran y\u233?nd t\u233?nmimndau mbormboram y\u233?nam\u233? Mediterian arakafam\u233?. W\u233?nde s\u233?mb\u225?r n\u233?ndk\u233?f ndimbal bout \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd y\u233?nd kaka n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?m mbandfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
Y\u233?mofem yufotam\u233?nd nuoene k\u233?njkam nden\u233? 40 mit\u233?. Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? w\u233?i yufotam\u233?nd a yinyoy\u233?nd 30 mit\u233? k\u233?njkam t\u233?morw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
Ndimbal bout \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r f\u233?rf\u233?r tamorw\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n m\u233?t\u233? t\u225?f k\u225?smetaw\u233?t w\u237?man. F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem ewitam\u233?nd 4 wer\u233?gh tot t\u233?f\u233?n ndimbal boutoene kw\u233?mb tamb\u233?n a f\u225? Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh nufngoy\u233?nd efogh kwayaghat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
Bout \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r m\u233?nde tamorw\u233?n s\u225?i t\u233?frangongay\u233?nd ndimbal bout. F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem yewory\u233?nd ndingi arakafot. F\u225? y\u233?ta kwankwane \u225?ligh\u233?t nufngoy\u233?nd. F\u225? norayay\u233?nd, "Y\u233?nd y\u233?ng\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n ndimbal bout s\u233?nkofaf m\u233?n\u225?t ndimbal boutoene wer\u233?gh tot t\u233?f\u233?n so taweworng\u233?m arakafot." W\u233?nde kuindaw\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
W\u233?nde Fol\u233?m emndai fiyar\u233? s\u233?nko \u225?r a fiyar\u233?, "Ndimbal bout \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r yau njam emor ndimbal boutan, f\u233?fene kamnang \u225?mb yau y\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t awanjargh\u233?t." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
F\u233?yo fiyaram y\u233?nfay\u233?nd \u225?ng\u233?gh \u225?rk\u233? teretaw\u233?t ndingi a nuyai arakafot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Faur\u233?gh\u233?tro t\u233?morw\u233?n Fol\u233?m ewamnendai njamke n\u233?net, a emndai, "14 efogh f\u233?m t\u233? tam m\u225?m\u233? mwigh\u233? a \u225?mb njamke yau t\u225?netati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Y\u233?ndon ewamnendan f\u233?m, f\u233?yo, njamke t\u225?netangi, gh\u233?rs\u233? s\u225?i m\u233? em. Y\u233?n\u233? yafrotati a f\u233?m so mer em."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
Si soram\u233?, Fol\u233?m yanay\u233?ng \u225?mb f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? kar\u233?f a k\u225?njo si yaramay\u233?ng Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne. F\u233?yo m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfene s\u225?fr\u233?re, y\u233?mo y\u233?tfoi f\u233?skaf flaw\u233? a t\u233?netau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
F\u225? m\u233?inyotio n\u225?uw\u233?tam\u233?nd a \u225?mb njamke enetam\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
K\u233?t\u233? tamorw\u233?n m\u233?inyotio 276 \u225?r ndimbal boutan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Njam y\u233?mofem enetam\u233?nd a eremngoi, y\u233?mofem tawitaw\u233?t flaw\u233? baik k\u233?t\u225?n arakafot ndimbal bout ofat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
\u193?mb akwan, y\u233?mofem yau y\u225?y\u225?mngoy\u233?nd mband, w\u233?nde y\u233?mofem yinjoy\u233?nd trewar m\u233?n\u225?yaf\u233? miri mbandaf\u233?. F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem mwigh\u233? yinjoy\u233?nd m\u233?n\u225?t w\u233?rset miriam\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Y\u233?mofem enfay\u233?nd wer\u233?gh t\u233?f\u233?n \u225?ng\u233?gh f\u233?yo eng\u233?frangoy\u233?nd arakafan. T\u225?fandio y\u233?mofem efery\u233?nd \u225?ng\u233?gh \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam teretaw\u233?t ndimbal bout wakny\u233?ghm\u233?n. Y\u233?namayo y\u233?mofem yakayoy\u233?nd s\u225?imai ndimbal bout s\u233?nko tamb\u233?n a mbormboram ndimbal bout r\u233?sagh yafngoi k\u233?t\u225?n mirifaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
W\u233?nde ndimbal bout miri mbandot n\u225?y\u225?toi. F\u233?yo ndimbal bout s\u233?nko n\u233?kmboi k\u233?t\u233? yau kimndau, a ndimbal s\u243?fam y\u233?smai ndimbal bout kw\u233?mbta m\u233?inyotio yirory\u233?ng.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Fiyar\u233? m\u233?ndefnar tamorw\u233?n efe yau so kakmetaw\u233?t tunat a k\u233?ngongay\u233?nd, f\u233?yo y\u233?mofem mwigh\u233? t\u233?frendaw\u233?t kw\u233?fkw\u233?f m\u233?ngo \u225?rfe ngiot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
W\u233?ndende, fiyar\u233? s\u233?nko \u225?r m\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n Fole wanjargh\u233?t a y\u233?mo yau taumyotau y\u233?n\u233? yam wafrogh\u233?t. W\u233?ndende, "M\u233?inyotio \u225?r efe mat em akm\u233?gh, katnangi arakafot, a kakmetangi tunat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
\u193?mb \u225?r\u233?m t\u225?f ewaitotat. Naw\u233?retat w\u233?n karfan o ndimbal bout kar\u233?fkar\u233?fan." F\u233?yo f\u225? nufary\u233?nd merro k\u233?t\u225?n tunat.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 28
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Fol t\u233?morw\u233?n Malta f\u233?ran
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Njam y\u233?nd merro nufary\u233?m, y\u233?ndfem y\u225?yamngoy\u233?m f\u233?r y\u233?tkw\u233?n Malta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
F\u233?r \u225?r efe t\u225?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u233?mofem y\u233?nmumyoy\u233?nd mere a f\u250?tar n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?m. Y\u233?mofem f\u233?s y\u233?tayam\u233?nd a y\u233?nmumyoy\u233?nd y\u233?nd m\u233?inyotio m\u233?nam\u233?n nu kafamndau a kurf\u233?rm\u233?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Fol\u233?m \u225?mb f\u233?s sut enwanai a efayoi f\u233?s\u233?t. F\u233?s waftayam y\u233?m\u233?indai kamban \u233?torgh\u233?t a yarary\u233?ng y\u225?ne ng\u225?ng\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Njam f\u233?r \u225?r\u233?m yinjoy\u233?nd kamban t\u233?rnyang\u233?rw\u233?n y\u225?ne ng\u225?ngayan, f\u225? korayangi y\u233?fe k\u233?nj\u250?nro, "Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r m\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m \u225?r ngi t\u233?fn\u225?r! F\u225? yau kolitote arakafan, w\u233?nde ng\u225?nj\u225?nam yau yumyo gh\u233?rsat." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
W\u233?nde Fol\u233?m y\u233?fnendai kamban f\u233?s\u233?t y\u233?neghoi a \u225?mb n\u233?m\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? yau yanai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
\u193?r kemnaw\u233?t y\u225?faf nden\u233? mbwe kar so tarenau o sune k\u233?r t\u233?morw\u233?n. W\u233?nde teke awanjeng\u233?gh soram\u233? yau n\u233?mndafi nufrotam y\u225?faf, y\u233?fefaf mwigh\u233? nufary\u233?nd a norayay\u233?nd, "F\u225? siy\u233?m ng\u225?nj\u225?n."
