Gafana t\u233?morw\u233?n Fablis y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?ran, y\u225?ne \u225?mb mband k\u233?t\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n. Fablis t\u233?morw\u233?n ng\u225?r\u225?m \u225?r t\u233?fefaf a y\u233?nmumyoi y\u225?njo m\u233?ngot nambio efogh \u225?mnjogh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u225?ref\u233? enjne t\u233?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n yameyan fifi waftam\u233?n a oghanem\u233?n. Fol n\u233?nglawai k\u233?nj\u250?t Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh\u233?t a ng\u225?ng\u233? y\u233?fayoi y\u225?faf a mer yiy\u225?toi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Njam y\u233?n\u233? yam nufrotam, y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?rta enjne t\u233?fn\u225?r tanmorw\u233?n a mer t\u225?y\u225?totau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?mofem t\u233?nmut\u233?mndaw\u233?t y\u233?nd t\u225?rf\u225?r ende, a y\u233?nd njam \u225?ligh\u233?tro t\u233?nmorw\u233?n, y\u233?mofem t\u233?nmarametaw\u233?t t\u233?fene m\u233?ndef\u233? rokar.
