Nambio gh\u233?rare soram\u233? mbormboram yiroy\u233?ng ndimbal bout. Ndimbal bout y\u233?m\u233?ghang\u233?rm\u233?n Maltan mbormborm\u233?n yunjfan. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n Aleksandriam\u233?n ndimbal bout a k\u233?t\u233? t\u225?rw\u233?n s\u243?mbio wafroghm\u233?n ng\u225?nj\u225?n ndimbal bout s\u233?nkoyan. Y\u233?nd n\u233?ngufary\u233?m ndimbal boute. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?nd ng\u233?rsaw\u233?m arakafam\u233? nungufary\u233?m Sirakus tesen a y\u233?nmorang\u233?rm\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? nambio efogh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
K\u233?t\u225?ndm\u233? y\u233?nd nufary\u233?m Regium tesen. \u193?mb efghon n\u225?ik\u225?i mbormbor wauf\u233?gh yafngoi, s\u243?mbio efogh soram\u233? y\u233?nd nufary\u233?m Fotioli tesen. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
K\u233?t\u233? y\u233?ndfem ewinjoy\u233?m Yesuene waitogh \u225?r, emofem y\u233?nmumyoy\u233?nd y\u233?maf\u233? \u225?mnjogh\u233?t 7 efghot. A f\u233?yo y\u233?nd n\u233?ngwanoy\u233?m Rom. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
\u193?mb Yesuene waitogh \u225?r Romm\u233?n n\u225?y\u225?ray\u233?nd t\u233?fenem\u233?n a enmorm\u233?n t\u233?fe wanf\u233?gh\u233?t Afius t\u233?rar\u233?gh sifayat a m\u233?ngotu y\u233?tkw\u233?n Nambio wan t\u233?fn\u225?r m\u233?ngot. Njam Fol\u233?m ewinjoi f\u225?, y\u233?mon k\u225?njo yaramai Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne a freng\u233?gh yanai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
